Coronavirus: Ni ibihe bihugu vyoba bitarandura ?

Ku wa 12/01/2020, amezi adashika atatu aheze - coronavirus yabarizwa mu Bushinwa honyene. Nta kindi gihugu na kimwe yari bwatorwemwo.
Ariko ku wa 13/01/2020, uwo mugera waciye utangura kurenga imbibe z'ico gihugu maze iba intango y'akaga.
Uwa mbere yatanguye kuboneka hanze y'u Bushinwa, yabonetse muri Thailand, imbere y'uko haboneka abandi mu Buyapani na Koreya y'Epfo, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika nazo zivamwo zirakurikira.
Yagenda ikwirakwira buke buke kw'isi yose.
Ubu ingene ibintu bimeze, abarenga umuliyoni kw'isi yose baramaze kwandura Covid-19.
Hagati aho, n'aho ibitigiri vy'abahitanwa n'uwo mugera bigenda vyiyongera, ibitaro navyo bikagenda vyuruza abarwayi, ubwo hoba hariho ibihugu bitarandukirwa?
Vyogutangaza, ariko inyishu ni ego.
Ishirahamwe ONU rihurikiyemwo ibihugu 193.
Gushika ku wa 02 z'uku kwa kane, ibihugu 18 ntivyari bwandukirwe na coronavirus, nk'uko vyerekanwa n'ishure kaminuza Johns Hopkins.
Amazinga ya Komore; Kiribati; Lesotho; Amazinga ya Marshall; Micronesia; Nauru; Korea ya Ruguru; Palau; Samoa; Sao Tome  et Principe; Amazinga ya Solomon; Tajikistan; Tonga; Turkmenistan; Tuvalu; Vanuatu na Yemen.
Abahinga bemeza ko bishoboka ko hari ibihugu vyoba bifise abanduye ariko bataramenyekana.
Batanga akarorero nka Koreya ya Ruguru, co kimwe na Yemen, igihugu catabaguwe n'intambara.
Hagati aho, hariho ibihugu uwo mugera utarashikamwo.
Vyinshi muri vyo bikaba ari amazinga matomato cane atagenderwa cane n'ingenzi - ikizwi ni uko mu bihugu cumi vya mbere bigenderwa n'ingenzi nke kw'isi k'uko ibiharuro vya ONU bivyerekana, indwi muri vyo nta coronavirus irabishikamwo.
Rero kubona, kubona ivyo bihugu biri kure cane y'ibindi - bisigura ko vyo nyene ubwavyo biri kure y'aho bishobora kwandurira uwo mugera, na rirya hari ingingo y'uko abantu bokwigira kure na kure kugira ngo ntibanduzanye.
Hagati aho, umukuru w'umwe muri ivyo bihugu yabwiye BBC ko Covid-19 ari ikibazo nyamukuru gihanze igihugu ciwe.
Nauru, izinga riri mw'ibahari Pasifike, riri ku birometero 320 uvuye ku mukapa w'igihugu kiri hafi yaryo, ico naco kikaba ari izinga rya Banaba ryegukira amazinga ya Kiribati. Igisagara gikomeye kiri hafi y'iryo zinga ni Brisbane muri Autralia kiri ku birometero 4023.36.
Nico gihugu kigira kabiri gito cane kw'isi kiri mw'ishirahamwe ONU (inyuma ya Monaco), kikaba gifise abantu barenga gato 10.000, kikaba kigira kabiri mu bihugu bifise abantu bake cane kw'isi (inyuma ya Tuvalu).
Kiri kandi mu bihugu bigenderwa n'ingenzi nke cane kw'isi.
Ufise kuba wibaza ko ibihugu nk'ivyo biri kure cane y'ibindi bitoba bikeneye kwikingira gusumba.
Ariko nk'igihugu gifise  inyubakwa imwe gusa y'ibitaro, navyo nyene bidafise ibikoresho bikwiye, mbere kikaba gikenye n'abaganga, nticoreka gufata ingingo ruhasha kugira ngo zikingire zitaronerwa.
Izo ngingo, nk'uko zivugwa n'umukuru w'ico gihugu Lionel Aingimea, zitwa "zibira utaronerwa".
Ati: "Tuzibirira ku mupaka. Ikibuga c'indege nico gikoreshwa nk'umupaka".
Abashizwe ukwabo bama bapimwa umunsi ku munsi.
Iyo hagize uwubonekako ubushuhe, aca yigizwa kure gusumba kugira ngo apimwe ko adafise Covid-19.
Ibipimo vyose twafashe, twabirungitse muri Australia, bikaba vyagarutse vyerekana ko ata wanduye.
N'aho bazi ko bari mu ngorane, abanyagihugu basanzwe ba Nauru "baratekanye", nk'uko bivugwa n'umukuru w'ico gihugu. Kubw'iwe, arashima cane ingene ibindi bihugu bimufasha - cane cane Australia na Taiwan - ariko kandi akishimikiza n'ijambo ry'Imana.
Ati: "Igihe dufata izi ngingo twise zibira utaronerwa, naciye niyegereza Imana, nayo impa umurongo wa Bibiliya nagumije cane ku mutima, uwo nawo ukaba ari Zaburi 147, 13-14. Ico cantumye nkomeza urugendo n'aho duca - nk'uko Bibiliya ibivuga - mu nzira y'urupfu".
Hanyuma n'aho agerageza kwigiza ico kiza kure ya Nauru, arazi ko ibindi bice vy'isi  bidafise ayo mahirwe.
Ati: "Igihe cose turavye ikarata yerekana Covid-19, bisa n'uko isi yatewe n'akaranda k'agasama - ibice vyose vyaranduye".
Nauru sico gihugu conyene kiri mw'ibahari Pasifike cafashe ingingo zo kwikingira  kitaraterwa - Kiribati, Tonga, Vanuatu, n'ibindi, navyo nyene vyariteguye. Abahinga bavuga ko ingingo vyafashe zabifashije kuzibira bitaraterwa.
Hariho kandi n'ibindi bihugu bidakikijwe n'amazi vyari vyashoboye kuzibira coronavirus.
Akarorero ni nka Malawi, igihugu co muri Afrika, kitanafise umuhora ushika kw'ibahari, kikaba gifise imiliyoni 18 z'abantu, aho umuntu wa mbere yatangajwe ko yanduye yagiye gutangazwa ku wa kane igenekerezo rya 02 z'uku kwa kane. Ariko cari citeguriye ico kiza.
Ico gihugu caciye gitangaza ko kiri mu "bihe bidasanzwe", amashure arugarwa, maze kinahagarika za murekarengane (visas) zari zatanzwe imbere ya 20 z'ukwa gatatu.
Hamande y'izo ngingo, carongereje n'ibikorwa vyo gupima uwo mugera.
Nk'uko bivugwa na Dr Peter MacPherson, umuhinga mu vyo amagara y'abantu asanzwe akorera muri Malawi, indwi hafi zibiri bamaze bitegura zarafashije cane kandi arizeye ko Malawi izoshobora kurwanya uwo mugera.
Malawi nk'igihugu giherutse gutangaza ko camaze kwandukirwa, coba ari co ca nyuma?
Dr MacPherson avuga ko hari ibimenyetso vyerekana ko uwo mugera uziruhira gushika mu bihugu vyose.
Abahinga babona ko ingingo zo kuzibira, nk'izafashwe n'igihugu ca Nauru, zishobora gufasha cane, ariko y'uko bigoye ko zizoshobora kuzibira burundu ico kiza muri kino gihe ubuhinga bwatumye isi iba nto cane.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-51959727' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-51959727' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: WHO yaburiye Afurika 'kwitegura ibihe bibi cyane' biri imbere
Umukuru w'ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS/WHO) yaburiye ibihugu by'Afurika "kwitegura ibihe bibi cyane" biri imbere kubera icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Umukuru w'ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS/WHO) yaburiye ibihugu by'Afurika "kwitegura ibihe bibi cyane" biri imbere kubera icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Bose hamwe, abantu 16 ni bo bamaze kwicwa na coronavirus muri Afurika: batandatu mu Misiri, batandatu muri Algeria, babiri muri Maroc, umwe muri Sudan n'umwe muri Burkina Faso.
Afurika ni wo mugabane kugeza ubu utarashegeshwe na coronavirus, ariko impuguke mu by'ubuvuzi zaburiye ko inzego zayo z'ubuzima zisanzwe zifite imikorere icumbagira zishobora kurengerwa ubushobozi byihuse kubera iki cyorezo, cyane cyane mu mijyi ituwemo mu bucucike.
Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, umukuru wa OMS, yaburiye ko nubwo umubare w'abamaze kwemezwa muri Afurika ko banduye Covid-19 kuri ubu ukiri hasi - abarenga 640 - nta mpamvu yo kujenjeka.
Ati: "Afurika ikwiye gukanguka, umugabane wanjye [mvukaho] ukwiye gukanguka".
Bwana Tedros ukomoka muri Ethiopia akaba ari na we Munyafurika wa mbere uyoboye OMS, yanavuze ko Afurika ikwiye kwigira ku kuntu iyi virusi yagiye ikwirakwira ku yindi migabane yo ku isi.
Ati: "... Mu bindi bihugu, twabonye mu by'ukuri ukuntu iyi virusi ifata umuvuduko mwinshi nyuma y'igihe runaka iyo hari ikiyitije imbaraga".
Ejo ku wa gatatu, igihugu cya Burkina Faso cyatangaje umuntu wa mbere wo muri Afurika yo munsi y'ubutayu bwa Sahara wishwe na coronavirus.
Ni umugore w'imyaka 62 wari usanzwe anarwaye indwara y'igisukari (diabète).
Abategetsi bavuga ko uwo murwayi yishe ari Rose Marie Compaoré, wari visi-perezida w'inteko ishingamategeko muri icyo gihugu.
Muri Afurika y'Epfo, ejo ku wa gatatu abantu bayanduye bariyongereye bikomeye bagera ku 116, benshi muri bo bakaba ari abantu bari baragiye i Burayi.
Uwo mubare urimo abarwayi 14 bavuye ku kuyanduzanya ko hagati mu gihugu.
Muri aka karere, ubu mu Rwanda hari abantu 11 basanzemo iyi ndwara, Tanzania batandatu, Kenya barindwi, DR Congo 14 naho mu Burundi na Uganda iyi ndwara nta muntu barayisangamo.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-51885894' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-51885894' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Icyemezo cyo guca ingendo ziva i Burayi zijya muri Amerika cyatangiye gukurikizwa
Icyemezo cya Perezida Donald Trump wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika cyo kubuza kugera muri Amerika abantu bo mu bihugu 26 by'i Burayi, nk'ingamba yo guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus, cyatangiye gukurikizwa uyu munsi.
Icyemezo cya Perezida Donald Trump wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika cyo kubuza kugera muri Amerika abantu bo mu bihugu 26 by'i Burayi, nk'ingamba yo guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus, cyatangiye gukurikizwa uyu munsi.
Icyo cyemezo kireba ibihugu bihuriye mu karere k'umupaka ufunguye ka Schengen, ariko hatarimo Ubwongereza, Repulika ya Ireland n'abaturage b'Amerika basubira iwabo.
Ibyo bihugu ni Autriche (Austria), Ububiligi, Czech Republic, Denmark, Estonia, Finland, Ubufaransa, Ubudage, Ubugereki, Hongrie (Hungary), Iceland, Ubutaliyani, Latvia, Liechtenstein, Lithuania, Luxembourg, Malta, Ubuholandi, Norvège (Norway), Pologne (Poland), Portugal, Slovakia, Slovenia, Espanye, Suède (Sweden) n'Ubusuwisi.
Bwana Trump yanatangaje ko igihugu kiri mu bihe bidasanzwe ndetse atanga miliyari zigera kuri 50 z'amadolari y'Amerika zo kwifashishwa mu guhangana na coronavirus.
Muri Amerika ubu habarirwa abantu bagera hafi ku 2,000 bemejwe ko banduye Covid-19 - indwara y'ifata mu myanya y'ubuhumekero iterwa n'ubu bwoko bushya bwa coronavirus. 43 imaze kubica.
Ubutegetsi bwa Bwana Trump bumaze igihe bunengwa kunanirwa guha abaturage b'Amerika ibikoresho bihagije byo kuyipima.
Mu yandi makuru yo kuri uyu wa gatandatu:
Nanone kandi, ejo ku wa gatanu Amerika yahamagaje ambasaderi w'Ubushinwa muri Amerika mu kwamagana amagambo yavuzwe n'umutegetsi w'Ubushinwa wo mu rwego rw'ububanyi n'amahanga (diplomat) avuga ko Amerika ari yo yateje coronavirus mu Bushinwa.
Ubu bwoko bushya bwa coronavirus bwatangiriye mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa mu mpera y'umwaka ushize.
Ariko umubare w'abayandura buri munsi mu Bushinwa ukomeje kugenda ugabanuka, Uburayi bukaba ari ryo "zingiro" rishya ry'iki cyorezo.
Ejo ku wa gatanu, Ubutaliyani bwagize umubare munini wa mbere w'abo yishe - abantu 250 mu gihe cy'amasaha 24, bituma umubare w'abo imaze kwica muri icyo gihugu bagera ku 1,266 n'abandi 17,660 bamaze kuyandura.
Mu rwego rwo guhuza neza uburyo byo kurwanya coronavirus, abategetsi bo mu bihugu 7 bikize kurusha ibindi ku isi - bihuriye mu itsinda rizwi nka G7 - bazakora inama y'igitaraganya ku wa mbere, inama bazakora mu buryo bw'amashusho bategeranye imbona nkubone (videoconference).
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52314348' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52314348' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Djibouti niyo ifite abanduye Covid-19 benshi muri Afurika y’uburasirazuba
Ejo kuwa kane Djibouti yatangaje abantu bashya 156 banduye Covid-19 mu masaha yari 24 ashize, umubare w'abayanduye muri icyo gihugu bose hamwe bahita bagera kuri 591.
Ejo kuwa kane Djibouti yatangaje abantu bashya 156 banduye Covid-19 mu masaha yari 24 ashize, umubare w'abayanduye muri icyo gihugu bose hamwe bahita bagera kuri 591.
Ni ko kwiyongera k'umubare w'abanduye kwa mbere kunini kubayeho mu munsi umwe gusa, kuva umurwayi wa mbere yagaragara muri icyo gihugu mu kwezi gushize.
Iki gihugu ni cyo gifite abaturage bacye cyane muri aka karere k'Afurika y'uburasirazuba - barenga gato 900,000.
Mohammed Warsame, Minisitiri w'ubuzima muri Djibouti, yavuze ko abarwayi babiri bamaze kwicwa n'iyo ndwara naho abandi 73 bakaba bamaze kuyikira.
Yemeje ko benshi mu banduye ari abanduriye imbere mu gihugu.
Djibouti ni igihugu gito kiri mu ihembe rya Africa mu marembo y'inyanja itukura inzira y'amato yose hagati ya Aziya n'Uburayi.
Ni igihugu gishingira ubukungu bwacyo ku byambu n'ubucuruzi.
Ikigo kitwa Stockholm International Peace Research Institute kivuga ko Djibouti ari igihugu gifite ibirindiro byinshi by'ingabo z'ibihugu by'amahanga.
Ibyo bihugu ni; Ubushinwa, Ubufaransa, Ubuhinde, Ubutaliyani, Ubuyapani, Espagne, Emira zunze ubumwe z'Abarabu, Leta zunze ubumwe za Amerika.
Perezida Ismail Omar Guelleh wa Djibouti ejo ku wa gatatu yatangaje ko igihe cy'inyongera y'iminsi 7 ku bihe bidasanzwe cyongerewe kigashyirwa ku minsi 10.
Yavuze ko ibihe bidasanzwe by'akato byatangiye mu byumweru bibiri bishize "nta gushidikanya ko byafashije umuryango mugari [sosiyete] kwirinda ubwandu bwinshi".
Kugeza ubu iki gihugu kimaze gupima abantu barenga 5,000.
Aba mbere mu banduye Covid-19 muri icyo gihugu bari abaganga bari basubiye mu gihugu bavuye hanze, nkuko minisitiri w'ubuzima yabitangaje.
Iki gihugu gifite 'laboratoire' yacyo bwite, buri munsi ipima abacyekwaho kuba barwaye Covid-19.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52290921' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52290921' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Abayanduye ku isi bageze kuri miliyoni 2, miliyoni 1 mu minsi 13
Umubare w'abantu basanzemo coronacirus ku isi uri kwiyongera vuba, mu minsi 13 ishize bavuye ku bantu miliyoni imwe uyu munsi bageze kuri miliyoni ebyiri nk'uko biri mu mibare itangwa na kaminuza y'ubushakashatsi ya Johns Hopkins.
Umubare w'abantu basanzemo coronacirus ku isi uri kwiyongera vuba, mu minsi 13 ishize bavuye ku bantu miliyoni imwe uyu munsi bageze kuri miliyoni ebyiri nk'uko biri mu mibare itangwa na kaminuza y'ubushakashatsi ya Johns Hopkins.
Muri abo bose banduye, iki cyorezo kimaze guhitana abantu barenga 126,000 naho abarenga 484,000 bamaze kugikira.
Leta zunze ubumwe za Amerika nizo zikomeje kuzahara kurusha ibindi bihugu ku isi.
Zifite abantu 614,246 bamaze kumenyekana ko banduye - ni hafi kimwe cya gatatu cy'abanduye bose ku isi -  naho 26,064 bishwe n'iyi ndwara.
Ubushinwa, aho iyi ndwara yabonywe mbere mu mpera z'ukwezi kwa 12 umwaka ushize, ubu ni igihugu cya karindwi mu byazahajwe n'iki cyorezo.
Ibihugu by'Iburayi nka Espagne, Ubutaliyani, Ubufaransa, Ubudage n'Ubwongereza byose byamaze guca ku Bushinwa mu banduye n'abishwe n'iki cyorezo.
Uko iki cyorezo gihagaze mu banduye muri aka karere kugeza mu ijoro ry'ejo kuwa kabiri;
Mu minsi 10 ishize abari baranduye iki cyorezo muri Afurika bari 8,018 abo yari imaze kwica bari 339, imibare yombi yikubye kabiri muri rusange ugereranyije n'ubu.
Kugeza mu ijoro ry'ejo kuwa kabiri, abantu 15,738 nibo bari bamaze kumenyekana ko banduye iyi virus, muri bo 838 yarabishe naho 2,920 barayikize.
Iyi imibare itangazwa n'urwego rushinzwe kurwanya ibiza rw'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bwa Afurika.
Imibare y'abakira iyi ndwara igenda yiyongera cyane ku isi no muri Afurika.
Mu minsi 13 ishize abayikize ku isi bari 210,000  ubu bamaze kugera ku 484,000 nk'uko bivugwa na kaminuza ya Johns Hopkins.
Iyi mibare yikubye kabiri no muri Afurika kuko mu minsi 10 ishize bari 652 ubu bakaba bageze kuri 2,920 bayikize nk'uko bivugwa na ruriya rwego rw'Ubumwe bwa Africa.
Leta y'u Rwanda yafashe ingamba zo guhagarika ubuzima busanzwe mu gihugu mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bine mu kwirinda ikwirakwira rya coronavirus.
Mu minsi 11 ishize, abanduye bavuye ku 102 ubu bageze ku 134,  icyo gihe nta muntu wari wakize iyi ndwara ubu bamaze kuba 49 nk'uko bivugwa na minisiteri y'ubuzima.
Mu mibare itangwa n'iyi minisiteri, mu minsi 11 mu bantu 32 bamenyekanye ko banduye 28 muri bo ni abanduriye imbere mu gihugu.
Bakizwa n'iki ko Covid-19nta muti ifite?
Inzobere mu buvuzi zivuga ko ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri ari ingenzi cyane mu guhashya iyi virus.
Zivuga kandi ko iyi virus yica cyane abari basanganywe izindi ndwara n'intege nke z'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri zigaragara ku bari mu zabukuru.
Iyi virus yibasira cyane ibihaha nta muti cyangwa urukingo irabonerwa.
Ibihugu bimwe na bimwe byamaze kwemeza ko bikoresha imiti yo mu bwoko bwa Chroloquine, hydroxychloroquine na Azithromycin mu gufasha abarwaye coronavirus.
Kugeza ubu ariko iyi miti ntabwo iremezwa na OMS/WHO nk'imiti ivura iki cyorezo.
BBC ifite amakuru yemeza ko na bimwe mu bihugu byo muri aka karere bikoresha iyi miti mu kuvura abafite iyi virus, ndetse hamwe na hamwe yagiye iba micye ku isoko.
Ikigo gishinzwe kugenzura ibiribwa n'imiti mu Rwanda giheruka kwibutsa abaturage ko iriya miti itavura coronavirus, ko kuyikoresha mu buryo itagenewe bibujijwe.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52185364' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52185364' term='COVID'>
Covid-19: Ubutaliyani na Espagne, imibare y'abapfa n'abandura iri kumanuka, muri Afurika bite?
Espagne niyo ifite imibare minini y'abanduye iyi virus mu Burayi,  ariko amakuru atangwa ubu arerekana ko imibare ubu noneho iri kumanuka.
Espagne niyo ifite imibare minini y'abanduye iyi virus mu Burayi,  ariko amakuru atangwa ubu arerekana ko imibare ubu noneho iri kumanuka.
Imibare itangwa na leta muri Espagne yerekana ko abapfuye ku munsi mu minsi ine ishize bamanutse bakagera kuri 637.
Uyu niwo mubare muto w'abapfuye ku munsi uri hasi mu byumweru hafi bibiri bishize. Kuwa kane ushize nibwo hapfuye abantu benshi ku munsi, 950.
Imibare y'abanduye nayo iri kumanuka bigaragara muri Espagne - abahanga bavuga ko ingamba zo guhagarika ubuzima busanzwe (lockdown) zishobora kuba ziri gutanga umusaruro.
Haracyari urugendo rurerure, ndetse leta ya Espagne ivuga ko abantu bashobora kuzakomeza gutegekwa kwambara udupfukamunwa mu bantu benshi no mu gihe izi ngamba zizaba zarakuweho.
Imibare mu Butaliyani, yerekana ko naho biri kumanuka.
Hano niho Covid-19 imaze kwica abantu benshi ku isi, 15,887. Ariko naho, abandura n'abapfa bari kugabanuka.
Mu Butaliyani, ejo ku cyumweru hapfuye abantu 525, umubare muto kurusha iyindi mu byumweru bibiri bishize.
Gusa, minisitiri w'intebe w'Ubutaliyani Giuseppe Conte yavuze ko atazi neza igihe ibihe bidasanzwe (lockdwon) mu gihugu bizarangirira.
</doc>
