Coronavirus: Abakinnyi ba Juventus n'umutoza Maurizio Sarri bemeye kumara amezi badahembwa
Abakinnyi b'ikipe ya Juventus n'umutoza wabo Maurizio Sarri bemeye ko imishahara yabo ihagarikwa mu gihe cy'amezi ane mu kurinda ikipe yabo igihombo cya miliyoni zigera kuri 90 z'ama-euro kubera iki cyorezo cya coronavirus.
Abakinnyi b'ikipe ya Juventus n'umutoza wabo Maurizio Sarri bemeye ko imishahara yabo ihagarikwa mu gihe cy'amezi ane mu kurinda ikipe yabo igihombo cya miliyoni zigera kuri 90 z'ama-euro kubera iki cyorezo cya coronavirus.
Imikino yose mu gihugu cy'Ubutaliyani yarahagaritswe kugeza nibura ku itariki ya gatatu y'ukwezi gutaha kwa kane.
Ni cyo cyibasiwe cyane na coronavirus i Burayi, aho abarwayi barenga 92,000 barwaye indwara y'ubuhumekero ya Covid-19 iterwa n'iyo virusi.
Abarenga 10,000 imaze kubica muri icyo gihugu naho abarenga 12,000 barayikize, nkuko imibare ya Kaminuza ya Johns Hopkins yo muri Amerika ibigaragaza.
Abo bakinnyi ba Juventus bemeye kwigomwa umushahara barimo nka rutahizamu Cristiano Ronaldo ukomoka muri Portugal n'umukinnyi wo hagati wo muri Wales, Aaron Ramsey.
Ntabwo bazahembwa umushahara wabo w'uku kwezi kwa gatatu, ukwa kane, ukwa gatanu n'ukwa gatandatu.
Iyi kipe ni yo iyoboye urutonde rwa shampiyona ya Serie A, ikaba irusha inota rimwe ikipe ya Lazio.
Mu gihe umupira w'amaguru waba wongeye gusubukurwa muri iki gihugu, ubuyobozi bwa Juventus buvuga ko buzongera kubisuzuma "bushyize mu gaciro".
Mu itangazo ubuyobozi bw'iyi kipe yegukanye igikombe cya shampiyona y'Ubutaliyani mu myaka umunani ishize bwasohoye, bwagize buti:
"Juventus yifuzaga gushimira abakinnyi n'umutoza ku bwitange bwabo muri iki gihe gikomereye buri wese".
Abakinnyi bo mu yandi makipe amwe akomeye y'i Burayi, barimo aba Bayern Munich na Borussia Dortmund yo mu Budage, na bo bemeye kugabanyirizwa umushahara.
</doc>
