Umuganga wo muri Nigeria yishwe na Covid-19 nyuma yo kuyandura mu gihe yariho yita ku muntu uyifite wari wagannye ivuriro rye ryigenga.
Uyu muganga yajyanywe mu bitaro bya Kaminuza i Lagos kuwa mbere apfa kuwa gatatu nk'uko uyobora ibi bitaro Chris Bode abitangaza.
Bwana Bode avuga ko uyu muganga yagejejwe ku bitaro arembejwe n'ibimeneyetso by'iki cyorezo.
Ishyirahamwe ry'abaganga muri Nigeria rivuga ko uyu wapfuye, Dr Chugbo Emeka, yanduye ubwo yariho yita ku murwayi wishwe n'iki cyorezo kuwa gatanu ushize.
Iri shyirahamwe rivuga ko amakuru rikesha ikinyamakuru Vanguard, ari uko uyu muganga w'imyaka 51 yari asanzwe arwara indwara ya Asthma.
Iri shyirahamwe rirasaba leta zigize Nigeria gufasha abaganga kubona imyambaro ibarinda kwandura mu gihe bita ku barwayi banyuranye muri iki cyorezo.
Risaba kandi abarwayi kubwira ukuri abaganga ku buzima bwabo, ingendo bakoze n'abantu babonanye kugira ngo bamenye uko bitwara.
Amatsinda y'abaganga b'Abashinwa yahagurutse iwabo aza muri Ethiopia na Burkina Faso gufasha ibi bihugu guhangana na coronavirus nk'uko bivugwa n'ikinyamakuru cya leta China Global Television Network.
Umubare wabo ntabwo uzwi neza, gusa bahagurutse uyu munsi kuwa kane baza muri Afurika nk'uko minisiteri y'ububanyi n'amahanga yaho ibivuga.
Biteganyijwe ko bazatanga ubunararibonye, ubuyobozi n'inama mu guhangana no kwirinda iki cyorezo muri ibi bihugu bibiri.
Nigeria nayo irateganya kuzana abaganga 18 bavuye mu Bushinwa bakaza kuyifasha kurwana n'iki cyorezo, gusa bamwe mu baganga bo mu gihugu bagaragaje ko batabyishimiye.
Ishyirahamwe ryabo rivuga ko hakwiye gukoreshwa abaganga benshi badafite akazi bari mu gihugu.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_52046117' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/52046117' term='COVID'>
Amakuru kuri Coronavirus: Umukecuru w’imyaka 97 yayikize, Afurika ibihugu 8 ntirahagera
Kaminuza y'ubushakshatsi mu buvuzi yo muri Amerika, Johns Hopkins University, yatangaje ko umubare w'abantu bishwe na Covid-19 muri iki gihugu warenze 1,000 ubu ukaba ugeze ku 1,050.
Kaminuza y'ubushakshatsi mu buvuzi yo muri Amerika, Johns Hopkins University, yatangaje ko umubare w'abantu bishwe na Covid-19 muri iki gihugu warenze 1,000 ubu ukaba ugeze ku 1,050.
Abamaze kwandura iyi ndwara muri leta zunze ubumwe za Amerika bamaze kurenga 69,000.
=====
Iyi ni inkuru nziza muri iki gihe abantu batewe ubwoba n'ikwirakwira ryihuse ry'iyi virus.
Umukecuru wo muri Koreya y'Epfo ufite imyaka 97 yabaye undi muntu ukuze cyane ku isi wakize iyi virus nk'uko bitangazwa n'ibiro ntaramakuur Yonhap.
Nta makuru arambuye yatangajwe kuri we, gusa nubwo ari we mukuru cyane hari n'abandi bashaje umubiri wabo wabashije kunesha iyi virus.
Mu ntangiriro z'ukwezi kwa gatatu, ibiro ntaramakuru bya leta y'Ubushinwa byatangaje ko hari umusaza w'imyaka 100 wakize iyi ndwara. Xinua yavuze ko ariwe muntu ushaje cyane ku isi wayikize.
====
Muri Afurika ibihugu umunani nibyo bitaragerwaho n'iyi virus.
Kugeza ubu abantu barenga 2,700 bo mu bihugu 46 bya Afurika bamaze kuyandura, muri bo 211 barayikize naho 73 imaze kubica.
Kuri uyu mugabane hari ibihugu umunani(8) iyi ndwara itarageramo.
Ibyo ni;
Ku isi yose, abamaze kwandura iyi virus bamaze kurenga 470,000. Abamaze kuyikira barenga 114,000 naho abo yishe barenze 21,000.
====
Ibihugu bizahajwe cyane n'iyi ndwara ku isi ubu ni;
Ubushinwa (abanduye 81,667, abapfuye 3,285, abakize 73,775)
Ubutaliyani (abanduye 74,386 abapfuye 7,503, abakize 9,362)
Leta zunze ubumwe za Amerika (abanduye 66,132, abapfuye 1,031, abakize 616)
Espanye (abanduye 49,515, abapfuye 3,647, abakize 5,367)
Ubudage (abanduye 37,323, abapfuye 206, abakize 3,547)
Irani (abanduye 27,017, abapfuye 2,077, abakize 9,625)
Ubufaransa (abanduye 25,600, abapfuye 1,333, abakize 3,907)
