<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-51960775' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-51960775' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Trump avuga ko ubu Amerika iri mu ntambara n'iki cyorezo
Yiyita "perezida wo mu ntambara", Perezida Donald Trump yasezeranyije ko Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika zizagera ku "ntsinzi yuzuye" mu ntambara zirimo kurwana na coronavirus.
Yiyita "perezida wo mu ntambara", Perezida Donald Trump yasezeranyije ko Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika zizagera ku "ntsinzi yuzuye" mu ntambara zirimo kurwana na coronavirus.
Yabivuze ubwo yasubizagaho ingamba yo mu gihe cy'intambara yo muri Koreya yemerera Amerika kongera ikorwa ry'ibikoresho by'ingenzi mu buvuzi.
Hagati aho, abadepite babiri ejo ku wa gatatu babaye aba mbere mu bagize inteko ishingamategeko y'Amerika banduye coronavirus.
Abo ni Ben McAdams, umudemokarate uhagarariye leta ya Utah, na Mario Diaz-Balart, umurepubulikani uhagarariye leta ya Florida.
Muri Amerika abantu barenga 9,300 bamaze kwandura Covid-19 - indwara yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero iterwa n'iyo virusi -  naho abagera 150 imaze kubica.
Ku isi, abantu barenga 220,000 bemejwe ko bayanduye kugeza ubu. Abarenga  8,800 imaze kubica.
Mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru mu biro bye bya White House, Perezida Trump yabajijwe n'umunyamakuru niba abifata nkaho iki gihugu kiri mu gihe nk'icy'intambara mu rwego rwo kurwanya iyo virusi.
Yasubije ati: "Ni intambara. Mbifata, urebye, nkaho ndi perezida wo mu ntambara".
Muri iki cyumweru, Bwana Trump yakoresheje ibiganiro bya buri munsi kuri ibi bihe bidasanzwe igihugu kirimo, nyuma yaho ashinjwe kuba yarirengagije coronavirus mu bihe bya mbere byayo muri Amerika.
Yagize ati: "Tugomba kwigomwa twese hamwe, kubera ko iki kibazo twese turagifatanyije, kandi tuzakirangiriza hamwe. Ni umwanzi utaboneshwa amaso. Uwo iteka ahora ari we mwanzi ukomeye cyane [kurwanya]".
"Ariko tugiye gutsinda uyu mwanzi utaboneshwa amaso. Ntekereza ko tugiye no kumutsinda byihuse kurusha uko twabitekerezaga, kandi izaba ari intsinzi yuzuye..."
Bwana Trump yatangaje ko agiye gushyira umukono ku itegeko-teka rizwi nka '1950 Defense Production Act', riha ububasha perezida gutegeka ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi by'abasivile gufasha mu gukora ibicyenewe ku bw'inyungu z'umutekano w'igihugu.
Ariko nyuma yatangaje ku rubuga rwa Twitter ko yafata iyo ngamba gusa "ibintu bigeze irudubi mu gihe kiri imbere".
Bwana Trump yanavuze ku magambo ya Steve Mnuchin, umukuru w'ibiro by'imari by'Amerika, yuko iki cyorezo gishobora gutuma ubushomeri bwiyongera bikomeye bukagera ku 20%.
Avuga kuri ayo magambo ya Bwana Mnuchin, Perezida Trump yavuze ko ibyo byaba ari uko "ibintu byageze irudubi burundu burundu".
Perezida Trump kandi yavuze ko ibitaro  byo mu bwato bubiri bw'abasirikare barwanira mu mazi bizakoreshwa mu gufasha kugabanya umuzigo witezwe kubaho kubera ukudahaza kw'ibitanda by'abarwayi.
Byitezwe ko ubwato buzwi nka 'USNS Comfort' bwoherezwa ku mwaro wa New York Harbor, nubwo abategetsi bo mu rwego rwa gisirikare bavuze ko kuri ubu buri gukorerwa isuzuma ry'imikorere muri leta ya Virginia.
Ubundi bwato, buzwi nka 'USNS Mercy', buri gutegurirwa koherezwa mu burengerazuba bw'Amerika.
Muri icyo kiganiro n'abanyamakuru cyo ku munsi w'ejo ku wa gatatu, Bwana Trump yongeye guhakana ibivugwa ko ugukoresha kwe kw'ijambo "virusi y'Ubushinwa" ashaka kuvuga Covid-19, kurimo ivangurabwoko.
Mbere yaho kuri uwo munsi, umupaka ugabanya Amerika na Canada, wa mbere mu burebure ku isi, urebye warafunzwe, usibye gusa ku ngendo z'ingenzi no ku bucuruzi.
Bwana Trump yanatangaje ingamba nshya yo guhashya abimukira n'abashaka ubuhungiro bambuka umupaka w'Amerika na Mexico.
Yavuze ko ubutegetsi bwe buzifashisha itegeko rituma abantu bakumirwa mu kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'indwara zandura.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52439108' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52439108' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus - Rwanda: Abatavuga rumwe na leta barayisaba koroshya amategeko ya Guma mu rugo
Amashyaka abiri atavuga rumwe n'ubutegetsi bw'u Rwanda arasaba leta koroshya amategeko yo kuguma mu rugo kuko ari "gushyira bucece mu kaga ubuzima" kurusha coronavirus.
Amashyaka abiri atavuga rumwe n'ubutegetsi bw'u Rwanda arasaba leta koroshya amategeko yo kuguma mu rugo kuko ari "gushyira bucece mu kaga ubuzima" kurusha coronavirus.
Itangazo rigenewe abanyamakuru ry'ishyaka DALFA Umurinzi riyoborwa na Mme Victoire Ingabire na PS-Imberakuri riyobowe na Bernard Ntaganda risaba leta y'u Rwanda ko hafatwa izindi ngamba zatuma ubuzima bw'igihugu bukomeza.
Mu byo aya mashyaka - yombi ataremerwa n'ubutegetsi bw'u Rwanda - asaba harimo;
Kugira ngo ibyo bikorwe, aya mashyaka asaba leta y'u Rwanda gukoresha neza amafaranga ava "mu mfashanyo z'amahanga n'ibigega by'imari FMI, Banki y'Isi, n'ibigega binyuranye nk'Agaciro Fund".
Bernard Ntaganda uyobora ishyaka PS-Imberakuri yabwiye BBC ko ingamba zafashwe zazahaje ubuzima ku Banyarwanda avuga ko hafi 90% batunzwe no gusohoka bagashaka ikibatunga uwo munsi.
Ati: "Abantu bari kuvuga Covid-19 kandi nibyo rwose iriho kandi irica, ariko ikibabaje kinakomeye ni icyorezo kitavugwa icyo ni inzara, kandi nayo irica.
"Impamvu yo itavugwa ni uko ari indwara y'abakene, kandi hano ubu abakene bakaba badafite kivugira".
Bwana Ntaganda avuga ko icyo cyorezo cy'inzara kitavugwa kuko leta iri gufunga abanyamakuru bigenga bagerageza kwerekana ingaruka z'ingamba zafashwe bigateza bamwe inzara.
Ati: "Niyo mpamvu tuvuga ko izo ngamba ziri gushyira mu kaga ubuzima bw'abantu bucece, ni uko abagombaga kubivuga bamwe bafunzwe, mu gihe mu bihe bikomeye nk'ibi ubundi aribwo itangazamakuru rihaguruka rikavuga uko ibintu bimeze".
Bwana Ntaganda avuga ko nk'abatavuga rumwe n'ubutegetsi bari mu gihugu, babona ko "niba leta idashoboye gutunga Abanyarwanda yabareka bakajya gushaka uko babaho".
Ati: "Uretse n'u Rwanda n'ibihugu by'Iburayi byatangiye kubona ko gufungira abaturage mu mazu batazabishobora.
"Turasaba leta kureka gukora ngo ishimishe amahanga, nikore ibifitiye akamaro abaturage bijyanye n'imiterere y'igihugu".
Leta y'u Rwanda yafashe ingamba - zigiye kumara ibyumweru bitandatu - zo guhagarika ubuzima busanzwe, hagakorwa ibyangombwa cyane gusa, mu kurwanya ikwirakwira rya coronavirus.
Leta kandi yatangije ibikorwa byo guha ibiribwa abagizweho ingaruka kurusha abandi, n'izindi ngamba mu by'ubukungu bigamije guhangana n'ingaruka za coronavirus.
Minisiteri y'ubuzima mu Rwanda ivuga ko hamaze kuboneka abantu 191 banduye coronavirus na 92 bayikize.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52290310' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52290310' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Donald Trump yategetse ko inkunga US iha OMS ihagarara
Perezida Donald Trump wa Leta zunze ubumwe za Amerika yavuze ko yategetse ubutegetsi bwe guhagarika inkunga bugenera ishami rya ONU rishinzwe ubuzima ku isi OMS/WHO.
Perezida Donald Trump wa Leta zunze ubumwe za Amerika yavuze ko yategetse ubutegetsi bwe guhagarika inkunga bugenera ishami rya ONU rishinzwe ubuzima ku isi OMS/WHO.
Yavuze ko OMS "yananiwe inshingano zayo z'ibanze" mu guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Ashinja uru rwego rwa ONU guhishira ikwirakwira ry'iyi virus nyuma y'uko ibonetse bwa mbere mu Bushinwa, akavuga ko ibyo ikwiye kubibazwa.
Bwana Trump mu cyumweru gishize yashinje OMS kubogamira ku Ubushinwa.
Icyemezo cya Trump biteganyijwe ko kibanza guca mu nteko ya Amerika mbere y'uko kijya mu bikorwa.
Muri Amerika, Trump yanenzwe imikorere y'ubutegetsi bwe mu guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Trump yabwiye abanyamakuru ati: "Ndi gutegeka abo dukorana ko bahagarika amafaranga mu gihe turi kwiga ku ruhare rwa OMS mu kunanirwa bikabije no guhishira ikwirakwira rya coronavirus".
Yongeraho ati: "OMS yananiwe inshingano zayo z'ibanze kandi igomba kubibazwa".
Mu gusubiza ku byari bimaze kuvugwa na Trump, Umunyamabanga mukuru w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye António Guterres yavuze ko "ubu atari cyo gihe" cyo guhagarikira inkunga OMS.
Leta ya Amerika niyo muterankunga mukuru wa OMS, umwaka ushize yayihaye miliyoni $400, ari munsi gato ya 15% by'ingengo y'imari yose ikoresha.
Mu mwaka w'imari wa 2018-2019, Ubushinwa bwahaye OMS inkunga ya miliyoni $76 nk'umusanzu wayo na miliyoni $10 nk'inkunga y'ubushake nk'uko biri mu makuru atangwa na OMS.
Mu kwezi kwa gatatu OMS yatangaje ko ikeneye miliyoni $675 yo kurwanya iki cyorezo, ndetse birateganywa ko ishobora gusaba andi miliyari imwe y'amadorari.
Bwana Trump yagize ati: "Mu gihe cy'iki cyorezo, twibajije cyane niba ubuntu bwa Amerika bwarakoreshejwe neza uko bishoboka".
Leta zunze ubumwe za Amerika, ubu nicyo gihugu kibasiwe na Covid-19 kurusha ibindi ku isi aho abantu 608,377 bayanduye naho abagera ku 25,981 ikaba imaze kubahitana.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52293369' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52293369' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Umutungo w’umuherwe Jeff Bezos wiyongereyeho miliyari $24
Umutungo w'uwashinze akaba n'umuyobozi w'urubuga rw'ubucuruzi bwo kuri internet rwa Amazon wiyongereyeho miliyari 24 z'amadolari y'Amerika muri iki gihe cya coronavirus.
Umutungo w'uwashinze akaba n'umuyobozi w'urubuga rw'ubucuruzi bwo kuri internet rwa Amazon wiyongereyeho miliyari 24 z'amadolari y'Amerika muri iki gihe cya coronavirus.
Ibyo byatewe nuko kubera ibihe bidasanzwe by'akato abantu bari kurukoresha cyane mu bikorwa byo guhaha.
Ubu, Jeff Bezos w'imyaka 56, afite umutungo ubarirwa muri miliyari 138 z'amadolari y'Amerika, nkuko bitangazwa na Bloomberg Billionaires Index.
Byatumye ashimangira umwanya we nk'umuntu wa mbere ukize cyane ku isi.
Kompanyi ye yungukiye cyane ku kuba abantu ku isi bari kuguma mu ngo zabo bagatumiza ibyo bacyeneye kuri internet, muri iki gihe cy'icyorezo cya Covid-19.
Byabaye ngombwa ko iha akazi abakozi babarirwa mu bihumbi kugira ngo ibashe guhaza abakiliya bayo biyongereye cyane muri iki gihe.
Ariko Amazon yananenzwe n'abakozi bayo muri Amerika ku bijyanye n'ingamba zo kubarinda ku kazi muri iki gihe cya coronavirus.
Bwana Bezos afite imigabane ingana na 11% muri Amazon, kandi ejo ku wa kabiri, imigabane yayo yiyongereyeho 5.3%.
Umuryango nyir'ikigo cy'ubucuruzi cya Wal-Mart, gifite iduka rya Asda mu Bwongereza, na wo warungutse muri iki gihe cy'ibihe bidasanzwe by'akato.
Umutungo w'uwo muryango - uzwi nka The Waltons - wiyongereyeho 5% muri uyu mwaka ugera kuri miliyari 169 z'amadolari y'Amerika.
Ubu ni wo muryango wa mbere w'abaherwe ku isi, nkuko bitangazwa na Bloomberg.
Mu gihe abantu babarirwa muri za miliyoni ubu bari gukorera mu ngo mu bice bitandukanye byo ku isi, umutungo w'uwashinze urubuga rw'inama zo kuri internet na wo wariyongereye.
Umutungo wa Eric Yuan washinze urubuga Zoom wikubye inshuro zirenga ebyiri, ugera kuri miliyari 7.4 z'amadolari y'Amerika.
Bloomberg Billionaires Index itangaza ko kugeza ubu muri uyu mwaka, abaherwe 500 ba mbere ku isi bamaze guhomba agera kuri miliyari 553 z'amadolari y'Amerika
Abashoramari mu rwego rw'ibikomoka kuri peteroli ndetse no muri 'gas' barahombye cyane kubera ko ibiciro byaguye kubera igabanuka ry'ababicyeneye ku isi.
Byanatewe kandi n'amakimbirane - ubu yamaze gucyemuka - hagati ya Arabie Saoudite n'Uburusiya ashingiye ku musaruro w'ibikomoka kuri peteroli.
Bwana Bezos yatangiye Amazon mu 1995 ku gishoro kigera hafi ku 100,000 by'amadolari y'Amerika akuye mu mutungo we bwite no mu mafaranga y'umuryango we.
Nyuma yo kubona imibare yagaragazaga kwiyongera kwihuse kw'ikoreshwa rya internet, yahise ava mu kazi keza ko mu kigo cy'ishoramari ubwo yari afite imyaka 30 y'amavuko.
Umugore we MacKenzie na we yahise amukurikira muri Amazon, bombi bakaba bari baramenyaniye muri icyo kigo cy'ishoramari cya DE Shaw bakoragamo i New York.
Babyaranye abana bane
Batandukanye mu mwaka ushize wa 2019 binyuze muri gatanya (divorce) - yagarutsweho cyane n'ibitangazamakuru bikora inkuru zijyanye n'ubucuruzi.
Muri uko gutandukana kwabo, MacKenzie yahawe miliyari 38 z'amadolari y'Amerika arimo no kugira umugabane wa 4% muri Amazon.
Mu kwezi kumwe amaze gutangiza Amazon, yari yamaze kubona 'commandes' zo kugemura ibicuruzwa muri leta 50 zose zigize Amerika ndetse no mu bihugu 45 ku isi.
Ayo makuru akubiye mu gitabo 'The Everything Store: Jeff Bezos and the Age of Amazon' kivuga ku buzima bwe bwite, cyanditswe na Brad Stone, cyasohotse mu mwaka wa 2013.
Mu myaka itanu ya mbere Amazon ibayeho, konti z'abakiliya bayo zavuye ku madolari 180,000 zigera kuri miliyoni 17 z'amadolari.
Muri iyo myaka kandi, ubucuruzi bwariyongereye cyane buva ku 511,000 by'amadolari burenga miliyari 1.6 y'amadolari.
Abashoramari b'ibyamamare bahise babyiganira mu gushora imari muri Amazon ubwo internet yari imaze gushinga imizi mu bice byinshi by'isi.
Yatangiye gukora ku mugaragaro mu mwaka wa 1997, ihita ikusanya miliyoni 54 z'amadolari.
Ndetse ihindura Bwana Bezos, wahoze afasha mu gufunga neza ibitabo byaguzwe, umwe mu bagabo b'abaherwe ku isi ataranagira imyaka 35 y'amavuko.
Mu mwaka wa 1999, ikinyamakuru Time Magazine cyagize Bwana Bezos umwe mu rubyiruko rwaranze uwo mwaka ku isi.
Ikinyamakuru Time Magazine cyamuhaye akabyiniriro k'"umwami w'ubucuruzi bwo kuri internet".
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52352119' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52352119' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Biyemeje kubona ‘dose’ miliyoni z’urukingo rwayo mu kwa cyenda
Abahanga muri siyansi bo muri kaminuza ya Oxford mu Bwongereza batangaje ko bagomba kuzaba barabonye nibura 'dose' (ingano runaka) miliyoni y'urukingo rwa coronavirus mu kwezi kwa cyenda uyu mwaka.
Abahanga muri siyansi bo muri kaminuza ya Oxford mu Bwongereza batangaje ko bagomba kuzaba barabonye nibura 'dose' (ingano runaka) miliyoni y'urukingo rwa coronavirus mu kwezi kwa cyenda uyu mwaka.
Leta y'Ubwongereza, ari nayo iri gutera inkunga uyu mushinga, ivuga ko idashobora gushyiraho itariki yo kuba uru rukingo rwabonetse.
Mu cyumweru gitaha biteganyijwe ko abarwayi ba mbere b'iki cyorezo bakorerwaho igeragezwa ry'uru rukingo n'abo bashakashatsi.
Gusa, haracyari kare kwemeza niba uru rukingo ruzaba rukora neza kandi nta bibazo ruteje ubuzima.
Inzobere nyinshi zivuga ko byafata amezi hagati ya 12 na 18 kugera ku rukingo no gukora ingano yarwo nyinshi.
Inkingo zitoza ubwirinzi bw'umubiri w'umuntu kurwana n'indwara, nka Covid-19.
Mu gihe abantu benshi baba badashobora kurwara coronavirus, ntabwo yashobora gukwirakwira nk'uko bimeze ubu, n'abantu ntibakongera kubuzwa kwegerana.
Amatsinda y'abahanga agera nibura kuri 80 ku isi, harimo na kompanyi nini z'imiti, ari gushakisha uko yagera kuri uru rukingo ndetse amwe yatangiye kurugerageza ku bantu.
Ubu bushakashatsi buri gukorwa ku muvuduko udasanzwe - imirimo ubundi ikorwa mu myaka barareba uko yafata amezi.
Itsinda ryo kuri iyi kaminuza rimaze igihe ryitegura icyorezo n'ubundi kimeze nka Covid-19 na mbere y'uko kibaho.
Bari baramaze gukora virus ifata inyamaswa za chimpanzee yaherwaho hakorwa urukingo rushya. Ubu virus bayihuje na coronavirus nshya (Covid-19).
Ibyavuyemo, ku bw'amahirwe, ni virusi ishobora gutoza ubwirinzi bw'umubiri kurwana na Covid-19.
Ikibazo gikomeye ubu ni; ese uru rukiko rugiye mu igeragezwa ruzakora neza?
Prof Sarah Gilbert, uyoboye itsinda ry'ubu bushakashatsi avuga ko ku gipimo cya 80% yizeye ko ruzakora neza.
Ati: "Njyewe niko mbibona, kuko nakoze iri koranabuhanga kenshi, kandi nakoze ku igeregeza ry'urukingo rwa Mers (ubundi bwoko bwa coronavirus) nabonye icyo bitanga.
"N'ubu, ndatekereza ko hari amahirwe menshi ko ruzakora".
Iri tsinda rigeze ku migambi yo gutunganya ingano nyinshi y'uru rukingo, ndetse na mbere y'uko bemeza ko rukora.
Prof Adrian Hill wo muri iri tsinda ati: "Intego ubu ni ukuba twabonye 'dose' miliyoni kugeza nibura mukwa cyenda, mu gihe tumaze kumenya ko rukora neza".
Adrian avuga ko biboneka neza ko isi izaba ikeneye 'dose' zibarirwa muri miliyoni amagana kugira ngo iki cyorezo gicike.
Agereranya 'dose' miliyoni imwe nk'intego idahambaye cyane kandi ko urukingo ariyo nzira ikwiye yo gucika kw'iki cyorezo.
Aba bashakashatsi bavuga ko mu mezi macye ari imbere bazamenya niba urukingo rwabo rukora neza.
Gusa, mu gihe abarwayi b'iki cyorezo bari kugabanuka kubera ingamba zikomeye zafashwe bishobora kuba intambamyi yo kumenya niba urukingo rukora neza.
Ubu baribaza niba bishobora kuba ngombwa ko hari abandu bazanduzwa Covid-19 ku bushake kugira ngo haboneke igisubizo vuba.
Leta y'Ubwongereza yashyizeho itsinda ryihariye ryo gufasha kwihutisha kugera ku rukingo rwa Covid-19 no gukora ingano nyinshi yarwo.
Ushinzwe ubushabitsi (business) muri guverinoma y'Ubwongereza avuga ko leta iri gufasha abo bahanga ngo bongere amahirwe yo kubigeraho mu buryo bushoboka.
Sir Patrick Vallance uyoboye iryo tsinda rya leta, avuga ko abantu bakwiye kumenya ko buri mushinga wose w'urukingo utaba ufite amahirwe menshi yo kurugeraho.
Ati: "Nubwo buri wese mu barukora aba afite ikizere, ntabwo uba uzi neza ko ubonye urukingo rugiye gukora".
