<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52430276' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52430276' term='COVID'>
Leta ya New York igiye kwemerera inzu zicuruza imiti kujya zinapima coronavirus
Guverineri wa leta ya New York avuga ko agiye kwemerera inzu zicuruza imiti (pharmacies) kujya zinapima icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Guverineri wa leta ya New York avuga ko agiye kwemerera inzu zicuruza imiti (pharmacies) kujya zinapima icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Iyi leta ni yo ndiri ya coronavirus muri iki gihugu.
Andrew Cuomo yavuze ko za 'pharmacies' zigera ku 5,000 zizajya zipima coronavirus, hagamijwe ko abantu bagera ku 40,000 bazajya bapimwa buri munsi.
Umubare w'abamaze kwemezwa ko barwaye Covid-19 - indwara yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero iterwa n'ubu bwoko bushya bwa coronavirus - muri Amerika barenga 939,000.
Hafi kimwe cya gatatu cy'abantu bose hamwe 53,934 imaze kwica muri Amerika ni abo muri leta ya New York yonyine.
Abarenga 105,000 bamaze kuyikira muri Amerika, nkuko imibare ya Kaminuza ya Johns Hopkins ibigaragaza.
Hagati aho, Perezida Donald Trump ntabwo yakoresheje ikiganiro cye cya buri munsi cyo gutanga amakuru yuko coronavirus ihagaze mu gihugu. Yavuze ko bitamutwarira "igihe cyangwa imbaraga".
Ku rubuga rwa Twitter ku munsi w'ejo ku wa gatandatu, Bwana Trump yavuze ko abanyamakuru "nta kindi bakora kitari ukubaza ibibazo byo kwibasira".
Yanenzwe bikomeye ubwo ku wa kane mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru yavuga ko harebwa niba umuti wa 'disinfectant' wica udukoko twa virusi na 'microbes' udashobora gukoreshwa mu kuvura coronavirus.
Abaganga n'inganda zikora imiti bamaganye ayo magambo ye bavuga ko ateye impungenge kandi yateza ibyago, bavuga ko imiti nk'iyo ya 'disinfectants' ari iyo kwitondera kandi ishobora kuba uburozi mu gihe yaba imizwe.
Mu mujyi wa New York, umubare w'abahamagara kuri nimero itishyurwa basaba ubutabazi kubera ko hari ibinyabutabire (chemicals) byabagizeho ingaruka, wikubye inshuro zirenga ebyiri mu masaha 18 ya nyuma yaho Bwana Trump avugiye ayo magambo.
Ni ukuvuga abantu 30 ugereranyije n'abantu 13 bakoresheje uwo murongo basaba ubwo butabazi mu gihe nk'icyo mu mwaka ushize.
Ibiganiro n'abanyamakuru bya Bwana Trump afatanyije n'itsinda ryo mu biro bye bya White House ryo kurwanya coronavirus, ubusanzwe byashoboraga kumara amasaha arenga abiri.
Ariko uko yitwaye mu kiganiro cyo ku wa kane byateye ipfunwe no muri bamwe mu bamushyigikiye, nkuko umunyamakuru wa BBC muri Amerika ya ruguru Peter Bowes abivuga.
Uyu munyamakuru yongeraho ko agendeye ku butumwa bwo kuri Twitter bwa Bwana Trump, bisa nkaho bwemeza ko ibiganiro nk'ibyo bishobora kuba birangiriye aho kuko amakusanyabitekerezo agaragaza ko bitongereye gukundwa kwe mu batora.
Ku wa gatanu, ikiganiro cya Bwana Trump cyari kigufi mu buryo budasanzwe - cyamaze iminota irenga gato 20 - ndetse ntabwo yemereye abanyamakuru kumubaza ibibazo.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_51971863' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/51971863' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: “Dufite ikizere ko Imana izaturinda” – Karerwa umuvugizi wa Perezida Nkurunziza
Mu Burundi ubuzima bukomeje nk'uko bisanzwe, umuvugizi w'umukuru w'igihugu Jean Claude Karerwa Ndenzako avuga ko iki gihugu cyahaye Imana umwanya udasanzwe bityo bizeye ko izakomeza kubarinda iki cyorezo, nubwo ngo biteguye kukirwanya kihageze.
Mu Burundi ubuzima bukomeje nk'uko bisanzwe, umuvugizi w'umukuru w'igihugu Jean Claude Karerwa Ndenzako avuga ko iki gihugu cyahaye Imana umwanya udasanzwe bityo bizeye ko izakomeza kubarinda iki cyorezo, nubwo ngo biteguye kukirwanya kihageze.
Nta murwayi wa Covid-19 uraboneka mu Burundi nk'uko abategetsi babitangaza, kugeza ubu iyi ndwara imaze kugera mu bihugu 33 muri 54 bya Afurika.
Ishami rya UN rishinzwe ubuzima ku isi OMS/WHO rigaragaza muri aka karere u Rwanda, Kenya, DR Congo na Tanzania ariho iyi ndwara imaze kugera, bitatu muri ibi bihugu ni ibituranyi n'u Burundi.
Aho iyi ndwara imaze kugera bahagaritse amashuri, amakoraniro y'abasenga, ingendo nyinshi z'indege, inama zihuza abantu benshi banashishikariza abantu kwirinda guhurira ahari abantu benshi.
Bwana Karerwa avuga ko mu Burundi ingamba zafashwe mu kwirinda iyi ndwara zigendanye no kuba iyi virus itarahagera.
Yabwiye BBC ati: "Izindi zizafatwa mu gihe bizagaragara ko koko icyo kiza kibangamiye igihugu ku rugero ibindi bihugu nk'Ubutaliyano n'Ubushinwa cyangwa ibyo by'Iburayi bigezeho.
"Ingingo ubu zafashwe ni izo kuzitira tutaronerwa, [ariko] uko umuntu yonerwa niko afata izindi ngingo nshyashya".
Mu burundi, ibikorwa bihuza abantu benshi, imyidagaduro, imikino, amaterani y'abasenga birakomeje nubwo ngo ababijyamo basabwa kwisunga ingingo nko gukaraba intoki, kwirinda kuramukanya, kwirinda kwegerana n'ibindi.
Bwana Karerwa ati"Ni ingingo zidasanzwe, abantu nubwo bahura ntibifata nk'uko bari basanzwe, biraboneka ko hari ikintu cyahindutse mu kubaho kw'abantu no mu mahuriro bahuriramo".
Bwana Karerwa avuga ko bizeye ko iyi ndwara nubwo yagera mu Burundi bizera ko itageza mu kwezi kwa gatanu ngo ibangamire amatora y'umukuru w'igihugu ateganyijwe tariki 20/05/2020.
Abajijwe niba bidashoboka ko iyi ndwara ishobora kubangamira amatora yagize ati:
"Byabangamira amatora mu gihe cyaba cyabaye ikiza cyakwiye igihugu cyose hafashwe ingingo nka ziriya zifatwa igihugu kiri mu ntambara".
Bwana Karerwa avuga ko u Burundi ari igihugu cyahaye Imana umwanya wa mbere, ko bizeye ko iyo Mana izaza ikabarinda ibyago byose.
Ati: "Ibyago byarateye hirya no hino ku isi ariko bigaca inyuma y'u Burundi, n'ubu rero dufite ukwizera ko ubu bwo kuko Imana twayihaye umwanya udasanzwe izaza nayo iturinde ibyo byose mwibaza ko bishobora gushyika".
Gusa avuga ko Imana nayo ngo isaba abantu kuba abanyabwenge ariyo mpamvu nabo biteguye bigendanye n'uko mu gihugu ubu bimeze.
