Coronavirus: Uganda iriko irondera umutanzania yanduye kugira imusubize iwabo
Ubushikiranganji bw'amagara yu'abantu bwa Uganda bumenyesha ko buriko burarondera umutanzania yanduye coronavirus kugira ngo bumusubize mu gihugu ciwe.
Ubushikiranganji bw'amagara yu'abantu bwa Uganda bumenyesha ko buriko burarondera umutanzania yanduye coronavirus kugira ngo bumusubize mu gihugu ciwe.
Uyo mugabo w'imyaka 34, asanzwe ari umushoferi w'amakamyo, akaba yinjiye muri ico gihugu  kuwa 16 z'uku kwa kane, yinjirira ku mupaka wa Mutukula avuye i Dar es Salaam.
Nk'uko bimenyeshwa n'ubwo bushikiranganji, uyo mugabo ntiyashotse yerekana ibimenyesto vya Covid-19.
Ingingo ya Uganda yo gusubiza iwabo abanyamahanga banduye umugeracoronavirus yateye impanri nyinshi ku mbuga hwaniro zitandukanye, haba mu gihugu canke no hanze.
Ku munsi wa kane, umushikiranganji w'amagara y'abantu Ruth Jane Aceng  yamenyesheje ko ibihugu bihurikiye mu muryango wa Afrika y'Ubuseruko vyumvikanye ko umuntu uwo ari we wese wo muri ivyo bihugu azopimwa agasanga yaranduye coronavirus ko azoca asubizwa iwabo kugira ngo avurirweyo.
Avuga ko buri munsi Uganda yakira abashoferi b'amakamyo bashika 3000 bava mu bihugu vy'akarere ka Afrika y'Ubuseruko, ko rero ata bushobozi ifise bwo kubavura.
Ejo ku wa gatanu, Uganda yatangaje ko mu badereva b'amakamyo bashika 774 bafashwe ibipimo ku mipaka imbere y'uko binjira mu gihugu hari umwe bahavuye basanga yaranduye.
Gushika ubu, Uganda ifise abantu 55 bamaze kwemezwa ko banduye Covid-19.
Mu ntango z'ino ndwi, umukuru w'ico gihugu, Yoweri Museveni, yarongereje ikiringo ca Gumamurugo gushika ku minsi 21 anavuga ko n'izindi ngingo zose zafashwe imbere y'iyo ngingo zizobandanya uko bisanzwe.
Muri zo harimwo kubuza amakoraniro, kwugara amasengero hamwe n'ibigo vy'amashure.
Abemerewe gukora akazi bonyene ni abo mu gisata c'amagara y'abantu, abajejwe umutekano, abakozi b'amabanki hamwe n'abamenyeshamakuru.
Amamodoka yunguruza abantu yarahagaritswe, co kimwe n'indege zitwara ingenzi.
Amamodoka atwara imizigo n'indege nazo nyene zitwara imizigo nivyo vyemerewe kubandanya bikora. Hagati aho, abadereva hamwe n'abandi bakozi bo muri izo ndege bategerezwa gushirwa mu bibanza vya leta vyateguwe gushirwamwo abiketswe ko banduye.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52217849' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52217849' term='COVID'>
Ubumwe bwa Afurika buri ku ruhande rwa OMS ku byo Trump ayishinja
Nyuma y'ibyavuzwe na Perezida Donald Trump, Perezida wa komisiyo y'Ubumwe bwa Afurika yatangaje ko iri shyirahamwe ry'ibihugu rishyigikiye ibikorwa n'ishami rya ONU ryita ku buzima (OMS/WHO) mu kurwanya coronavirus yabaye icyorezo ku isi.
Nyuma y'ibyavuzwe na Perezida Donald Trump, Perezida wa komisiyo y'Ubumwe bwa Afurika yatangaje ko iri shyirahamwe ry'ibihugu rishyigikiye ibikorwa n'ishami rya ONU ryita ku buzima (OMS/WHO) mu kurwanya coronavirus yabaye icyorezo ku isi.
Mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru ejo kuwa kabiri ,Perezida Donald Trump yavuze ko OMS/WHO yabagiriye inama mbi, ndetse yitaye cyane ku Bushinwa mu kurwanya iki cyorezo.
Bwana Trump yatangaje ko "WHO, ku mpamvu runaka, nubwo iterwa inkunga nini na Amerika, yibanze cyane ku Bushinwa" Ati: "Ibi tuzabisubiramo".
Bwana Trump avuga ko yanze inama mbi yagiriwe na WHO yo gukomeza gufungura imipaka yayo ku Bushinwa.
Moussa Faki Mahamat, Perezida wa komisiyo y'Ubumwe bwa Afurika yanditse kuri Twitter ko "yatunguwe no kubona hari inkubiri ya leta ya Amerika yo kurwanya WHO mu bikorwa iyoboye ku isi".
Bwana Faki yavuze ko umuryango w'ubumwe bwa Afurika ushyigikiye WHO n'umuyobozi wayo Dr Tedros Ghebreyesus.
Akavuga ko ubu "abatuye isi bakwiye gushyira hamwe mu kurwanya Covid-19". Ko igihe cyo kubaza abantu ibyo bakoze kizaza nyuma.
Kuri Twitter, ibyavuzwe na Bwana Trump bamwe babishyigikiye abandi barabinenga, bamwe bavuze ko leta ye itafashe ingamba zo kwirinda kare.
Leta zunze ubumwe za Amerika ubu nicyo gihugu gifite abantu benshi ku isi banduye Covid-19 bamaze kumenyakana, bararenga 400,000 ,imaze kwica abarenga 12,000.
OMS/WHO ntacyo iratangaza ku byavuzwe na Bwana Trump.
Perezida Paul Kagame w'u Rwanda, yasubije ashyigikira ibyavuzwe na Moussa Faki Mahamat, abaza niba ari Dr.Tedros, WHO, cyangwa Ubushinwa bugarijwe n'iki cyorezo gusa, cyangwa ari bose.
Bwana Kagame avuga ko imbaraga zikwiye gushyirwa mu kurwanya iki cyorezo, abafite ibyo bakoze bakazabibazwa nyuma. Ati: "Mudukize politiki nyinshi Africa ntibikeneye".
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52513914' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52513914' term='COVID'>
WHO yashyigikiye uko yitwaye mu guhangana na coronavirus
Ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS/WHO) rivuga ko "ritataye igihe" mbere yuko ritangira guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus, ni nyuma yo kunengwa uburyo ryitwaye mu ntangiriro.
Ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS/WHO) rivuga ko "ritataye igihe" mbere yuko ritangira guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus, ni nyuma yo kunengwa uburyo ryitwaye mu ntangiriro.
Dr Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, umukuru wa OMS, yavuze ko yatangaje ko iyi virusi ari ikibazo cyihutirwa kibangamiye ubuzima ku isi ku itariki ya 30 y'ukwa mbere, hari "igihe gihagije kugira ngo isi ihangane nacyo".
Icyo gihe abantu 82 gusa ni bo bari bamaze kwandura coronavirus hanze y'Ubushinwa ndetse nta muntu yaribwice
Kugeza ubu, abantu barenga miliyoni 3,3 bamaze kuyandura ku isi, muri bo abarenga 238,000 imaze kubica naho abarenga 1,000,000 bamaze kuyikira, nkuko imibare ya Kaminuza ya Johns Hopkins yo muri Amerika ibigaragaraza.
Perezida Donald Trump w'Amerika yavuze ko OMS "rwose yazambije" uburyo bwayo bwo guhangana na Covid-19, indwara y'ubuhumekero iterwa n'ubu bwoko bushya bwa coronavirus. Anayishinja kubogamira ku Bushinwa.
Amerika ni cyo gihugu cya mbere ku isi gitera inkunga nyinshi OMS ndetse Bwana Trump yavuze ko azayihagarika.
Mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru ku munsi w'ejo ku wa gatanu, Dr Tedros yarwanye bikomeye ku buryo OMS yitwaye nyuma yaho Covid-19 yadukiye.
Yashimangiye ko OMS yakoresheje igihe cyayo neza mbere yo gutangaza ko coronavirus ari ikibazo cyihutirwa kibangamiye ubuzima ku isi, harimo no gusura Ubushinwa ngo imenye kurushaho inkomoko y'iyi virusi.
Dr Tedros yemeje ko iki cyorezo na n'ubu kikiri "ikibazo cyihutirwa giteye impungenge ku buzima ku isi", amezi atatu nyuma yaho gitangarijwe ko kimeze gutyo.
Kugira ngo OMS ijye yatangaza ibyo, biba ari ibintu "bidasanzwe" kandi bisaba ko amahanga asenyera umugozi umwe.
Dr Tedros yavuze ko afite impungene "zikomeye" ku ngaruka iki cyorezo gishobora kugira muri iki gihe kiri kwiyongera mu bihugu bifite inzego z'ubuvuzi zijegajega.
Abakozi ba OMS bavuga ko babonye ukwiyongera guteye impungenge kwa coronavirus mu bihugu byinshi birimo nka Haïti, Somalia na Sudan.
OMS kandi yashishikarije ibihugu biri koroshya ingamba zo kutegerana kwigengesera mu kubikora. Yashimangiye akamaro ko kugenzura ubwiyongere bushya bw'ubwandu mu gihe cyo koroshya gahunda ya "guma mu rugo".
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-51885887' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-51885887' term='COVID'>
Impamvu utagomba gushya ubwoba kubera coronavirus
Coronavirus ntabwo ikiri kure n'u Rwanda rwatangaje umuntu wa mbere kuri uyu wa gatandatu, hafi buri wese aribaza ko ari ikibazo cy'amasaha cyangwa iminsi igakwira henshi kurushaho, ariko ntukwiye gushya ubwoba. Dore impamvu:
Coronavirus ntabwo ikiri kure n'u Rwanda rwatangaje umuntu wa mbere kuri uyu wa gatandatu, hafi buri wese aribaza ko ari ikibazo cy'amasaha cyangwa iminsi igakwira henshi kurushaho, ariko ntukwiye gushya ubwoba. Dore impamvu:
Ubu bwoko bushya bwa coronavirus bwahawe izina rya Covid-19 buri mu bwoko bwa za virus, udukoko duto cyane tutaboneshwa amaso, bita corona. Utu dukoko turandura cyane ariko ntidutinda mu mubiri w'umuntu.
Iyo tugeze mu muntu tujya mu mazuru, mu muhogo no mu bihaha tugatangira kuzahaza umubiri kimwe na virus isanzwe itera ibicurane bisanzwe.
Iyi virus irihuta cyane mu kwandura no kwiyongera ariko ingufu zayo mu kuzahaza umubiri kugeza ku rupfu rw'umuntu ziri hasi.
Ku bantu bayandura ishobora kwica hagati ya 2% na 3% gusa byabo.
Ibyago by'uko yakwica umuntu bifite gusa abantu bari hejuru y'imyaka 60 n'abantu basanzwe bafite ibindi bibazo by'ubuzima mu mubiri.
Ibihuha no kutagira amakuru nyayo ni byo bitera ubwoba abantu igikuba kigacika kuko iyo virus ari nshya abantu ntibaba bazi ubukana bwayo n'uko bayirinda.
Oya. 80% by'abayirwara bagira ibimenyetso byayo (indwara itera) byoroheje kandi iyi virus igapfa (igashira mu mubiri wabo) mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Nyinshi muri izi ndwara itera zisanzwe zivurwa zigakira iyo zivuwe kare.
Abantu bakuze bagira ibyago kurushaho kuko ituma baremba kubera intege z'umubiri.
Indwara itera, ku bantu bakiri bato cyangwa abana ibimenyetso byazo biba byoroheje.
Covid-19 biboneka ko ari gacye cyane ifata abana n'abo ifashe ibimenyetso byayo biba byoroheje.
Mu bantu bose bamaze kuyandura ku isi, ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS/WHO) rivuga ko 2% gusa ari abantu bari munsi y'imyaka 18.
Muri abo nabo, munsi ya 3% ni bo bagaragaje indwara iyi virus itera zazahaje bakaremba.
Kimwe na virus itera ibicurane bisanzwe, iva ku muntu uyirwaye mumatembabuzi yose ava mu gukorora, kwitsamura, kwikora mu maso, ku munwa no ku mazuru ikajya ku muntu utarayanduye muri ubwo buryo.
Yandurira kandi mu kwegerana cyane (nibura muri metero 1) n'uyifite cyangwa gukora ku bikoresho byakoreshejwe n'uyifite.
Oya. Nta byemezo bya gihanga birahamya ibi. Ndetse na virus za corona zabanjirije iyi nka SARS na MERS byabonetse ko zitandurira mu biryo.
Oya. Nabyo nta bushakashatsi burabyemeza. Gusa abahanga bavuga ko ari byiza buri gihe guteka inyama n'amagi bigashya neza.
Irinde gukora ku bantu benshi no kujya ahari abantu benshi.
Irinde kwikorakora ku mazuru, amaso n'umunwa kuko mu gihe waba wakoze ku wayanduye cyangwa aho iyi virus iri ihita ikugeraho.
Karaba intoki kenshi n'isabune kuko iyi virus yicwa n'amazi meza n'isabune mu gihe yaba iri ku ntoki zawe itaragera ku gicumbi cyayo (mu muhogo, mu mazuru, mu bihaha).
Niba ucyeka ko waba warayanduye ishyire mu kato, uhamagare abaganga, bwa mbere byaba byiza kuri telefone.
Ni umuriro, gukorora no kunanirwa guhumeka neza, bijya gusa n'iby'ibicurane (grippe/cold) bisanzwe, byo bishobora kugaragara hagati y'iminsi 2 na 14 iyi virus ikugezeho.
Niba ufite ibi bimenyetso wishya ubwoba, ushobora gukoresha uburyo bwo kuzibura inzira z'ubuhumekero (steam) kabiri ku munsi, ukanywa amazi kenshi, ugakaraba intoki kenshi wirinda gukwiza virus, ukavugana n'abaganga kandi ugafata imiti baguhaye.
Coronavirus uyirwaye ntakunze kuribwa mu muhogo (gapfura) kandi ntakunze kugira ikimyira mu mazuru (runny nose); ibyayo ni umuriro, gukorora no kunanirwa guhumeka neza.
Oya. Gupima coronavirus bikorwa gusa bisabwe n'abaganga igihe gusa umuntu yiswe ko "acyekwaho iyi ndwara".
Ibihugu byo mu karere ubu bimaze kugira ubushobozi bwo kuyipima, ariko ipimwa na 'laboratoires' nkeya zabugenewe gusa.
Impamvu ni uko iyi virus yandura cyane bityo hateganywa za 'laboratoires' zifite ubushobozi bwo kugenzura izi virus.
Izo ni 'laboratoires' zo ku rwego rwa "biosafety level 4"(BSL4), ni zo gusa zishobora gufata ibipimo bya Covid-19.
Yego. Kugeza ubu 80% by'abayanduye bayikira badakeneye ubuvuzi budasanzwe.
Ibimenyetso byayo (umuriro, inkorora no kunanirwa guhumeka neza) ni byo bivurwa bigakira mu gihe iyi virus igenda ipfa mu mubiri igashira.
Kimwe n'uko nta muti cyangwa urukingo biraboneka bivura virus itera ibicurane bisanzwe, coronavirus nayo ntirabonerwa umuti cyangwa urukingo.
Nta bushakashatsi bwa siyansi bwemeza ko birinda iyi virus.
Abahanga bemeza ko ubushyuhe n'imirasire y'izuba bigabanya ikwirakwira rya Covid-19.
Hagati y'amasaha 8 - 10 ku hantu horohereye nko ku giti kidatunganyije, iponji (sponge), igikarito, n'amasaha arenzeho kuri ayo ku hantu hakomeye nko ku kirahuri, plastike, icyuma, urubaho…
Nta bushakashatsi buragaragaza ko amatungo yororerwa cyangwa inyamaswa zo mu rugo birwara coronavirus.
Gusa ni byiza buri gihe gukaraba neza intoki mbere yo gukorakora ayo matungo n'inyamaswa.
IBINTU BITATU BYO GUTSINDA IYI VIRUS
KWIRINDA
KURINDA ABO MUBANA
KURINDA UMURYANGO MUGARI AHO URI
Aya makuru ntasimbura inama z'abaganga, yegeranyjwe gusa ku bw'impamvu zo guha abantu amakuru kuri Covid-19.
Yegeranyijwe hifashishijwe amakuru atangwa na OMS (WHO) n'ikigo cya leta y'Amerika Centers for Disease Control and Prevention.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52131598' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52131598' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus mu Rwanda: Abanduye biyongereye mu bidasanzwe, ubu byongerewe igihe
Leta y'u Rwanda yemeje ikindi gihe cy'iminsi 15 yo guhagarika ubuzima busanzwe hagakorwa ibyangombwa cyane gusa, ni mu gihe mu byumweru hafi bibiri habonetse abantu 65 banduye iyi ndwara.
Leta y'u Rwanda yemeje ikindi gihe cy'iminsi 15 yo guhagarika ubuzima busanzwe hagakorwa ibyangombwa cyane gusa, ni mu gihe mu byumweru hafi bibiri habonetse abantu 65 banduye iyi ndwara.
Ibyumweru bibiri byari byafashwe mbere byari bisigaje iminsi ibiri, gusa umubare w'abanduye Covid-19  wavuyeku bantu 17 ugera ubu kuri 82 mbere y'uko ibyo byumweru bibiri byuzura.
Ibihugu umunani bya Afurika bimaze gufata ingamba nk'izi zo kubuza abantu kuva mu ngo zabo no guhagarika ibikorwa bisanzwe mu rwego rwo kwirinda iki cyorezo.
Leta y'u Rwanda yatangaje ko mu kindi gihe cy'indi minsi 15, kugeza tariki 19/04/2020, abantu babujijwe kuva mu ngo kereka bagiye guhaha, kwivuza, kuri banki cyangwa gutanga izo serivisi.
Amashuri yose mu gihugu, utubari n'imyidagaruro, insengero, ingendo mu gihugu, imipaka n'ibindi bizakomeza gufungwa.
Abantu ariko bemerewe gukomeza imirimo y'ubuhinzi n'ubworozi, imipaka izafungurwa ku bwikorezi bw'ibintu n'amasoko acuruza ibiribwa n'imiti bizakomeza gukora.
Leta y'u Rwanda kandi ivuga ko izakomeza gufasha Abanyarwanda babuze amikoro kubera ingaruka z'iki cyorezo.
U Rwanda nicyo gihugu cya mbere cya Afurika yo munsi y'ubutayu bwa Sahara cyafashe izi ngamba (lockdwon) mu kwirinda iki cyorezo ubu kimaze kwandura abarenga 6,000 mu bihugu birenga 45 bya Afurika.
Minisiteri y'ubuzima mu Rwanda yaraye itangaje ko hari abandi bantu bashya barindwi banduye iyi ndwara.
Mu bantu 82 bamaze kubonwaho Covid-19 mu Rwanda, muri bo 13 ni abayanduriye mu gihugu.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_52382707' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/52382707' term='COVID'>
Tanzania: Ibiharuro vy'abanduye vyaduze, barasabwa kwizera leta mu ntambara na Covid-19
Umushikiranganji wa mbere wa Tanzania Kassim Majaliwa asaba abanyagihugu kwizera leta yabo n'abahinga bayo mu vy'ubuvuzi mu rugamba rwo kurwanya coronavirus. Ni mu gihe ibiharuro vy'abanduye bikomeje kuduga.
Umushikiranganji wa mbere wa Tanzania Kassim Majaliwa asaba abanyagihugu kwizera leta yabo n'abahinga bayo mu vy'ubuvuzi mu rugamba rwo kurwanya coronavirus. Ni mu gihe ibiharuro vy'abanduye bikomeje kuduga.
Umushikiranganji Majaliwa yashikirije ayo majambo mu gisabisho cabereye mu gisagara ca Dar es Salaam, cahuje amashengero atandukanye categuwe mu ntumbero yo gusaba  Imana ko yobakiza coronavirus.
Ati: " Ndatahura ko bamwe mu baTanzaniya bagenzacu bipfuza kubona ingingo zindi zifashwe mu ntumbero yo kurwanya iki kiza".
"Ariko, ni vyiza ko botahura ko ingingo iyo ari yo yose ifise ingaruka mbi na nziza. Rero leta ibandanya yihweza ingingo imwe ku yindi ingaruka mbi na nziza zishobora kuyivamwo".
Muri Tanzania hatangajwe abandi bantu 30 bashya banduye coronavirus, bose hamwe ubu bamaze kuba 284, muri bo 11 barakize naho 10 barapfuye.
Uyo mutegetsi avuze ivyo asa n'uwishura ku kamo kama kariko gaterwa n'abanyagihugu basaba leta ko yofata ingingo ruhasha, nk'izijanye na Gumamurugo mu gisagara  ca Dar es Salaam, mu gihe ibiharuro vy'ababandanya kwandura coronavirus biduga nk'umwampi.
Bamwe mbere basaba ko amakoraniro y'amashengero yohagarikwa mu ntumbero yo guhagarika ikwirakwira ry'uwo mugera.
Gushika ubu, leta ya Tanzania yaranse gufata ingingo ruhasha zo guhagarika uruja n'uruza .
Umukuru w'Inama Nshingamateka, Job Ndugai, avuga ko ingingo za Gumamurugo zibereye ibihugu vya Bulaya, akavuga ko zomerera nabi cane abantu babeshejweho n'intica ntikize.
Ico gisabisho c'uno munsi categuwe n'ubushikiranganji bw'amagara y'abantu bufadikanije n'abakuru b'amadini, kikaba cerekanywe ikibiriraho ku binyamakuru vyo muri Tanzania.
Abaserukira amadini batari bake bari bitabiriye ivyo bisabisho bakaba berekanywe bicaye ku buryo atawegera uwundi.
Ni inyuma y'akamo gaherutse guterwa na Perezida John Magufuli w'ico gihugu asaba ko hoba ibisabisho mu gihugu cose vyo gusaba Imana ngo ibakize ico kiza.
Tanzania itangaza ko gushika ubu,  abantu bashika 254 ari bo bamaze kwandura coronavirus, nayo 10 ikaba imaze kubahitana.
Ibiharuro bishasha vyerekana ko uwo mugera umaze gushika mu ntara zirenga igice c'intara zose za Tanzania.
</doc>
