Uyu ni umunsi mpuzamahanga w'isi, ni iki igusaba kuyikorera?
Tariki 22/04 ni umunsi mpuzamahanga wahariwe isi dutuyeho, ubu urizihizwa ku nshuro ya 50 nubwo ibikorwa bisanzwe biwukorwaho byinshi bitaba nk'ibisanzwe kuko isi yugarijwe n'icyorezo coronavirus.
Tariki 22/04 ni umunsi mpuzamahanga wahariwe isi dutuyeho, ubu urizihizwa ku nshuro ya 50 nubwo ibikorwa bisanzwe biwukorwaho byinshi bitaba nk'ibisanzwe kuko isi yugarijwe n'icyorezo coronavirus.
Insanganyamatsiko y'uyu munsi ni "ukugira icyo dukora turwanya ihindagurika ry'ikirere" nk'uko bivugwa n'umuryango w'abibumbye.
Iki cyo ikibazo gihangayikishije isi n'abayituye uyu munsi ndetse kizagora cyane abazayitura mu gihe kizaza, uyu munsi washyiriweho kugira icyo duhindura mu gukemura icyo kibazo.
Tariki 22/04/1970 abaturage ba Amerika bagera kuri miliyoni 20 bagiye mu mihanda bamagana ubujiji bwariho mu kwangiza isi, basaba ingamba nshya ngo irengerwe.
Iyo tariki yahise yitwa "umunsi w'isi" ndetse ugenda wizihizwa no mu bindi bihugu by'isi.
Kuva ubwo muri Amerika hatowe amategeko arengera ibidukikije, itegeko rirengera amazi meza, umwuka mwiza n'ibinyabuzima biri gucika.
Mu 2016 UN yahisemo ko ku itariki nk'iyi aribwo hasinywa amaserano mpuzamahanga ya Paris yo kurwanya ihindagurika ry'ikirere.
Ubutumwa bwatanzwe n'Umuryango w'Abibumbye (UN/ONU) buvuga ko isi idutuje idusaba kugira icyo dukora mu kuyirengera.
Umunyamabanga mukuru w'umuryango w'abibumbye Antonio Guterres yagize ati:
„Tugomba kurushaho kugira icyo dukora mu kurinda umubumbe wacu coronavirus ndetse n'akandi kaga kose gakomoka ku iyangirika ry'ikirere"
Imiriro y'ishyamba n'ubushyuhe bw'ikirenga biherutse gutwika Australia, icyorezo cy'inzige giheruka kwibasira Afurika y'iburasirazuba.
Ubu n'icyorezo kidasanzwe mu mateka y'isi cya virus yiswe Covid-19 kiri kugarika ingogo, inkomoko yabyo abahanga bavuga ko ari urusobe rw'imibereho ya none.
UN ivuga ko ihindagurika ry'ikirere ryahinduye byinshi ku buzima kamere n'urusobe rw'ibinyabuzima.
Ibyo ni nk'iyangizwa ry'amashyamba, ikoreshwa nabi ry'ubutaka, kwiyongera kw'imyuka ihumanya ikirere no kwiyongera kw'ubucuruzi butemewe bw'inyamaswa n'ibizikomokaho.
Iki cyanyuma kikaba kivugwa mu gukwira kw'indwara ziva ku nyamaswa zijya mu bantu nka Covid-19.
Ishmi ry'ibidukikije rya UN rivuga ko mu ndwara nshya ziboneka mu bantu buri mezi ane(4), 75% byazo ziva ku nyamaswa.
UN isaba abatuye isi ko umunsi nk'uyu ubibutsa ko bakwiye gutekereza ku kugera ku bukungu bitabangamiye isi n'ubuzima.
Bakirinda bimwe cyangwa byose muri biriya bikorwa byandiza uyu mubumbe dutuye bigashyira ubuzima mu kaga.
UN ivuga ko igikorwa gito mu kurengera isi, ariko gikozwe na buri wese n'umutima ushaka, cyakiza benshi none n'abazaza nyuma yacu.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-51988634' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-51988634' term='COVID'>
Chloroquine kuri coronavirus: Uwo muti waba wemejwe muri Amerika nkuko Trump abivuga?
Perezida Donald Trump wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika yavuze ko umuti ukoreshwa mu kuvura malaria wemejwe muri Amerika nk'uvura ubu bwoko bushya bwa coronavirus.
Perezida Donald Trump wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika yavuze ko umuti ukoreshwa mu kuvura malaria wemejwe muri Amerika nk'uvura ubu bwoko bushya bwa coronavirus.
Chloroquine ni umwe mu miti imaze igihe kinini ikoreshwa kandi uzwi cyane ku isi mu miti ivura malaria.
None Perezida Trump yaba avugisha ukuri? Ni iki se kizwi ku bushobozi bw'uwo muti? Ishami rya BBC rya 'Reality Check' ryasuzumye ukuri kwabyo.
Ibinini bya chloroquine bimaze imyaka ibarirwa muri za mirongo bikoreshwa ku isi.
Ntabwo ibyo binini bigikoreshwa mu bice byinshi ku mugabane w'Afurika kubera ko imibu itera malaria yagiye yongera ubukana kuburyo ibyo binini bitakiyihangara ngo biyivure.
Ibihugu bimwe na bimwe byashyizeho amategeko yo kugabanya ikoreshwa ry'uwo muti, ariko wakomeje gukoreshwa cyane mu bihugu bifite urwego rw'abikorera ku giti cyabo mu by'imiti bashabutse cyane ndetse uragurishwa cyane ku isoko ry'imiti.
Ibyo bigaragara cyane nko muri Nigeria ahavuzwe amakuru yuko ibyo binini bya chloroquine biri kugurwa cyane muri za farumasi (pharmacies) bikaba ubu bitagihagije, ku ruhande rumwe bitewe n'ibyatangajwe na Bwana Trump.
Mu kiganiro agirana n'abanyamakuru buri munsi, Perezida Trump yavuze ko chloroquine yemejwe nk'umuti uvura icyorezo cya coronavirus, avuga ko wemejwe n'urwego rugenzura ubuziranenge bw'ibiribwa n'imiti muri Amerika, US Food and Drugs Administration (FDA).
Yagize ati: "Tugiye gutuma uwo muti uboneka ku bantu nk'aka kanya. Kandi icyo ni ikintu urwego FDA rwagaragaje ko rushoboye cyane. Banyuze mu cyiciro cyo kwemeza - waremejwe".
Kugira ngo bisobanuke neza, chloroquine yemejwe nk'umuti uvura malaria ndetse n'indwara yo kubabara mu muteramangingo izwi nka 'arthritis'.
Ariko ikigo FDA cyasobanuye neza ko atari uko bimeze ku kuvura abarwaye indwara ya Covid-19 yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero iterwa n'ubu bwoko bushya bwa coronavirus.
Icyo kigo cyagize kiti: "Nta miti yemejwe na FDA ivura cyangwa irinda kwandura Covid-19".
Ariko nanone, ikigo FDA kivuga rwose ko ubushakashatsi butandukanye buri gukorwa ngo harebwe niba chloroquine ishobora gutanga umusaruro mu kuvura Covid-19.
Ikigo FDA kinavuga ko cyategetswe na Bwana Trump gushyiraho ikigo kinini cyo kugerageza uwo muti ku barwayi ngo hagenzurwe ubushobozi bwawo.
Ntibitangaje ko chloroquine iri mu miti ikomeje gushakirizwaho mu gufasha abarwayi ba coronavirus.
Irazwi cyane, irahendutse kandi biroroshye kuyikora. Mu kuvura abarwayi ba malaria, uwo muti ukoreshwa mu kugabanya umuriro no kubabuka k'umubiri kubera uburwayi (inflammation).
James Gallagher, umunyamakuru wa BBC ukurikiranira hafi inkuru z'ubuzima, yagize ati:
"Chloroquine isa nkaho ihagarika coronavirus mu bushakashatsi bwo muri za 'laboratoires'. Hari ibimenyetso by'ibivugwa n'abaganga bavuga ko yagaragaye nk'ifasha".
Ariko - kandi ibi ni ingenzi - nta kuyigerageza ku barwayi ba coronavirus kwari kwarangira, mu gihe iryo gerageza ari ingenzi mu kugaragaza uko uwo muti witwara ku barwayi nyabarwayi atari abo muri 'laboratoire', nubwo hari amagerageza nk'ayo ari gukorwa kuri ubu mu Bushinwa, Amerika, Ubwongereza no muri Espanye.
Ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS/WHO) rivuga ko kugeza ubu nta kimenyetso ntakuka gihari kigaragaza umusaruro wa chloroquine ku barwayi ba coronavirus, ariko ko ari imwe mu birimo gukorwaho igerageza.
Profeseri Trudie Lang, ukuriye ikigo cy'ubushakashatsi mu buzima ku isi cya The Global Health Network cyo kuri Kaminuza ya Oxford mu Bwongereza, agira ati:
"Mu rwego rwo kumenya imiti yashobora kuvura iyi virusi, ducyeneye kuyikorera amasuzuma ku barwayi mu kubona gihamya yuzuye yatuma tumenya niba iyo miti ikora cyangwa idakora".
Kuri internet, abantu bakomeje kwiyongera bashaka kumenya byinshi kuri uwo muti.
Amashakisha y'ijambo "chloroquine" yari yongereye ku kigero cyo hejuru cyane mu cyumweru gishize, nkuko bigaragazwa n'imibare y'uburyo bwa Google Trends bugaragaza ibiri gushakishwa cyane hifashishijwe Google.
</doc>
