Coronavirus : Zitto Kabwe abwira Leta ati ‘Reka guha Abatanzania ivyizere bitari vyo’
Zitto Kabwe, umukuru w'abatavuga rumwe na leta muri Tanzania, aragabisha leta ko yoreka gushira imbere ivyizere bitari vyo mu gihe igitigiri c'abandura coronavirus mu gihugu kibandanya kiduga ku rugero ruteye ubwoba.
Zitto Kabwe, umukuru w'abatavuga rumwe na leta muri Tanzania, aragabisha leta ko yoreka gushira imbere ivyizere bitari vyo mu gihe igitigiri c'abandura coronavirus mu gihugu kibandanya kiduga ku rugero ruteye ubwoba.
Bwana Kabwe avuga ko abanyagihugu bakeneye kubwirwa ukuri ku bijanye n'ico kiza.
Abatavuga rumwe na leta muri Tanzania babandanya kunegura ingingo za leta mu guhangana n'icorezo Covid-19
Bamwe basaba leta gufata ingingo zo guhagarika ubuzima busanzwe mu bisagara nka Dar es Salaam ahabaye ikiririmbiro ry'iki kiza.
Ejo ku wa gatatu, Tanzania yatangaje ko hari abandi 30 banduye coronavirus, ivyatumye igitigiri c'abamaze kwandura mu gihugu gishika kuri 284, harimwo cumi bamaze gupfa.
Ejo nyene ku wa gatatu, umushikiranganji wa mbere, Kassim Majaliwa, yasavye Abatanzaniya kwizera leta yabo hamwe n'abahinga bayo muvyo ubuvuzi muri iyo ntambara na coronavirus.
Yamenyesheje ko leta itegerezwa kwihweza ingingo imwe ku yindi imbere y'uko ifata ingingo ruhasha mu ntumbero yo kurwanya ikwirakwira ry'uwo mugera.
Amakoraniro y'amadini arabandanya muri ico gihugu ukuri kwamye, nayo Perezida John Magufuli yumvikana avuga ko coronavirus idashobora kuba mu mubiri wa Kristu, akabwira abantu ko bosenga kandi bakabandanya baja mu masengero.
Perezida Magufuli yaranse gufata ingingo za Gumamurugo mu gisagara ca Dar es Salaam, aharangwa igitigiri kini c'abanduye uwo mugera, nk'uko bivugwa n'itororokanirizo ry'amakuru Reuters.
Avuga ko iyo ngingo yobangamira ubutunzi, mu gihe ikivuko ca Dar es Salaam cinjiriza igihugu amafaranga menshi.
Ejo ku wagatatu, Perezida Magufuli yasavye ibihugu bitanga ingurane gufuta amadeni ibihugu vya Afrika bibifitiye kugira ngo bishobore gukoresha uburyo vyaziganije mu kurwanya coronavirus.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_52119937' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/52119937' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Ku ncuro ya mbere hatangajwe ica rimwe abantu benshi bayanduye mu karere
Ubushikiranganji bw'amagara y'abantu muri Kenya bwatangaje ko habonetse abantu bashasha 22 batowemwo umugera coronavirus, vyatumye ibitigiri  vy'abayanduye biba 81 muri ico gihugu.
Ubushikiranganji bw'amagara y'abantu muri Kenya bwatangaje ko habonetse abantu bashasha 22 batowemwo umugera coronavirus, vyatumye ibitigiri  vy'abayanduye biba 81 muri ico gihugu.
Mutahi Kagwe arongoye ubwobushikiranganji yavuze ko muri abo 22 batoyemwo uwo mugera, 21 muri bo basanzwe barashizwemu cumba ca bonyene.
Ibi nivyo bitigiri vy'abantu benshi batoyemwo Covid-19 ku munsi umwe muri aka karere k'ibiyaga binini.
Muri abo bayitoyemo 18 ni abanyagihugu ba Kenya, babiri ni abo muri Pakistan bandi babiri ni abo muri Cameroun. Muri bose, 13 ni abagabo icenda ni abagore.
Bwana Kagwe amenyesha ko abo 22 batowe mu bipimo 300 vyafashwe mu masaha 24 aheze.
Muri Kenya kandi, umukenyezi wa mbere yatanguye kumenyekana ko yari yanduye coronavirus amenyesha ko yakize neza inyuma y'iminsi 23 ariko aravurwa.
Uyo mukenyezi azwi kw'izina rya Brenda, yabwiye abanyamakuru ko yari yagiye muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika mu kwa cumi na kabiri guheze, ariko akaba yagiye kwikeka ko yoba yaranduye uwo mugera amaze kugaruka muri Kenya avuye i Londres mu ntango z'ukwa gatatu.
Uyo mukenyezi hamwe na mugenziwe Brian bagiriraniye ikiyago na Perezida Uhuru Kenyatta mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru baciye ku buhinga bwa bw'imboneshakure ica ku mbuga ngurukanabumenyi.
Brenda ati: "Nafashwe n'inkorora mu kiringo c'iminsi itatu yose maze kugaruka mu gihugu".
Avuga ko yaciye anyarukira ku kigo leta yategekanije co kwakira abanduye uwo mugera ku mugwa mukuru Nairobi kugira ngo yivuze.
Ahanura abanyagihugu ba Kenya, Brenda yavuze ati: "Covid-19 ni indwara ishobora kuvurwa igakira".
Eka na mugenziwe Brian avuga ko yanduye uwo mugera inyuma y'aho abonaniye na Brenda, amenyesha ko na we nyene yakize.
Avuga ko ivyamubayeko vyatumye n'ababanyi biwe bemera ko iyo ndwara "ivurwa kandi igakira".
Perezida Kenyatta yashimiye cane Brenda kubona yaciye yibwiriza agafata ingingo we nyene yo kwijana ku kigo gishirwamwo abanduye uwo mugera, amaze kwumva ko akitswe n'amagara.
Brian yagiye gushikanwa muri ico kibanza nk'umwe mu bagenzi ba hafi cane ba Brenda.
Baciye ku mbuga hwaniro, Abanyakenya benshi bashimye kubona amakuru y'abo bantu babiri yatangajwe ku mugaragaro, bakavuga ko ivyo bibaha icizere.
Kuva Kenya itangaje umuntu wa mbere yanduye Covid-19 kuwa 13 z'uku kwa gatatu, abashika 81 nibo bamaze gutangazwa ko  bamaze kuyandura gushika ubu.
Nico gihugu gifise abayanduye benshi mu ari Afirika y'Iburasirazuba.
</doc>
