<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-51640156' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-51640156' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Minisitiri wungirije w'ubuzima wa Iran bayimusanzemo
Minisitiri wungirije w'ubuzima wa Iran ndetse n'umudepite bombi basanzwemo ubu bwoko bushya bwa coronavirus, mu gihe iki gihugu imaze kwicamo abantu 15 gikomeje kugorwa no kuyihagarika.
Minisitiri wungirije w'ubuzima wa Iran ndetse n'umudepite bombi basanzwemo ubu bwoko bushya bwa coronavirus, mu gihe iki gihugu imaze kwicamo abantu 15 gikomeje kugorwa no kuyihagarika.
Iki gihugu ni kimwe mu hantu hatatu hugarijwe cyane na coronavirus hanze y'Ubushinwa, ibintu biri gutera impungenge ko iyi virusi ishobora kuba iri guhinduka icyorezo.
Uwo Minisitiri wungirije w'ubuzima,  Iraj Harirchi, ku wa mbere yahakanye ko hari ibikorwa byo guhishira amakuru ajyanye na coronavirus mu gihugu.
Yagaragaye nk'utameze neza ku mubiri ubwo yaganiraga n'abanyamakuru, akorora ndetse agaragara abira icyuya.
Iran imaze gutangaza abantu 95 banduye coronavirus, ariko umubare w'ukuri w'abamaze kuyandura byibazwa ko ushobora kuba ari munini kurushaho.
Umukuru w'ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS/WHO) yavuze ko uko kwiyongera kw'ako kanya kw'abanduye coronavirus hanze y'Ubushinwa "guteye impungenge zikomeye".
Ejo ku wa kabiri, Mike Pompeo, umunyamabanga wa leta y'Amerika, yavuze ko Amerika itewe impungenge nuko Iran ishobora kuba yarahishiriye "amakuru y'ingenzi" ajyanye na coronavirus ndetse ashishikariza ibihugu byose "kuvugisha ukuri kuri coronavirus".
Abantu benshi kurushaho bamaze kwicwa na coronavirus muri Iran kurusha ahandi hantu aho ari ho hose ho hanze y'Ubushinwa. Ibi bihugu byombi bifitanye umubano ukomeye ushingiye ku bucuruzi.
Ibindi bihugu ubu biri kuvugwaho cyane kubera coronavirus ni Koreya y'Epfo n'Ubutaliyani, aho umubare w'abayanduye wiyongereye cyane mu minsi micye ishize.
Ku isi abantu barenga 80,000 bamaze kwandura indwara yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero izwi nka Covid-19 iterwa n'ubu bwoko bushya bwa coronavirus kuva yakwaduka mu mwaka ushize.
Abantu bagera hafi ku 2,700 imaze kubahitana - benshi muri bo bakaba ari abo mu Bushinwa.
Ariko uko ibintu bimeze ubu muri Iran byateje impungenge zikomeye zuko coronavirus ishobora kuba igiye kwibasira akarere k'uburasirazuba bwo hagati.
Muri icyo gihugu hari ahantu hafatwa nk'ahatagatifu hahurira abantu babarirwa muri za miliyoni buri mwaka kandi hakaba ari mu karere aho ibihugu byinshi bifite inzego z'ubuzima zifite intege nke.
Mu hantu hugarijwe cyane muri iki gihe ho hanze y'Ubushinwa, Iran ni yo ihangayicyishije cyane kuko nta shusho yuzuye y'ukuri y'uko ibintu bimeze muri icyo gihugu ihari, nkuko bivugwa na Dr Nathalie MacDermott, impuguke mu ndwara zandura wo kuri Kaminuza ya King's College London mu Bwongereza.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52074467' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52074467' term='COVID'>
Covid-19: Perezida Kagame ati, 'Umubare uzakomeza uzamuke kuko hakomeje gushakishwa abahuye n'abarwayi'
Perezida Paul Kagame w'u Rwanda yaraye aburiye abaturage ko umubare w'abamaze kwandura coronavirus mu gihugu uzakomeza kwiyongera, ariko ko ari mu rwego rwo guhashya iki cyorezo burundu.
Perezida Paul Kagame w'u Rwanda yaraye aburiye abaturage ko umubare w'abamaze kwandura coronavirus mu gihugu uzakomeza kwiyongera, ariko ko ari mu rwego rwo guhashya iki cyorezo burundu.
Minisiteri y'ubuzima ejo yatangaje ko umubare w'abanduye coronavirus kugeza ubu ari 54.
Bwana Kagame yagize ati: "Uyu mubare uzakomeza uzamuke kuko hakomeje gushakishwa abahuye n'abarwayi b'iyo ndwara kugira ngo bapimwe, ndetse abagaragayeho uburwayi bavurwe".
Bwana Kagame avuga ko ari bwo "buryo bwiza bwo gufasha abashobora kuba baranduye mu rwego rwo kurinda imiryango yabo ndetse natwe twese aho dutuye".
Perezida Kagame kandi yahamagariye abaturage gukomeza gushyira mu bikorwa ingamba n'amabwiriza byafashwe, "tukihanganira ingorane zose byaba bitera kugira ngo dutsinde iki cyorezo burundu, cyo guhitana abantu benshi".
Izo ngamba zirimo nko kuguma mu rugo, gusiga intambwe ndende hagati y'umuntu n'undi, gukaraba intoki neza kandi kenshi ndetse no kubimenyesha inzego z'ubuyobozi igihe hari ugaragaje ibimenyetso birimo inkorora y'akayi no guhinda umuriro.
Yavuze ko inzego zitandukanye ziri gutegura uburyo ab'amikoro macye ahanini bari batunzwe n'imirimo y'amaboko bakora bavuye mu rugo, bafashwa kandi ko bigiye kwihutishwa.
Anastase Shyaka, Minisitiri w'ubutegetsi bw'igihugu, yanditse kuri Twitter kuri uyu wa gatandatu ko ubwo bufasha - bw'ibiribwa n'ibindi bikoresho by'ibanze - butangwa urugo ku rundi binyuze muri za komite zo mu mudugudu, akagari n'umurenge.
Abari batunzwe n'imirimo nk'iyo bakomeje kugira impungenge ku mibereho yabo mu gihe kuri ubu batemerewe gukora akazi kabo uko bisanzwe.
Bwana Kagame kandi yashimiye abakora mu rwego rw'ubuzima mu gihugu bakomeje kwitanga, ndetse n'ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima n'umuherwe w'Umushinwa Jack Ma ku nkunga y'ibikoresho byo gupima Covid-19.
Yongeyeho ati: "Ibyemezo dufata uyu munsi nibyo bizatuma dushobora guhashya iki cyorezo vuba, kugira ngo dusubire mu buzima busanzwe".
Perezida Kagame yatangaje ubwo butumwa - bwa kabiri kuva umurwayi wa mbere yatangazwa mu gihugu mu byumweru bibiri bishize - mu gihe ku munsi w'ejo ku wa gatanu umubare w'abanduye coronavirus mu Rwanda wageze kuri 54.
Ni nyuma yuko kuri uwo munsi w'ejo hiyongereyeho abarwayi bane.
Minisiteri y'ubuzima mu Rwanda ivuga ko abo barwayi harimo umwe wavuye i Dubai n'undi wavuye muri Amerika, aba bakaba barahise bashyirwa mu kato bakihagera.
Abandi ni abantu babiri bayanduriye mu Rwanda bahuye n'abayirwaye, nabo bakaba barashyizwe mu kato.
Iyi minisiteri ivuga ko mu barwayi b'iyi ndwara ubu nta numwe urembye, ko bari koroherwa kandi abenshi muri bo ubu nta bimenyetso by'iyi ndwara bagaragaza.
Nkuko bitangazwa na Kaminuza ya Johns Hopkins yo muri Amerika, kugeza ku munsi w'ejo ku wa gatanu, ku isi hari abarwayi barenga 540,000 ba coronavirus, naho abagera ku 24,000 yari imaze kubica. Abandi 124,000 barayikize.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52216514' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52216514' term='COVID'>
Umuyobozi wa Twitter yemeye gutanga inkunga ya miliyari y’amadolari yo kurwanya Covid-19
Jack Dorsey washinze urubuga rwa Twitter na 'app' yo kwishyuriraho izwi nka 'Square', yavuze ko azatanga imfashanyo ya miliyari y'amadolari y'Amerika yo kurwanya coronavirus.
Jack Dorsey washinze urubuga rwa Twitter na 'app' yo kwishyuriraho izwi nka 'Square', yavuze ko azatanga imfashanyo ya miliyari y'amadolari y'Amerika yo kurwanya coronavirus.
Bwana Dorsey avuga ko iyo mfashanyo ingana hafi na 28% by'umutungo we wose.
Yabitangarije kuri Twitter, avuga ko "ibicyenewe biri kurushaho kwihutirwa".
Bwana Dorsey ntabwo yasobanuye neza aho iyo mfashanyo izoherezwa mu gufasha kurwanya Covid-19.
Muri Amerika, hari ikibazo cy'ubucye bw'ibyuma bya 'ventilators' bifasha abarwayi ba Covid-19 gukomeza guhumeka, ndetse n'ibikoresho byo kurinda abantu bidahagije.
Abanyamerika n'abakora ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi na bo kandi muri rusange bari kugira ibibazo bijyanye n'amikoro.
Bwana Dorsey avuga ko azifashisha imigabane afite muri Square mu kubona amafaranga y'iyo mfashanyo, akazayatanga abinyujije mu kigo 'Start Small Foundation'.
Uyu mugabo w'imyaka 43 y'amavuko ni umuyobozi mukuru wa Twitter na Square.
Yavuze ko azifashisha imigabane ye muri Square - aho kuba iyo muri Twitter - kuko "myinshi" muri yo ari iye bwite.
Iyo migabane avuga ko izagenda itangwa uko igihe gishira, bigashobora kuba hari icyo byahindura ku gaciro kayo ndetse no ku ngano y'imfashanyo yose muri rusange.
Yavuze ko igihe icyorezo cya Covid-19 kizaba "kimaze kuneshwa", iyo mfashanyo izahita ikomereza mu birimo nko gufasha mu buzima n'uburezi bw'abakobwa.
Mu ruhererekane rw'ubutumwa bwo kuri Twitter bugizwe n'ibice bitandatu, Bwana Dorsey yavuze ko ashaka gufasha mu nzego azabona icyo zigezeho ku bw'iyo mfashanyo akiriho.
Izo mfashanyo zizatangwa binyujijwe mu buryo abaherwe bakunze gukoresha mu gutanga imfashanyo, ariko bukunze kunengwa kudakorera mu mucyo.
Asa nk'utanguranwa mu kwisobanura, Bwana Dorsey yahise atangaza 'link' ijyana ku nyandiko yo kuri Google izajya igaragaza ku mugaragaro iyo mfashanyo n'uko ikoreshwa.
Uyu mukuru wa Twitter ntabwo ari we muherwe wenyine mu ikoranabuhanga utunze za milyari y'amadolari usezeranyije igice cy'umutungo we mu kurwanya coronavirus.
Mark Zuckerberg washinze Facebook yatanze miliyoni 30 z'amadolari, nyinshi muri zo zizakoreshwa mu bikorwa byo gushaka umuti wa coronavirus.
Jeff Bezos, umukuru wa Amazon, yatanze imfashanyo ya miliyoni 100 z'amadolari ku magaburiro rusange (food banks) yo muri Amerika, mu gufasha abashonje muri iki gihe.
Mu kwezi kwa gatatu, Tim Cook ukuriye Apple yatangaje ko kompanyi ye izatanga imfashanyo y'ibikoresho byo mu buvuzi ku Butaliyani bwashegeshwe n'iyi virusi.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_52561064' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/52561064' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Niger yakiriye ‘wa muti' wa Madagascar
Abategetsi muri Niger ejo kuwa kabiri bakiriye umuzigo wa Covid Organics, umuti leta ya Madagascar ivuga ko uvura coronavirus.
Abategetsi muri Niger ejo kuwa kabiri bakiriye umuzigo wa Covid Organics, umuti leta ya Madagascar ivuga ko uvura coronavirus.
Umwe mu bakozi ba minisiteri y'ubuzima yaho yabwiye BBC ko uyu muti wakiriwe na Ismagail Annar umuyobozi muri minisiteri y'ubuzima nk'impano yoherejwe na Madagascar.
Uwo muti upfunyitse mu mashashi urahita uhabwa "abantu 900; muri abo 300 ni abarwaye naho 600 barawufata nko kubakingira" - ni ibivugwa n'uyu mukozi wa minisiteri y'ubuzima.
Kuva iki cyorezo cyagera muri Niger, abantu 755 nibo bayanduye naho 37 yarabishe.
Mu bo iyi ndwara yishe muri iki gihugu harimo uwari minisitiri w'umurimo Mohamed Ben Omar wapfuye ku cyumweru.
Covid-Organics ni umuti ukoze mu kimera kitwa Artemisia, ikimera gisanzwe gikoreshwa mu kuvura malaria, kivangwa n'ibindi bisanzwe bimera muri Madagascar mu gukora uyu muti.
Perezida Andry Rajoelina wa Madagascar yemeza ko uyu muti uvura iyi ndwara yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero, iterwa n'ubwoko bushya bwa coronavirus.
Ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye rishinzwe ubuzima ku isi, OMS/WHO, riburira abantu kwirinda gukoresha imiti itarapimwe.
Mu itangazo OMS yasohoye, ivuga ko "Abanyafurika bakwiye kubona imiti yabanje guca mu mageragezwa nyayo kabone niyo yaba ari imiti gakondo".
Uretse Niger yakiriye uyu muti ejo, Guinea-Bissau na Equatorial Guinea mu cyumweru gishize nabyo byakiriye kuri uwo muti.
Leta za Tanzania na Liberia nazo zivuga ko zasabye Madagascar kubaha kuri uwo muti.
Umuryango w'ubumwe bwa Afurika wasohoye itangazo rivuga ko uri gusaba amakuru arambuye Madagascar ngo upime niba uyu muti ntacyo utwaye kandi uvura coronavirus koko.
OMS ivuga ko kugeza ubu nta muti cyangwa urukingo bya coronavirus biraboneka.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-51993139' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-51993139' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Uganda yemeje umurwayi wa mbere wa Covid-19, Tanzania na DR Congo bariyongera
Leta ya Uganda yaraye itangaje umurwayi wa mbere wa coronavirus, iki gihugu kikaba kiri mu bya nyuma byo muri aka karere k'Afurika y'uburasirazuba byari bisigaye bitaragerwamo n'iki cyorezo.
Leta ya Uganda yaraye itangaje umurwayi wa mbere wa coronavirus, iki gihugu kikaba kiri mu bya nyuma byo muri aka karere k'Afurika y'uburasirazuba byari bisigaye bitaragerwamo n'iki cyorezo.
Uwo murwayi ni umugabo ukomoka muri Uganda w'imyaka 36 y'amavuko wageze ku kibuga cy'indege mpuzamahanga cya Entebbe avuye i Dubai.
Mbere yaho kuri uwo munsi w'ejo ku wa gatandatu, Perezida Yoweri Museveni wa Uganda yari yatangaje ingamba zikaze kurushaho ku mipaka yose y'iki gihugu, ingamba zijyanye no guhagarika ingendo.
Hagati aho, muri Tanzania abanduye coronavirus biyongereye bagera kuri 12 bavuye kuri 6, muri Repubulika ya Demokarasi ya Kongo naho bageze kuri 30 bavuye kuri 23.
Ubwo uwo mugabo yageraga ku kibuga cy'indege mpuzamahanga cya Entebbe, yahindaga umuriro mwinshi - nyuma ibizamini byo kwa muganga biza kwemeza ko arwaye coronavirus.
Abandi bagenzi bari kumwe na we muri iyo ndege ya kompanyi ya Ethiopian Airlines bashyizwe mu kato nkuko bikorwa nk'itegeko muri iki gihugu. Abategetsi bavuga ko abo bari kugenzurwa.
Ku mugoroba w'ejo ku wa gatandatu, Perezida Museveni yatangaje ko ingendo zose z'indege zitwara abagenzi zerekeza mu gihugu ziza guhagarikwa guhera saa sita z'ijoro zo kuri iki cyumweru.
Ingendo kandi zo ku butaka no mu mazi zambuka imipaka zizagabanywa ku buryo bukomeye, nkuko Bwana Museveni yabivuze. Indege zitwara imizigo ndetse n'imodoka z'amakamyo zo zemerewe gukomeza gukora.
Indege z'umuryango w'abibumbye n'iz'ubutabazi bwihuse zishobora kugera mu gihugu ariko zibanje guhabwa uruhushywa rw'umwihariko na leta ya Uganda.
Abategetsi bo muri Uganda bamaze igihe banengwa nyuma yaho abaturage bamwe n'abanyamahanga binubiye kuba babaho mu buzima bubi iyo bashyizwe muri ako kato abageze mu gihugu bashyirwamo by'itegeko.
Abo binuba bavuga ko hoteli bashyirwamo idafite ibikoresho bihagije, kandi bakaba ari bo biyishyurira.
Abandi bagenzi bamwe bagiye bashobora kunyura mu rihumye inzego z'umutekano n'izishinzwe gupima abinjira mu gihugu, ndetse bamwe mu basabwe kwishyira mu kato ntabwo bakurikije ayo mategeko, nkuko umunyamakuru wa BBC Catherine Byaruhanga uri i Kampala abivuga.
Jane Aceng, Minisitiri w'ubuzima wa Uganda, avuga ko ingendo nyinshi mu ngendo zerekeza mu gihugu zizahagarikwa kuko uburyo bwo gushyira mu kato butari gukora.
Nta gahunda ihari muri Uganda yo gupima Covid-19 - indwara yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero iterwa n'ubu bwoko bushya bwa coronavirus - abantu benshi kuko nta bushobozi buhagije igihugu gifite.
Kugeza kuri iki cyumweru, muri aka karere u Burundi ni bwo busigaye butaragerwamo na coronavirus.
Ni mu gihe mu Rwanda abarwayi bayo ari 17, muri Tanzania biyongereye bagera kuri 12 bavuye kuri 6, muri Repubulika ya Demokarasi ya Kongo naho bageze kuri 30 bavuye kuri 23 - n'umugabo imaze kwica muri iki gihugu.
Perezida John Magufuli yavuze ko umunani muri abo barwayi ari Abanyatanzania naho abandi bane basigaye ari abanyamahanga, avuga ko guhera ejo ku wa mbere, abasura Tanzania bose bavuye mu bihugu byiganjemo coronavirus bazajya bashyirwa mu kato k'iminsi 14 kandi ari bo birihira.
Bwana Magufuli yavuze ko iyo ngamba ireba n'Abanyatanzania basubira iwabo.
Bwana Magufuli, usanzwe asengera muri Kiliziya Gatolika, ubwo yari yagiye gusenga kuri iki cyumweru mu murwa mukuru Dodoma, yavuze ko kuri ubu amateraniro y'amadini azakomeza kubaho.
Ati: "Ntabwo dushobora kugamburuzwa n'iyi coronavirus ngo tunanirwe kurangamira Imana ngo tureke kandi no guteza imbere ubukungu bwacu".
"Iyi ndwara izacika nkuko izindi nyinshi zacitse. Ariko dukwiye gukomeza kwigengesera nkuko inzobere zikomeje kubitugiramo inama".
Leta ya Tanzania isanzwe yarafashe ingamba zo gufunga amashuri arimo na za kaminuza ndetse no guhagarika ibikorwa byose by'imikino mu gihe nibura cy'iminsi 30. Inama na zo zaraciwe.
Muri Kenya ho haracyari abarwayi 7.
Uwo mugabo wishwe na coronavirus muri DR Congo ku mugoroba wo ku wa gatanu, yari umuganga ukora mu biro bya minisitiri muri icyo gihugu, nkuko ibitangazamakuru byaho bibivuga.
Abo mu muryango we bavuze ko bayimusanzemo ku wa gatatu w'iki cyumweru, hashize iminsi 10 asubiye mu gihugu avuye mu rugendo mu Bufaransa aho yitabiriye igitaramo cy'umuhanzi Fally Ipupa ukomoka muri DR Congo.
Ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS/WHO) rivuga ko muri Afurika ubu hamaze kwemezwa abantu 1,117 banduye Covid-19 bari mu bihugu 42 by'Afurika.
Ku isi, abantu barenga 300,000 bamaze kuyandura, abarenga 13,000 imaze kubica naho abarenga 95,000 bamaze kuyikira.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52117329' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52117329' term='COVID'>
UNICEF ivuga ko DR Congo ihanganye n’indwara eshanu icyarimwe
Ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku bana (UNICEF) rivuga ko urwego rw'ubuzima muri Repubulika ya Demokarasi ya Kongo rucyeneye ubufasha bwihutirwa, bitihise ejo hazaza h'abana hakajya mu kaga.
Ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku bana (UNICEF) rivuga ko urwego rw'ubuzima muri Repubulika ya Demokarasi ya Kongo rucyeneye ubufasha bwihutirwa, bitihise ejo hazaza h'abana hakajya mu kaga.
Iki gihugu kigari kandi kirangwamo umutekano mucye, kiri kugorwa no guhangana n'indwara eshanu icyarimwe - malaria, iseru, cholera, coronavirus na Ebola iri kuhashira ubu.
Mu mwaka ushize, hatangajwe abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 16.5 barwaye malaria muri DR Congo.
Muri uwo mwaka kandi, iki gihugu cyanibasiwe n'icyorezo cy'iseru cya mbere kibi cyane ku isi - cyishe abana babarirwa mu bihumbi bafite munsi y'imyaka itanu y'amavuko
Cholera yo ikunze kugaragara muri iki gihugu, mu mwaka ushize abantu barenga 30,000 bakaba barayirwaye.
DR Congo kandi iri no kugerageza guhagarika ikiza cy'indwara ya Ebola mu burasirazuba.
Ako karere k'uburasirazuba bw'igihugu karangwamo imitwe y'inyeshyamba ibarirwa muri za mirongo, ndetse abaturage bagera kuri miliyoni imwe bataye izabo.
None ubu hari na Covid-19 - indwara yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero iterwa n'ubu bwoko bushya bwa coronavirus.
Nubwo umubare w'abamaze kuyandura urebye muri rusange ukiri hasi - abarwayi 98 kugeza kuri uyu wa gatatu, hari ubwoba bwuko ibintu byadogera mu gihe yaba ihashinze imizi.
UNICEF yasabye leta y'iki gihugu gikize ku mabuye y'agaciro gutera inkunga kurushaho urwego rw'ubuzima ruri gucumbagira.
Bitabaye ibyo, ni ko UNICEF ivuga, ubuzima bw'abana benshi bo muri DR Congo buzatsembatsembwa n'indwara ubundi zishobora kwirindwa.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_52147719' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/52147719' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: IMF yemereye u Rwanda inguzano ya miliyoni $109 yo kurwanya Covid-19
Ikigega mpuzamahanga cy'imari ku isi (IMF/FMI) cyatangaje ko nyuma y'ubusabe bw'u Rwanda cyemeje inguzanyo yihutirwa ya miliyoni $109 yo gufasha leta guhangana n'ingaruka z'icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Ikigega mpuzamahanga cy'imari ku isi (IMF/FMI) cyatangaje ko nyuma y'ubusabe bw'u Rwanda cyemeje inguzanyo yihutirwa ya miliyoni $109 yo gufasha leta guhangana n'ingaruka z'icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Inama y'ubutegetsi y'iki kigega yatangaje ko Covid-19 yahagaritse ubukungu bw'u Rwanda.
Ivuga ko ingamba zihuse za leta y'u Rwanda zo guhagarika ikwirakwira ry'iki cyorezo zagize ingaruka ku nzego zose z'ubukungu.
Ivuga kandi ko mu gihe hatazwi neza igihe iki cyorezo kizamara, ubukungu bushobora kuzahara kurushaho.
Kristalina Georgieva uyobora IMF/FMI yatangaje kuri Twitter ko yaganiriye na Perezida Paul Kagame akamubwira umuhate w'iki kigega mu gufasha Afurika guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Madamu Kristalina yavuze ko IMF yemeye ubusabe bw'u Rwanda bw'ariya mafaranga, kandi iki kigega vuba kizasubiza ku bundi busabe bwinshi gifite.
Covid-19 imaze kugera mu bihugu bigera kuri 50 bya Afurika aho abantu barenga 7,000 bamaze kuyandura.
Hari ubwoba ko iyi ndwara ishobora gukwira vuba kurushaho no kwica benshi mu bihugu byinshi bya Afurika bisanzwe bifite intege nke mu buvuzi.
Gusa abahanga bavuga ko hari n'ikizere kuko ibihugu byinshi bya Afurika byafashe ingamba zo kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'iki cyorezo hakiri kare.
Ubwoko bw'inguzanyo yihutirwa yahawe u Rwanda, ni inguzanyo itariho amabwiriza kandi yishyurwa nta nyungu nyuma nibura y'imyaka itanu cyangwa 10 nk'uko IMF ibivuga.
