Ejo kuwa kane nimugoroba nibwo Bwana Johnson yagaragaye imbere y'ibiro bye nawe akomera amashyi ibiro bishinzwe kurwanya iyi ndwara mu Bwongereza.
Mu ntangiriro z'uku kwezi, Nadine Dorries, umudepite akaba n'umuyobozi mukuru wo muri minisiteri y'ubuzima mu Bwongereza, bamupimye basanga afite coronavirus.
