Rwanda: Umugabo yafunzwe nyuma yo kuvuga ko avura coronavirus
Mu majyaruguru y'u Rwanda, urwego rukurikirana ibyaha ejo ku wa kabiri rwafunze umugabo watangaje amashusho kuri 'internet' avuga ko avura coronavirus.
Mu majyaruguru y'u Rwanda, urwego rukurikirana ibyaha ejo ku wa kabiri rwafunze umugabo watangaje amashusho kuri 'internet' avuga ko avura coronavirus.
Amashusho yari kuri YouTube y'uyu mugabo wo mu karere ka Musanze, yavugaga ko asanzwe ari "umuvuzi gakondo" kandi afite umuti uvura icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Aya mashusho yari amaze kurebwa inshuro zibarirwa mu bihumbi kugeza ku wa kabiri mu gitondo, kuva ejo yagizwe umwihariko aho atabonwa na bose uretse uwayashyizeho.
Marie Michelle Umuhoza, umuvugizi w'urwego rukurikirana ibyaha mu Rwanda (Rwanda Investigation Bureau), yabwiye BBC ko uyu mugabo yafashwe agafungwa.
Yagize ati: "Nibyo yatawe muri yombi, akekwaho icyaha cyo gukwirakwiza ibihuha no kwihesha ikintu cy'undi hakoreshejwe uburiganya".
Madamu Umuhoza avuga ko ubu hari gukorwa iperereza ku byaha uyu mugabo aregwa.
Michelle avuga ko uru rwego rugenza ibyaha mu Rwanda rutazihanganira abantu bose bashobora gukora ibyaha bitwaje iki cyorezo.
Ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima OMS (WHO) riburira abantu kwirinda amakuru adatanzwe n'inzego z'ubuvuzi zizewe muri iki gihe cy'icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Covid-19 ni imwe mu bwoko bwa virus zisanzwe zizwi ziswe coronavirus, iyi virus nta muti cyangwa urukingo rwayo biraboneka.
Ibimenyetso byayo ni inkorora, umuriro no guhumeka bigoranye, abaganga bavura ibi bimenyetso kugeza iyi virus ishize mu mubiri w'umuntu.
Abagera kuri 80% by'abayandura bashobora kuyikira nk'uko OMS ibivuga.
