Umugabo witwa Kitonyo yatawe muri yombi mu mujyi wa Mwingi mu burasirazuba bwa Kenya ashinjwa gutangaza amakuru y'impuha kuri coronavirus.
Perezida Uhuru Kenyatta wa Kenya yari aherutse kuburira Abanyakenya kwirinda gutangaza amakuru atari ukuri kuri Covid-19.
Uyu mugabo yafashwe kuri iki cyumewru nijoro n'abakozi b'ibiro bishinzwe iperereza ku byaha muri Kenya.
Arashinjwa gutangaza amakuru akoresheje 'account' itari nyayo (fake account) avuga ko leta yabeshye abaturage ku makuru y'umuntu wa mbere basanzemo iyi ndwara muri Kenya.
Ibyo yanditse byarakwirakwijwe henshi mu gihugu ku mbuga nkoranyambaga muri iyi weekend.
