Ubu arashinjwa gutangaza amakuru y'impuha agaca igikuba muri rubanda, araregwa hagendewe ku itegeko rihana ibyaha byifashishije mudasobwa ryo mu 2018.
Mu iyaduka n'ikwirakwira ry'iyi ndwara, abahanga mu buvuzi bavuga ko amakuru y'ibihuha ku buryo yandura, uko yirindwa, abayanduye n'ibindi ari bimwe mu bica igikuba mu baturage.
