<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52123688' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52123688' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Ibinyoma 5 bivugwa kuri Covid-19 muri Africa
Byinshi mu bihugu by'Afurika bikomeje kwiyongeramo ubwandu bushya bwa coronavirus, none ubu za leta zashyizeho ingamba zikomeye zirimo no kutegerana.
Byinshi mu bihugu by'Afurika bikomeje kwiyongeramo ubwandu bushya bwa coronavirus, none ubu za leta zashyizeho ingamba zikomeye zirimo no kutegerana.
Mu gihe izo leta zitegura ko ubwandu burushaho kwiyongera, amakuru ayobya nayo akomeje gukwirakwira kuri uyu mugabane.
Hari ubutumwa bwakwirakwiriye cyane ku mbuga nkoranyambaga buvuga ko Abanyafurika ari bo bazageragerezwaho urukingo rushya rwa coronavirus.
Ariko ayo makuru ntwabwo ari ukuri. Nta rukingo ruriho rwa Covid-19 - indwara yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero iterwa n'ubu bwoko bushya bwa coronavirus.
Amagerageza macye gusa y'imiti ku bantu ni yo ari gukorwa, kandi nta gerageza na rimwe muri ayo ubu riri gukorerwa mu bihugu by'Afurika.
Ntabwo tuzi neza aho ayo makuru ayobya yavuye, ariko akunze kwibanda ku kuntu ngo Abanyafurika bazahabwa urukingo ngo harebwe niba ntacyo ruzatwara ab'i Burayi n'Amerika.
Ubwoba abantu bamwe bagirira inkingo, si ikintu gishya kuko hari bamwe bakomeje kutizera ubuvuzi bugezweho.
Mu bice by'Afurika bimwe bivugwamo Igifaransa aho ibyo bihuha kuri Covid-19 byakwirakwiriye cyane, hanumvikanye impungenge no kuyobya nk'uko ku rukingo rwa Ebola.
Urwo rukingo kuri ubu ni rwo rwagize uruhare mu guhashya iyo ndwara ya Ebola.
Hari ibikomeje kuvugwa ku mbuga nkoranyambaga bijyanye n'uruhu rwirabura no kudakorwaho n'iyo ndwara.
Ku itariki ya 13 y'ukwezi gushize kwa gatatu, Minisitiri w'ubuzima wa Kenya yamaganye ibihuha byuko "abafite uruhu rwirabura badashobora kwandura coronavirus".
Twavuganye na Profeseri Thumbi Ndug'u wo ku ishuri ry'ubuvuzi bw'abantu rya Nelson R Mandela School of Medicine riri i Durban, kuri Kaminuza ya KwaZulu-Natal muri Afurika y'epfo.
Yavuze ko "nta gihamya na busa ihari yemeza icyo gitekerezo - ndetse mu by'ukuri, turabizi ko abantu bafite uruhu rwirabura bayandura".
Gukomeza kugira amazi mu mubiri ni ingenzi ku buzima bwawe, ariko kunywa icyayi cya mukaru ntabwo ari umuti uvura Covid-19 nkuko bamwe babivuze.
Nkuko bimwe mu bitangazamakuru byo muri Kenya byabitangaje, abantu bakomeje guhamagarwa kuri telefone bagirwa inama yo kunywa icyayi mu kwirinda coronavirus.
Ndetse ko ngo nibatabigenza gutyo bashobora kwicwa n'iyo virusi.
Ni inkuru imeze nk'umugani yakwirakwiriye n'ahandi, ariko idafite gihamya ishingiye ku buvuzi.
Abahanga mu bumenyi bwa siyansi ku isi bari gukora ubushakashatsi ku bishobora kuzavamo inkingo, ariko byitezwe ko nta rukingo ruzaboneka nibura atari hagati mu mwaka utaha.
Igishushanyo cyakozwe n'abo mu nzego z'ubuzima muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika kijyanye n'ubwanwa n'ibyuma byo guhumekeramo, ubu cyakoreshejwe nabi.
Mu buryo bwo kugoreka no kuyobya, ubu kiri kwifashishwa mu kuvuga ko abagabo bakwiye kogosha ubwanwa mu kwirinda kwandura coronavirus.
Ikinyamakuru Punch cyo muri Nigeria cyatangaje umutwe w'inkuru ugira uti:
"Mu kwirinda coronavirus, ugosha ubwanwa bwawe, ni ko CDC iburira".
Iyo foto-gishushanyo y'ikigo cy'Amerika cyo kurwanya indwara (CDC) igaragaza ingero zibarirwa muri za mirongo z'ubwanwa ndetse n'inyogosho yabwo yo kwirinda iyo wambaye icyo kugukingira mu maso (masque).
Hari inyogosho zimwe z'ubwanwa icyo kigo kivuga ko zabangamira iyo 'masque' bigatuma umurwayi adahumeka neza uko bikwiye.
Icyo gishushanyo ni umwimerere - ariko ni icyo mu mwaka wa 2017 (mbere cyane yuko coronavirus yaduka). Kigenewe abakozi bakora mu mirimo ituma bipfuka 'masques'.
Bitandukanye n'ibyatangajwe, ikigo CDC ntabwo cyatangaje icyo gishushanyo mu gihe cya vuba gishize ndetse icyo kigo ntabwo kigira abagabo inama yo kwiyogoshesha ubwanwa.
Nko mu Bwongereza, inama itangwa n'urwego rw'ubuzima ni uko nubwo 'masques' ari ingenzi ku baganga bari gukora mu bitaro, "hari gihamya nto cyane yuko hari akamaro kanini zifitiye rubanda".
Muri Nigeria, umuvugabutumwa yatangaje video n'inyandiko ku mbuga nkoranyambaga avuga ko isupu (sauce) y'urusenda ivura coronavirus. Ibyo byanatangajwe kuri WhatsApp.
Nta muti uriho uzwi wa coronavirus ndetse ibyo yatangaje bitanga amakuru macye ku bushobozi bwo kuvura bw'isupu y'urusenda.
Ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS/WHO) rivuga ko icyorezo cya coronavirus cyateje "icyorezo cy'amakuru" atari ukuri kandi agamije kuyobya.
OMS yongera kwibutsa ko gukaraba intoki neza kandi buri gihe ari ingenzi cyane mu rugamba rwo kwirinda kwandura coronavirus.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_52090693' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/52090693' term='COVID'>
Covid-19: Hari ivyo tutaramenya kuri uyu mugera
Umengo ni ikintu kimaze imyaka n'imyaka, ariko isi yaje kumenya coronavirus mu kw'icumi na kabiri guheze kw'umwaka uheze.
Umengo ni ikintu kimaze imyaka n'imyaka, ariko isi yaje kumenya coronavirus mu kw'icumi na kabiri guheze kw'umwaka uheze.
N'aho hari utwigoro tudasanzwe tw'abahinga kw'isi yose, haracariho ibintu bitari bike bataratahura.
Ng'ibi bimwe mu bibazo nyamukuru abantu bibaza:
Ico ni kimwe mu bibazo vya mbere abantu bibaza, ariko kandi kikaba kiri mu bibazo nyamukuru.
Turabwirwa ko abamaze kwemezwa ko banduye  baharurwa mu bihumbi amajana n'amajana kw'isi yose, ariko ico twomenya ico ni igice gitoya c'abantu bose bamaze kwandura uwo mugera.
Ivyo biharuro ntivyerekana abanduye, ariko ibimenyetso bitaratangura kwigaragaza, kandi nabo nyene bakaba ata ngorane bumva.
Kugira ngo tuzoshobore kumenya neza abanduye, ni uko abahinga batora uburyo bwo gupima inguvu z'abasoda b'umubiri. Aho niho tuzoshobora kumenya neza ingene coronavirus iriko irakwiragira.
Tutaramenya neza igitigiri nyezina c'abanduye, ntibishoboka ko tumenya urugero rw'abahitanwa n'uwo mugera.
Gushika ubu, bivugwa ko igice 1% c'abanduye ari bo bahasiga ubuzima. Ariko mu gihe hoba hari igitigiri kinini c'abanduye umugera ariko bakaba atabimenyetso berekana, urugero rw'abahitanwa n'uwomugera gishobora kuzoba ari gito.
Ibimenyetso nyamukuru vya coronavirus ni ubushuhe bwinshi, gucika inkokora, hamwe n'ugukorora - ibi nivyo wofatirako.
Ububabare mu muhogo,  kumeneka umutwe hamwe n'ugucibwamwo navyo ni ibimenyetso vyibonekeza kuri bamwe.
Ariko rero ikibazo nyamukuru ni ukumenya nimba hatoba hari ibindi bimenyetso bito bisa n'ivyo uwurwaye ibicurane, nk'ibiseru canke ukwasamura, buturutse kuri uwo mugera.
Ivyigwa vyerekana ko ivyo bishoboka, ivyo rero bigashobora gutuma abantu bashobora kwanduza abandi batazi ko bafise uwo mugera.
Abana nabo nyene barashobora kwandura coronavirus.
Hagati aho, abenshi berekana ibimenyetso bito, kandi n'abapfa ni na bake mu bana ugereranije n'iyindi mirwi ufatiye ku myaka.
Mu bisanzwe abana nibo bantu bakwiragiza indwara ku rugero runini, ahanini kubera usanga bivangatiranije n'abantu batandukanye, ariko kuri uyu mugera, ntibigaragara neza urugero rw'ingene bashobora gukwiragiza uwo mugera.
Uwo mugera watanguye kwibonekeza mu gisagara ca Wuhan mu Bushinwa, mu mpera za 2019, neza na neza mw'isoko ridandaza ibiva mu ruzi.
Coronavirus, izwi nka Sars-CoV-2, ifitaniye isano n'iyindi migera ifata uduhungarema, ariko bikavugwa ko utwo duhungarema twoba twashoboye kwandukiza ubundi bwoko bw'inyamaswa butaramenyekana neza, ari nazo rero zagiye kwandukiza abantu.
Ingene rero ivyo vyagenze gushika ubu ntibiramenyekana, ivyo bigashobora gutuma haba abandi bantu bandukirwa.
Indwara y'ibicurane irakunze kwibonekeza cane mu mezi y'urushana gusumba mu ci, ariko nta wuzi nimba ubushuhe bwo mu ci bushobora gutuma uwo mugera ugabanya ubukari.
Abahanuzi ba leta y'Ubwongereza mu vyo ubuhinga bagabisha ko bitaboneka neza nimba ibihe vyo mu ci bishobora guhindura ibintu. Mu gihe hoba igihinduka, biboneka ko hazoba ari ku rugero ruto ugeneranije n'ibicurane.
Mu gihe kandi hoba agahengwe kanini mu ci, hari ubwoba ko ibintu bishobora gusubira kuyangara mu rushana, aho mbere n'amavuriro aba ariko yakira ibitigiri binini vy'abarwaye indwara zitandukanye zizanana n'urushana.
Covid-19 iza bukebuke ku bantu batari bake. Ariko hafi ibice 20% bagenda babangamirwa gusumba, none vyoba biva kuki?
Kimwe mu nsiguro zotangwa ni ubushobozi bw'umubiri w'umuntu mu kwigwanira, ariko kandi hashobora kuba n'ibituma bishingiye ku kuntu umuntu aremwe.
Mu gihe ibi vyotahurika neza, bishobora gufasha mu gutora inzira yotuma abantu batabangamirwa cane.
Hari vyinshi bivugwa ariko nta vyemezo bifadika vyerekana ikiringo umubiri ushobora kumara wirwanira.
Iyo abarwayi bashoboye gukira, birumvikana ko abasoda b'umubiri baba bashoboye kwirwanira. Ariko mu gihe haciye amezi makeya gusa uwo mugera wibonekeje, nta makuru nyayo arashobora kuboneka.
Hariho amakuru avuga ko hari abarwayi bakize hanyuma bagasubira kwandura ubugira kabiri.
Ivyo bishobora kuva ku bipimo bitagenze neza bikabahenda ko bari bakize uwo mugera ariko atari vyo.
Ikibazo c'ubushobozi bw'abasoda b'umubiri kirakomeye kugira ngo umuntu amenye ibishobora kumubako muri kazoza.
Imigera igenda ihinduka umwanya wose, ariko iryo hinduka kuri kamere yayo nta kintu kinini rihindura.
Ikiriho ni uko imigera igenda ihinduka igatakaza inguvu uko umwanya ugenda, ariko ivyo ntawovyizera kuri coronavirus.
Impungenge zihari ni uko, mu gihe uwo mugera wohinduka, abasoda b'umubiri ntibasubira kuwumenya kandi mbere n'urucanco rworamuka rutowe ntirwoba rugikora (nk'uko bimeze ku ndwara y'akamangu).
</doc>
