Coronavirus: Urukundo rusesuye kuri uyu mukecuru n’umusaza no muri iki gihe cya Covid-19
Umukecuru n'umusaza bahindutse ibyamamare kubera ukuntu bahurira ku mupaka buri munsi, muri iki gihe isi ihanganye n'icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Umukecuru n'umusaza bahindutse ibyamamare kubera ukuntu bahurira ku mupaka buri munsi, muri iki gihe isi ihanganye n'icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Umukecuru Ingan Rasmussen w'imyaka 85 wo muri Denmark n'umusaza Karsten Tüchsen Hansen w'imyaka 89, bahurira hafi y'umujyi wa Aventoft wo mu Budage, buri munsi.
Bakaganira bakanasangira icyo kunywa, ari nako bubahiriza intera ya metero imwe hagati yabo, yagenwe n'inzego z'ubuzima.
Hashize ibyumweru bibiri umupaka ugabanya Ubudage na Denmark ufunzwe, mu kwirinda ikwirakwira rya coronavirus.
Iyi ni indwara imerera nabi kandi yica benshi mu bari mu zabukuru kurusha abakiri bato, ibi byatumye henshi ku isi bashishikarizwa kuguma mu ngo zabo no kwirinda cyane.
Ubudage bufite abarwayi bagera ku 63,000 bemejwe ko banduye iyo virusi, naho Denmark yo ifite abarenga 2,500.
Akarere k'u Burayi ka Schengen - gatuma abatuye mu bihugu bikagize batembera nta nkomyi bava mu gihugu kimwe bajya mu kindi - ariko ubu siko bikimeze.
Mu bihugu bimwe byo muri ako karere ka Schengen, ibyo ni bwo bwa mbere bibaye mu myaka 25 ishize. Bavaga mu gihugu kimwe bajya mu kindi nkaho ari igihugu kimwe.
Ariko uyu mukecuru n'umusaza ntibazareka iki cyorezo cyugarije isi ngo kibabuze guhura.
Umukecuru Rasmussen yabwiye igitangazamakuru cya rubanda cyo mu Budage, Deutsche Welle, ati:
"Birababaje, ariko ntidushobora kubihindura".
Bombi bamaze kumenyekana cyane muri ako gace muri iki gihe cy'icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Ni nyuma yaho umuyobozi w'akarere ko mu mujyi waho wa Tonder, muri Denmark, ahabasanze ubwo yari ari kunyonga igare.
Uwo mukecuru n'umusaza bamenyanye mu myaka ibiri ishize, ndetse bamaze umwaka urenga baba bari kumwe hafi buri munsi.
Umukecuru Rasmussen atwara imodoka ye akava mu mujyi atuyemo wa Gallehus, mu gihe umusaza Hansen we anyonga igare rye akava mu mujyi wa Süderlügum.
Iyo bahuye, rimwe na rimwe uwo musaza yinywera ikirahure kimwe cy'inzoga ya 'schnapps'.
Umukecuru Rasmussen we buri gihe anywa ikawa gusa.
Yabwiye ikinyamakuru Der Nordschleswiger cyo muri Denmark ati:
"Cyane ko mba ngomba gutwara imodoka".
Rasmussen n'umusaza Hansen bagiye batemberana mu bihe byashize, ndetse bafite gahunda yo kongera gutemberana iki cyorezo cya coronavirus nikirangira.
Ni bamwe mu bakundana batahuye uburyo bushya bwo gukomeza umubano wabo muri iki cyorezo.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52343076' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52343076' term='COVID'>
Covid-19 yoba igihe gutuma ama ‘robots’ asubirira abantu ku kazi?
Mu gihe ikiza ca coronavirus ciganziye isi yose, abahinga babona ko ama robots agiye gukora akazi kokozwe n'umuntu.
Mu gihe ikiza ca coronavirus ciganziye isi yose, abahinga babona ko ama robots agiye gukora akazi kokozwe n'umuntu.
Iyo migambi yari isanzwe ihari, ariko iki kiza catumye umurindi wongerekana.
Martin Ford, umuhinga aherutse kwandika igitabo yerekana ingene ama robots azokoreshwa mu ikorwa vy'ubutunzi, avuga ati:
"Abantu mu bisanzwe bipfuza ko umuntu ari we yobakurikirana kugira ngo abaremeshe, ariko rero Covid-19 iriko irabihindura".
"Covi-19 igiye gutuma ivyipfuzo vy'umuntu bihinduka".
Amakompanyi yaba manini canke mato  ariko arakomeza ikoreshwa ry'ama robots mu ntumbero yo gufasha abantu kudakoranako be no kugabanya igitigiri c'abakozi batonda ku kazi.
Ayo ma robots kandi ariko arakoreshwa mu bikorwa abakozi badashobora gukorera muhira.
Akarorero no nko muri Koreya y'Ubumanuko aho ama robots ariko arakoreshwa mu bupima ubushuhe be no gutanga imiti yo kwica imigera.
Mu gihe abahinga muvyo amagara y'abantu bavuga ko mu 2021 bishobora kuba ngombwa ko hafatwa ingingo zo kudakoranako, ama robots ashobora gukenerwa cane gusumba.
Ubu hari amakompanyi atari make akora ibikoresho vy'isuku n'imiti yo kwica imigera ariko aragura ama robots ku rugero runini.
Eka n'amaduka canke amazu y'uburiro agurisha imfungurwa zitekerwa ariko arakoresha cane ama robots.
Abahinga bavuga ko mu gihe ibikorwa vy'ukwiyungunganya bibandanya vyongerekana, abantu bokwitega mu minsi iri imbere ikoreshwa ry'ubu buhinga, aho abantu bazotangazwa no kubona ama robots ariko arakoropa amashure canke ibiro.
Blake Morgan, umwanditsi w'igitabo yise The Customer of the Future, ati: "Muri kino gihe, abakiriya bashira imbere umutekano wabo, umutekano n'ubuzima bw'abakozi babo".
Hagati aho, haracari inzitizi. Umupfasoni Morgan abona ko ari vyo ko ikoreshwa ry'ama robots rishobora gutuma abantu badakoranako, ariko ko kubera ivyo vyuma bitama bikora neza canke bigakunda gupfa, abakiriya bashima kwegera abantu kugira ngo babatunganirize.
Hariho igihe umuntu azoba akenewe kuronka inyigisho kanaka canke insiguro y'ibintu kanaka.
Nico gituma ubu bariko bahingura ivyuma bikoresha ubwenge bwa kiremwa muntu, bishobora gusubirira umwigisha kw'ishure, mu myimenyerezo y'ukwinonora imitsi eka mbere no mu kzigisha ibijanye n'ikoreshwa ry'amafaranga.
Ubu hari n'amakompanyi manini ariko arakwiragiza izo mashini zikoresha ubwenge nk'ubw'abantu.
Akarorero ni nka Facebook na Google zikoresha cane ubwo buhinga mu guhiga no gufuta amakuru mabi acishijwe kuri izo mbuga kubera abakozi b'izo kompanyi hari ivyo badashobora kubona mu gihe bakorera muhira.
</doc>
