Coronavirus: Umuntu wa mbere yayikize muri Kenya, Leta yagabanyije imisoro
Byatangajwe na Perezida Uhuru Kenyatta mu ijambo yagejeje ku gihugu, ntabwo yavuze umwirondoro w'uwakize iyi ndwara, gusa yavuze ko ari amakuru meza kuri iki gihugu.
Byatangajwe na Perezida Uhuru Kenyatta mu ijambo yagejeje ku gihugu, ntabwo yavuze umwirondoro w'uwakize iyi ndwara, gusa yavuze ko ari amakuru meza kuri iki gihugu.
Kenya ubu ifite abantu 28 bamaze kwandura iyi ndwara, harimo batatu bashya batangajwe ejo na Bwana Kenyatta.
Birakekwa ko uwakize iyi ndwara ari mu bantu batangajwe bwa mbere ko bayanduye muri Kenya.
Abahanga mu buvuzi bavuga ko umuntu ufite ibimenyetso bidakabije ashobora gukira iyi virus mu byumweru bibiri.
Umuntu wa mbere yabonywemo iyi ndwara muri Kenya tariki 12/03/2020 bitangazwa na minisiteri y'ubuzima yaho tariki 13/03/2020.
Bwana Kenyatta ko mu gihugu hose guhera kuwa gatanu, kuva saa moya z'umugoroba (7PM) kugeza saa kumi n'imwe za mugitondo (5AM) hazajya haba umukwabu.
Uyu mukwabu (curfew) ugamije gutegeka abantu kuguma mu ngo zabo mu rwego rwo kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'iyi ndwara.
Perezida Kenyatta yatangaje kandi ivanwaho ry'imisoro yose ku bantu bahembwa amadorari $240 ku kwezi (ni arenga gato 200,000Frw), naho abandi bakajya bishyura umusoro ungana na 5% gusa.
Leta yagabanyije kandi imisoro ku mitungo ndetse n'umusoro ku nyongera gaciro (TVA), ibi bigatangira gukurikizwa kuva tariki 01/04/2020.
Hejuru y'ibi, Bwana Kenyatta yatangaje ko ku bushake bwe, n'abandi bategetsi bakuru bemeye gutanga ku mushahara wabo kugira ngo batere inkunga ikigega cyo kurwanya Covid-19.
Perezida Kenyatta na Visi Perezida William Ruto batanga 80% y'umushahara wabo mu gihe abagize guverinoma bo bazagabanya 30% ku mushahara wabo.
Yanatangaje ko leta yagennye miliyoni $100 z'amadorari yo kugoboka abakennye kurusha abandi bari kugirwaho ingaruka n'iyi ndwara, abantu bakuze ndetse n'impfubyi.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52423644' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52423644' term='COVID'>
Ubushinwa bwanze ko hakorwa iperereza mpuzamahanga ku nkomoko ya Covid-19
Ubushinwa bwanze ubusabe bwuko hakorwa iperereza mpuzamahanga ryigenga ku nkomoko y'iki cyorezo cya coronavirus cyugarije isi muri iki gihe.
Ubushinwa bwanze ubusabe bwuko hakorwa iperereza mpuzamahanga ryigenga ku nkomoko y'iki cyorezo cya coronavirus cyugarije isi muri iki gihe.
Chen Wen, umudiplomate w'Ubushinwa wo ku rwego rwo hejuru muri ambasade yabwo mu Bwongereza, yabwiye BBC ko ubwo busabe bushingiye ku mpamvu za politike.
Yongeyeho ko byarangaza Ubushinwa mu rugamba burimo bwo kurwanya iki cyorezo.
Amakuru ku nkomoko ya Covid-19 - indwara yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero iterwa n'ubu bwoko bushya bwa coronavirus - n'uburyo yakwirakwiriye mu ntangiriro, ashobora gufasha ibihugu mu kuyirwanya.
Byibazwa ko iyi virusi yakomotse mu isoko ricuruza ibikomoka mu mazi ryo mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa mu mpera y'umwaka ushize.
Hagati aho, icyegeranyo cy'umuryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi (EU/UE) gishinja Ubushinwa gukwirakwiza amakuru ayobya ajyanye n'iki cyorezo.
Ikigo cya EU gikurikirana ibikorwa byo hanze (External Action Service) kivuga ko Uburusiya, n'Ubushinwa ku kigero gito, "byohereje amakuru ayobya" muri EU no mu bihugu bihana imbibi nayo.
Perezida Donald Trump wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika na we yakomeje kugenda yibasira Ubushinwa ku buryo bwitwaye kuri iki cyorezo.
Ndetse na leta ya Missouri - imwe mu zigize Amerika - igiye kurega mu nkiko leta y'Ubushinwa, iyishinja kuba ari nkaho ntacyo yakoze mu guhagarika ikwirakwira ry'iyi virusi.
Abahanga mu bumenyi bwa siyansi bagiye bamagana amakuru ahwihwisa ko ubu bwoko bushya bwa coronavirus bwakorewe mu kigo cy'ubushakashatsi (laboratoire) cyo mu mujyi wa Wuhan.
Bavuga ko nta gihamya ishingiye kuri siyansi ihari kugeza ubu ibyemeza.
Nta kanya karashira iki cyorezo cyadutse, habayeho ubusabe bwuko abapererezi mpuzamahanga bakwemererwa kujya mu Bushinwa ngo batahure ukuntu cyatangiye.
Ku wa kane w'iki cyumweru, Minisitiri w'intebe wa Australia Scott Morrison yavuze ko mu nama ngarukamwaka yo mu kwezi gutaha y'urugaga rw'isi rw'ubuzima, azaharanira ko habaho iperereza ku nkomoko y'iyi coronavirus.
Uru rwego (World Health Assembly) ni rwo rufata ibyemezo mu ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS/WHO). Australia ni kimwe mu bihugu bigize inama nkuru y'ubuyobozi bwarwo.
Uru rwego rwamaze kuvuga ko rufite gahunda yo kungurana ibitekerezo ku "masomo yigiwe" muri iki cyorezo mu nzego z'ubutabazi bwihuse.
Ariko Madamu Chen, wa mudiplomate w'Ubushinwa ukorera mu Bwongereza, yabwiye BBC ko igihugu cye kidashobora kwemera ko hakorwa iperereza mpuzamahanga.
Yagize ati: "Iperereza ryigenga rishingiye ku mpamvu za politike".
"Turimo kurwanya iyi virusi muri iki gihe, ibikorwa byacu byose biri kwibanda ku kurwanya iyi virusi. Kuki havugwa ku kubikoraho iperereza? Ibi bizarangaza atari gusa [twebwe], ahubwo n'uburyo bw'amikoro buri gukoreshwa".
"Iyi ni gahunda ishingiye kuri politike, ntekereza ko nta muntu n'umwe wabyemera... Nta n'umwe byagira icyo bimarira na gito".
Madamu Chen yavuze ko hari ibihuha byinshi biri guhwihwiswa ku nkomoko ya coronavirus, ariko ko amakuru nkayo ayobya ateje ikibazo gikomeye.
Yavuze ko ayo makuru y'ibihuha ameze nka virusi ya politike mbi cyo kimwe na coronavirus ubwayo, niba ahubwo atanayirusha ubukana.
Umunyamakuru wa BBC Gordon Corera ukurikiranira hafi inkuru zivuga ku mutekano, avuga ko ibihugu by'i Burayi biri kwigengesera byirinda kurakaza Ubushinwa muri iki gihe gikomeye.
Ibi bihugu bicyenera cyane ibikoresho by'ingenzi bivuye mu Bushinwa byo gufasha mu guhangana na coronavirus.
Gusa muri Amerika ho, ikibazo cy'Ubushinwa gikomeje kugarukwaho n'abanyapolitike muri uyu mwaka uzabamo amatora ya perezida w'Amerika, hasabwa ko Ubushinwa bwotswa igitutu ngo bwemere ko hakorwa iperereza ku nkomoko ya coronavirus.
</doc>
