Coronavirus: Trump yategetse uruganda General Motors 'rw'imburamukoro' gukora 'ventilateurs'
Perezida Donald Trump wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika yategetse uruganda rukora imodoka rwa General Motors (GM) gukora ibikoresho byongera ubuhehere n'umuyaga mu nzu (ventilators/ventilateurs) byo gufasha abarwayi ba coronavirus.
Perezida Donald Trump wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika yategetse uruganda rukora imodoka rwa General Motors (GM) gukora ibikoresho byongera ubuhehere n'umuyaga mu nzu (ventilators/ventilateurs) byo gufasha abarwayi ba coronavirus.
Bwana Trump yabitegetse nyuma yo kwibasira umuyobozi mukuru w'urwo ruganda rukora imodoka rwo muri Amerika.
Yafashe icyo cyemezo ashingiye ku itegeko ryagiyeho mu gihe cy'intambara yo muri Koreya rizwi nka 'Defense Production Act', riha ububasha perezida bwo gutegeka amakompanyi gukora ibikoresho ku bw'umutekano w'igihugu.
Bwana Trump yavuze ko "GM iri guta igihe" muri ibi bihe hacyenewe kugira igikorwa mu kurokora ubuzima bw'Abanyamerika.
Ibikoresho byo mu buvuzi bituma abarwayi ba Covid-19 - indwara y'ubuhumekero iterwa n'ubu bwoko bushya bwa coronavirus - bashobora guhumeka, biri gucyenerwa cyane muri iki gihe muri Amerika.
Ni yo mpamvu hari kwifashishwa na 'ventilateurs' mu kunganira ibikoresho bisanzwe by'ubuvuzi bw'iyo ndwara yibasira ibihaha.
Kugeza ubu muri Amerika habarurwa abarwayi 104,000 banduye coronavirus, bakaba ari bo benshi cyane ku isi.
Mu gihe muri iki gihugu abagera hafi ku 1,700 imaze kubica, uwo mubare uracyari inyuma y'abo imaze kwica mu Butaliyani no mu Bushinwa.
Mbere, Bwana Trump yari yavuze ko kwitabaza iryo tegeko ryo mu gihe cy'intambara yo muri Koreya bishobora kutazaba ngombwa, kubera ko amakompanyi ari kwibwiriza agahindura ibyo yari asanzwe akora, mu gufasha kurwanya ikwirakwira rya coronavirus.
Ariko ku munsi w'ejo ku wa gatanu, Bwana Trump yasohoye itangazo agira ati:
"Iyi virusi irihutirwa cyane kuburyo hatakurikizwa uburyo busanzwe..."
Mbere yaho ku munsi w'ejo ku wa gatanu, Bwana Trump yanditse kuri Twitter ko uruganda rwa GM rwagabanyije umubare wa 'ventilateurs' rwari rwemeye gukora, uva ku 40,000 ugera ku 6,000 kandi ko rwifuje "igiciro cyo hejuru".
Yananenze Mary Barra, umuyobozi mukuru w'urwo ruganda, avuga ko ibintu "buri gihe biba ari akavuyo" mu buyobozi bwe bw'urwo ruganda rw'imodoka rufite icyicaro mu mujyi wa Detroit.
Uruganda GM ejo ku wa gatanu rwatangaje ko rushobora gukora 'ventilateurs' zigera ku 10,000 ku kwezi, guhera mu kwezi gutaha kwa kane.
Nkuko bitangazwa na Kaminuza ya Johns Hopkins yo muri Amerika, kugeza ku munsi w'ejo ku wa gatanu, ku isi hari abarwayi barenga 540,000 ba coronavirus, naho abagera ku 24,000 yari imaze kubica. Abandi 124,000 barayikize.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-51765110' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-51765110' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: U Burundi bugiye gushyira bamwe mu kato, u Rwanda rusaba 'kugabanya ingendo zitari ngombwa'
Leta y'u Burundi yatangaje ko guhera uyu munsi abagenzi bajya mu Burundi bavuye mu bihugu bimwe birimo coronavirus bashyirwa mu kato k'iminsi 14 bakurikiranwa mu kwirinda ko igera mu Burundi, u Rwanda rusaba abaturage "kugabanya ingendo zitari ngombwa" mu bihugu irimo.
Leta y'u Burundi yatangaje ko guhera uyu munsi abagenzi bajya mu Burundi bavuye mu bihugu bimwe birimo coronavirus bashyirwa mu kato k'iminsi 14 bakurikiranwa mu kwirinda ko igera mu Burundi, u Rwanda rusaba abaturage "kugabanya ingendo zitari ngombwa" mu bihugu irimo.
Ibihugu byombi byatangaje ko nta muntu wari wabigaragaramo wanduye ubu bwoko bushya bwa coronavirus.
Mu itangazo yanyujije kuri radio na televiziyo y'u Burundi (RTNB) ejo ku wa kane, Minisitiri w'ubuzima Thaddée Ndikumana yavuze ko abo bazajya bashyirwa mu kato bakigera ku kibuga mpuzamahanga cy'indege cyitiriwe Melchior Ndadaye cy'i Bujumbura.
Abo ni abavuye mu Bushinwa, Koreya y'epfo, Iran, Ubutaliyani, Ubudage, Ubufaransa, Ubuyapani na Espanye.
Ku isi abategetsi bamaze kwemeza ko abantu barenga 92,000 bamaze kwandura coronavirus - itera indwara yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero izwi nka Covid-19, muri abo abarenga 80,000 bakaba ari abo mu Bushinwa.
Ku isi kandi abantu barenga 3,000 imaze kubica, benshi muri bo bakaba ari abo mu Bushinwa aho iyo virusi yatangiriye.
Kuri uyu wa gatanu, u Rwanda rwatangaje ko rumaze iminsi rwarashyizeho itsinda ryo "gusesengura no gukurikirana" uko rwiteguye "gukumira no guhangana" na coronavirus.
Mu ruhererekane rw'ubutumwa bwo ku rubuga rwa Twitter, ibiro bya minisitiri w'intebe w'u Rwanda byibukije Abanyarwanda ko iyo virusi ntayirangwa mu gihugu kugeza ubu.
Ubwo butumwa bwongeraho buti:
"Icyakora dukurikije ubukana bw'iki cyorezo n'uburyo gikomeje guhitana umubare munini w'abantu ku isi, turasaba abanyarwanda kutirara no gukurikiza inama zo kwirinda iki cyorezo zitangwa n'inzego zitandukanye".
Muri izo nama nkuko ibyo biro bya minisitiri w'intebe w'u Rwanda bibitangaza, harimo nko kwirinda kuramukanya abantu bahana ikiganza cyangwa bahoberana kubera ko yandurira mu matembabuzi aturuka mu guhumeka, mu gukorora, kwitsamura n'ibindi.
Harimo  kandi no gukaraba intoki hakoreshejwe amazi asukuye n'isabune cyangwa ubundi buryo bwo gusukura intoki no kwirinda kwegera abandi mu gihe cyose urwaye ibicurane, inkorora cyangwa ufite umuriro mwinshi.
Mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru ku munsi w'ejo, umukuru w'ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS/WHO) yavuze ko riri hafi gutangaza urutonde rw'ibihugu bikiri inyuma mu myiteguro y'igihe coronavirus yaba ibigaragayemo.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52422955' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52422955' term='COVID'>
Ubucuruzi bumwe bwongeye gukora muri Amerika mu gihe abishwe na Covid-19 barenze 50,000
Umubare w'abamaze kwicwa na coronavirus muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika wamaze kurenga 51,000, nkuko bigaragazwa n'imibare ya Kaminuza ya Johns Hopkins.
Umubare w'abamaze kwicwa na coronavirus muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika wamaze kurenga 51,000, nkuko bigaragazwa n'imibare ya Kaminuza ya Johns Hopkins.
Iki ni cyo cyorezo cya coronavirus cya mbere kibi cyane kibayeho ku isi.
Muri abo iyi virusi imaze kwica muri Amerika, abarenga 3,000 yabishe mu masaha 24 ashize. Ubu muri iki gihugu habarurwa abantu barenga 870,000 bemejwe ko banduye coronavirus.
Ariko Amerika iracyafite ikigero kiri hasi cy'abicwa n'iyi virusi ugereranyije na byinshi mu bihugu byo ku mugabane w'Uburayi ugendeye ku bamaze kubarurwa, nkuko byashimangiwe n'itsinda ryo kurwanya coronavirus ryo mu biro bya perezida w'Amerika bya White House.
Aya makuru ateye inkeke atangajwe mu gihe ibice bimwe by'Amerika byongeye gusubira mu buzima busanzwe nyuma yo kumara igihe mu bihe by'akato.
Inzu zitunganya imisatsi zimwe na zimwe zo muri leta za Georgia na Oklahoma zishobora kongera gufungura imiryango, naho leta ya Alaska yo yongeye guha impushya zo gukora za 'restaurants'.
Gusa hari ababurira ko hakiri kare cyane.
Kugeza ubu Amerika ni yo ifite umubare munini cyane ku isi w'abamaze kwicwa na Covid-19 - indwara yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero iterwa n'ubu bwoko bushya bwa coronavirus - ndetse n'abanduye ba mbere benshi ku isi.
Ariko, Amerika ituwe n'abaturage miliyoni 330, baruta cyane abo mu bindi bihugu nka Espagne n'Ubutaliyani byibasiwe cyane na coronavirus.
Dr Deborah Birx, inzobere yo mu itsinda ryo kurwanya coronavirus ryo muri White House, yavuze ko iki gihugu gifite "rumwe mu ngero nto cyane z'abo yica ku isi yose".
Ugendeye ku mubare w'abaturage, umubare w'abishwe na coronavirus umaze gutangazwa muri Amerika uri hasi ugereranyije n'uw'abo imaze kwica muri Espagne, Ubutaliyani, Ubufaransa, Ububiligi n'Ubwongereza.
Ukwiyongera kw'umubare wa buri munsi w'abicwa na coronavirus muri Amerika, ku ruhande rumwe kandi byatewe no kongeraho impfu "bishoboka ko" zatewe na coronavirus.
Ku itariki ya 14 y'uku kwezi kwa kane, ikigo cy'Amerika cyo kurwanya indwara cyatangaje ko umubare w'iki gihugu w'abapfuye uzajya wongerwamo abemejwe ko bazize na coronavirus ndetse n'abacyekwa ko ari yo bazize.
Urupfu rucyekwa ko rwatejwe na Covid-19 ni urwujuje ibimenyetso by'iyi ndwara ariko bikaba bitaremejwe n'ipimwa ryo muri 'laboratoire'.
Ni n'ingenzi ariko kuvuga ko impfu nyinshi zatewe na Covid-19 itarakara cyane ngo igaragaze ibimenyetso na n'ubu zitaratangazwa.
Rero ikigero cy'abapfuye gishingiye ku bemejwe ko ari yo bazize ntabwo gihuye n'abo yishe bose muri rusange muri iki gihugu.
Ibikorwa byo gupima ni ingenzi mu kumenya by'ukuri uko abo iyi virusi imaze kwica bangana ndetse n'uburyo ubwandu buri gukwirakwira.
Visi Perezida w'Amerika Mike Pence, ukuriye itsinda ryo muri White House ryo kurwanya coronavirus, yavuze ko Amerika imaze gupima abaturage 4.9 kugeza ubu, kandi iri gukorana na ba guverineri mu kongera uwo mubare w'abapimwa.
Umushinga w'itegeko ry'inkunga y'ingoboka mu bukungu ingana na miliyari 484 z'amadolari, ryatowe n'inteko ishingamategeko ku wa kane, rikubiyemo no gutera inkunga no kwagura ibikorwa byo gupima.
Ni inkunga ya kane yemejwe n'ubutegetsi bw'Amerika ijyanye na Covid-19. Ndetse iteganya no kugoboka ibitaro no gutanga inguzanyo ku bucuruzi buciriritse.
Ejo ku wa gatanu Perezida Donald Trump yashyize umukono kuri uwo mushinga w'itegeko uhita uhinduka itegeko, avuga ko ashaka "kwihutisha kugoboka mu bukungu abaturage bacu".
</doc>
