<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52336372' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52336372' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: OMS ifise impungenge ko Afrika ishobora kuba ikiririmbiro rishasha
Umuryango ujejwe amagara y'abantu kw'isi OMS/WHO uragabisha ko umugabane wa Afrika ushobora kuba ikiririmbiro rishasha rya wa mugera w'icaduka coronavirus.
Umuryango ujejwe amagara y'abantu kw'isi OMS/WHO uragabisha ko umugabane wa Afrika ushobora kuba ikiririmbiro rishasha rya wa mugera w'icaduka coronavirus.
Abategesti ba ONU bamenyesha kandi ko ico kiza gishobora kwirahira abantu baharurwa mu bihumbi 300 muri Afrika, nayo abashika imiliyoni 30 bagashobora gusigara mu kangaratete.
Mu ndwi iheze, ibiharuro vy'abanduye coronavirus kuri uyo mugabane vyariyongereye bidasanzwe.
Gushika ubu, hafi abashika 1000 baramaze guhitanwa n'uwo mugera, mu gihe abashika ku 19.000 bamaze kuwandura, ibitigiri biri hasi cane ugereranije n'ibirangwa mu bice bimwe bimwe vya Bulaya na Amerika.
Umurwi wa ONU ujejwe ibibazo vy'ubutunzi muri Afrika - ari nawo wagabishije ko abashika ibihumbi 300 bashobora gupfa - wasavye ko hotegurwa amafaranga ashika imiliyoni 100 y'amadorari yo guha uwo mugabane, harimwo kandi n'ingingo yo guhagarika amadeni yo hanze.
OMS ivuga ko uwo mugera usa n'uwuriko urakwiragira hanze y'ibisagara.
Ivuga kandi ko uwo mugabane ubuze ibikoresho nyamukuru, nk'ibikoresho bifasha abarwaye guhema.
Abarenga ica gatatu c'abanyagihugu ba Afrika nta mazi meza bafise, mu gihe hafi ibice 60% vy'ababa mu gisagara baba begeranye cane - ivyo navyo bigatuma umugera ushobora kukwirakwira cane.
Gushika ubu abashika 19.000 baramaze gutangazwa ko banduye  coronavirus muri Afrika nzima, nayo abashika 970 bakaba aribo bamaze kumenyekana ko yabahitanye kuri uyo mugabane wose utuwemwo n'abantu hafi umuliyaridi 1.3.
Akarere ka Afrika y'uburaruko niko kabangamiwe . Alijeriya, Mirisi na Maroke bifise kimwe kimwe cose abarenga 2000 bamaze kwandura, hamwe n'imiburiburi 100 bamaze kuhasiga ubuzima. Alijeriya nico gihugu kimaze kubura benshi, abashika 348.
Mu bundi burere, Afrika y'Epfo nayo nyene ifise abarenga 2000 bamaze kuyandura, hamwe na 48 bamaze gupfa, mu gihe igihugu gifise abantu benshi gusumba ibindi muri Afrika, ari co Nijeriya, kimaze guharura abantu 442 bamaze kuyandura hamwe na 13 bamaze gupfa ku banyagihugu bashika imiliyoni 200.
Raba ikarata y'ingene coronavirus yifashe muri Afrika
Uwuserukira OMS muri Afrika Dr Matshidiso Moeti yabwiye BBC ko ingendo mpuzamakungu zifise uruhara rukomeye mw'ikwirakwira ry'uwo mugera.
Avuga ati: "Uravye urugero rw'abantu bafata ingendo, Afrika ifise abantu bake cane bafata ingendo mpuzamakungu".
Hagati aho, mu gihe uwo mugera wamaze gushika muri Afrika, avuga ko umuryango aserukira uriko ukora utiziganya kuko uzi ko uwo mugera ushobora gukwiragira ku muvuduko munini cane gusumba ahandi.
OMS iramaze kubona ko uwo mugera uriko urakwiragira uva mu bisagara binini uja hagati mu gihugu mu bihugu vya Afrika y'Epfo, Nijeriya, Cote d'Ivoire, Kameruni na Ghana, nk'uko bivugwa na Dr. Moeti.
Hari ibihugu bishika 15 vya Afrika uwo mugera utarashika kure gushika ubu, akizera ko mu gihe ivyo bihugu vyofata ingingo zikomeye zituma abantu bareka kwegerana, vyoshobora gutuma ivyo bihugu biwuhagarika.
OMS ifise ubwoba ko mu mezi atatu gushika kuri atandatu ari imbere abarenga imiliyoni 10 bashobora kwandura uwo mugera, ariko ivyo biharuro bikaba bidafatira ku ngingo zijanye n'isuku zigenda zirafatwa.
None vyogenda gute mu gihe uwo mugera worandagara hagati mu gihugu muri Afrika?
Mu gihe Covid-19 yoshinga imizi kuri uwo mugabane, inkurikizi zoba umurengera gusumba izibonekeza i Bulaya na Amerika, nk'uko bivugwa n'umunyamakuru wa BBC mu gisata c'amagara y'abantu.
OMS ivuga ko mu bihugu hafi vyose vya Afrika usanga hari ibitanda hafi bitanu gusa vyo kuvurirako indembe ku bantu umuliyoni wose, igitigiri kiri hasi cane rwose ugereranije n'I Bulaya, aho hari ibitanda 4000 ku bantu umuliyoni.
Dr. Moeti avuga ko OMS ishira imbere ugukinga uwo mugera hakurondera kuvura, kubera ibihugu vyinshi va Afrika bidafise ubushobozi bwo kuvura abarwayi benshi ba coronavirus.
Ati:"Dushaka ko ibitigiri vy'abakenera kuvurirwa mu bibanza vy'indembe biguma hasi, kuko tuzi neza ko mu bihugu vyinshi vya Afrika ubu buryo atabwo bifise".
Dr. Moeti avuga ko "imwe mu ngorane nyamukuru" ibihugu vya Afrika bifise ari ubukene bwa vya vyuma bifasha guhema abariko baravurwa uwo mugera.
Ku barwaye Covid-19 baremvye, kubura ivyo bikoresho ni nk'urupfu.
Mu gihe indembe zidashobora guhema neza zo nyene ukwazo, ivyo vyuma nivyo vyinjiza impwemu nziza (oxygène) mu mahaha bigasohora impwemu mbi (gaz carbonique) mu mubiri.
Umwe mu bantu bahitanywe n'uwo mugera ubwa mbere muri AFrika yari umumenyeshamakuru wa Zimbabwe Zororo Makamba, hari mu kwa gatatu.
Abategetsi b'umugwa mukuru Harare, bavuga ko vyatumwe n'uko batari bwaronke ico cuma co kumufahsa guhema kugira ngo bashobore kumuvura.
Dr. Moeti avuga ko ibintu nyamukuru vyokorwa muri ivyo bihugu ari:
Ibihugu bitari bike biramaze gufata ingingo zo kugabanya uruja n'uruza.
Mu bihugu bimwe bimwe, nk'amashure yarahiduwe ibibanza vyo gufashirizamwo abanduye, aho bashobora kugumizwa ukwabo mbere no kuvurwa bakavurirwamwo.
Amahinguriro ahingura impuzu yarasabwe gufasha mu guhingura ibikoresho vyo kwikingira nka ya makanzu yambarwa n'abaganga.
Ikigo kijejwe gukinga indwara muri Afrika kimenyesha ko kigiye gutanga ibikoresho vyo gupima coronavirus bishika ku muliyoni kugira ngo bizibire "igihengeri kinini" cibonekeza kuri uwo mugabane.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_52378555' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/52378555' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Leta yo muri US irasaba ko Ubushinwa buryozwa ingaruka za Covid-19
Leta ya Missouri irarega guverinoma y'Ubushinwa n'ishyaka rya gikomunisiti riri ku butegetsi icyo yise uburiganya bugambiriwe bwaganishije ku cyorezo ubu kibasiye isi cya Covid-19.
Leta ya Missouri irarega guverinoma y'Ubushinwa n'ishyaka rya gikomunisiti riri ku butegetsi icyo yise uburiganya bugambiriwe bwaganishije ku cyorezo ubu kibasiye isi cya Covid-19.
Eric Schmitt, intumwa nkuru ya leta ya Missouri yagize iti: "Guverinoma y'Ubushinwa yabeshye isi ku kaga iyi virus iteje n'uburyo yandura, icecekesha avugaga ibyayo inakora bicye mu guhagarika ikwirakwira ryayo".
Avuga ko ibi iyi guverinoma igomba kubiryozwa mu mategeko.
Ikirego kirasaba impozamarira ku guteza abantu akaga, impfu no kugusha ubukungu bidasanzwe byose byibasiye iyi leta.
Ntihatangajwe urukiko iyi leta yarezemo Ubushinwa.
Leta y'Ubushinwa yahakanye ishimitse ibyo yagiye iregwa na bamwe mu bategetsi ba leta zunze ubumwe za Amerika.
Abanyamategeko bavuga ko ikirego cya leta ya Missouri kizahura n'inzitizi zirimo ko itegeko rya leta zunze ubumwe za Amerika riha leta z'ibindi bihugu ubudahangarwa.
Iki kirego se gikwiye guhangayikisha Ubushinwa?
Iki kirego kije mu gihe gutunga urutoki Ubushinwa ko ari bwo nyirabayazana w'iki cyorezo bikomeje gukorwa cyane cyane n'ubutegetsi bwa Washington.
Mu bihe bya mbere by'iki cyorezo, Bwana Trump yashimagije uko Ubushinwa buri guhangana n'iyi virus, ariko imaze kwibasira na US yahindukiranye Ubushinwa avuga ko aribwo nyirabayazana.
Gusa bamwe babibona nko kwegeka ku bandi amakosa y'ubutegetsi bwe mu kurwanya iki cyorezo.
Tom Ginsburg umwarimu w'amategeko mpuzamahanga muri kaminuza ya Chicago yabwiye Reuters ati:
"Turi kubona abantu benshi bo mu ruhande rw'abatsimbaraye ku mahame ya cyera (conservatives) bibanda ku Bushinwa mu guhisha amakosa ya guverinoma ya Amerika".
Ubushinwa bufite gutinya ibi birego nubwo guverinoma z'ibihugu zidashobora gukurikiranwa mu nkiko z'imbere muri Amerika.
Niba iki kirego kigejejwe mu rukiko bizasaba urukiko mpuzamahanga aho Ubushinwa nabwo buzagira ijambo kubyo buregwa.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_52108745' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/52108745' term='COVID'>
Burundi: “Guhisha amakuru kuri Covid-19 bizashyira ubuzima mu kaga” – HRW
Umuryango uharanira uburenganzira bwa muntu Human Rights Watch uvuga ko mu gihe hadatangwa amakuru nyayo kuri Covid-19 mu Burundi, abategetsi bari gushyira mu kaga gakomeye ubuzima bw'abantu benshi.
Umuryango uharanira uburenganzira bwa muntu Human Rights Watch uvuga ko mu gihe hadatangwa amakuru nyayo kuri Covid-19 mu Burundi, abategetsi bari gushyira mu kaga gakomeye ubuzima bw'abantu benshi.
Uyu muryango uvuga ko nubwo leta y'u Burundi hari ingamba yafashe, zirimo gushyira mu kato abavuye mu mahanga ariko bidakorwa neza kuko bamwe aho bashyizwe hatari isuku n'ibiribwa bikwiye.
Umuvugizi wa leta y'u Burundi yabwiye BBC ko ibyatangajwe na Human Rights Watch "ntacyo abivugaho".
Mu cyumweru cyashize, umuvugizi w'umukuru w'igihugu Jean Claude Karerwa yabwiye BBC ko mu Burundi hafashwe ingamba mu kwirinda iyi ndwara zigendanye no kuba iyi virus itarahagera.
Mu itangazo ryasohowe na Human Rights Watch (HRW) uyu munsi kuwa kabiri, umuyobozi wawo muri Afurika yo hagati Lewis Mudge yagize ati:
"Kunanirwa gutanga amakuru nyayo ku bukana bw'iyi ndwara, uko yandura n'uburyo ikomeye,ni uburyo busanzwe bwo guhakana no kuyobya uburari mu gukemura ibibazo, [ariko] ni ukwirengangiza amasomo akomeye ahandi bari kuvana kuri iki cyorezo".
Bwana Mudge yasabye leta y'u Burundi gukorera mu kuri no gufatanya n'imiryango n'ibigo mpuzamahanga mu kuba bafasha abagirwaho ingaruka kurusha abandi iki cyorezo kiramutse gikwirakwiriye.
Kugeza ubu mu Burundi nta muntu ufite Covid-19 urahaboneka, gusa mu bihugu bitatu bihana imbibi; DR Congo, u Rwanda na Tanzania hamaze kuvugwa abafite iyi ndwara.
HRW ivuga ko hari imiryango myinshi ikora ibikorwa byo gufasha yayibwiye ko mu Burundi hadapimwa abantu bahagije kugira ngo bamenye abashobora kuba baranduye.
Mu cyumweru gishize, Gaston Sindimwo, visi perezida wa mbere w'u Burundi yabwiye BBC ko iki gihugu kiteguye kurwanya iyi virus iramutse ihageze.
Bwana Sindimwo yavuze ko mu ngamba bafashe harimo gusaba abantu kudakora ingendo baza cyangwa basohoka mu gihugu, guhagarika uruja n'uruza rw'indege mu minsi irindwi no gusaba abantu kwirinda kwegerana aho bishoboka, no gukoranaho.
HRW ivuga ko mu 2019, abategetsi mu Burundi banze gutangaza ko Malaria yabaye icyorezo mu gihe habonetse abantu miliyoni 8,5 bayirwaye mu gihugu gifite miliyoni 11,5 ikica abantu barenga 3,000.
Uyu muryango uvuga ko ibi byatumye nta ngamba zo gufasha igihugu kurwanya iki cyorezo zifatwa.
Covid-19 iravugwa mu karere mu gihe mu kwezi kwa gatanu mu Burundi bitegura amatora rusange y'umukuru w'igihugu.
Mu kiganiro aheruka kugirana na BBC Bwana Jean Claude Karerwa yavuze ko bizeye ko iyi ndwara nubwo yagera mu Burundi itageza mu kwezi kwa gatanu ngo ibangamire ayo matora ateganyijwe tariki 20/05/2020.
Yagize ati: "Byabangamira amatora mu gihe cyaba cyabaye ikiza cyakwiye igihugu cyose hafashwe ingingo nka ziriya zifatwa igihugu kiri mu ntambara".
HRW mu itangazo ryayo uyu munsi, ivuga ko ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye (OMS) mu Burundi ryayibwiye ko rizi gusa ahantu hamwe hagenewe gushyira mu kato abakekwaho iyi ndwara.
Ko aho ari muri hoteli iri mu murwa mukuru Bujumbura irimo abantu bagera kuri 40.
HRW ivuga ariko ko, ibinyamakuru mu Burundi bivuga ko hari abantu amagana bashyizwe mu kato ahantu 11 hanyuranye mu gihugu mu mashuri, hoteli n'izindi nzu za leta.
Ikavuga ko abo batabona ibyangombwa nkenerwa, kandi hari abarara hanze ndetse biyishyurira bicye mu byo babonye.
Umuvugizi wa leta y'u Burundi yavuze ko ibivugwa na HRW ntacyo yabivugaho.
Umwe mu bari mu kato mu Ntara ya Muyinga, HRW ivuga ko yayibwiye ko abategetsi bababwiye ko uzananirwa kwishyura ashobora kujyanwa muri gereza.
Uyu muryango usaba abategetsi mu Burundi ko bakomeza ingamba zo kwirinda no kwita ku bakekwaho n'abashobora kurwara iki cyorezo.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52513419' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52513419' term='COVID'>
DR Congo: Imfungwa 43 zo muri gereza ya gisirikare zanduye coronavirus
Gereza ya gisirikare ya N'dolo muri Repubulika ya Demokarasi ya Kongo yatangaje ko imfungwa 43 zemejwe ko zanduye icyorezo cya coronavirus, abategetsi ba gereza n'abo mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi bakaba bari gukumira ko izindi mfungwa zakwandura.
Gereza ya gisirikare ya N'dolo muri Repubulika ya Demokarasi ya Kongo yatangaje ko imfungwa 43 zemejwe ko zanduye icyorezo cya coronavirus, abategetsi ba gereza n'abo mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi bakaba bari gukumira ko izindi mfungwa zakwandura.
Profeseri Steve Ahuka ukuriye ibikorwa by'ubutabazi muri DR Congo, yavuze ko hari kurebwa uburyo bwo guhagarika ubwandu muri iyo gereza iri mu murwa mukuru Kinshasa.
Ubwo yasuraga iyo gereza ku munsi w'ejo ku wa gatanu, Bwana Ahuka yagize ati:
"Turi gutekereza ku gushyira amahema mu mbuga ya gereza mu rwego rwo kwita ku bantu banduye ndetse no guhumanura ahantu handuye".
Yanavuze ko hakomeje gukorwa iperereza ngo harebwe niba hari abandi banduye.
Kuva ku itariki ya 10 y'ukwezi kwa gatatu uyu mwaka, muri DR Congo hamaze kwemezwa abantu 604 barwaye Covid-19, indwara yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero iterwa n'ubu bwoko bushya bwa coronavirus.
96% by'abo babwayi bose babonetse i Kinshasa, umujyi wahindutse indiri y'iyi ndwara muri icyo gihugu. Muri abo 32 imaze kubica naho 75 barayikize.
</doc>
