<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52456227' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52456227' term='COVID'>
Ubwirinzi bw’umubiri: Ushobora kurwara coronavirus kabiri?
Ubwirinzi bw'umubiri nibwo burebwa cyane n'ibibazo nk'ibi abantu bakibaza kuri coronavirus. Gusa ikibazo ni uko ibyo tuzi ari bicyeya.
Ubwirinzi bw'umubiri nibwo burebwa cyane n'ibibazo nk'ibi abantu bakibaza kuri coronavirus. Gusa ikibazo ni uko ibyo tuzi ari bicyeya.
Ushobora gukira coronavirus ukongera ukayandura? Urukingo rwayo ruzakora? Iyi virus izahora igaruka buri gihe cy'urugaryi? Ni gute tuzahangana nayo mu buryo burambye?
Iyi ni inkuru y'umunyamakuru wa BBC wibanda gusa kuri siyansi n'ubuzima.
Ubwirinzi bw'umubiri wacu mu kurwanya indwara buza mu byiciro bibiri.
Ikiciro cya mbere ni igihora kiteguye kurwanya ikintu cyose kibangamiye umubiri kiwugezemo.
Ni nk'ubutabazi bwihuse, burekura ibinyabutabire bitera ubushyuhe hamwe n'insoro zera (white blood cells) bigatwika uturemangingo twagezweho n'uburwayi.
Gusa ubu buryo ntabwo bukora kuri coronavirus kuko ntibuyimenya bityo ntabwo buyikurinda.
Ahubwo ukenera ubundi buryo (bwa kabiri) bw'imikorere nk'iyo bushobora kuyimenya.
Ubwo burimo insoro zikora uturindamubiri/abasirikare b'umubiri (antibodies) dushobora kumenya iyi virus no kuyihagarika, n'insoro zishobora gutera zikica uturemangingo twagezweho n'iyi virus.
Ibyo bifata igihe - hari ubushakashatsi bugaragaza ko bifata iminsi 10 ngo umubiri utangire gukora uturindamubiri dushobora kubona no kurwanya coronavirus kandi hari abarwayi bafite umubiri ukomeye ubasha gukora ubwo buryo bwo kwirinda.
Iyo ubu buryo bw'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri bushya bukomeye bihagije buha umubiri kwibuka bihoraho iriya virus igihe cyose yazagaruka ukayirwanya.
Ntabwo bizwi neza niba abantu bagira ibimenetso byoroheje gusa, cyangwa abatanabigira, umubiri wabo ukora ubu buryo bushya bw'ubwirinzi.
Ubwirinzi bw'umubiri bugira ubushobozi bwo kwibuka nk'ubwacu - bwibuka neza indwara zimwe na zimwe, ariko rimwe na rimwe bukibagirwa izindi.
Ubu bwirinzi bwibuka cyane indwara nk'iseru -  kuyirwara rimwe ukayikira biha ubwirinzi ubushobozi buhoraho bwo kuyibuka.
Gusa hari izindi bwibagirwa kenshi. Abana bashobora kurwara indwara zo mu buhumekero ziterwa na virus inshuro zirenze imwe mu gihe kimwe cy'ubukonje.
Coronavirus nshya Covid-19, ntabwo iramara igihe kinini ngo abahanga bamenye igihe ubwirinzi bw'umubiri bumara bukiyibuka, gusa hari izindi coronavirus esheshatu zifata abantu zatanga ishusho.
Enye (4) muri zo zigira ibimenyetso nk'iby'ibicurane, ubwirinzi buyibagirwa vuba. Ubushakashatsi bwerekanye ko bamwe mu bazikize bashobora kongera bakazirwara mu mwaka umwe. Gusa ibicurane byazo biba byoroheje.
Hari izindi coronavirus ebyiri zo ziteye ibibazo bikomeye - imwe ni itera ibibazo bikomeye mu buhumekero (Sars) n'indi yitwa Mers  - zabonetse mu myaka ishize.
Kuri izi coronavirus, Paul Hunter, umwarimu mu ishami ry'ubuvuzi muri kaminuza ya East Anglia agira ati: "Ikibazo si ukumenya niba umubiri uzigiraho ubwirinzi, ikibazo ni ubw'igihe kingana gute"
Avuga ko ibyagaragaye ari uko ubwirinzi bw'umubiri kuri izi virusi budahoraho.
Ati: "Ubushakashatsi ku turindamubiri bwerekana ko kuri Sars ubwirinzi bumara gusa umwaka umwe cyangwa ibiri, nubwo bitazwi neza neza niba ari iki gihe gusa bumara".
Gusa nubwo ubwirinzi bw'umubiri bwaba budahoraho kuri izi virus kuyirwara bwa kabiri ntabwo bizahaza umubiri nk'ubwa mbere.
Hari amakuru atandukanye yagiye agaragaza ko hari abayirwaye inshuro zirenze imwe mu gihe gitoya.
Hari abemeza ko atari ukuri ko umuntu ayandura kabiri. Hari n'abavuga ko iyi virus igera aho imera nk'isinziriye ikihisha mu mubiri, ikazongera ikazamuka nyuma.
Gusa, icyo abahanga muri siyansi bemeranyaho ni uko hari abarwayi basuzumwa nabi bakabwira ko bakize.
Nta muntu kugeza ubu urakira iyi virus ngo yemere ko bayimutera nanone kugira ngo basuzume ubwirinzi bw'umubiri, ariko ingunge (macaque) ebyiri zabikozweho.
Zandujwe inshuro ebyiri Covid-19, bwa mbere kugira ngo umubiri utangire gukora ubwirinzi n'ubwa kabiri nyuma y'ibyumweru bitatu.
Ubu bushakashatsi bwerekanye ko izi nyamaswa zisa n'abantu zitondeye kugira ibimenyetso byo by'iyi virus nyuma y'icyo gihe gito zongeye kuyanduzwa.
Ntabwo ari cyo bisobanuye, niyo mpamvu ishami rya ONU rishinzwe ubuzima ku isi OMS riri kurwanya ibihugu biri gukoresha ibyitwa "immunity passports" mu koroshya amategeko ya 'guma mu rugo'.
Iki gitekerezo gishingiye ko ukorewe ikizamini cy'uturindamibiri/abasiriakare b'umubiri bagasanga ahagaze neza bamureka agasubira mu kazi.
Gusa abarwayi hafi ya bose uzabasangana urugero runaka rw'uturindamubiri. Ariko si bose uzasangana uturindamubiri duhagarika coronavirus ngo ntigere mu tundi turemangingo tw'umubiri.
Ubushakashatsi ku barwayi 175 bakize Covid-19 mu Bushinwa bwerekanye ko 30% byabo bari bafite ikigero kiri hasi cyane cy'utu turindamubiri tubasha kurwanya covid-19.
Niyo mpamvu OMS ivuga ko kuba ufite uturindamubiri duhagije bitavuze ko ari utwo umubiri ukeneye mu gukira no kurinda iyi ndwara.
Ikindi ni uko kuba gusa warindwa n'utwo turindamubiri, bidasobanuye ko umubiri wawe utabana n'iyo virus kandi ngo uyanduze abandi.
Ni ingenzi cyane ku buzima bw'umubiri wawe no kuba wakwandura Covid-19 inshuro nyinshi mu gihe kingana runaka.
Ubwirinzi kandi buzagena uburyo iki cyorezo cyakuzahaza cyangwa kikaba cyanakwica. Ubwirinzi bw'umubiri ku kigero runaka butuma iki cyorezo kitazahaza umubiri.
Niba bigoye cyane ko umubiri ukora ubwirinzi wibuka by'igihe kirekire, bishobora no kugorana gukora urukingo, cyangwa bigahindura uko urwo rukingo rwakoreshwa, inshuro n'igihe.
Igihe ubwirinzi bw'umubiri bumara bwibuka iyi virus kizatubwira niba hari amahirwe yo kubasha guhagarika ikwirakwira ryayo.
Ibi ni bimwe mu bibazo bitarabonerwa ibisubizo.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_52049137' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/52049137' term='COVID'>
Rwanda: Hari abacuruzi bari 'kwikinga mu kiza' bakuriza ibiciro
Abaturage batandukanye mu Rwanda, bagaragaza ko hamwe na hamwe aho bajya kugura ibiribwa basanga abacuruzi barabizamuye bikabije bitwaje ibihe bidasanzwe byatangajwe mu gihugu.
Abaturage batandukanye mu Rwanda, bagaragaza ko hamwe na hamwe aho bajya kugura ibiribwa basanga abacuruzi barabizamuye bikabije bitwaje ibihe bidasanzwe byatangajwe mu gihugu.
Leta y'u Rwanda ivuga ko yafashe ingamba zo guhangana n'abacuruzi bahenda abaguzi bitwaje ibi bihe igihugu cyatangaje byo kurwanya ikwirakwira rya coronavirus.
Gutuganya no kugeza ibicuruzwa ku isoko ndetse n'urujya n'uruza rw'abaza kubigura byose byarahungabanye kubera ingamba zafashwe n'ibihugu mu kugabanya ingendo.
Nubwo ibihugu byinshi mu ngamba zazo bikomeze kwemera ingendo z'abatwaye ibiribwa, ababitwara n'abo babishyira ku masoko bose baragabanutse.
Egide Ntwari, umwarimu wigisha mu ishami ry'ubukungu muri za kaminuza mu Rwanda avuga ko kuzamuka kw'ibiciro kw'ibikenerwa cyane mu bihe nk'ibi biba byitezwe, kuko ubuzima buba bwahindutse.
Yabwiye BBC ati: "Icyakora mu bihugu nk'ibyacu muri aka karere uko ibintu bimeze ubu, ubona ibiciro bizamuka kubera ibihuha (speculations) n'ubwoba bw'abantu".
Bwana Ntwari avuga ko hari abantu bumva ko mu bihe nk'ibi bagomba kugura ibintu byinshi bakuzuza ibigega byabo (stocks), bityo abacuruzi bamwe babona ubusabe (demand) ari bunini bakazamura ibiciro.
Ati: "Ni igihe gisaba za leta gukoresha imbaraga mu kurengera abaturage, zigashyiraho ingamba zo kwirinda izamuka rikabije ry'ibiciro".
Mu Rwanda, minisiteri ishinzwe ubucuruzi  yatangaje ko yakoze igenzura mu gihugu igasanga hari abacuruzi bazamuye ibiciro by'ibiribwa n'ibikoresho by'isuku.
Ivuga kandi ko yasanze hari abacuruzi bahisha ibicuruzwa muri za 'depot' kugirango bumvishe abantu ko byabuze maze bazamure ibiciro.
Mu itangazo yasohoye, iyi minisiteri ivuga ko yahannye abacuruzi bagera ku 109 mu gihugu hose kubera ibikorwa nk'ibyo, muri iki gihe cy'icyorezo.
Ibiciro by'umutobe w'amacunga(orange) bimaze kuzamukaho 20% muri uku kwezi kuko abantu benshi bakeneye gufata ibintu by'umwimerere muri iki gihe cy'icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Mu gihe ababikeneye babaye benshi, kubibagezaho byarakomeye kubera ingorane mu gutwara ibintu ziriho ubu.
Ibi byatumye ibyo abahanga mu bukungu bita "igiciro kizaza" cy'umutobe w'amacunga kizamuka, ibi bigasobanura ko bizaguma bityo no mu gihe cy'amezi ari imbere.
Stephen Innes umuhanga mu by'amasoko ku isi mu kigo AxiCorp avuga ko Covid-19 iri kuzahaza abaguzi n'abacuruzi b'imitobe y'amacunga.
Abatunganya n'abacuruza ibintu nkenerwa, bose bafite ingorane zo kubana abakozi bakora muri ibi bihe kubera ingamba zibuza abantu kwegerana.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_51907823' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/51907823' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: 'Kwishyira mu kato', kuki? gute? ryari? bigatanga iki?... Sobanukirwa
Mu kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'indwara zandura, kwishyira mu kato (self- isolation), aho ukeka ko yanduye atajya ahari abandi ni kimwe mu bishobora kurinda ikwirakwira nk'uko abaganga babivuga.
Mu kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'indwara zandura, kwishyira mu kato (self- isolation), aho ukeka ko yanduye atajya ahari abandi ni kimwe mu bishobora kurinda ikwirakwira nk'uko abaganga babivuga.
Uwahuye (contact) n'umuntu byamenyekanye ko yanduye Covid-19 ni byiza ko yishyira mu kato akanabimenyesha abaganga nk'uko Dr Olivier Manzi umuganga w'inzobere mu ndwara z'ibyorezo zandura yabisobanuriye BBC.
Minisitiri w'intebe wa Canada ni umwe mu bantu bazwi baheruka kwishyira mu kato, abakinnyi b'ikipe ya Arsenal mu Bwongereza nabo bishyize mu kato nyuma y'uko umutoza wabo yanduye.
Iyi ndwara imaze kugera muri aka karere, mu Rwanda hamaze kuboneka abantu batanu bayanduye harimo Abanyarwanda bane.
Uretse umwe, abandi banduye bageze mu Rwanda mu ntangiriro z'uku kwezi, hari gushakishwa abandi baba barahuye nabo ngo basuzumwe kuko hari impungenge ko nabo baba baranduye.
Abaganga bavuga ko umuntu ashobora kwishyira mu kato iwe mu rugo aho ashobora gufashwa gukomeza kubaho mu buzima busanzwe ariko adahura (contact) n'abandi.
Dr Manzi, inzobere mu ndwara z'ibyorezo ikorana na OMS, avuga ko kwishyira mu kato bikorwa iyo umuntu aketse ko yanduye, ashobora kuba yarabonanye (contact) n'umuntu wayanduye.
Avuga kandi ko bitewe n'ibyo igihugu runaka cyemeje, abantu bavuye mu bihugu ibi na biriya birimo coronavirus nabo bashobora gutegekwa kwishyira mu kato.
Ati: "Bikorwa mu minsi 15 kuko ariyo iyi ndwara ishobora kubonekamo, ni ukuvuga hagati y'umunsi umuntu yaba yarahuye na virus n'iminsi 15 nibwo iyi ndwara ishobora kuboneka, ariko ishobora no kuboneka mu minsi ibiri cyangwa itatu kugeza".
Muri iyo minsi umuntu ari mu kato, Dr Manzi avuga ko uwo muntu agomba kureba niba nta bimenyetso by'iyi ndwara agaragaza.
Ibimenyetso by'iyi ndwara ni umuriro, gukorora no guhumeka bigoranye.
Ati: "Ibihugu nabyo bishyiraho uburyo bwo gukurikirana aba bantu bari mu kato, bakababaza buri munsi uko bameze, niba nta bimenyetso bafite...kugeza iyo minsi 15 irangiye".
Dr Manzi avuga ko mu kurwanya indwara zandura ibi bitanga umusaruro kuko kuva iyo uwo muntu ukekwa  atangiye kwirinda, bivuze ko aramutse yaranduye iyi virus atayanduza abandi.
Ati: "Umuntu uri mu kato bamubwira ibyo agomba gukora, kwirinda kubonana n'abantu, kwirinda gusangira ibikoresho n'abandi...
Hari ibintu  byinshi bamwigisha bigamije kwirinda kwanduza abandi mu gihe ibimenyetso byaba bitangiye kuboneka".
Umuntu utaragaragaza ibimenyetso bya coronavirus nawe ashobora kuyanduza nubwo bwose 'risques' ziba ari nkeya ugeranyije n'uwatangiye kubigaragaza nk'uko Dr Manzi abivuga.
Dr Manzi avuga ko kwishyira mu kato ari ibintu by'ingenzi kandi bishoboka bitewe n'ingamba igihugu cyafashe hamwe na 'discipline' y'abantu.
"Hoya ntabwo ari akato, biriya biriya ni ingamba zo kwirinda gukwirakwira kw'indwara". - Dr Manzi.
"Urugero muri Senegal, iyi ndwara itangira abantu bari bacye, ariko haje kuba ihuriro ry'abantu benshi nyuma yaryo nibwo hamenyekanye abantu benshi banduye.
"Guhagarika biriya rero ni ingamba z'ingenzi cyane kuko ingero mu bihugu byinshi zarabonetse aho mu guhura kw'abantu benshi ari ho nyuma habonetse benshi banduye.
Dr Manzi avuga ko iyi ari indwara nshyashya ko mu kuyirwanya ababishinzwe bareba ahandi yabanje uko bayirwanyije nabo bakabiheraho bafata ingamba.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_imikino-52549062' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/imikino-52549062' term='COVID'>
Abakinnyi ba Barcelona bagiye gupimwa Covid-19 mbere yo gusubira mu myitozo
Abakinnyi ba Barcelona bazapimwa Covid-19 ejo ku wa gatatu ku kibuga cy'imyitozo cy'iyi kipe, mbere yuko batangira imyitozo buri umwe ku giti cye "mu minsi iri imbere".
Abakinnyi ba Barcelona bazapimwa Covid-19 ejo ku wa gatatu ku kibuga cy'imyitozo cy'iyi kipe, mbere yuko batangira imyitozo buri umwe ku giti cye "mu minsi iri imbere".
Amakipe yo mu cyiciro cya mbere muri Espagne - La Liga - yahawe uruhushya rwo gusubira mu myitozo muri iki cyumweru nyuma yaho leta idohoreye ingamba zimwe na zimwe.
Barça ivuga ko shampiyona "yahaye uruhushya" iryo pimwa nyuma yo kugenzura ibikoresho biri ku kibuga cyayo cy'imyitozo.
Abategura imikino ya shampiyona ya La Liga bari gushaka ko imikino y'uyu mwaka yongera gutangira mu kwezi gutaha kwa gatandatu.
Abakinnyi bo mu byiciro bibiri bya mbere - icya mbere n'icya kabiri - bazajya bitoza buri umwe ku giti cye.
Ni nyuma y'amasezerano hagati y'urwego rw'imikino n'urwego rw'ubuvuzi muri Espagne atuma habaho kubungabunga ubuzima bw'abakinnyi n'abayobozi b'amakipe.
Mu kwezi kwa gatatu nibwo umupira w'amaguru muri Espagne wahagaritswe mu gihe bitazwi igihe kizarangirira, kubera icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Kandi abakinnyi bose bagomba gupimwa mbere yuko basubira ku bibuga by'imyitozo.
La Liga yafashe ingamba zisesuye zo gutuma imyitozo yongera gukorwa ariko mu buryo bukurikije amabwiriza y'inzego z'ubuvuzi.
Zimwe muri zo ni nko gutangira buri mukinnyi yitoza wenyine, nyuma agashyirwa mu itsinda rito, kugeza noneho igihe nyuma yaho ikipe yose izitoreza hamwe.
Itangazo rya La Liga rigira riti: "Izi ngamba zizamara igihe kigera hafi ku byumweru bine bigabanyije mu byiciro, aho muri buri cyiciro hazubahirizwa ingamba zo kwirinda ubwandu zashyizweho na leta".
Hasigaye iminsi 11 y'imikino ngo shampiyona ya La Liga y'uyu mwaka irangire.
Kugeza ubu Barcelona ni yo iyoboye urutonde rw'agateganyo rwa shampiyona n'amanota 58. Ikurikiwe na Real Madrid ifite 56.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52226958' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52226958' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Dr Tedros wa OMS ati: "reka kugira Covid-19 ikibazo ca politike"
Umukuru w'umuryango ujejwe amagara y'abantu kw'isi OMS/WHO asaba ko abantu bagira ubumwe mu kurwanya ikiza ca coronavirus, ni mu gihe uwo muryango waneguwe n'umukuru wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, Donald Trump.
Umukuru w'umuryango ujejwe amagara y'abantu kw'isi OMS/WHO asaba ko abantu bagira ubumwe mu kurwanya ikiza ca coronavirus, ni mu gihe uwo muryango waneguwe n'umukuru wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, Donald Trump.
Mw'ijambo yaraye ashikirije, umukuru wa OMS Tedros Ghebreyesus, yarashimagije igikorwa kiriko gikorwa n'uwo muryango, anasaba ko abantu boreka kugira covid-19 ikibazo ca politike.
Bwana Trump avuga ko agiye kwihweza ingene yohagarika imfashanyo itangwa na Amerika muri uwo muryango.
Trump yagiriza OMS ko "yegamiye cane ku ruhande rw'u Bushinwa".
Dr. Tedros ariyamiriza ayo majambo, agashimangira ati "Turi kumwe n'ibihugu vyose, kandi nta vangura rituranga".
Inyuma y'aho yifatiye mu gahanga OMS ku wakabiri, Bwana Trump yarasubiye aranegura kandi ejo ku wa gatatu uwo muryango mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru, avuga ko uwo muryango "utegerezwa kwerekana neza ibikorwa ushira imbere".
Avuga ko Amerika igiye gukora umwihwezo kugira ngo ifate ingingo nimba ishobora kubandanya itanga intererano yayo muri OMS.
Ati: "Babanje kuvuga ko ari ibinyoma. Tugiye guhagarika amahera dutanga muri OMS".
Eka n'umunyamabanga ajejwe imigenderanire w'ico gihugu Mike Pompeo na we ejo ku wa gatatu yabwiye abanyamakuru ko ubutegetsi bwariko "bwihweza intererano yacu duha OMS".
Pompeo ati: "Amashirahamwe ategereza gukora. Ategerezwa kwerekana ko ariko akora ivyo yiyemeje".
Coronavirus yatanguye kwibonekeza mu kwa 12 kw'umwaka uheze mu gihasagara ca Wuhan mu Bushinwa, ababa muri ico gisagara ubu basubiye kwemererwa gusohoka inyuma y'ivyumweru 11 bugaranywe.
Umwe mu bahanuzi b'umukuru wa OMS yari yavuze ko kubona  barakoranye cane n'u Bushinwa "vyabaye ngirakamaro cane" mu gushobora gutahura ivy'iyo ndwara kuva icaduka.
Ayo majambo anegura OMS yashikirijwe na Perezida Trump aje mu gihe ubutegetsi bwiwe bunegurwa cane ko bwavyifashemwo nabi mu guhangana n'ico kiza.
Tedros ntafise ubwoba ko Amerika yohagarika intererano yayo
Ejo ku wagatatu, Dr Tedros yavuze ati: "Ndabasavye, mugire ubumwe mu gihugu cose, reka kugira Covid-19 ikibazo ca politike".
"Ubwa kabiri, isi yose ifatane mu nda. Hanyuma n'ubutegetsi bwa Amerika n'u Bushinwa bube ubutegetsi bwizigiwe".
Yishura ku majambo yavuzwe na Trump, Dr. Tedros yateye akamo ati: "Ibihugu bikomeye vyategerezwa gufata iya mbere, kandi ndabasavye mureke gukorera politike kuri Covid-19".
Amerika ni kimwe mu bihugu bitanga intererano nini muri uwo muryango, ibiharuro vya OMS bikerekana ko itanga ibice 15% vy'amahera yose akoreshwa.
Dr. Tedros ejo ku wagatatu yavuze ko ata bwoba afise kuri ayo majambo yo guhagarika intererano, akavuga ko yizeye ko Amerika izobandanya iyitanga.
Imbere y'aho, umunyamabanga w'ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ONU, António Guterres, yari yashikirije ijambo ashigikira uwo muryango.
Yavuze ko coronavirus ari ikiza "kitari bwaboneke", amenyesha ko ivyo kwihweza ingene isi yahanganye naco vyoba ivyo muri kazoza.
Ati : "Ubu ni umwanya wo kuja hamwe, aho isi yose itegerezwa gukorera hamwe, dufatane mu nda kugira ngo duhagarike uwu mugera n'inkurikizi zawo".
Abategetsi b'ibihugu vya Afrika nka Paul Kagame w'u Rwanda, Cyril Ramaphosa wa Afurika y'Epfo na Hage Geingob wa Namibia batangaje ko bashigikiye OMS mu rugamba irongoye rwo kurwanya Covid-19.
