<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52226031' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52226031' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Mu Burundi abantu 2,261 bavuye mu kato
Minisiteri y'ubuzima mu Burundi yatangaje ko mu bantu 2,936 bari barashyizwe mu kato bakekwaho coronavirus muri bo 2,261 barekuwe ngo bajye mu ngo zabo nyuma y'ibyumweru bibiri.
Minisiteri y'ubuzima mu Burundi yatangaje ko mu bantu 2,936 bari barashyizwe mu kato bakekwaho coronavirus muri bo 2,261 barekuwe ngo bajye mu ngo zabo nyuma y'ibyumweru bibiri.
Minisiteri y'ubuzima ivuga ko aba bari barashyizwe mu kato mu bice bitandukanye by'igihugu, harimo abavuye mu bindi bihugu nk'uko amategeko yashyizweho ubu abitegeka.
Iyi minisiteri ntisobanuro niba aba bavuye mu kato bose barapimwe Covid-19, gusa ivuga ko nta bimenyetso by'iki cyorezo bagaragaje muri iki gihe bamaze mu kato.
Iyi minisiteri ivuga ko abantu 34 bapimwe, bahuye na batatu kugeza ubu babonywemo iyi virus, 21 bapimwe inshuro ebyiri, abandi 13 bamaze gupimwa rimwe, bose ntibanduye iyi virusi.
Leta y'u Burundi yafashe ingingo yo gushyira mu kato iminsi 14 abantu bose bavuye mu mahanga, ibi bishyirwa mu bikorwa cyane mu ntara zihana imbibi n'ibihugu bituranye n'u Burundi.
Ku mbuga nkoranyambaga, bamwe banenga uburyo ibyo gushyira abantu mu kato bikorwa, bavuga ko hari abafunzwe bavanywe mu kato kuko bananiwe kwishyura amafaranga y'aho bari barashyizwe.
Leta y'u Burundi ntacyo iratangaza ku bivugwa.
Minisiteri y'ubuzima ihakana amakuru avugwa ku mbuga nkoranyambaga ko mu Burundi hageze 'urukingo' rw'iki cyorezo rugiye kugeragezwa ruvuye mu Bushinwa.
Ikavuga ko "u Burundi butazigera bwemera kuba ahantu ho kugeragereza urukingo n'iyo rwaba urwa Covid-19".
Abamaze kwandura Covid-19 ku isi ubu bamaze kurenga miliyoni 1,5. Muri bo abarenga 430,000 bari muri USA.
Iyi ndwara ku isi, imaze kwica abantu barenga 88,000 naho abayikize bararenga 330,000 nk'uko bivugwa na kaminuza y'ubushakashatsi ya Johns Hopkins.
Abantu 371 nibo bamaze kwandura Covid-19 mu bihugu bigize umuryango wa Afurika y'iburasirazuba;
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-51513781' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-51513781' term='COVID'>
Umuntu wa mbere wishwe na coronavirus i Burayi yatangajwe mu Bufaransa
Mukerarugendo w'Umushinwa yapfiriye mu Bufaransa nyuma yo kwandura ubwoko bushya bwa coronavirus - uyu akaba ari we wa mbere yishe hanze y'umugabane w'Aziya.
Mukerarugendo w'Umushinwa yapfiriye mu Bufaransa nyuma yo kwandura ubwoko bushya bwa coronavirus - uyu akaba ari we wa mbere yishe hanze y'umugabane w'Aziya.
Uwo mugabo w'imyaka 80 yakomokaga mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa, nkuko byavuzwe na Agnès Buzyn, Minisitiri w'ubuzima w'Ubufaransa.
Yapfuye azize kwangirika kw'ibihaha kwaturutse kuri coronavirus.
Yageze mu Bufaransa ku itariki ya 16 y'ukwezi kwa mbere, ku itariki ya 25 y'uko kwezi ashyirwa mu kato mu bitaro bya Bichat biri mu majyaruguru y'umurwa mukuru Paris, nkuko Madamu Buzyn yabivuze.
Impfu eshatu gusa ni zo zari zaratangajwe mbere zo hanze y'Ubushinwa - muri Hong Kong, Philippines no mu Buyapani.
Ariko abantu barenga 1,500 bamaze kwicwa na coronavirus mu Bushinwa, benshi muri bo i Hubei aho yagaragaye bwa mbere.
Abandi bantu 2,641 bemejwe ko bayanduye, ubu umubare w'abamaze kuyandura mu Bushinwa bose hamwe bakaba ari 66,492.
Mu mpera y'ukwezi kwa mbere, Ubufaransa bwabaye igihugu cya mbere i Burayi cyemeje ko hari abantu cyasanganye coronavirus.
Bufite abantu 11 byemejwe ko barwaye ubu bwoko bushya bwa coronavirus - buzwi ku izina rya Covid-19, kandi batandatu baracyari mu bitaro.
Madamu Buzyn yavuze ko mushiki w'uwo mugabo wapfuye ari umwe muri abo bayanduye, ariko byemezwa ko arimo koroherwa.
Hanze y'Ubushinwa, hamaze kugaragara abantu barenga 500 bo mu bihugu 24 banduye coronavirus.
