<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52379293' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52379293' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus - ONU iti ‘isi ishobora guhura n’amapfa twumva muri Bibiliya’
Ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ONU riragabisha ko isi ishobora guhura n'amapfa "avugwa muri Bibiliya" bitumwe n'ikiza ca coronavirus.
Ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ONU riragabisha ko isi ishobora guhura n'amapfa "avugwa muri Bibiliya" bitumwe n'ikiza ca coronavirus.
David Beasley, arongoye ishami rya ONU rijejwe imfungurwa kw'isi PAM/WFP, avuga ko hakenewe gufatwa ingingo zihuta kugira ngo bazibire ayo mahano.
Hari icegeranyo cerekana ko abantu babarizwa hagati y'imiliyoni 135 gushika kuri 250 zirenga bashobora guhura n'ikigoyi.
PAM ivuga ko hari ibihugu cumi bishobora kubangamirwa n'ico kigoyi kubera intambara, ibibazo vy'ubutunzi hamwe n'ihindagurika ry'ikirere.
Icegeranyo kigira kane gisohoka uko umwaka utashe ku bibazo vy'imfungurwa cerekana ko ibihugu vya Yemen, Republika y'Intwaro Rusangi ya Congo,  Afghanistani, Venezuela, Ethiopia, Sudan y'Epfo, Sudani, Syria, Nijeriya na Haiti,ari vyo bishobora guhura n'ico kigoyi.
Ico cegeranyo kivuga ko mu mwaka uheze, ibice 61% vy'abanya Sudani y'Epfo ari bo bahuye n'ibibazo vy'ubukene bw'ibifungurwa.
Eka n'imbere y'uko iki kiza caduka, hari ibice bimwe bime vya Afrika y'Ubuseruko na Aziya y'Ubumanuko vyari mu kibazo gikomeye c'ubukene bw'ibifungurwa bivuye ku ruzuba hamwe n'ibitero vy'inzige.
Mu mubonano yagiranye n'Inama nkuru ya ONU ijejwe umutekano aciye ku buhinga bwa videwo, Bwana Beasley yasavye ko isi "ihagurukira rimwe kandi igafata ingingo zihuta".
Ati: "Burya turashobora guhura n'amapfa y'ubwoko bwinshi nk'arya avugwa muri Bibiliya mu mezi make ari imbere. Ikiri ukuri ni uko umwanya uriko uratujana".
Yongerako ati: "Ndemera ko ubuhinga dufise, dukoreye hamwe, dushobora gushira hamwe inguvu be n'imigambi ikenewe kugira ngo ikiza ca Covid-19 nticihe inkumbi kandi ngo kidusige mu kangaratete".
Umuhinga muvyo ubutunzi mw'ishirahamwe OMS, Arif Husain, avuga ko ingaruka z'ico kiza ku butunzi  ari mbi cane ku miliyoni " z'abantu basanzwe bageze ahatemba".
Mw'itangazo yasohoye yavuze ati: "Ni amagorwa ku miliyoni z'abandi batari bake basanzwe babeshejweho n'agashahara baronka iyo bakoze".
"Ingingo za Gumamurugo hamwe n'ibibazo vyubutunzi kw'isi biramaze kwiha inkumbi.
"Akagorane gato gusa gashobora gutuma ibintu biyangara. Ni ngombwa ko dukorera hamwe kugira ngo duhagarike ingaruka mbi z'iki kiza".
Mu ntango z'uku kwezi, PAM yamenyesheje ko yari igiye gucamwo kubiri imfashanyo isanzwe itanga mu bice vya Yemen bigenzurwa n'abarwanya ubutegetsi vyasinzikajwe n'intambara kubera ikibazo c'amafaranga.
Yavuze ko abasanzwe batanga imfashanyo bazihagaritse kubera bari bafise amakenga ko abarwanyi ba Houthi babuza izo mfashanyo gushikira abo zigenewe.
PAM isanzwe ifasha abantu barenga imiliyoni 12 ba Yemen buri kwezi, ibice 80% muri bo bakaba bari mu burere buri mu minwe y'abarwanyi b'aba Houthi.
Igihugu ca Yemen catangaje umuntu wa mbere yanduye coronavirus mu ntango za kuno kwezi, abagiraneza bakagabisha ko mu kanya gato cane iyo ndwara ishobora kurengera ubushobozi bwo kuvura ico gihugu gifise busanzweatako bwifashe.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-51943931' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-51943931' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus ubu yageze muri leta 50 zose zigize Amerika
Icyorezo cya coronavirus ubu kimaze kugera muri leta zose 50 zigize Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, nyuma yaho leta ya West Virginia ejo ku wa kabiri itangarije umuntu wa mbere wanduye iyo virusi.
Icyorezo cya coronavirus ubu kimaze kugera muri leta zose 50 zigize Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, nyuma yaho leta ya West Virginia ejo ku wa kabiri itangarije umuntu wa mbere wanduye iyo virusi.
Ubwo yatangazaga uwo muntu wa mbere urwaye indwara y'ubuhumekero ya Covid-19 iterwa n'ubu bwoko bushya bwa coronavirus, Jim Justice, Guverineri w'iyo leta, yagize ati:
"Twari tubizi ko ibi biri hafi gushyika".
Ubuyobozi bw'umujyi wa New York City bwatangaje ko buri kwiga ku guhagarika ubuzima mu mujyi nk'uko byakozwe mu karere ka San Francisco Bay.
Kugeza ubu muri Amerika abantu 108 bamaze kwicwa n'iki cyorezo cya coronavirus naho abarenga 6,300 ni bo bamaze kwemezwa ko barwaye coronavirus muri iki gihugu.
Ku isi ubu habarurwa abantu hafi 200,000 bamaze kuyandura. Abagera hafi ku 8,000 imaze kubica.
Mu gihe ubutegetsi bwa Perezida Donald Trump buri gushaka amafaranga y'ingoboka ku bukungu angana na triyari imwe y'amadolari, umunyamabanga w'Amerika ushinzwe iby'imari hari ibyo yaburiye.
Amakuru avuga ko ejo ku wa kabiri nimugoroba, Steven Mnuchin yaburiye ukwabo abasenateri bo mu ishyaka ry'abarepubulikani ko inteko ishingamategeko ninanirwa kugira icyo ikoze, abadafite akazi muri Amerika bashobora kugera ku kigero cya 20%.
Icyo kigero cyaba cyenda gukuba inshuro ebyiri umubare w'abashomeri bari bariho mu gihe cy'ihungabana rikomeye ry'ubukungu ryabayeho muri Amerika mu mwaka wa 2008.
Bill de Blasio, umukuru w'umujyi wa New York City, yavuze ko mu minsi ibiri iri imbere azafata icyemezo niba yategeka ko abaturage miliyoni 8.5 "baguma iwabo".
Icyemezo nk'icyo ahanini cyatuma abantu batemererwa kuva mu ngo zabo, kikabemerera gukora ingendo za ngombwa bajya kugura imboga zo guteka cyangwa imiti, batembereza imbwa zabo cyangwa bakora imyitozo ngororangingo mu gihe cyose baba birinze guhura n'abandi bantu.
Bwana de Blasio yagize ati: "Ni icyemezo gikomeye cyane. Nta na rimwe mbere twigeze tuba mu bihe nk'ibi. Nta na rimwe nigeze numva ikintu nk'iki mu mateka y'umujyi wa New York City".
Abategetsi bo mu gace ka San Francisco Bay bamaze gutegeka abaturage miliyoni 6.7 bahatuye kuguma mu ngo zabo igihe cyose, ukuyemo aho bibaye ngombwa ko bava mu rugo, kugeza ku itariki ya 7 y'ukwezi gutaha kwa kane.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-51904449' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-51904449' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Mu Rwanda abandi bantu bane bashya bayibasanzemo
Minisiteri y'ubuzima mu Rwanda yatangaje ko hari abandi bantu bane(4) basanzemo Covid-19 mu Rwanda, aba bose ni Abanyarwanda kandi umwe muri bo ntaheruka kuva mu gihugu.
Minisiteri y'ubuzima mu Rwanda yatangaje ko hari abandi bantu bane(4) basanzemo Covid-19 mu Rwanda, aba bose ni Abanyarwanda kandi umwe muri bo ntaheruka kuva mu gihugu.
Nyuma y'amasaha 24 hatangajwe umuntu wa mbere ufite iyi ndwara mu Rwanda, hahise hatangazwa abandi bane.
Imibare iheruka ya OMS/WHO ivuga ko abantu 169,610 ku isi bamaze kwandura iyi ndwara, imaze kwica 6,518 naho 77,776 barayikize.
Laboratoire yitwa National Referral Laboratory mu Rwanda niyo isuzuma iyi virus.
Minisiteri y'ubuzima ivuga ko abandiye iyi ndwara ari; Umunyarwanda w'imyaka 34 wageze mu Rwanda tariki 06/03 aturutse muri Sudani y'Epfo.
Muri Sudani y'Epfo ariko kugeza ubu iyi ndwara ntabwo irahavugwa.
Minisiteri y'ubuzima ivuga ko undi ari umuvandimwe w'uyu, ufite imyaka 36 wageze mu Rwanda tariki 08/03 waje avuye mu birwa bya Fiji anyuze muri Amerika no muri Qatar.
Muri Fiji ntabwo haravugwa iyi ndwara ariko aho bavuga ko yanyuze muri Amerika imaze gufata abantu 3,782 yica 69, naho muri Qatar imaze kwandura abantu 401.
Undi, minisiteri y'ubuzima ivuga ko ari umugabo w'umunyarwanda w'imyaka 30 udaherutse kugira ingendo mu mahanga.
Naho uwa kane ni umusore w'imyaka 22 ufite ubwenegihugu bwa Uganda wageze mu Rwanda ejo ku cyumweru tariki 15 avuye i Londres mu Bwongereza.
Aba bakurikira umuhinde waje mu Rwanda tariki 05/03 nyuma bakamusangamo iyi ndwara nk'uko byatangajwe kuwa gatandatu.
Minisiteri y'ubuzima ivuga ko aba bantu bose bari kuvurirwa ahabugenewe ari nako hashakishwa abantu bahuye nabo ngo basuzumwe.
Kugeza ubu u Rwanda nirwo rufite umubare munini w'abamaze kwandura iyi ndwara mu karere.
