<doc docid='bbc_52050130' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/52050130' term='COVID'>
Covid-19: Umurwayi mushya muri Tanzania yinjiye aciye ku mupaka uyihuza n'u Burundi
Minisitiri w'ubuzima muri Tanzania yatangaje ko habonetse umurwayi mushya wa coronavirus, abayanduye ubu bakaba bamaze kuba 13.
Minisitiri w'ubuzima muri Tanzania yatangaje ko habonetse umurwayi mushya wa coronavirus, abayanduye ubu bakaba bamaze kuba 13.
Mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru, minisitiri Ummy Mwalimu yavuze ko uyu bayibonyemo ari umushoferi w'amakamyo winjiye muri Tanzania aciye ku mupaka uyihuza n'u Burundi.
Ati: "Uyu mushoferi w'amakamyo yinjiye mu gihugu aciye ku mupaka wa Kabanga uri hagati ya Tanzania n'u Burundi kuko asanzwe atwara amakamyo hagati ya DR Congo, Burundi na Tanzania".
Kabanga ni agace kari mu karere (district) ka Ngara mu Ntara ya Kagera muri Tanzania, aka gace gahana imbibi n'intara ya Kirundo mu burasirazuba bushyira amajyaruguru y'u Burundi.
Mu Burundi, kuwa kabiri nijoro minisiteri y'ubuzima yasohoye itangazo rivuga ko nta murwayi wa ufite virus ya Covid-19 uraboneka mu gihugu.
Minisiteri y'ubuzima mu Burundi yanditse kuri Twitter ko "leta y'u Burundi iri gukora iperereza ku makuru y'uwo mushoferi w'amakamyo bivugwa ko yavuye mu Burundi".
Uwo bayisanze muri Tanzania, ari mu ntara ya Kagera mu burengerazuba bwa Tanzania nk'uko minisitiri Mwalimu abivuga, ntiyatangaje andi makuru arambuye.
Madamu Ummy Mwalimu yavuze ko abantu bose babonyemo Covid-19 muri Tanzania umwe gusa muri bo ari we udaheruka mu mahanga wahuye n'uwavuye mu mahanga.
Umuntu umwe mu bari barwaye coronavirus muri Tanzania yarayikize neza, uwo ni umugore witwa Isabella Mwampampa, ubu ugiye kuva mu kato.
Tanzania imaze gufata ibipimo by'iyi ndwara 273, muri byo 13 nibyo basanzemo iyi virus naho abagera ku 111 bari mu kato ahantu hatandukanye habugenewe mu gihugu.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52298482' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52298482' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Trump ati 'virus iri kumanuka kandi vuba turasubira mu buzima busanzwe'
Perezida Donald Trump yatangaje ko Amerika yarenze igihe cy'agasongero k'imibare y'abandura Covid-19 ndetse ateganya ko leta zimwe zishobora gusubira mu buzima busanzwe muri uku kwezi.
Perezida Donald Trump yatangaje ko Amerika yarenze igihe cy'agasongero k'imibare y'abandura Covid-19 ndetse ateganya ko leta zimwe zishobora gusubira mu buzima busanzwe muri uku kwezi.
Mu ijambo avuga buri munsi uko iyi virus yifashe, Bwana Trump yavuze ko gahunda irambuye yo gufungura ubuzima busanzwe ivugwa kuri uyu wa kane amaze kuganira n'abategeka leta zigize Amerika.
Amerika ifite abantu barenga 638,000 babonyweho Covid-19  naho abarenga 30,800 yarabishe mu gihe cy'ukwezi n'igice gusa umuntu wa mbere apfuye azize iyi ndwara muri Amerika.
Bwana Trump yabwiye abanyamakuru ati: "Imibare irerekana ko twarenze agasongera mu bantu bandura. Turizera ko ibyo bizakomeza".
Abajijwe impamvu muri Amerika ariho iyi virus iri kwica abantu benshi, Bwana Trump yashinje ibindi bihugu kubeshya imibare y'abapfa.
Avugamo n'Ubushinwa, ati: "Hari umuntu koko wemera imibare ya bimwe muri ibi bihugu?"
Yatangaje ko Amerika iri no kwiga ku makuru ataremezwa avuga ko iyi virus nshya ya Covid-19 yaba yaravuye muri laboratoire i Wuhan, aho kuva mu isoko nk'uko bizwi.
Ubutegetsi bwa Trump bwihaye itariki ya 01 z'ukwezi kwa gatanu nk'igihe cyo gusubiza igihugu mu buzima busanzwe, gusa Trump yavuze ko leta zimwe zishobora kubusubiramo na mbere y'icyo gihe.
Abajijwe ko bishobora guteza akaga mu gihe abantu basubiye mu buzima busanzwe vuba, Bwana Trump yasubije ati: "No mu gukomeza gufunga harimo urupfu".
Yavuze ibijyanye n'indwara zo mu mutwe, ko nko kwiyahura bishobora kwiyongera cyane mu gihe ubukungu nabwo buri gushonga.
Miliyoni z'Abanyamerika zatakaje akazi kubera amategeko yo guhagarika ubuzima busanzwe, imibare y'abadafite akazi iri ku kigero kitigeze kibaho mbere muri Amerika.
Abaturage muri leta ya Michigan bigabije imihanda bamagana amategeko yo kubaheza mu ngo zabo.
Muri iyi leta ituwe n'abaturage hafi miliyoni 10, abarenga 27,000 banduye coronavirus naho 1,700 imaze kubica.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52242403' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52242403' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: New York ifise ibitigiri bibini vy’abanduye gusumba ibihugu vyose kw’isi
Intara ya New York muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika muri kino gihe ifise ibitigiri binini vy'abanduye coronavirus gusumba ibihugu vyose kw'isi uretse ico gihugu.
Intara ya New York muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika muri kino gihe ifise ibitigiri binini vy'abanduye coronavirus gusumba ibihugu vyose kw'isi uretse ico gihugu.
Iyo ntara yamenyesheje ko abamaze kwandura Covid-19 gushika ejo ku wa kane bageze kuri 159.937.
Iyo ntara ikaba isumbije ibihugu vyari bizwi ko ari vyo bifise abanduye benshi nka Espanye (153,000 ) hamwe n'Ubutaliyano (143,000).
U Bushinwa, aho uwo mugera watanguriye mu mpera z'umwaka uheze, bufise igitigiri ca 82.000 c'abantu bose hamwe banduye.
Amerika imaze kugera kuri 462.000 banduye uwo mugera hamwe n'abashika hafi 16.500 bahitanywe nawo.
Kw'isi yose, abashika umuliyoni 1.6 nibo bamaze kwandura, nayo 95.000 bakaba bamaze kuhasiga ubuzima.
N'aho New York ariyo ifise igitigiri kinini c'abanduye coronavirus kw'isi, ico abamaze guhitanwa n'uwo mugera (7000) kiri hasi y'ica Espanye (15.500) n'ico Ubutaliyano (18.000), n'aho gisumba incuro zirenga zibiri ico abahitanywe nawo mu Bushinwa.
Hari amasanamu yerekanywe y'abakozi bambaye imyambaro yo kwikingira impanuka bariko barahamba abapfuye mu kinogo kimwe mu gisagara ca New York.
Amasanamu yafashwe na za ndege zitagira umudereva, drones, yerekana abakozi bariko bamanuka mu kinogo kirekire bakoresheje ingazi,  aho amasandugu y'ibiziga yariko arashingurwa.
Ayo masanamu yafatiwe mu karere kitwa Hart Island, kigeze gukoreshwa n'abategetsi b'ico gisagara imyaka 150 iheze mu guhamba abapfuye batagira ab'iwabo, canke abo mu miryango itari ishoboye kwihambira abayo.
Ibikorwa vyo guhamba kuri iryo tongo ry'abapfuye vyariyongereye kubera ico kiza, biva ku munsi umwe mu ndwi bishika ku minsi itanu mu ndwi, nk'uko bimenyeshwa n'igisata kijejwe amabohero.
Abapfungwa bo mw'ibohero rya Rikers Island nibo mu bisanzwe bakora ico gikorwa, ariko kubera barengewe, vyabaye ngombwa ko barondera abandi bakozi babikora.
Umukuru w'igisagara ca New York, Bill de Blasio yavuze mu ntango z'iyi ndwi ko iryo tongo ry'abapfuye rishobora kwikorwako mu guhamba abahitanywe na kino kiza.
Igitigiri c'abahitanwa na coronavirus i New York cariyongereye gushika kuri 799 ku wa gatatu, igitigiri kinini kitari bwahebo ku munsi ugira gatatu.
Ariko buramatari w'intara ya NewYork, Andrew Cuomo, yagize icizere kinini inyuma y'aho  igitigiri c'abinjijwe ibitaro kubera covid-19 mu mavuriro ya New York cagabanutse ku ncuro igira kabiri, gushika kuri 200.
Avuga ko ivyo vyerekana ko ingingo yo kwirinda kwegerana yazanye akarusho.
Avuga ko iki kiza ari "ikibombe kiriko kirakwiragira mu bantu kidacagura, ikibi gisa n'ico twabonye ku wa 11 z'ukw'icenda 2000".
Icizere cabonetse kandi ejo ku wa kane aho ibitigiri vyari vyitezwe kurwego rw'igihugu vyagabanutse.
Dr Anthony Fauci, umwe mu bategetsi bakomeye bagize umurwi wo kurwanya coronavirus washinzwe n'ibiro vy'umukuru w'iguhugu wa Amerika.
Yabwiye ikinyamakuru NBC co muri Amerika ko ibiharuro vyerekana ko Abanyamerika bashobora kuzohitanwa na Covid-19 "bashobora kuba muri 60.000".
Mu mpera z'ukwa gatatu, uyo Dr. Fauci yari yavuze ko "abari hagati ya 100.000 na 200.000" aribo baboneka ko bashobora guhitanwa n'uwo mugera.
Ico gitigiri ca 60.000 gishobora kungana n'ic'abahitanywe n'indwara y'ibicurane hagati y'ukw'icumi 2019 n'ukwa gatatu 2020 muri Amerika, nk'uko ibiharuro bitangwa n'ubutegetsi bivyerekana.
Hagati aho, icegera c'umukuru w'ico gihugu Mike Pence ashimangira ko covid-19 yandukira gusumba indwara y'ibicurane hafi incuro zitatu.
Ibiro vy'umukuru w'igihugu vyarerekanye ubwoba ko abashika imiliyoni 2.2 z'Abanyamerika bashobora guhitanwa na coronavirus mu gihe atacokorwa ngo uwo mugera uhagarare.
</doc>
