Covid-19: Perezida Museveni yatangaje ibihe bidasanzwe muri Uganda
Perezida Museveni wa Uganda amaze gutangaza ibindi byemezo mu gihugu mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 bigamije kurwanya ikwirakwira rya coronavirus.
Perezida Museveni wa Uganda amaze gutangaza ibindi byemezo mu gihugu mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 bigamije kurwanya ikwirakwira rya coronavirus.
Yari aherutse gutangaza ihagarikwa ryo gutwara abantu muri rusange mu gihugu hose.
Muri Uganda, kuva haboneka umuntu wa mbere wanduye iyi ndwara tariki 20/03/2020 kugeza uyu munsi tariki 30/03/2020 hamaze kuboneka abantu 33 banduye iyi virus.
Bwana Museveni yavuze ko guhera saa sita z'iri joro uyu munsi ingendo z'abantu mu gihugu hose zibujijwe.
Yavuze ko uyu mwanzuro ufashwe utunguranye kugira ngo bibuze abantu guhita bakora ingendo bava mu mijyi bajya mu cyaro aho bashobora gushyira iyo ndwara abantu baho.
Bwana Museveni yavuze ko guhura kw'abantu barenze batanu bitemewe, kereka abari gushyingura.
Yavuze ko guhera ejo kuwa kabiri hashyizweho umukwabu uzajya utangira saa moya z'ijoro kugeza saa kumi n'imwe za mugitondo, abantu bose bakaguma mu ngo zabo uretse abatwara imizigo.
Yatangaje ko kuva tariki 01/04/2020 inzu zose z'ubucuruzi zifunga uretse gusa izicuruza ibiribwa, imiti, n'ibikenerwa by'amatungo.
Aha yagize ati: "Ibi bigomba kubahirizwa mutazagira ngo ni wa munsi wo kubeshya."
Yavuze ko abakozi bose ba leta baguma mu ngo zabo kereka gusa abasirikare, abapolisi, abaganga n'abandi bazatangazwa na minisitiri w'intebe.
Bwana Museveni yavuze ko umuntu uzafatwa akoranya abantu benshi azakurikiranwaho icyaha cy'ubwinjiracyaha cyo kwica, kuko bazamufata nk'ushaka gukwiza iyi virus.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52180710' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52180710' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Mu Burundi abakinnyi babujijwe kwishimira igitego mu kivunge
Shampiyona y'umupira w'amaguru mu Burundi irakomeje, gusa mu kwirinda coronavirus abakinnyi babujijwe kwishimira igitego mu kivunge, abafana nabo bagomba gukaraba intoki binjiye kuri stade.
Shampiyona y'umupira w'amaguru mu Burundi irakomeje, gusa mu kwirinda coronavirus abakinnyi babujijwe kwishimira igitego mu kivunge, abafana nabo bagomba gukaraba intoki binjiye kuri stade.
Kugeza ubu mu Burundi habonetse abantu batatu bafite icyorezo cya Covid-19.
Ishyirahamwe ry'umupira w'amaguru mu Burundi ryatangaje ko mu nama rusange y'amakipe na minisiteri y'ubuzima yabaye muri Weekend, bemeje ko shampiyona y'umupira w'amaguru ikomeza.
Imikino mu bihugu byinshi mu karere no ku isi yarahagaritswe kubera iki cyorezo,  gusa mu bindi bihugu nka Belarus, Nicaragua na Tajikistan shampiyona zaho zirakomeje nk'uko Reuters ibivuga.
Mu Burundi ariko batangaje ingamba nshya ku bibuga zirimo;
Muri weekend, ku mikino ya shampiyona mu Burundi habonetse abafana benshi kandi begeranye ku bibuga, iminsi ine hatangajwe abantu ba mbere bafite coronavirus mu Burundi .
Muri weekend, ku mukino wahuje Messager Ngozi na Vital'O warangiye ari 0 - 0 wagaragayeho abantu benshi ku kibuga, Messager Ngozi niyo ubu ya mbere muri shampiyona.
Ishyirahamwe ry'umupira w'amaguru mu Burundi rivuga ko ubu ku bibuga by'umupira hatangiye gushyirwa indobo zirimo imiti kugira ngo abafana nabo bakarabe intoki mbere yo kwinjira.
Mu bisanzwe, mbere y'umukino abakinnyi b'amakipe batonda umurongo bakaramutsa abasifuzi nabo bakaramukanya, ibi nabyo ubu birabujijwe.
Kimwe no kuramukanya kw'abakinnyi, abasifuzi cyangwa abatoza nyuma y'umukino, nabyo birabujijwe.
Ibihugu byo muri aka karere Kenya, Rwanda, Uganda na Tanzania byahise bihagarika shampiyona z'umupira w'amaguru nyuma y'uko iyi ndwara igeze muri ibi bihugu.
Umukino wa UEFA Champions League wabaye tariki 19/02/2020 hagati ya Atalanta yo mu Butaliyani na Valencia yo muri Espagne, waba warakwije bidasanzwe iki cyorezo muri ibi bihugu.
Ikinyamakuru Marca kivuga nyuma y'uyu mukino wabereye kuri stade San Siro ijyamo abantu 40,000 mu majyaruguru y'Ubutaliyani, habonetse abantu benshi muri aka gace banduye iyi ndwara.
Umukino wo kwishyura muri Espegne hagati ya Atalanta na Valencia wabaye nta bantu bemerewe kujya ku kibuga, ariko abakinnyi benshi b'aya makipe nyuma babasanzemo coronavirus.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_52091341' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/52091341' term='COVID'>
Uko byifashe ahandi: Muri Espagne Covid-19 yishe abantu 812 mu masaha 24
Kugeza ubu ku isi harabarurwa abantu barenga ibihumbi 735.000 banduye Covid-19, abo imaze guhitana muri bo bararenga 34.000 naho abayikize bararenga 156.000 nk'uko bivugwa na kaminuza y'ubushakashatsi ya Johns Hopkins.
Kugeza ubu ku isi harabarurwa abantu barenga ibihumbi 735.000 banduye Covid-19, abo imaze guhitana muri bo bararenga 34.000 naho abayikize bararenga 156.000 nk'uko bivugwa na kaminuza y'ubushakashatsi ya Johns Hopkins.
Mu Butaliyani iyi ndwara imaze kwica abantu barenga 10.000  muri Espagne ho imaze kwica abarenga 7.000 mu gihe mu Bushinwa yishe abarenga 3.000.
Uko byifashe ahanyuranye:
Muri Tanzania na Kenya uyu munsi habonetse abantu bashya banduye iyi ndwara.
Muri Kenya habonetse abantu bashya umunani (8) naho muri Tanzania haboneka batanu (5).
Mu bihugu bigize umuryango wa Afurika y'iburasirazuba ubu harabarwa abanduye iyi virus 172 bamaze kuboneka.
=======
Espagne
Mu bo imaze kwica, Espagne ubu nicyo gihugu cya kabiri kizahaye nyuma y'Ubutaliyani.
Mu masaha 24 ashize abantu 812 bishwe n'iyi ndwara, abategetsi muri Espagne bavuga ko abantu bashya bagera ku 6.400 banduye iyi ndwara.
=====
Igiciro cy'ibitoro ku isi cyaguye bidasanzwe
Igiciro cy'ibitoro ku isoko mpuzamahanga cyamanutse ku kigero kitabayeho kuva mu myaka 18 ishize kubera ko isoko ryabyo ryagabanutse cyane.
Igiciro cy'akagunguru ka lisansi cyageze ku madorari ya Amerika 23 kuri uyu wa mbere mu gitondo, igiciro cyo hasi cyane giheruka mu kwa 11/2002.
Abahanga mu isoko mpuzamahanga bavuga ko nta kindi cyateye ibi uretse ikwirakwira rya Covid-19 ryahagaritse ingendo n'ubuzima busanzwe ku isi.
----
Gupima Covid-19 abadepite bose ba Kenya
Inteko ishinga amategeko ya Kenya, umutwe w'Abadepite, urashaka ko abawugize bagera kuri 50 bapimwa coronavirus kuko hari ubwoba ko bayandujwe na mugenzi wabo baherutse kuyibonamo.
Ikinyamakuru Nation cyo muri Kenya kivuga ko Inteko yahaye minisiteri y'ubuzima urutonde rw'abadepite ishaka ko basuzumwa kandi bagashyirwa mu kato.
Umudepite witwa Kamoti Mwamkale bivugwa ko yandujwe na guverineri wungirije w'intara ya Kilifi nawe wanduye mu cyumweru gishize, akaba yaherukaga kuva mu Budage.
=====
Kuki abo yica ari bacye mu Budage?
Abayanduye mu Budage ubu ni 62.435 ariko imaze kwica 541, umubare muto ugereranyije no mu bindi bihugu nk'Ubutaliyani, Ubufaransa, Espagne cyangwa Ubwongereza aho imaze kwica ibihumbi.
Igisobanuro gishoboka cyane cy'ibi ni uburyo bukomeye kandi bwihuse mu gupima:
Ubudage bwatangiye gukwirakwiza uburyo bwo gupima hakiri kare, bituma bubona abanduye benshi bagifite ibimenyetso byoroheje.
Ibi bivuze ko umubare w'abemejwe ko banduye uri hafi y'uwabashobora kuba bafite iyi virus, mu gihe ahandi aho abo byemejwe ko banduye ari agace gato k'abashobora kuba baranduye.
Ikindi gisobanuro ni ubushobozi bw'ubuvuzi bw'iki gihugu; Ubudage bufite ubushobozi bwo kuvura indembe kurusha Ubufaransa, Ubutaliyani cyangwa Ubwongereza.
Mu minsi itatu ishize mu Budage umubare w'abamenyekanye ko banduye Covid-19 wiyongereyeho abantu 4.751.
=====
Ubuhinde burahumeka umwuka mwiza
Iki cyorezo cyatumye leta y'Ubuhinde itangaza ihagarikwa ry'ubuzima busanzwe (lockdown) mu gihugu.
Ibi byatumye mu minsi micye ishize iki gihugu gifite ibipimo byo hasi cyane kurusha ibindi mu guhumana kw'ikirere, gusa nanone nta usohoka kwishimira ako kuka keza.
Ku munsi wa gatatu wo guhagarika ubuzima busanzwe, iki gikorwa cyateje impaka nyinshi n'ingorane kuri bamwe ubu gifite ingaruka nziza.
Muri New Delhi - ahantu haherutse guca umuhigo w'isi mu kirere gihumanye - muri weekend  abahatuye baramukanye ikirere cy'ubururu bucyeye.
Abafite telephone zigezweho zaberetse ibipimo byiza by'umwuka - ikintu kidasanzwe i New Delhi.
Indi mijyi igera kuri 90 y'Ubuhinde nayo yabonye ibipimo byiza by'umwuka udahumanye nk'uko ibinyamakuru byaho bibitangaza.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52425211' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52425211' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Ubutaliyani bugiye koroshya amategeko ya Guma mu rugo
Leta y'Ubutaliyani yatangaje koroshya amategeko akomeye yashyizweho mu cyumweru birindwi bishize yo kurwanya coronavirus, ni nyuma y'uko imibare y'abapfa buri munsi igeze ku gipimo cyo hasi kuva hagati mu kwezi kwa gatatu.
Leta y'Ubutaliyani yatangaje koroshya amategeko akomeye yashyizweho mu cyumweru birindwi bishize yo kurwanya coronavirus, ni nyuma y'uko imibare y'abapfa buri munsi igeze ku gipimo cyo hasi kuva hagati mu kwezi kwa gatatu.
Minisitiri w'intebe Giusepe Conte yavuze ko ibyo bizatangira tariki 04 z'ukwezi gutaha kwa gatanu, aho abantu bazemererwa gutangira gusurana ariko ari bacyeya kandi bambaye udupfukamunwa.
Za pariki zizafungurwa ariko amashuri ntazatangira kugeza mu kwezi kwa cyenda.
Ibindi bihugu nka Afurika y'Epfo, Ubusuwisi na Espagne nabyo byatangaje ko bigiye koroshya izi ngamba.
Ejo ku cyumweru, Mu Butaliyani hapfuye abantu 260, umubare muto ku munsi kuva tariki 14/03/2020. Abo iyi ndwara imaze guhitana bose ni 26,644, nibo benshi mu Burayi.
Abamaze kwandura Covid-19 mu Butaliyani ni 197,675 nk'uko bivugwa n'imibare ya kaminuza ya Johns Hopkins.
Abategetsi mu Butaliyani bavuga ko ikigereranyo cy'abantu umuntu ufite iyi virus ubu yanduza kigeze hasi, ko ariyo mpamvu bagiye koroshya amategeko asanzweho.
Avugira kuri televiziyo, minisitiri w'intebe Conte yavuze ko izo ngamba zirimo ko;
Ntihatangajwe igihe shampiyona y'umupira w'amaguru mu Butaliyani ishobora gurangirira.
Bwana Conte yavuze ko ibikorwa byo kwirinda guhura kw'abantu benshi bizakomeza mu yandi mezi ari imbere, nk'insengero zizakomeza gufungwa. Yasabye abantu gukomeza kutegerana nibura ku ntera ya 3m.
Ati: "Niba ukunda Ubutaliyani ha intera mugenzi wawe".
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52321576' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52321576' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Facebook iratangira kuburira abantu ku makuru ayobya ayishyirwaho
Abakoresha Facebook basomye, barebye cyangwa bakwiza amakuru atari yo kuri coronavirus bazabona ubutumwa bubaburira mu gihe iki kigo kiri kugerageza kurwanya gukwiza amakuru atari ukuri.
Abakoresha Facebook basomye, barebye cyangwa bakwiza amakuru atari yo kuri coronavirus bazabona ubutumwa bubaburira mu gihe iki kigo kiri kugerageza kurwanya gukwiza amakuru atari ukuri.
Ubu buryo bushya bwo kuburira abantu ni ukurwanya icyo umuryango ushinzwe ubuzima ku isi OMS witwa "infodemic" kiriho muri iki gihe cya Covid-19.
Ubushakashatsi bwigenga buvuga ko Facebook ari yo "zingiro ry'amakuru ayobya kuri coronavirus", aho byiganje cyane akaba ari mu ndimi zirimo Igisipanyole.
Kompanyi ya Facebook ivuga ko ubwo bushakashatsi bititaye ku kazi yakoze mu gihe cya vuba.
Iyi kompanyi yo muri California ivuga ko kuva mu byumweru biri imbere itangira kwereka abantu ubutumwa (pop-ups) bubaburira bagifungura konti zabo za Facebook.
Ubwo butumwa buzakujyana kuri 'page' ya OMS aho amakuru y'ibinyoma abeshyuzwa.
Umuvugizi wa Facebook avuga ko bizafasha "abantu bashobora kuba baragezweho n'amakuru ayobya kuri iyi virusi kubona amakuru yizewe y'ababishinzwe, nubwo ayo makuru ayobya baba barayabonye ahandi hatari kuri Facebook".
Izi mpinduka zigiye gukorwa kuri uru rubuga zatewe n'ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'ikigo Avaaz ku makuru atari ukuri atambuka kuri Facebook.
Abashakashatsi bavuga ko miliyoni nyinshi z'abakoresha Facebook bakomeza kubona amakuru ayobya kuri coronavirus mu gihe nta kibaburira kiri kuri uru rubuga.
Abo bashakasatsi bavuga ko ibinyoma bikomeye cyane kuri iki cyorezo birimo nka; "abirabura ntibafatwa na coronavirus" na "coronavirus yicwa na chlorine dioxide"(umuti ukoreshwa mu gusukura amazi), basanze byararebwe inshuro ibihumbi amagana.
Ikigo Avaaz kivuga ko igiteye impungenge ari uko Facebook idaha ubutumwa abayiriho ko amakuru aya n'aya atari ukuri cyangwa ayobya.
Facebook yo ivuga ko iri gukomeza kwagura abo ikorana nayo mu ndimi zirenga 50 mu kugenzura ukuri kw'amakuru ayishyirwaho.
Ikindi kinyoma aba bashakashatsi basanze cyarakwiriye, ni ikivuga ko abantu bashobora kwikiza iyi virus banyweye amazi menshi na tungurusumu n'umunyu cyangwa vinaigre/vinegar.
Nyuma yo kuyashyiraho, ayo makuru yakwirakwijwe inshuro zirenze 31,000 kuri Facebook, mbere y'uko avanwaho ubwo Avaaz yari imaze kubibwira Facebook.
Gusa, abagiye bayakwiza bo yagumye kuri konti zabo kandi nta kintu Facebook yayashyizeho cyerekana ko ayo makuru atari ukuri.
Mark Zuckerberg, washinze akaba n'umukuru wa Facebook, arengera kompanyi ye yanditse ati:
"Kuri Facebook na Instagram ubu twashyizeho uburyo bwo kujyana abantu barenga miliyari ebyiri ahari amakuru y'abashinzwe ubuzima kuri Covid-19, abarenga miliyoni 350 bakanzeho ngo bamenye byinshi".
Avuga ko iyo hari amakuru ayobya babonye bayavanaho, ko bamaze kuvanaho amakuru ayobya arenga ibihumbi amagana agendanye na Covid-19.
Bwana Zuckerberg avuga ko ubutumwa bwituyeho (pop-ups) bukora kuko 95% bahitamo kutareba ubwo butumwa iyo bwanditse bisanzwe.
Emily Taylor umuhanga mu bigendanye n'amakuru ayobya ku mbuga nkoranyambaga avuga ko batazi neza niba ibi bizakora itandukaniro rinini, gusa ati:
"Ni byiza kubigerageza kuko amakuru ayobya mu gihe cy'icyorezo ashyira ubuzima mu kaga".
</doc>
