Coronavirus: Abahanga bo muri Australia batahuye uko ubwirinzi bw'umubiri buyirwanya
Abahanga muri siyansi bo muri Australia bavuga ko batahuye ukuntu ubwirinzi bw'umubiri burwanya virusi ya Covid-19.
Abahanga muri siyansi bo muri Australia bavuga ko batahuye ukuntu ubwirinzi bw'umubiri burwanya virusi ya Covid-19.
Ubushakashatsi bwabo bugaragaza ko abantu bari koroherwa ubu bwoko bushya bwa coronavirus nkuko boroherwa ibicurane bisanzwe.
Bwasohotse ejo ku wa kabiri mu kinyamakuru cy'ubushakashatsi mu buvuzi cya Nature Medicine journal.
Gutahura utunyangingo nyirizina tw'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri turwanya Covid-19 byanafasha mu gukora urukingo rw'iki cyorezo, nkuko impuguke zibivuga.
Ku isi ubu harabarurwa abarenga 200,000 bamaze kuyandura naho abarenga 8,000 imaze kubica.
Profeseri Katherine Kedzierska, umwe mu bakoze ubwo bushakashatsi, yagize ati:
"Ibi twagezeho ni ingenzi kuko ni bwo bwa mbere twumvise mu by'ukuri uburyo ubwirinzi bwacu bw'umubiri burwanya ubu bwoko bushya bwa coronavirus".
Ubu bushakashatsi bw'abo bahanga muri siyansi bo mu kigo Peter Doherty Institute for Infection and Immunity cyo kuri Kaminuza ya Melbourne (University of Melbourne), bwashimagijwe n'izindi mpuguke.
Umwe muri izo mpuguke zindi yavuze ko ari "igikorwa cy'ingenzi kigezweho".
Hari abantu benshi bakize Covid-19, bivuze ko byari bisanzwe bizwi ko ubwirinzi bw'umubiri w'umuntu bushobora kwica burundu iyo virusi.
Ariko ubu noneho ku nshuro ya mbere, ubushakashatsi bwavumbuye amoko ane y'utunyangingo turwanya Covid-19.
Twatahuwe bakurikirana umurwayi wari urwaye byoroheje iyo virusi kandi utari usanzwe afite ubundi burwayi.
Uwo mugore w'imyaka 47 y'amavuko wo mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa, yari yagiye ku bitaro byo muri Australia. Yayikize mu gihe cy'iminsi 14.
Profeseri Kedzierska yabwiye BBC ko itsinda ry'abashakashatsi bagenzi be basuzumye "uburyo bwose uko bwakabaye bw'uko ubwirinzi bw'umubiri burwanya iyo virusi" muri uwo murwayi.
Iminsi itatu mbere yuko uwo mugore atangira koroherwa, utunyangingo twihariye twabonywe mu maraso ye.
Ku barwayi b'ibicurane cyangwa 'influenza', utwo tunyangingo nabwo nubundi tugaragara muri icyo gihe mbere yuko abarwayi bakira, nkuko Profeseri Kedzierska yabivuze.
Madamu Kedzierska yabwiye BBC ati: "Twashimishijwe cyane n'ibyo twagezeho mu bushakashatsi bwacu - n'ukuntu mu by'ukuri twashoboye gufata ifoto yuko utunyangingo tw'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri tugaragara muri uwo murwayi mbere yuko atangira koroherwa".
Yongeyeho ko byafashe ibyumweru bine abahanga muri siyansi barenga icumi ngo bagere kuri iryo sesengura.
Gutahura igihe utunyangingo tw'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri tuhagerera bishobora gufasha "guteganya aho iyo virusi izaca".
Ibi bivugwa na Profeseri Bruce Thompson, umukuru w'ishami rya za siyansi z'ubuzima kuri Kaminuza ya Swinburne University of Technology yo muri Australia.
Profeseri Thompson yabwiye BBC ati: "Iyo uzi igihe ibikorwa bitandukanye byo guhangana nayo bibera, ushobora guteganya aho ugeze ukira iyo virusi".
Greg Hunt, Minisitiri w'ubuzima wa Australia, yavuze ko ibyavuye muri ubwo bushakashatsi binashobora "kwihutisha" urukingo ndetse n'uburyo bwo mu gihe kiri imbere bwo kuvura abarwaye Covid-19.
Profeseri Kedzierska yavuze ko ubu igikurikiyeho kuri we n'abo bahanga muri siyansi bagenzi be ari ugutahura impamvu uko ubwirinzi bw'umubiri w'umuntu burwana n'iyo virusi bigira intege nke kurushaho ku bo yashegeshe.
Ati: "Ubu rwose ni ikintu cy'ingenzi gusobanukirwa n'ikibura cyangwa igitandukanye ku barwayi bapfuye cyangwa abo yashegeshe - kugira ngo tumenye uburyo twabarinda".
Mu kwezi kwa mbere uyu mwaka, icyo kigo cya Peter Doherty Institute for Infection and Immunity cyabaye icya mbere gishoboye kwigana muri 'laboratoire' uko iyo virusi iteye, cyo hanze y'Ubushinwa.
Kuva icyo gihe, cyahawe indi nkunga y'inyongera na leta ya Australia ndetse n'imfashanyo ivuye ahandi hatandukanye, harimo n'iyo cyahawe na Jack Ma, umuherwe wo mu Bushinwa utunze abarirwa muri za miliyari z'amadolari y'Amerika.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_52030946' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/52030946' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Umujyi wa Kinshasa muri DR Congo washyizwe mu kato
Perezida Félix Tshisekedi yaraye atangaje ko igihugu kiri mu bihe bidasanzwe, anatangaza ko umurwa mukuru Kinshasa ubu uri mu kato mu rwego rwo kurwanya coronavirus.
Perezida Félix Tshisekedi yaraye atangaje ko igihugu kiri mu bihe bidasanzwe, anatangaza ko umurwa mukuru Kinshasa ubu uri mu kato mu rwego rwo kurwanya coronavirus.
Yabitangaje mu ijoro ryakeye mu ijambo ryaciye kuri televiziyo y'igihugu.
Uretse gufunga imipaka yose y'igihugu, Bwana Tshisekedi yavuze ko binabujije kwinjira cyangwa gusohoka mu murwa mukuru ujya cyangwa uva mu zindi ntara kuva agitangaza iri jambo.
Imodoka, indege n'amato bitwaye imizigo nibyo byemerewe kwinjira i Kinshasa gusa.
Mu cyumweru gishize nibwo iki gihugu cyari cyatangaje ingamba ziburira abantu kugabanya ingendo zitari ngombwa.
Kugeza ubu muri DR Congo imibare y'abanduye Covid-19 igeze kuri 48, batatu bamze gupfa nk'uko bitangazwa na minisitiri w'ubuzima Bwana Eteni Longondo.
Dr. Jean-Jacques Muyembe ushinzwe ibikorwa byo kurwanya Covid-19 muri DR Congo yatangaje ko uduce dutatu (municipalities) muri 24 tugize Kinshasa ari two twabonetsemo abanduye benshi.
Benshi muri bo babonetse mu gace kitwa La Gombe, ahantu hatuwe cyane kandi haba ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi byinshi.
Uburyo iyi ndwaraikwirakwira byihuse:
Umujyi wa kabiri muri iki gihugu, Lubumbashi, kuwa mbere watangiye ibihe bidasanzwe aho ibintu byose bihagarikwa, kereka ibyangombwa cyane, mu gihe cy'amasaha 48.
Hari habonetse abantu babiri banduye iyi virus, aba bageze i Lubumbashi n'indege ya Congo Airways yavuye i Kinshasa ku cyumweru nk'uko bivugwa na Jacques Kyabula guverineri w'intara ya Katanga.
Abantu 77 bari muri iyo ndege.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52136472' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52136472' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Abahanga bo muri Australia batangiye kugerageza inkingo za Covid-19
Abahanga muri siyansi bo muri Australia batangiye kugerageza ebyiri zishobora kuzaba inkingo za coronavirus, mu magerageza y'"ingenzi" yo muri 'laboratoire'.
Abahanga muri siyansi bo muri Australia batangiye kugerageza ebyiri zishobora kuzaba inkingo za coronavirus, mu magerageza y'"ingenzi" yo muri 'laboratoire'.
Izo nkingo zakozwe na Kaminuza ya Oxford yo mu Bwongereza na kompanyi Inovio Pharmaceuticals yo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika.
Zahawe uruhushya n'ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS/WHO) rwo kugeragerezwa ku nyamaswa.
Ikigo cya Australia cyita ku bumenyi bwa siyansi kizagenzura niba izo nkingo zikora, ndetse niba nta ngaruka zagira ku bantu.
Igerageza rya mbere ry'urukingo ku bantu ryabereye muri Amerika mu kwezi gushize kwa gatatu, ariko risimbuka icyiciro cyo kubanza kugeragerezwa ku nyamaswa.
Hari izindi nkingo nyinshi zirimo gukorwa mu bice bitandukanye by'isi muri iki gihe, kandi ku muvuduko udasanzwe.
Ariko izo nkingo ziri kugeragezwa n'ikigo cya Australia cya siyansi n'ubushakashatsi bugari gishamikiye ku muryango wa Commonwealth (CSIRO) zirihariye, nkuko kibivuga.
Ikigo CSIRO kivuga ko ayo magerageza azaba abaye aya mbere yimbitse yo ku nyamaswa abanziriza ko izo nkingo zigeragerezwa ku barwayi nyabarwayi.
Abashakashatsi bavuga ko umuvuduko n'ubufatanye ku rwego rw'isi byatumye iki cyiciro cy'igerageza kigerwaho mu buryo butari bwarigeze bubaho mbere.
Dr Rob Grenfell wo mu kigo CSIRO yabwiye abanyamakuru kuri uyu wa kane ati:
"Ubusanzwe bifata hafi igihe cy'umwaka umwe kugera ku myaka ibiri kugira ngo hagerwe kuri iki cyiciro, none mu by'ukuri twakigabanyije kiba igihe cy'amezi macye".
Mu minsi micye ishize, itsinda ry'abashakashatsi bo mu kigo CSIRO bashyize ingero z'izo nkingo mu nyamaswa z'inyamabere zo mu muryango w'agasamunyiga.
Byamaze kugaragara ko izo nyamaswa zo mu muryango w'agasamunyiga zandura coronavirus mu buryo bumwe nkuko abantu bayandura.
Sars-CoV-2 ni bwo bwoko bwa coronavirus butera indwara yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero ya Covid-19. Ku isi ubu hari gukorwa inkingo zigera kuri 20 za Covid-19.
Rero ikigo CSIRO kirikugerageza ebyiri muri izo zatoranyijwe n'urugaga rwo ku isi ruri kugenzura bwinshi mu bushakashatsi bugamije kubona urukingo.
Urwo rugaga rwitwa 'Coalition for Epidemic Preparedness Innovations'.
Uburyo bumwe bushobora kuzavamo urukingo nyirizina bwakozwe na Kaminuza ya Oxford. Ni urukingo mwikorezi (vector vaccine), rukoresha virusi 'mpimbano' rwifitemo.
Bityo rugashyira intungamubiri za coronavirus mu bwirinzi bw'umubiri, ubundi rukareba uko bigenda n'uko umubiri ubyitwaramo.
Profeseri Trevor Drew ukuriye 'Laboratoire' ya Australia ipima ibijyanye n'ubuzima bw'inyamaswa aho iryo gerageza riri gukorerwa, yagize ati:
"Ariko ntabwo ziyongera [intungamubiri z'iyo coronavirus y'inkorano]…rero ntabwo bishoboka ko umuntu yarwara bitewe n'uru rukingo".
Yavuze ko urundi rukingo ruri kugeragezwa - rwa kompanyi ikora imiti Inovio Pharmaceuticals - "rutandukanye cyane [n'urwo rundi] ariko rurashimishije".
Rwakorewe gutahura intungamubiri (proteins) zimwe na zimwe coronavirus ishyira mu bwirinzi bw'umubiri, zigatuma utunyangingo tw'umubiri twihutira gukora nk'izo ntungamubiri mbere yuko ubwirinzi bw'umubiri butangira kugira icyo buzikoraho.
Profeseri Drew yagize ati: "Ni ingenzi cyane gukoresha uburyo bwo gushakiriza henshi. Biduha amahirwe menshi cyane yo kugera ku ntsinzi".
Abo bahanga muri siyansi bavuze ko ibya mbere mu bizava muri ayo magerageza y'inkingo ku nyamaswa bishobora gutangazwa mu kwezi kwa gatandatu uyu mwaka.
Mu gihe byaba bitanze umusaruro mwiza, izo nkingo zahita zoherezwa kugeragerezwa ku barwayi, bigakorerwa muri za 'laboratoire' z'ahandi ku isi.
Kuri icyo cyiciro, kwihutira kugeza uwo muti ku isoko bishobora guhita byihutishwa cyane, ariko impuguke ziburira ko haba hagisigaye nibura amezi 18 ngo urwo rukingo ruhabwe ibyangombwa ndetse rusuzumwe n'ubuziranenge.
Nk'urugero, urukingo rwa Kaminuza ya Oxford ubu ruri no gukorerwa igerageza mu yindi 'laboratoire' ku yindi nyamaswa yo mu bundi bwoko, kugira ngo rwuzuze ibisabwa n'amategeko yo muri Amerika.
Dr Grenfell yagize ati:
"Mu by'ukuri ibishobora kuvamo inkingo byose biba bihuriweho na za kompanyi n'imiryango myinshi kuko nta muryango umwe rukumbi ushobora mu by'ukuri gukora urukingo [wonyine]".
Ariko yavuze ko "afite icyizere" ku kizava muri ayo magerageza, ashingiye ku bufatanye bw'abantu n'ibigo bitandukanye ku isi bari kuyagiramo uruhare.
Ati: "Ubu ni ubufatanye bw'ukuri mu rwego rw'ubushakashatsi, muri rubanda ndetse n'abikorera ku giti cyabo kugira ngo rwose tugere ku ntsinzi aho ibintu bigeze ubu".
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52116760' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52116760' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: 'Ikintu gikomereye isi kuva ku ntambara ya kabiri y’isi' - Guterres
Uburyo icyorezo cya coronavirus kibasiye isi muri iki gihe nicyo kintu gikomereye cyane isi nyuma y'intambara ya kabiri y'isi nk'uko bivugwa na António Guterres umunyamabanga mukuru w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye(UN).
Uburyo icyorezo cya coronavirus kibasiye isi muri iki gihe nicyo kintu gikomereye cyane isi nyuma y'intambara ya kabiri y'isi nk'uko bivugwa na António Guterres umunyamabanga mukuru w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye(UN).
Yavuze ko iki cyorezo gishobora gusubiza ibintu hasi "ku rwego rutabayeho mu gihe cya vuba gishize".
Bwana Guterres yavuze ibi mu kugaragaza raporo ya UN ku ngaruka z'iki cyorezo ku mibereho n'ubukungu by'abantu.
Imibare y'abamaze kwandura iyi ndwara ku isi irasatira 860,000 mu gihe imaze kwica abarenga 42,000.
Ku mibare ya kaminuza ya Johns Hopkins, abamaze kuyandura (188,578) n'abo imaze guhitana (4,054) muri Amerika bararenga cyane abayanduye n'abo yishe mu Bushinwa aho yahereye.
Hagati aho, Espagne - kimwe mu bihugu bizahajwe cyane, mu masaha 24 ashize iyi ndwara yishe abantu 849, kugeza ubu nibo bantu benshi cyane iyi ndwara yishe ku munsi umwe.
Ari ku kicaro cya UN i New York, Bwana Guterres yagize ati: "Icyorezo gishya cya coronavirus kiri kuzahaza imiryango y'abantu, kigatwara ababo".
"Covid-19 ni ikibazo gikomeye kurusha ibindi twahuye nacyo twese hamwe kuva Umuryango w'Abibumbye washingwa."
Bwana Guterres yasabye ko habaho ubufatanye bwihutirwa mu rwego rw'ubuzima mu guhagarika ubwandu bushya no kurangiza iki cyorezo.
Yasabye ibihugu bikize gufasha ibiri mu nzira y'amajyambere cyangwa se bigahura "n'akaga ko gukwirakwirwa kw'iyi ndwa nk'umuriro w'ishyamba".
UN ivuga ko ikigereranyo cy'imirimo miliyoni 25 ku isi izabura nk'ingaruka z'iki cyorezo.
Iteganya kandi ko ishoramari mpuzamahanga rishobora kugabanuka ku kigero cya 40%.
Amakuru agezweho kuri iki cyorezoku isi ?
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52526642' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52526642' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Trump avuga ko urukingo rwayo ruzaboneka muri uyu mwaka
Perezida Donald Trump wa Amerika avuga ko yizeye neza ko leta zunze ubumwe za Amerika zizaba zifite urukingo rwa coronavirus mbere ya 2021.
Perezida Donald Trump wa Amerika avuga ko yizeye neza ko leta zunze ubumwe za Amerika zizaba zifite urukingo rwa coronavirus mbere ya 2021.
"Twizeye neza ko tuzaba dufite urukingo mu mpera z'umwaka", ni ibyo yatangaje mukiganiro na Fox News.
Abashakashatsi batandukanye ku isi barahiganirwa kugera kuri urwo rukingo, ariko benshi mur bo bavuga ko mu mwaka utaha aribwo rushobora kuba rwabonetse, rushobora kugezwa kuri benshi.
Bitandukanye n'ibyo abajyanama be bwite mu buvuzi bavuga ku gihe uru rukingo ruzabonekera, Bwana Trump we biboneka ko abangutsa icyo gihe.
Yagize ati: "Abaganga bashobora kuvuga bati 'sinari nkwiye kubivuga gutyo'. Ariko ko njye mvuga icyo ntekereza".
Isesengura rya James Gallagher umunyamakuru wa BBC wibanda kuri siyansi n'ubuvuzi
Hashize ukwezi kurenga abahanga bagerageje urukingo rwa mbere ku bantu mu mujyi wa Seattle muri Amerika.
Gusa haracyari byinshi byo gukora nubwo iryo gerageza rya mbere ryagenze neza.
Urwo rukingo rugomba kubanza kugeragezwa kenshi, kwemezwa n'abagenzuzi mu by'ubuvuzi no gushyiraho uburyo bwo gukora ingano yarwo ikenewe.
Kugira ngo zigerweho, inkingo ubusanzwe zifata imyaka, rimwe na rimwe irenga 10.
Inzobere nyinshi zivuga ko urukingo rwa Covid-19 rushobora kuboneka hagati mu mwaka wa 2021, hazaba hashize amezi ari hagati ya 12 na 18 iyi virusi igaragaye.
Ibyo nabyo byaba ari intsinzi ikomeye kuri siyansi, nubwo bitizewe nanone ko urwo rukingo ruzaba rukora neza.
Coronavirus zigera kuri enye zisanzwe ziri mu bantu. Zitera ibimenyetso nk'iby'ibicurane bisanzwe kandi kugeza ubu nta n'imwe muri zo irabonerwa urukingo.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52425217' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52425217' term='COVID'>
Amatora mu Burundi: Imyiyamamazo yatanguye mu cuka atari ciza -HRW
Kuri uyu wa 27 niho abazokwitoza mu matora yimirije mu Burundi batanguye icese imyiyamamazo mu ntumbero yo kurondera abanywanyi.
Kuri uyu wa 27 niho abazokwitoza mu matora yimirije mu Burundi batanguye icese imyiyamamazo mu ntumbero yo kurondera abanywanyi.
Abakandida indwi bitoza kurwego rw'umukuru w'igihugu,bari kumwe n'abitoza mu bashingamateka hamwe n'abahanuzi bakomine, batangura ibikorwa vyabo mu ntara zitangukanye.
Ku wa 20 z'ukwa gatanu, hategekanijwe amatora atatu, aho Abarundi bazotora umukuru w'igihugu, abashingamateka hamwe n'abahanuzi b'amakomine.
Imyiyamamazo yatanguye mu gihe mu gihugu hamaze gutorwa abantu 14 bandukiye Covid-19, hakanavugwa kandi icuka kibi ca politiki.
Human Rights Watch uyu munsi yatangaje ko ifise amakenga ko amatora atazoba mu mwidegemvyo, aho ivuga ko igihugu kirangwamwo agatotezo n'ayandi mabi akorerwa abatavuga rumwe n'ubutegetsi.
Mu kiganiro yahaye abanyamakuru mu mpera z'indwi iheze, umukuru w'umurwi ujejwe gutegura amatora mu Burundi, CENI, amenyesha ko imyiyamamazo izokwama itangura isaha cumi na zibiri z'igitondo ikarangira isaha cumi na zibiri z'umugoroba.
Pierre-Claver Kazihise umukuru wa CENI asaba abahiganwa gukora ibikorwa vyabo vyo kwiyamamaza bubahiriza umutekano kandi bagakurikiza amategeko agenga amakoraniro mu kwirinda Covid-19.
Bwana Kazihise kandi asaba abahiganwa kwirinda amajambo yo gutyoza canke gutuka abo bariko barahiganwa.
Mu bahiganira ikibanza c'umukuru w'igihugu, Evariste Ndayishimiye w'umugambwe CNDD-FDD uri kubutegetsi uyu munsi aza kwugururira ibikorwa muri komine Bugendana y'intara ya Gitega.
Agathon Rwasa w'umugambwe utavuga rumwe n'ubutgetsi, CNL, aza gutangurira ibikorwa vyiwe mu ntara ya Ngozi.
Abandi bahiganirwa ico kibanza harimwo Gaston Sindimwo aserukira umugambwe Uprona, Léonce Ngendakumana aserukira umugambwe FRODEBU, hamwe na Domitien Ndayizeye aserukira urunani Kira Burundi.
Hampande y'abaserukira imigambwe, hari kandi n'abigenga babiri aribo Francis Rohero hamwe na Dieudonné Nahimana.
Ishirahamwe Human Rights Watch riharanira agateka ka zina muntu, rivuga ko iyo myiyamamazo itanguye mu gihe iterabwoba n'ikubagurwa ku batavuga rumwe n'ubutegetsi hamwe n'abamenyeshamakuru" vyiraye mu gihugu.
Iryo shirahamwe rivuga ko abakora ayo mabi babarizwa mu bategetsi bo hasi, bamwe mu nzego zijejwe umutekano no mu muhari w'urwaruka rw'umugambwe uri ku butegetsi, Imbonerakure, kandi bo ubutungane butabakurikirana.
Lewis Mudge arongoye igisata ca HRW igisata ca Afrika yo hagati avuga ati: "Ubukozi bw'ikibi n'ikubagurwa nivyo birangwa mu Burundi kuva mu 2015…
"Biragaragara ko ayo matora azorangwamwo ayandi mabi, aho abategetsi b'u Burundi n'abari mu Imbonerakure bakoresha igikenye kandi ntibahanwe, mu ntumbero yo gufasha umugambwe uri ku butegetsi gutsimbatara kubutegetsi".
HRW ivuga ko mu mezi atandatu aheze mu Burundi hibonekeje ubwicanyi, ihohotera, inyuruza, guhagarika abantu bidaciye mu mategeko, iterabwoba n'ikubagurwa, vyakorewe abatavuga rumwe n'ubutegetsi.
HRW isaba abategetsi b'u Burundi  kwihaniza abanywanyi hamwe n'abarongoye Imbonerakure guhagarika ayo mabi.
Sibwo bwa mbere umuhari w'imbonerakure, bamwe mu nzego zijejwe umutekano n'abategetsi bakomoka mu mugambwe uri ku butegetsi bagirizwa amabi nk'ayo, ivyamye vyiyamirizwa n'ubutegetsi hamwe n'abarongoye CNDD-FDD.
Umugambwe utavuga rumwe n'ubutegetsi CNL urongowe n'icegera ca mbere c'umukuru w'Inama nshingamateka, Agathon Rwasa, umenyesha ko abanywanyi bawo irya n'ino mu gihugu bahohoterwa, bagaterwa ubwoba, bakanyuruzwa abandi nabo bakanicwa.
Umugambwe CNDD-FDD wowo uvuga ko ibibazo hagati y'abanyamigambwe biganirwako mw'ihuriro ry'abaserukira iyo migambwe ryama riba uko ukwezi gutashe ritegurwa n'ubushikiranganji bw'intwaro yo hagati.
Amatora arateguwe mu gihe mu Burundi naho nyene havugwa ikiza cacoronavirus, abashika 14 gushika ubu nibo bamaze gutangazwa ko banduye, n'aho muri bo bane(4) bakize kandi basubiye mu miryango yabo.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_52016610' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/52016610' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Mu gihe isi ikomerewe, Wuhan aho yahereye bari koroherwa
Abategetsi bo mu Bushinwa bavuga ko ingamba zari zisanzweho zo guhagarika ubuzima mu mujyi wa Wuhan aho icyorezo cya coronavirus cyatangiriye mu mwaka ushize, igice kimwe cyazo kizakurwaho ku itariki ya 8 y'ukwezi gutaha kwa kane.
Abategetsi bo mu Bushinwa bavuga ko ingamba zari zisanzweho zo guhagarika ubuzima mu mujyi wa Wuhan aho icyorezo cya coronavirus cyatangiriye mu mwaka ushize, igice kimwe cyazo kizakurwaho ku itariki ya 8 y'ukwezi gutaha kwa kane.
Ingendo zari zarahagaritswe mu bindi bice by'intara ya Hubei, ari nayo irimo umujyi wa Wuhan, zirongera gusubukurwa guhera saa sita z'ijoro zo kuri uyu wa kabiri - ku baturage bafite ubuzima bwiza.
Umuntu umwe gusa mushya ni we watangajwe kuri uyu wa kabiri ko yanduye Covid-19 muri uyu mujyi, hari hashize hafi icyumweru nta muntu n'umwe uhatangazwa ko yayanduye.
Ibihugu bitandukanye ku isi biri guhagarika ubuzima busanzwe, ibindi nabyo bishyiraho amabwiriza abuza byinshi mu bikorwa bisanzwe byo mu buzima bwa buri munsi.
Hagati aho, impuguke mu buvuzi zivuga ko Abanyamerika bagomba kugabanya ibikorwa bibahuza, bitaba ibyo umubare w'abandura ukazarengera urwego rw'ubuzima muri icyo gihugu rugasigara rutagishoboye guhangana n'ubwo bwandu bushya.
Abasirikare bo muri Espanye bari gutanga ubufasha mu guhangana n'iki cyorezo, batahuye abarwayi bageze mu zabukuru aho babaga mu nzu yabagenewe, batereranywe, ndetse hamwe na hamwe, bapfiriye mu buriri bwabo, nkuko bitangazwa na minisiteri y'ingabo muri icyo gihugu.
Ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS/WHO) ryaburiye ko iki cyorezo kiri kongera umuvuduko.
Ubu abantu banduye bamaze kwegera 400,000. OMS iri gusaba ibihugu gushyiraho uburyo bwimbitse bwo gupima iyo virusi ndetse no gufata ingamba zihamye zo gutahura abagize aho bahurira n'abanduye.
Kuva hagati mu kwezi kwa mbere, umujyi wa Wuhan warafunzwe kuburyo nta muntu uwusohokamo.
Ariko ubu abategetsi bavuga ko buri muntu wese wahawe "uruhushya" binyuze kuri 'app' y'ubuzima ikoreshwa cyane kuri telefone zigezweho (smartphones), azemererwa kuva muri uyu mujyi guhera ku itariki ya 8 y'ukwezi gutaha kwa kane.
Mbere yaho kuri uyu munsi, abategetsi batangaje ko hari umuntu umwe mushya wanduye coronavirus, bisoza iminsi itanu yari ishize nta wundi muntu mushya wanduye iyo virusi muri uwo mujyi.
Imibare ya leta y'Ubushinwa ivuga ko mu Bushinwa hose abantu 78 bashya ari bo banduye iyo ndwara mu masaha 24 ashize.
Uretse bane gusa banduye bitewe n'abagenzi bageze mu gihugu, abandi bose bavuye mu mahanga.
Iki kiri kwitwa "icyiciro cya kabiri" cy'ubwandu buzanano kiri no kugira ingaruka ku bihugu nka Koreya y'epfo na Singapour, ubundi byari byarashoboye guhagarika ikwirakwira ry'ubwandu mu byumweru bicye bishize.
Umubare w'abandura bashya buri munsi ukomeje kugabanuka muri Koreya y'epfo.
Kuri uyu wa kabiri, yatangaje umubare wayo uri hasi cyane w'abanduye ku munsi wa mbere guhera ku itariki ya 29 y'ukwezi gushize kwa kabiri.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52136705' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52136705' term='COVID'>
China: Umujyi wa Shenzhen wabujije kongera kurya imbwa n’injangwe
Shenzhen wabaye umujyi wa mbere wo mu Bushinwa utegetse guhagarika ubucuruzi ndetse no kurya inyama z'imbwa n'injangwe.
Shenzhen wabaye umujyi wa mbere wo mu Bushinwa utegetse guhagarika ubucuruzi ndetse no kurya inyama z'imbwa n'injangwe.
Ni nyuma y'uko icyorezo cya coronavirus bivuzwe ko cyakomotse ku nyama z'inyamaswa, byatumye abategetsi mu Bushinwa bahagarika kurya no kugurisha bene izo 'mbonekarimwe'.
Shenzen ariko yo yateye indi ntambwe, igera no ku guca kurya imbwa n'injangwe. Iri tegeko rizatangira gukurikizwa tariki 01/05/2020.
Imbwa zigera kuri miliyoni 30 ziricwa buri mwaka muri Aziya ngo bazirye nk'uko bivugwa n'ikigo Humane Society International (HSI).
Gusa mu Bushinwa, hari umubare munini w'Abashinwa batarya imbwa.
Ubutegetsi bw'umujyi wa Shenzhen buvuga ko "imbwa n'injangwe byacuditse n'abantu kurusha izindi nyamaswa, kandi hari n'ahandi bibujijwe kurya izi nyamaswa nko muri Hong Kong na Taiwan".
Iki cyemezo cyishimiwe na HSI iharanira uburenganzira bw'inyamaswa.
Dr Peter Li wo muri iki kigo yagize ati: "Iyi ni intambwe nziza ishobora guhagarika ubucuruzi bubi butuma mu Bushinwa hicwa imbwa zigera kuri miliyoni 10 n'injangwe miliyoni 4 buri mwaka".
Gusa mu Bushinwa nanone ubu bemeje ikoreshwa ry'urugingo ruzwi nka 'bile' rw'inyamaswa z'ibirura (bears) mu kuvura abarwaye coronavirus.
Urwo rugingo rugizwe n'amatembabuzi ava mu mwijima w'ikirura, rusanzwe rukoreshwa mu buvuzi gakondo mu Bushinwa.
Abo mu miryango iharanira uburenganzira bw'inyamaswa bamaganye iki cyemezo, bavuga ko uyu atari umuti wemejwe n'abahanga ko uvura iyi virusi.
Kugeza ubu, abanduy eiyi virusi ku isi barasatira miliyoni imwe, abo imaze kwica bararenga 47,000 nk'uko bivugwa na kaminuza y'ubushakashatsi ya Johns Hopkins.
Mu Bushinwa abanduye iyi ndwara ni 81,589 naho abo yishe ni 3,318, ni imibare itangwa n'ikigo cya leta y'Ubushinwa gishinzwe ubuzima.
Abahanga mu bushakashatsi mu by'ubuzima ntibarabona umuti cyangwa urukingo rw'iyi virusi bise Covid-19.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_52184616' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/52184616' term='COVID'>
Ghana: Abaganga bahanganye na Covid-19 bongejwe 50%, abaturage nabo ntibazishyuzwa amazi
Perezida Nana Akufo-Addo wa Ghana ejo ku cyumweru yantangaje ko leta izishyurira abaturage bose amazi  mu gihe cy'amezi atatu uhereye muri uku kwa kane, naho abakozi bo mu rwego rw'ubuzima bahanganye na coronavirus umushahara wabo wongeweho 50%.
Perezida Nana Akufo-Addo wa Ghana ejo ku cyumweru yantangaje ko leta izishyurira abaturage bose amazi  mu gihe cy'amezi atatu uhereye muri uku kwa kane, naho abakozi bo mu rwego rw'ubuzima bahanganye na coronavirus umushahara wabo wongeweho 50%.
Gukaraba intoki n'amazi meza n'isabune ni bumwe mu buryo bukomeye abahanga bavuga ko burinda gukwirakwiza iyi virus.
Muri Ghana hamaze kuboneka abantu 214 banduye Covid-19, muri bo batanu imaze kubica naho batatu barayikize.
Mu ijambo ryaciye kuri televiziyo y'igihugu, Bwana Akufo-Addo yavuze ko hejuru ya biriya, abakora mu rwego rw'ubuzima bose bazasonerwa imisoro ku mishahara yabo mu mezi atatu ari imbere uhereye muri uku kwa kane.
Bwana Akufo-Addo yavuze ko ibi ari ibyemezo bigamije gufasha abantu guhangana n'ingaruka mu bukungu z'izi ngamba zo kurwanya iki cyorezo.
Mu cyumweru gishize, Ghana yafashe ingamba zo kurwanya ikwirakwira ry'iyi ndwara zirimo guhagarika ubuzima busanzwe (lockdwon) mu mijyi ya Accra, Tema na Kumasi aho iyi virus yiganje mu gihugu.
Kompanyi igurisha amashanyarazi nayo yategetswe kutagira umuntu ikuriraho amashanyarazi muri iki gihe.
Bwana Akufo-Addo yategetse ibi bigo byombi - igitanga amazi n'igitanga amashanyarazi - gukora ibishoboka ibyo byombi ntibibure muri ibi bihe.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_52051942' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/52051942' term='COVID'>
Covid-19: Ba minisitiri bo muri EAC bahuriye mu nama kuri video biga kuri iki cyorezo
Umuryango w'ibihugu bya Afurika y'iburasirazuba watangaje ko ejo kuwa gatatu abaminisitiri bashinzwe ubuzima n'abashinzwe ibireba uyu muryango mu bihugu biwugize, bakoze inama (video conference) kuri iki cyorezo.
Umuryango w'ibihugu bya Afurika y'iburasirazuba watangaje ko ejo kuwa gatatu abaminisitiri bashinzwe ubuzima n'abashinzwe ibireba uyu muryango mu bihugu biwugize, bakoze inama (video conference) kuri iki cyorezo.
Iyi nama niyo ya mbere itangajwe n'uyu muryango yahuje aba bategetsi kuri iki cyorezo cya Covid-19.
Itangazo ryasohowe n'uyu muryango, rivuga ko iyi nama yari igamije "guhana amakuru kuri Covid-19, gufatira hamwe ingamba, gushyiraho uburyo bwo gukumira ikwirakwira ryayo mu karere no guhangana n'ingaruka zayo".
Kugeza ubu, mu bihugu bitandatu bigize uyu muryango bibiri nibyo bitarabonekamo ubwandu bw'iyi virus; u Burundi na Sudani y'Epfo.
Mu myanzuro yafashwe n'aba ba minisitiri harimo;
Gusaba ibihugu bigize uyu muryango gukomeza gushyira mu kato k'iminsi 14 abaza muri aka karere.
Gusaba ibi bihugu gukomeza gusuzuma 100% abinjira n'abasohoka hakoreshejwe uburyo bugezweho bwifashisha imirasire mu kwirinda icyuho mu bagenzi bashobora kuyikwiza.
Bemeje ko urujya n'uruza rw'ibicuruzwa mu karere rukomeza ariko imodoka zibitwara zikagenzurwa ko zitarengeje abantu batatu, nabo bagasuzumwa kuko bari mu bafite ibyago byo kwandura no kwanduza.
Bavuze ko ibyo batwaye mbere yo kwambuka bizajya bibanza gukizwa ibishobora kubyanduza kandi ababitwaye bagashyirwa mu kato k'iminsi 14 bigendanye n'amabwiriza y'aho bagiye.
Mu rugendo rwabo, abatwara amakamyo basabwe guhagarara ahantu hagenwe gusa mu kwirinda ko habaho gukwirakwiza iyo ndwara.
Aba bategetsi bashyizeho uburyo bahuriyeho bwo kugenzura ibyo bumvikanyeho no guhanahana amakuru kuri iki cyorezo mu karere nk'uko itangazo ryabo ribivuga.
Kugeza uyu munsi nimugoroba mu bihugu bya Kenya, Rwanda, Tanzania na Uganda harabarwa abantu 99 bamaze kwandura iyi virus, imibare iri igenda yiyongera.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52282733' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52282733' term='COVID'>
IMF ivuga ko ‘isi yugarijwe n’ihungabana ry’ubukungu rya mbere ribi guhera mu myaka ya 1930’
Ikigega cy'isi cy'imari (IMF/FMI) kivuga ko ubukungu bw'isi buzagabanukaho 3% uyu mwaka muri iki gihe ubukungu bw'ibihugu ku isi buri kugabanuka byihuse cyane bwa mbere mu myaka ibarirwa muri za mirongo ishize.
Ikigega cy'isi cy'imari (IMF/FMI) kivuga ko ubukungu bw'isi buzagabanukaho 3% uyu mwaka muri iki gihe ubukungu bw'ibihugu ku isi buri kugabanuka byihuse cyane bwa mbere mu myaka ibarirwa muri za mirongo ishize.
IMF ivuga ko iri ari ryo hungabana ry'ubukungu bw'isi ribi cyane ribayeho nyuma y'iryabayeho mu myaka ya 1930 ryiswe 'Great Depression'.
Ivuga ko icyorezo cya coronavirus cyashoye isi mu "kaga ntagereranywa".
Iki kigega cyongeyeho ko mu gihe iki cyorezo cyaba gikomeje byagira ingaruka ku bushobozi bwa za leta na banki z'ibihugu bwo kugihagarika.
Gita Gopinath, ukuriye impuguke mu bukungu za IMF, yavuze ko akaga katewe na coronavirus gashobora kugabanura tiriyari (trillion) 9 z'amadolari y'Amerika ku musaruro mbumbe w'ibihugu mu myaka ibiri iri imbere.
Iri teganya ry'ishusho y'ubukungu bw'isi rya IMF rishimagiza uburyo "bwihuse kandi bwagutse" mu bihugu nk'Ubwongereza, Ubudage, Ubuyapani n'Amerika bwo guhangana na coronavirus.
Ariko IMF yavuze ko nta gihugu na kimwe kitazakorwaho n'iri hungabana ry'ubukungu.
Iki kigega cyiteze ko mu mwaka utaha ubukungu bw'isi buziyongera ku kigero cya 5.8% niba coronavirus igenjeje macye mu gice cya kabiri cy'uyu mwaka wa 2020.
Madamu Gopinath yavuze ko ibihe bidasanzwe byashyizweho kubera coronavirus ari "ukuri kuryana" ku bakora igenamigambi mu bihugu bitandukanye ku isi.
Avuga ko ubu abo "bari mu rujijo rw'igihe bizamara n'ingaruka bizateza".
Madamu Gopinath yagize ati: "Kuzahuka gucagase [mu bukungu bw'isi] kwitezwe kuba mu mwaka wa 2021.
"Ariko ikigero cy'umusaruro mbumbe [GDP] kizaguma kiri munsi y'uko byari bimeze mu bihe bya mbere y'iyi virusi, ndetse hari n'urujijo rwinshi ku kuba niba ibyo bizarama.
"Biranashoboka ko ubukungu bwakwiyongera nabi kurushaho".
Madamu Gopinath yavuze ko ku nshuro ya mbere guhera mu gihe cy'ihungabana ry'ubukungu bw'isi ryiswe 'Great Depression', ubu noneho ibihugu bikize n'ibiri mu nzira y'amajyambere byose ubukungu bwabyo buzahungabana.
IMF yaburiye ko kwiyongera mu bukungu mu bihugu bikize kutazongera kugera hejuru bwari buri mbere yuko coronavirus yaduka, atari nibura mu mwaka wa 2022.
Nubwo ibihe bidasanzwe by'akato bizagira ingaruka ku bukungu, IMF ivuga ko ibyo ari ngombwa cyo kimwe n'ingamba zo kwirinda kwegerana.
Igira iti: "Ingamba z'ukuri ni ingenzi mu kugabanya umuvuko wa virusi ndetse no gufasha inzego z'ubuzima guhangana no gucira inzira urwego rw'ubukungu ngo rwongere rukore kare kandi rufite ingufu nyinshi kurushaho.
"Urujijo n'igabanuka rya serivisi nkenerwa bishobora kuba bibi kurushaho mu gihe virusi yaba yiyongereye cyane nta n'uburyo bwo kutegerana buriho".
IMF kandi yatangaje ingamba enye zihutirwa zo guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Yasabye ko inzego z'ubuzima zihabwa andi mafaranga yo gukoresha n'abakora mu nzego z'ubuvuzi n'ubucurizi bagaterwa inkunga y'amafaranga.
Yanasabye ko banki nkuru z'ibihugu zikomeza gufashwa ndetse hagashyirwaho gahunda yumvikana neza yuko ibintu bizagenda nyuma yo gusohoka muri iki gihe cya coronavirus.
IMF yasabye isi gusenyera ku mugozi umwe mu gushaka no gukwirakwiza imiti n'inkingo.
Yongeyeho ko ibihugu byinshi biri mu nzira y'amajyambere bizacyenera gusonerwa imyenda, mu mezi no mu myaka iri imbere.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-51987250' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-51987250' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Umuririmbyi Kidum ati, 'Dukora ahahurira abantu benshi, bitagishoboka duca twicara muhira'
Jean-Pierre Nimbona uzwi cyane nka Kidum, umuririmbyi w'Umurundi uzwi cyane muri aka karere k'Afurika y'uburasirazuba uba muri Kenya, avuga ko ari ibintu birenze ukwemera kuba ubu abantu benshi ku isi batagisohoka mu nzu zabo atari ukubera intambara cyangwa imyuzure, ahubwo ari ukubera icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Jean-Pierre Nimbona uzwi cyane nka Kidum, umuririmbyi w'Umurundi uzwi cyane muri aka karere k'Afurika y'uburasirazuba uba muri Kenya, avuga ko ari ibintu birenze ukwemera kuba ubu abantu benshi ku isi batagisohoka mu nzu zabo atari ukubera intambara cyangwa imyuzure, ahubwo ari ukubera icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Mu kiganiro na BBC Gahuzamiryango, Kidum yavuze ko nubwo umuryango we - cyo kimwe n'iyindi myinshi muri Kenya - wari wahashye ukiziganira ibiribwa uko iki cyorezo cyagendaga kirushaho gukara, ubu bigoye ku muririmbyi nka we ubona icyo kurya ari uko yakoresheje ibitaramo.
Ati: "Tuguma duteka indya (ibiribwa) dufise mu nzu, hanyuma abana na bo barabaturungikiye, ku ma 'internats' (ibigo aho abanyeshuri biga ari naho baba), ubu tubana n'abana muhira, amashuri yose yarugaye, urumva ni ibintu bigoye kabisa (rwose) gutahura".
"Akazi kacu twebwe, dukora ahantu hahurira abantu benshi, rero ibyo bitagishoboka, urumva duca twicamara muhira".
"Mu gutangura rero kwicara, urumva nta kazi gushika isi ironse umuti w'iyi ngorane dufise, [umuti] wa coronavirus".
Avuga ko nk'umuhanzi ukoresha ibitaramo ahantu hatandukanye hahurira abantu benshi harimo no mu tubari two mu murwa mukuru Nairobi, iki cyorezo kimaze kumugiraho ingaruka zikomeye mu mibereho ye kubera ko abategetsi babujije guterana kw'abantu benshi nk'ingamba yo kwirinda ikwirakwira rya coronavirus.
Ati: "Ncuraranga kuva ku munsi wa kabiri gushika ku munsi wa Mungu, rero ntagicuraranga ubuzima nari nsanzwe mbayemo burahindutse, byaciye rero kandi gutangira kwikora ku ntegabizoza (ku mafaranga y'ubwizigame), urumva si ibintu byoroshye, si ibintu byoroshye, sininjiza nguma ndya ibyo nakoreye gusa kera".
Avuga ko kandi hari ibitaramo yateganyaga gukora byamaze gusubikwa harimo nk'igitaramo cyari kuzabera mu mujyi wa Mombasa ku munsi mukuru wa Pasika, kubera ko abategetsi baho bahagaritse ibintu byose bijyanye n'inzu z'urubyiniro, utubari n'amahoteli.
Hasubitswe kandi n'igitaramo yateganyaga gukorera i Kampala muri Uganda.
Nubwo bimeze gutyo ariko, Kidum w'imyaka 45 y'amavuko yabwiye BBC ko muri iki gihe asigaye amara igihe kinini mu rugo, anyuzamo agafata akanya ko guhimba indirimbo azacuranga igihe iki cyorezo cyaba kirangiye.
Avuga ko iyo amaze guhimba ubu yitwa 'Hatuachani', mu Giswayile, bishatse kuvuga ngo 'Ntiturekanye', ugenekereje mu Kinyarwanda.
Amwe mu magambo yo muri iyo ndirimbo agira ati:
"Imbaraga zaheze kabisa, inguvu zaheze, hanyuma kandi n'inyota yose yo kunywa amazi yaheze, meze sawa, nguma nicaye, nguma nsamara ndiko ndakuraba".
"Ariko coronavirus irakaranduka, irakagenda kabisa, icyo kintu cyaje kutwononera umufuko wacu, hanyuma no kuzana kwicyekana mu bantu aho umuntu yasamuye [yitsamuye], bimwe bisanzwe gusa byo kwasamura 'tse', abantu baca biruka bibaza yuko umengo urabanduje kandi".
Muri aka karere, kugeza ubu muri Kenya abantu 7 ni bo bamaze gutangazwa ko banduye indwara ya Covid-19 yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero iterwa n'ubu bwoko bushya bwa coronavirus.
Mu Burundi nta muntu bari bayisangamo cyo kimwe no muri Uganda, mu gihe mu Rwanda bamaze kuyisanga mu bantu 17, Repubulika ya Demokarasi ya Kongo ifite abarwayi 23 naho Tanzania batandatu.
Ku isi abarenga 280,000 bamaze kuyandura, naho abarenga 11,000 imaze kubica.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_52103483' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/52103483' term='COVID'>
Covid-19: Muri Botswana habonetse abantu ba mbere bayanduye
Umukuru w'igihugu ca Botswana ahamagarira abanyagihugu  gushira umutima mu nda inyuma y'aho ico gihugu gitangarije abantu ba mbere banduye umugera wa coronavirus.
Umukuru w'igihugu ca Botswana ahamagarira abanyagihugu  gushira umutima mu nda inyuma y'aho ico gihugu gitangarije abantu ba mbere banduye umugera wa coronavirus.
Umushikiranganji w'amagara y'abantu muri ico gihugu, Lems Kwape,  yatangaje ko hari ingenzi zitatu - babiri bavuye muri Thailand uwundi mu Bwongereza - bapimwe bagasanga baranduye uwo mugera.
Perezida Masisi amenyesha ko igihugu ciwe cari cariteguye guhangana n'uwo mugera, kandi ko categekanije uburyo bwo gukingira abanyagihugu.
Botswana cari mu bihugu bike vya Afrika bitari bwigere vyandukirwa n'uwo mugera ruhonyabantu, hampande ya Lesotho, amazinga ya Comores, Sierra Leone, Sudani y'Epfo, u Burundi na São Tomé et Príncipe.
Perezida Masisi asaba abanyagihugu gukurikiza ingingo zo kwikingira uwo mugera zishobora gutangazwa umwanya uwo ari wo wose n'abajejwe amagara y'abantu.
Leta imenyesha ko umukuru w'igihugu ahava ashikiriza ijambo kuri uno munsi wa kabiri.
Ku mugabane wa Afrika, hamaze kwibonekeza abanduye uwo mugera bashika 5319, muri bo 330 bakaba bamaze gukira, nayo 174 bakaba baritavye Imana.
Afrika y'Epfo nico gihugu gifise abantu benshi banduye uwo mugera muri Afrika, bashika ku 1,326 , muri bo 31 barakize, nayo batatu bakaba bamaze gupfa.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52430090' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52430090' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Abo Covid-19 imaze kwica ku isi barenze 200,000
Abantu barenga 200,000 ku isi bamaze kwicwa n'icyorezo cya coronavirus naho abarenga 800,000 bamaze kugikira, nkuko imibare mishya ya Kaminuza ya Johns Hopkins yo muri Amerika ibigaragaza.
Abantu barenga 200,000 ku isi bamaze kwicwa n'icyorezo cya coronavirus naho abarenga 800,000 bamaze kugikira, nkuko imibare mishya ya Kaminuza ya Johns Hopkins yo muri Amerika ibigaragaza.
Ku isi abarenga miliyoni 2,9 bamaze kwemezwa ko banduye coronavirus, nkuko iyo mibare ikomeza ibigaragaza.
Iyi ntambwe nshya iteye impungenge itewe mu gihe abo yishe muri Amerika barenze 500,000, Abanyamerika bakaba bakomeje gushegeshwa n'iki cyorezo cya mbere kibi cyane isi ihuye nacyo.
Ku itariki ya 11 y'ukwezi kwa mbere uyu mwaka nibwo igitangazamakuru cya leta y'Ubushinwa cyatangaje umuntu wa mbere uzwi ko yishwe na coronavirus.
Kuva icyo gihe, ibihugu n'uturere birenga 210 bimaze gutangaza abantu bishwe na Covid-19, indwara yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero iterwa n'ubu bwoko bushya bwa coronavirus.
Kugeza ubu ibihugu bitanu bimaze gutangaza buri kimwe umubare urenga 20,000 w'abishwe na coronavirus, nubwo uburyo buri gihugu kibara abo yishe butandukanye cyane.
Amerika, Ubutaliyani na Espagne ni byo byagaragaje umubare uri hejuru cyane w'abo yishe.
Urwego rw'ubuzima rw'Ubwongereza ejo ku wa gatandatu rwatangaje ko ubu abantu barenga 20,000 bamaze kwicwa na coronavirus mu bitaro byo muri iki gihugu.
Priti Patel, umunyamabanga wa leta ushinzwe ubutegetsi bw'igihugu, yavuze ko uwo mubare w'abo imaze kwica mu Bwongereza ari "intambwe ibabaje kandi iteye ubwoba".
Yongeyeho ko "igihugu cyose kiri mu kababaro".
Kubera ko umubare w'abishwe na coronavirus mu Bwongereza utarimo abapfira mu ngo zabo cyangwa mu nzu zita ku bageze mu zabukuru, umubare w'ukuri w'abo imaze kwica ugomba kuba urenze aho.
Ubufaransa, igihugu kitabarira mu mubare w'abo yishe abantu baba mu nzu zo kubitabo nk'abageze mu zabukuru, ejo ku wa gatandatu cyatangaje ko umubare w'abo yishe wiyongereyeho 369.
Kuva mu ntangiriro y'ukwezi gushize kwa gatatu, umubare w'abo yishe mu Bufaransa umaze kugera ku 22,648. Ariko abategetsi bo mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi bavuga ko abapfira mu bitaro bari kugabanuka.
Ndetse n'umubare w'indembe wongeye kugabanuka ku munsi wa 17 wikurikiranya.
Muri iki cyumweru, umukuru w'ishami ry'umuryago w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS/WHO) yavuze ko Covid-19 iri kwiyongera muri Afurika, Uburayi bw'uburasirazuba, Amerika yo hagati n'iy'amajyepfo.
Dr Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus yavuze ko nubwo iki cyorezo kigaragara ko ahanini kiri guhama hamwe cyangwa kugabanuka mu Burayi bw'uburengerazuba, mu bihugu bimwe ho ari bwo kigitangira.
Yagize ati: "Ndetse no muri bimwe (ibihugu) byibasiwe mu ntangiriro y'iki cyorezo kirimo kongera kwiyongera".
Kimwe muri byo ni Singapour, ku ikubitiro cyari cyashimagijwe kubera uburyo cyashoboye guhagarika iyi virusi.
Ariko kuva icyo gihe, Singapour ikomeje kwiyongeramo ubwandu bushya bukomoka aho inganda zikorera ndetse no kuryama mu bucucike aho abakozi bo mu nganda barara.
Ahandi ku mugabane w'Aziya, abategetsi bo mu Bushinwa ejo ku wa gatandatu nta bishwe na coronavirus batangaje - ukaba ubaye umunsi wa 10 wikurikiranya nta muntu mushya yishe muri icyo gihugu.
Ndetse no muri Koreya y'epfo, umunsi w'ejo ku wa gatandatu wabaye uwa kabiri hatabonetse umuntu mushya wishwe na coronavirus.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52576760' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52576760' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: AU na OMS bivuga ko Magufuli yibeshye avuga ko ibipimo byayo bidakora neza
Ukuriye urwego rw'umuryango wa Afurika yunze ubumwe ruri kugenzura ibikorwa byo kurwanya coronavirus muri Afurika yahakanye ibyavuzwe na Perezida John Magufuli wa Tanzania ko ibikoresho byifashishwa mu kuyipima bidakora neza.
Ukuriye urwego rw'umuryango wa Afurika yunze ubumwe ruri kugenzura ibikorwa byo kurwanya coronavirus muri Afurika yahakanye ibyavuzwe na Perezida John Magufuli wa Tanzania ko ibikoresho byifashishwa mu kuyipima bidakora neza.
Muri weekend ishize, Bwana Magufuli, wakunze kunengwa ko atafashe ingamba zikwiye mu kwirinda iki cyorezo, yakemanze ibikoresho byifashishwa mu gupima iyi ndwara.
Yavuze ko, mu ibanga, bahaye ibipimo by'inyamaswa n'imbuto laboratoire y'igihugu isuzuma iyi ndwara, ibisubizo bikemeza ko ipapayi, inyoni n'ihene babisanzemo Covid-19.
Mu gupima iki cyorezo ubusanzwe hafatwa ikigero gito cy'amatembabuzi y'imbere cyane mu mazuru y'umuntu.
Asubiza ku byavuzwe na Magufuli, John Nkengasong ukuriye Africa Centres for Disease Control and Prevention (Africa CDC) yabwiye abanyamakuru ko "ibikoresho bikoreshwa byizewe kandi bikora neza".
Yakomeje avuga ko ubufatanye mu ari ingenzi cyane niba abantu bifuza gutsinda urugamba rwa Covid-19.
Dr Nkengasong ati: "Nta gihugu cyaba nyamwigendaho muri Afurika" iyo bigeze mu guhangana n'iyi virus.
Dr Matshidiso Moeti, ukuriye OMS/WHO muri Africa nawe yatangaje ko ibyavuzwe na Bwana Magufuli atari ukuri.
Madamu Moeti yavuze ko bagenzuye ibyo yavuze bagasanga nta cyerekana ko ibikoresho biri kwifashishwa muri Tanzania bifite ikibazo.
Ubutegetsi muri Tanzania bwahisemo gukomeza ibikorwa by'ubukungu bwirinda gufunga amasoko n'ibyambu n'ahandi hahurira abantu benshi mu mijyi.
Bwana Magufuli kandi yavuze ko abantu bakomeza bakajya guteranira mu nsengero kuko ari ho "hari umuti nyawo" wa coronavirus.
Kuva kuwa kane w'icyumweru gishize nta makuru mashya aratangazwa na leta ya Tanzania kuri Covid-19.
Uwari ukuriye ibikorwa bya laboratoire y'igihugu isuzuma iyi virus yahise ahagarikwa ku kazi hashize umunsi umwe Bwana Magufuli avuze ko ibisubizo batanga bitizewe.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52424581' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52424581' term='COVID'>
Rwanda: Leta ikoresha 'ukuboko kw'icyuma' ku bazahajwe n'ibihe bidasanzwe – HRW
Umuryango uharanira uburenganzira bwa muntu Human Rights Watch (HRW) uvuga ko gushyira mu bikorwa amabwiriza yo kurwanya coronavirus mu Rwanda bidaha uburenganzira inzego z'umutekano bwo gukora ibikorwa bibangamira uburenganzira bwa muntu.
Umuryango uharanira uburenganzira bwa muntu Human Rights Watch (HRW) uvuga ko gushyira mu bikorwa amabwiriza yo kurwanya coronavirus mu Rwanda bidaha uburenganzira inzego z'umutekano bwo gukora ibikorwa bibangamira uburenganzira bwa muntu.
Raporo yasohowe n'uyu muryango ejo ku wa gatanu, ivuga ko kubangamira uburenganzira bwa muntu biri kuba muri ibi bihe mu Rwanda, byibasira cyane cyane abazahaye kurusha abandi kubera amabwiriza abategeka kuguma mu rugo.
Mu bivugwa n'iyi raporo hirimo gufunga abantu binyuranyije n'amategeko, gufunga abanyamakuru berekana ibikorwa nabi muri iki gihe, gufata abagore ku ngufu, ubwicanyi, n'ibindi.
BBC yagerageje kuvugana n'uruhande rwa leta y'u Rwanda kuri iyi raporo, inshuro zose yagerageje ntiyahawe igisubizo.
HRW ivuga bimwe mu bikorwa birimo gufata abagore ku ngufu byakozwe n'abasirikare i Kigali mu murenge wa Remera mu kagari ka Nyarutarama, kandi abanyamakuru bahaye ijambo abaturage ibi bikamenyekana ubu bafunzwe bashinjwa ibindi byaha.
Igisirikare cy'u Rwanda cyatangaje ko kiri mu iperereza ku basirikare bagera kuri batanu bashinjwa ibyo byaha.
Iyi raporo ivuga ku iyicwa ry'abantu babiri mu karere ka Nyanza mu majyepfo y'u Rwanda ryabaye mu kwezi kwa gatatu, nyuma polisi y'u Rwanda yavuze abo barashwe barwanya abapolisi.
Ivuga ku ifungwa ry'abantu mu mujyi wa Gisenyi, bafungiwe muri stade igihe cy'amasaha menshi bashinjwa kurenga ku mabwiriza yo kuguma mu rugo.
Inenga kandi ibikorwa byo kubangamira abanyamakuru bagerageje kugenzura amakosa avugwa mu itangwa ry'ibiribwa leta y'u Rwanda ivuga ko bigenewe abazahajwe cyane n'ibi bihe bidasanzwe.
HRW ikorera mu bihugu birenga 90 ku isi, iheruka gusohora raporo ivuga ku bikorwa nk'ibi mu bihugu bimwe byo mu karere nabyo biri mu bihe bidasanzwe.
Raporo z'uyu muryango mu bihe bishize leta y'u Rwanda yagiye ivuga ko ari inyandiko zimwe z'ibyo banditse mu myaka yashize baterura bagahinduramo bicye bakongera bagatangaza.
Lewis Mudge ushinzwe ibikorwa bya HRW muri Afurika yo hagati, yabwiye BBC ko mu gihe cyashize bagiye bagaragaza ibikorwa byo kutubahiriza uburenganzira bwa muntu mu Rwanda ariko igitangaje ubu ari uko mu gihe nk'iki cy'icyorezo ibi bikorwa byibasiye abanyantege nke.
Ati: "Igikomeye ubu ni uko nubwo hari icyorezo kinafite ingaruka zikomeye, nubwo hafashwe ingamba zigamije ibyiza ariko hari gukoreshwa 'ukuboko kw'icyuma' mu kuzubahiriza.
"Igitangaje rero ni uko abantu bazahaye cyane kurusha abandi, kandi bashobora no kwibasirwa na Covid-19, ari na bo bazahajwe cyane n'uko 'kuboko kw'icyuma'.
"Urugero naguha, ni ukuba hari abantu benshi bakennye batunzwe no gushakisha buri munsi ariko bagategekwa kuguma mu rugo, ugerageje gusohoka ngo ajye gushaka ikimutunga agafatwa akirirwa yicajwe muri stade ku zuba.
"Ibyo ni byo HRW ibona nk'ukuboko kw'icyuma mu kubahiriza izo ngamba, ubundi nziza, ariko zubahirizwa mu buryo buremereye cyane".
Bwana Mudge avuga ko ubu batari kubona raporo z'abantu benshi bafungirwa mu bigo bya gisirikare, ahantu hatazwi cyangwa "kwa Kabuga".
Avuga kandi ko ubu batari kumva cyane Abanyarwanda bicwa kubera ibitekerezo byabo bya politiki hanze no mu gihugu nk'uko byari bimeze mu myaka ishize.
Ati: "Ubu ntituri kubona amakuru y'abantu bicwa nk'ibyo twagarutseho vuba aha ku rupfu rwa Kizito Mihigo bivugwa yishwe nubwo bitaremezwa.
"Ahubwo ikivugwa ubu ni ihohoterwa rikorerwa abantu bazahaye cyane muri ibi bihe aho polisi ikoresha imbaraga z'umurengera".
BBC yagerageje kuvugana n'uruhande rwa leta y'u Rwanda ku bikorwa bibangamiye uburenganzira bwa muntu bivugwa na raporo nshya ya HRW, ariko ntibyashoboka kugeza ubu.
Bwana Mudge avuga ko umuryango wa HRW - umaze imyaka warirukanwe mu Rwanda - watangiye gukora ku Rwanda mbere ya jenoside kandi intego yawo ari iyubahirizwa ry'uburenganzira bwa muntu mu gihe kirambye.
Ati: "Iyo urebye mu gihe kizaza, biragoye kuvuga ko mu gihugu nk'u Rwanda haboneka impinduka zirambye mu gihe cya vuba mu gihugu cyakomeje kubangamira amahame ya demokarasi, aho ubwisanzure bw'itangazamakuru nubwo gutanga ibitekerezo bikomeje kugorana".
Gusa avuga ko hari ibintu bimwe bigaragaza ko hari impinduka nziza zabayeho.
Ati: "Ndaguha urugero, kuva mu 2006 twakomeje kwandika ku bibera ahafungirwa abantu hitwa "Kwa Kabuga", iyo urebye ubu ubona ko nubwo abana bo ku mihanda bakihafungirwa ariko uburyo abahafungirwa babaho bwarahindutse.
"Twumva ko uburyo twakomeje guhozaho tugaragaza ibibazo bihari, nibura ubu uburyo abantu bafungwamo 'Kwa Kabuga' tuzi neza ko byahindutse bitakiri nka mbere".
"Urundi rugero ni ingengabitekerezo ya jenoside, niba ubyibuka nko mu myaka 10 ishize iyi yakoreshwaga mu kwibasira abatavuga rumwe na leta muri politiki.
"Yakoreshwaga kandi hagamijwe gucecekesha abantu, ariko ubu iyo urebye ubona ko hari intambwe yatewe mu guhindura imigirire nk'iyo".
Bwana Mudge avuga ko impinduka z'igihe gito ziboneka ariko HRW ibyo ikora biba bigamije ko habaho impinduka nziza z'igihe kirambye mu kubaha no kubahiriza uburenganzira bwa muntu.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52252665' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52252665' term='COVID'>
Uko coronavirus yatumye imiti itari iy'ukuri yiyongera ku isi
Ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS/WHO) ryaburiye ko imiti mpimbano ivugwaho kuvura coronavirus yiyongereye mu bihugu biri mu nzira y'amajyambere.
Ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS/WHO) ryaburiye ko imiti mpimbano ivugwaho kuvura coronavirus yiyongereye mu bihugu biri mu nzira y'amajyambere.
Iperereza rya BBC ryasanze hari imiti mpimbano icuruzwa muri Afurika, abayicuruza bakaba baca urwaho ku kuba nta muti wa coronavirus uraboneka ndetse n'ibura ry'indi miti y'ibanze.
OMS ivuga ko imiti nk'iyo ishobora kugira "ingaruka zikomeye" ku buzima.
Impuguke imwe yaburiye ko hashobora kwaduka "ikindi cyorezo gitewe n'imiti itujuje ubuziranenge kandi mpimbano".
Ku isi abantu bakomeje kwirundaho imiti y'ibanze bakayihunika mu ngo zabo.
Ariko mu gihe ibihugu bibiri bya mbere bikora imiti myinshi ku isi - Ubushinwa n'Ubuhinde - biri mu bihe bidasanzwe, abacyeneye imiti baruta imiti iri ku isoko.
Ndetse n'icuruzwa ry'imiti mpimbano riri kwiyongera.
Ubwo ku itariki ya 11 z'ukwa gatatu OMS yatangazaga ko ubu noneho coronavirus ari icyorezo cyugarije isi, muri icyo cyumweru polisi mpuzamahanga Interpol yafashe abigana imiti.
Operation Pangea, itsinda rya Interpol rirwanya imiti mpimbano, yataye muri yombi abantu 121 bo mu bihugu 90 ku isi mu gihe cy'iminsi irindwi gusa.
Ibyo byatumye ifata imiti mpimbano yajyaga gushyira ubuzima mu kaga ifite agaciro karenga miliyoni 14 z'amadolari y'Amerika.
Mu bihugu byo kuva muri Malaysia kugera muri Mozambique, abapolisi ba Interpol bafashe ibyo kwipfuka mu maso (masques/masks) bibarirwa mu bihumbi za mirongo.
Nyinshi muri izo 'masques' byavugwaga ko zifite ubushobozi bwo kuvura coronavirus.
Jurgen Stock, umunyamabanga mukuru wa Interpol, yagize ati:
"Ubucuruzi butemewe n'amategeko bw'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mpimbano nk'ibyo muri iki gihe cy'akaga mu buzima, bugaragaza kutita na gacye ku buzima bw'abantu".
Nkuko OMS ibitangaza, ubucuruzi bwose hamwe bw'imiti mpimbano, harimo n'imiti ishobora kuba yifitemo ubwandu runaka, buba bugizwe n'imiti ifite ibikora imiti bitari iby'ukuri.
OMS yongeraho ko hari nubwo nta n'ibigize imiti iyo miti mpimbano iba yifitemo, cyangwa yaramaze kurangiza igihe.
OMS ivuga ko ubucuruzi bw'imiti nk'iyo itari yo mu bihugu biri mu nzira y'amajyambere n'ibyateye imbere biciriritse, bubarirwa agaciro karenga miliyari 30 z'amadolari y'Amerika.
Pernette Bourdillion Esteve, wo mu itsinda rya OMS rirwanya imiti itari yo, yagize ati:
"Ibintu bigenze neza iyo miti ishobora kutavura indwara bivugwa ko yagombaga kuvura".
"Bigenze nabi bwo iyo miti iteza ikibazo ku buzima, kubera ko ishobora kuba yarandujwe n'ikintu kirimo uburozi".
Urwego rujyanye no gukora imiti rubarirwa agaciro karenga tiriyari (trillion) imwe y'amadolari y'Amerika.
Uko ikwirakwizwa mu buryo bugari bihera mu nganda z'ingenzi z'imiti nk'izo mu Bushinwa no mu Buhinde, bikagera n'aho ishyirirwa mu bikarito n'amacupa i Burayi, muri Amerika y'epfo cyangwa muri Aziya.
Bigakomereza kandi ku bashinzwe gukwirakwiza imiti bayohereza muri buri gihugu cyo ku isi.
Esteve yavuze ko "bishoboka ko nta kindi kintu cyakwiriye ku isi kurusha imiti".
Ariko muri iki gihe isi yinjiye mu bihe bidasanzwe, urwego rwo gukwirakwiza imiti rwamaze gutangira gucumbagira.
Inganda nyinshi zikora imiti zo mu Buhinde zabwiye BBC ko ubu zikora ku kigero kiri hagati ya 50% na 60% cy'ubushobozi zisanzwe zifite.
Kandi kubera ko inganda zikora imiti zo mu Buhinde zihariye 20% by'imiti yibanze yoherezwa muri Afurika, ibihugu byo kuri uyu mugabane biri kugirwaho ingaruka zikomeye.
Ephraim Phiri, ucuruza imiti mu murwa mukuru Lusaka wa Zambia, yavuze ko byatangiye kumugiraho ingaruka.
Yagize ati: "Imiti yatangiye gushira kandi nta yindi turikongera muri 'stock' yo kuyisimbura. Nta kintu na kimwe twabikoraho".
"Birikutugora rwose kubona imiti…cyane cyane nk'irwanya za 'microbes' (antibiotics) n'irwanya malaria".
Abakora n'abakwirakwiza imiti na bo bari kugorwa kuko ibikoresho by'ibanze bikoreshwa mu gukora ibinini kuri ubu bihenze cyane.
Bigatuma inganda zimwe zitabyigerezaho ngo zibone n'uko zunguka - zikabona zaba ziri gukorera mu gihombo.
Umwe mu bakora imiti wo muri Pakistan yavuze ko yajyaga agura ibyibanze byo gukoramo umuti wa hydrochloroquine uvura malaria ku madolari agera hafi ku 100 ku kilo.
Ariko ubu avuga ko ikilo kimwe cy'ibyo bikoresho by'ibanze bivamo uwo muti cyazamutse kikaba gihagaze ku madolari 1,150.
Mu gihe ibihugu byinshi bikomeje kwinjira mu bihe bidasanzwe aho ubuzima busanzwe busa n'ubwahagaze, ntabwo ari gusa igabanuka mu ikorwa ry'imiti riteje ikibazo.
Ahubwo hari n'ikibazo cy'abacyeneye imiti barushaho kwiyongera, mu gihe abantu ku isi bo bahangayikishijwe n'uko bakwibikaho imiti y'ibanze myinshi ishoboka.
Ni uru ruhurirane rw'igabanuka ry'ingano y'imiti ikorwa no kwiyongera k'umubare w'abayicyeneye rwatumye OMS iburira ko hari ukwiyongera guteye impungenge kw'ikorwa ry'imiti itari yo n'icuruzwa ryayo.
Esteve, wo muri OMS, yagize ati:
"Iyo imiti ikorwa idahuye n'ikigero cy'abayicyeneye, bituma habaho ko imiti mibi cyangwa imiti itari yo igerageza kuziba icyo cyuho cy'abacyeneye imiti nyayo ariko ntibayibone".
Ubwo BBC yaganiraga n'abacuruzi b'imiti n'inganda ziyikora mu bice bitandukanye byo ku isi, byagaragaye ko imiti ivura malaria yugarijwe ku isi.
Ni kuva Perezida Donald Trump wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika yatangira kuvuga ko chloroquine n'umuti bifitanye isano wa hydroxychloroquine, ishobora kuvura coronavirus.
Yabivugiye mu biganiro bya buri munsi agirana n'abanyamakuru mu biro bye bya White House.
Ibyo byatumye ku isi abantu batangira kugura ku bwinshi iyo miti, ubusanzwe ikoreshwa mu kuvura malaria.
OMS yakomeje gutangaza ko nta gihamya ntakuka iriho yuko chloroquine cyangwa hydroxychloroquine ishobora kwifashishwa mu kuvura virusi itera indwara y'ubuhumekero ya Covid-19.
Ariko mu kiganiro aherutse kugirana n'abanyamakuru, Perezida Trump, avuga kuri iyo miti ubundi ivura malaria, yagize ati:
"Ni iki uhomba [mu kuwunywa]? Wunywe".
Muri iki gihe aho abacyeneye iyo miti barushaho kwiyongera, BBC yatahuye ko chloroquine nyinshi itari iy'ukuri iri kugurishwa muri Repubulika ya Demokarasi ya Kongo no muri Cameroun.
OMS nayo yatahuye ko imiti mpimbano iri gucuruzwa mu gihugu cya Niger.
Chloroquine y'ukuri ivura malaria ubusanzwe igurishwa ku madolari hafi 40 y'Amerika ku ipaki irimo ibinini 1,000.
Ariko abacuruzi b'imiti muri DR Congo batahuwe ko ubu basigaye bayigurisha ku giciro kigera ku madolari 250 y'Amerika.
Uwo muti uri kugurishwa yo bivugwa ko wakorewe mu Bubiligi n'uruganda "Brown and Burk Pharmaceutical limited".
Ariko uruganda rw'imiti rwa 'Brown and Burk' rwanditswe ko rukorera mu Bwongereza, rwatangaje ko "ntaho ruhuriye n'uyu muti"
Rwongeyeho ruti: "Ntabwo dukora uyu muti, ni mpimbano".
Muri iki gihe icyorezo cya coronavirus gikomeje ku isi, Profeseri Paul Newton, impuguke mu bijyanye n'imiti mpimbano wo kuri Kaminuza ya Oxford mu Bwongereza, yagize icyo aburira.
Yavuze ko icuruzwa ry'imiti mpimbano kandi mibi ku buzima ahubwo rizarushaho kwiyongera.
Profeseri Newton avuga ko ari aha za leta z'ibihugu byo ku isi kwishyira hamwe zigahashya iyo miti mpimbano zisenyeye ku mugozi umwe.
Yagize ati: "Dufite ibyago ko haduka ikindi cyorezo, kivuye mu miti itujuje ubuziranenge n'imiti itari yo, keretse twese ku isi niduhuriza hamwe tugashyiraho gahunda ihuriweho y'ikorwa, ikwirakwizwa ryo mu buryo bungana n'igenzura ry'ubudakemwa by'amagerageza, imiti n'inkingo".
"Bitabaye ibyo, ibyo ducyesha ubuvuzi bugezweho…bizahatikirira".
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_imikino-51925163' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/imikino-51925163' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Sadio Mané yageneye imfashanyo igihugu cye cya Senegal yo kurwanya iki cyorezo
Rutahizamu Sadio Mané wa Liverpool yageneye imfashanyo ya miliyoni 30 z'ama-CFA - ni arenga gato ibihumbi 41 by'amapawundi - komite y'igihugu cy'iwabo muri Sénégal yo kurwanya icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Rutahizamu Sadio Mané wa Liverpool yageneye imfashanyo ya miliyoni 30 z'ama-CFA - ni arenga gato ibihumbi 41 by'amapawundi - komite y'igihugu cy'iwabo muri Sénégal yo kurwanya icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Sadio yafashe icyo cyemezo cyo gutanga iyo mfashanyo "mu buryo bw'ako kanya atabanje kubitekerezaho mbere nyuma yo kubona uko ibintu bikomeje kumera" iwabo, nkuko umuhagarariye yabivuze.
Abanduye Covid-19 - indwara yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero iterwa n'ubu bwoko bushya bwa coronavirus - bakomeje kwiyongera mu gihugu cye cy'amavuko cya Sénégal.
Sadio kandi yatangaje video ku mbuga nkoranyambaga asaba abaturage b'iwabo muri Sénégal "guhagurukira bivuye inyuma" iyo virusi.
Uyu  mukinnyi watsindiye igihembo cy'uwahize abandi mu mupira w'amaguru muri Afurika mu mwaka ushize wa 2019, yanagiriye inama abamukurikira ku mbuga nkoranyambaga yo gufata ingamba zo kwirinda.
Zirimo "gukoresha imiti yica udukoko (imigera, mu Kirundi) cyangwa gukaraba intoki nibura mu gihe cy'amasegonda 30".
Umubare w'abamaze kwemezwa ko banduye coronavirus muri Sénégal ugeze ku bantu 27, ariko babiri muri bo bamaze gukira, nkuko bitangazwa na minisiteri y'ubuzima muri icyo gihugu.
Ejo ku wa mbere, abategetsi bo muri Sénégal batangaje ko bahagaritse ingendo z'indege hagati y'icyo gihugu cyo mu burengerazuba bw'Afurika n'ibihugu byinshi by'i Burayi (Ubufaransa, Ububiligi, Espanye, Portugal n'Ubutaliyani).
Banahagaritse ingendo z'indege hagati yayo n'ibihugu byo mu majyaruguru y'Afurika (Algeria, Tunisia), mu gihe Maroc yamaze guhagarika ingendo zerekeza muri Sénégal.
Ibikorwa byose ku kibuga Melwood cy'imyitozo cya Liverpool bijyanye n'abakinnyi n'abandi bakozi byahagaritswe.
Kandi kubera ko Liverpool ari imwe mu makipe akina muri shampiyona y'icyiciro cya mbere mu Bwongereza izwi nka Premier League, imikino yayo yarasubitswe kugeza nibura ku itariki ya 4 y'ukwezi gutaha kwa kane, ubwo hazongera gusuzumwa niba yasubukurwa.
Hagati aho, Sadio n'abakinnyi bagenzi be bakinana muri Liverpool bakomeje imyitozo buri muntu ku giti cye.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52450215' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52450215' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus - New York: Umuganga wavuraga abayirwaye yiyahuye
Umuganga wari mu bari kwita ku barwayi ba coronavirus mu mujyi wa New York muri Amerika yapfuye yiyahuye.
Umuganga wari mu bari kwita ku barwayi ba coronavirus mu mujyi wa New York muri Amerika yapfuye yiyahuye.
Dr Lorna Breen yari umuganga mu ishami ryita ku ndembe mu bitaro biri i Manhattan, yapfuye ku cyumweru kubera ibikomere yiteye ubwe nk'uko bivugwa na polisi.
Se umubyara, Dr Philip Breen yabwiye ikinyamakuru New York Times ati: "Yagerageje gukora akazi ke ariko karamwica".
Leta ya New York yonyine ibarura abantu 17,500 bamaze gupfa mu bantu 56,000 bose hamwe bamaze kwicwa na Covid-19 muri Amerika.
Dr Philip yavuze ko umukobwa we nta kibazo yajyaga agira cy'uburwayi bwo mu mutwe. Yiyahuriye aho yari atuye muri Virginia, aho yabanaga n'umuryango we.
Dr Lorna Breen mu gihe cy'akazi ke nawe yarwaye coronavirus ariko agaruka mu kazi nyuma y'icyumweru n'igice amaze koroherwa nk'uko se abivuga.
Se avuga ko ibitaro yakoreraga byari byongeye kumwohereza mu rugo, ntiyabyemera kugeza ubwo umuryango we umusabye kubyemera agataha.
Se avuga ko ubwo aheruka kuvugana n'umukobwa we yari mu gahinda, akamubwira uburyo abantu bari kwicwa na Covid-19 kugeza ubwo hari n'abapfa batarabavana mu modoka zitwara indembe.
Ati: "Mu by'ukuri yari mu bari ku murongo wa mbere muri uru rugamba. Tumubona nk'intwari kimwe n'abandi bose bamaze kugwa kuri uru rugamba".
New York Times ivuga ko Dr Lorna Breen yari umukirisitu ukomeye, yari umuntu ukunda guceza injyana ya salsa ndetse ko rimwe mu cyumweru yahaga umwanya we inzu z'abashaje.
Ibitaro yakoreraga byasohoye itangazo bivuga ko "Dr Breen ari intwari yazanye umuti ku rugamba rukomeye mu ishami ryo kuvura indembe".
Polisi yatangaje ko nyuma yo gutabazwa tariki 26 z'uku kwezi, Dr Breen yajyanywe ku bitaro ngo avurwe ariko "akicwa n'ibikomere yiteye ubwe".
Ukuriye polisi muri aka gace mu itangazo yasohoye, yavuze ko "Abaganga bari muri uru rugamba nabo bashobora kwibasirwa n'indwara zo mu mutwe bitewe n'iki cyorezo".
Uyu avuga ko aba bakozi basanzwe bakora akazi kagoranye cyane, "none coronavirus ikaba yarongereye ugukomera kw'akazi kabo".
Leta ya New York imaze kubonekamo hafi 1/3 cy'abamaze kwandura bose hamwe muri Amerika ubu basatira miliyoni imwe.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_52050757' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/52050757' term='COVID'>
Covid-19: Miliyoni z’Abanya-Uganda babangamiwe no guhagarika gutwara abantu muri rusange
Mu maduka, aho abagenzi bategera no mu nzu z'ubucuruzi rwagati mu murwa mukuru Kampala wa Uganda, ubuzima bwahagaze - kubera ihagarikwa ry'ingendo za rusange.
Mu maduka, aho abagenzi bategera no mu nzu z'ubucuruzi rwagati mu murwa mukuru Kampala wa Uganda, ubuzima bwahagaze - kubera ihagarikwa ry'ingendo za rusange.
Mu masaha ya mbere ya saa sita kuri uyu wa kane, videwo zatangiye guhererekanywa ku mbuga nkoranyambaga zerekana abashinzwe umutekano batatanya abacuruzi.
Hari ibirego byuko abapolisi n'abasirikare bari gukoresha ingufu z'umurengera aho boherejwe rwagati muri Kampala, bakaba bagaragaye bakubita abantu ku mihanda.
Abanyamakuru bavuga ko nubwo amaduka atagomba gufungwa, bijyanye n'amabwiriza Perezida Yoweri Museveni yatanze ejo, abashinzwe umutekano bahagaritse ubucuruzi.
Bavuga ko hasigaye hakora gusa amaduka manini (supermarkets) na za 'restaurants'.
Perezida Museveni wa Uganda yaraye atangaje ko gutwara abagenzi bya rusange bihagaritswe mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 mu kurwanya ikwirakwira rya coronavirus.
Mu ijambo ryanyuze kuri televiziyo ejo ku wa gatatu nijoro, Bwana Museveni yavuze ko akibivuga byahise biba itegeko rigomba gutangira gukurikizwa.
Ingendo zaciwe zirimo n'izikorwa na moto zizwi nka "boda-boda" zimenyerewe cyane muri iki gihugu.
Ingorane ku barya ku munsi ari uko bavuye mu ngo
Imodoka z'abantu ku giti cyabo zemerewe gusa gutwara abagenzi batatu ubariyemo n'umushoferi.
Ibyo byahise bigira ingaruka ku bantu babarirwa muri za miliyoni - atari uko gusa bigabanya ingendo zabo, ahubwo kuko binabangamiye imibereho yabo cyane cyane ab'amikoro macye.
Nk'urugero, abantu ntibagishobora kujya ku kazi cyangwa mu bucuruzi bwabo, bivuze ko batagishoboye kubona imibereho.
Abarya ku munsi ari uko bavuye mu rugo bakajya gushakisha ibiraka, na bo byabagizeho ingaruka zikomeye kurushaho.
Mu masaha ya nyuma ya saa sita kuri uyu wa kane, polisi yatangaje ko abantu 14 batawe muri yombi basahura ibiribwa.
Videwo yatangajwe n'umunyamakuru ku rubuga rwa Facebook igaragaza abagabo bacye bashikuza inanasi mu gice cy'inyuma cy'imodoka nto y'ikamyo.
Abel Mwesigye, umukuru w'ishyirahamwe ry'abacuruzi muri Uganda, yabwiye BBC ko amatsinda y'abantu bagerageje kwiba ibicuruzwa bitanditse ku mihanda.
Yongeyeho ko polisi yahise itabara ikabatatanya.
Hari urujijo, ubwoba no kutamenya ikizakurikiraho mu minsi iri imbere, cyane cyane ku bantu bazagorwa n'imibereho mu gihe batagishoboye gushakisha ikibatunga.
Uganda imaze kwemeza abarwayi 14 ba Covid-19 - indwara yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero iterwa na coronavirus - barimo n'umwana w'umukobwa w'amezi umunani.
Hari amakuru yuko abaturage ba Uganda batigeze na rimwe basohoka mu gihugu na bo bari muri abo banduye.
Abategetsi rero barashaka kugabanya urujya n'uruza rw'abantu hagati y'imijyi n'uturere.
Amasoko - akunze kuba ari manini kandi ahinda - yemerewe gusa gucuruza ibiribwa.
Mu cyumweru gishize, Bwana Museveni w'imyaka 75 y'amavuko yatangaje ifungwa ry'amashuri, utubari, inzu zireberwamo filime ndetse aca n'inama, mu gihe cy'iminsi 32.
Abatwara abantu ku binyabiziga ni abantu b'ingenzi muri politike y'iki gihugu, bakaba babarirwa mu bihumbi za mirongo mu murwa mukuru Kampala.
Ndetse akenshi Perezida Museveni arigengesera mu gufata ibyemezo bishobora kubagiraho ingaruka - kubera nk'amajwi bashobora gutanga mu matora cyangwa urundi ruhare rwabo.
Bishobora kuba ari yo mpamvu ingendo zahagaritswe gusa mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
