Coronavirus: Uyu mwaka w’imikino wagizwe impfabusa muri Ethiopia
Ishyirahamwe ry'umupira w'amaguru muri Ethiopia ryaraye ritangaje ko imikino yose ya shampiyona iburijwemo kubera icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Ishyirahamwe ry'umupira w'amaguru muri Ethiopia ryaraye ritangaje ko imikino yose ya shampiyona iburijwemo kubera icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Uwo mwanzuro wafashwe nyuma y'ikiganiro cyabaye abo bireba bahari naho abandi bakitabiriye mu buryo bw'iyakure bwa videwo, harimo n'abahagarariye shampiyona y'icyiciro cya mbere.
Itangazo ry'inama nkuru y'ubuyobozi bw'ishyirahamwe ry'umupira w'amaguru muri Ethiopia rigira riti:
"Hashingiwe ku kuba igihugu kiri mu bihe bidasanzwe no kuba hatazwi igihe ikiza cya coronavirus kizamara, twafashe icyemezo cyo kuburizamo imikino ya shampiyona y'uyu mwaka".
Muri Ethiopia, abantu 162 ni bo bamaze kwemezwa ko banduye Covid-19, indwara y'ubuhumekero iterwa n'ubu bwoko bushya bwa coronavirus.
Muri bo imaze kwicamo abantu bane naho 93 bamaze kuyikira, nkuko imibare ya Kaminuza ya Johns Hopkins yo muri Amerika ibigaragaza.
Kubera iryo burizwamo ry'imikino ya shampiyona, uyu mwaka w'imikino wagizwe impfabusa - bivuze ko nta kipe izazamuka mu cyiciro cyangwa ngo imanuke.
Ethiopia kandi ntabwo izahagararirwa mu irushanwa rya Champions League nyafurika (CAF Champions League) n'iry'igikombe cya CAF Confederations Cup.
Kugeza ubwo iyi shampiyona y'uyu mwaka yaburizwagamo, Fasil Kenema ni yo yari iyoboye urutonde rw'agateganyo n'amanota 30 mu mikino 17 yari imaze gukina.
Mekele 70 Enderta ni yo yari ku mwanya wa kabiri, irushwa na Fasil Kenema inota rimwe.
Iyi Mekelle 70 Enderta ni yo yegukanye igikombe cya shampiyona y'umwaka ushize wa 2019.
Ishyirahamwe ry'umupira w'amaguru muri Ethiopia ryanafashe icyemezo cyuko amakipe akwiye kugumana abakinnyi bari bafite kontaro zizarangira ku itariki 30 y'ukwezi gutaha kwa gatandatu.
Liberia nayo imaze gukurikira Ethiopia mu kuburizamo uyu mwaka w'imikino.
Ubu ibihugu by'Afurika bimaze kuburizamo shampiyona z'uyu mwaka bigeze kuri birindwi.
Mu ntangiriro y'uku kwezi, Ibirwa bya Maurice nibyo byabaye igihugu cya mbere muri Afurika kiburijemo imikino ya shampiyona y'uyu mwaka.
Ibindi bihugu ni Kenya, Angola, Burkina Faso na Guinea-Conakry.
Byitezwe ko ibindi bihugu by'Afurika bitangaza imyanzuro byafashe, mu gihe impuzamashyirahamwe y'umupira w'amaguru muri Afurika (CAF) yari yatanze itariki ntarengwa 5 y'uku kwezi.
Ishyirahamwe ry'umupira w'amaguru mu Rwanda ejo ryatangaje ko rizafata umwanzuro kuri shampiyona "bitarenze tariki 30 z'uku kwezi bitewe n'amabwiriza ya leta ategerejwe muri uku kwezi".
Mu Burundi, shampiyona yabaye ihagaritswe mu gihe cy'ibikorwa byo kwiyamamaza, ishyirahamwe ry'umupira w'amaguru rimenyesha ko imikino y'iminsi itatu yari isigaye izakinwa nyuma y'ibyo bikorwa.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_52488646' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/52488646' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Trump avuga ko Ubushinwa bushaka ko azatsindwa amatora
Perezida Donald Trump yavuze ko Ubushinwa "buzakora icyo bushoboye cyose" kugira ngo ntiyongere gutorerwa kuyobora Amerika.
Perezida Donald Trump yavuze ko Ubushinwa "buzakora icyo bushoboye cyose" kugira ngo ntiyongere gutorerwa kuyobora Amerika.
Aya magambo ya Bwana Trump akajije uburyo yakomeje kunenga Ubushinwa muri ibi bihe by'icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Mu kiganiro n'ibiro ntaramakuru Reuters mu biro bye bya White House, Bwana Trump yavuze ko bushobora guhura n'ingaruka "nyinshi" zivuye kuri Amerika kubera coronavirus.
Yavuze ko Ubushinwa bwakabaye bwaramenyesheje amahanga hakiri kare ibijyanye n'iki cyorezo.
Umuvugizi wa minisiteri y'ububanyi n'amahanga y'Ubushinwa yahakanye ibyo birego.
Geng Shuang yavuze ko Ubushinwa bufata amatora y'Amerika nk'ikibazo kireba Amerika ubwayo.
Bwana Shuang yongeyeho ko yizeye ko abanyapolitiki bo muri Amerika bazareka gukoresha izina ry'Ubushinwa muri politiki y'imbere mu gihugu cyabo.
Bwana Trump na we ubwe akunze gushinjwa kudakora ibihagije mu guhangana na Covid-19, indwara yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero iterwa n'ubu bwoko bushya bwa coronavirus.
Coronavirus yashegeshe ubukungu bw'Amerika mbere bwari buhagaze neza - bukaba ari cyo kintu cy'ingenzi yagezeho yagenderagaho mu kwiyamamaza cyo gutuma yongera gutorwa mu kwa 11.
Bwana Trump, watangije intambara y'ubucuruzi n'Ubushinwa, ntabwo yasobanuye neza uburyo ashobora kugira icyo akora ku Bushinwa.
Yabwiye Reuters ati: "Hari ibintu byinshi nshobora gukora. Turimo kureba icyabaye".
Yongeyeho ati: "Ubushinwa buzakora icyo bushoboye cyose kugira ngo ntsindwe aya matora".
Uyu perezida wo mu ishyaka ry'abarepubulikani yavuze ko yemeza ko Ubushinwa bushaka ko uwo bashobora kuzahangana, umudemokarate Joe Biden, ari we utsinda amatora.
Bwana Trump yanavuze ko adashira amakenga amakuru y'ikusanyabitekerezo agaragaza ko Bwana Biden ari we uzatsinda amatora.
Yagize ati: "Ntabwo ngendera ku bivugwa n'amakusanyabitekerezo. Nemera ko abaturage b'iki gihugu bazi ubwenge. Kandi sintekereza ko bazatora umugabo udashoboye".
Mbere yaho ku munsi w'ejo, ibitangazamakuru byo muri Amerika byatangaje ko Bwana Trump yatonganyije abajyanama be muri politike ku wa gatanu ushize nimugoroba.
Ibyo bitangazamakuru bivuga ko hari nyuma yaho amakuru y'ikusanyabitekerezo agaragaje ko azatsindwa mu matora muri za leta ziba ari ingenzi ngo umukandida yizere gutsinda.
Abajyanama be bafite impungenge niba Bwana Trump azatsinda muri leta ziba ari isibaniro nka Florida, Wisconsin na Arizona, nkuko bitangazwa n'ibiro ntaramakuru Associated Press.
Associated Press yongeraho ko itsinda ry'abamwamamaza ryataye icyizere ko azatsinda muri leta ya Michigan.
Amakuru avuga ko ubwo yaganiraga mu nama yo mu buryo bw'iyakure n'abakuriye ibikorwa byo kumwamamaza, yagize ati: "Ntabwo nzatsindwa na Joe Biden", akarenzaho n'indahiro.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_51922831' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/51922831' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Muri US bwa mbere bagerageje urukingo rwayo ku bantu
Igerageza rya mbere ku bantu ry'urukingo rwo kurinda abantu kwandura coronavirus ryakozwe muri Amerika.
Igerageza rya mbere ku bantu ry'urukingo rwo kurinda abantu kwandura coronavirus ryakozwe muri Amerika.
Abarwayi bane batewe inshinge z'uru rukingo ku kigo cy'ubushakashatsi cya Kaiser Permanente kiri i Seattle muri leta ya Washington nk'uko bivugwa n'ibiro ntaramakuru Associated Press.
Uru rukingo (urucanco mu Kirundi) ntabwo rushobora gutera Covid-19 ariko rufite igice kirugize cyavanwe muri iyi virus itera iyi ndwara.
Abahanga bavuga ko bizafata amezi menshi kumenya niba uru rukingo, cyangwa izindi ziri mu bushakashatsi, ruzakora.
Umuntu wa mbere watewe uru rukingo ejo kuwa mbere, ni umugore wo muri Seattle w'imyaka 43 ufite abana babiri.
Uyu mugore witwa Jennifer Haller yabwiye AP ati: "Aya ni amahirwe akomeye kuri njye yo kugira icyo nkora".
Abashakashatsi ku isi bari gukora iyo bwabaga bashaka urukingo rw'iki cyorezo vuba.
Iri gerageza rya mbere rikorewe ku bantu ni indi ntambwe kuko amagerageza menshi yakorerwaga ku nyamaswa.
Dr John Tregoning, inzobere mu ndwara z'ibyorezo zandura wo muri Imperial College London mu Bwongereza yabwiye BBC ko "uru rukiko rwageragejwe rwifashishije ikoranabuhanga risanzweho".
Ati: "Rukoze mu bintu dusanzwe tuzi ko bitagira ingaruka mbi ku muntu kandi ababigizemo uruhare nabo barakomeza gukurikiranwa.
"Nibyo, birihutisha ubushakashatsi - ariko ntibisanzwe kuri virus".
Inkingo zimeze gutya za virusi, nk'iseru, zikorwa kuri virus zacitse intege cyangwa zapfuye.
Abatewe uru rukingo rwakozwe bazahabwa ingano (dose) zitandukanye zarwo.
Buri wese azaterwa, ku kaboko hagana ku rutugu, inshinge ebyiri mu minsi 28 itandukanye
Abahanga bavuga ko nubwo iri gerageza rya mbere ryatanga umusaruro, bishobora gufata amezi 18 kugira ngo uru rukingo rukwizwe mu bantu.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52487363' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52487363' term='COVID'>
Remdesivir: Umuti uri kugaragaza imbaraga mu kurwanya coronavirus
Ubu hari ibihamya "biboneka neza" ko umuti wa Remdesivir ushobora gufasha abantu gukira coronavirus nk'uko bivugwa n'abahanga mu by'ubuzima muri Amerika.
Ubu hari ibihamya "biboneka neza" ko umuti wa Remdesivir ushobora gufasha abantu gukira coronavirus nk'uko bivugwa n'abahanga mu by'ubuzima muri Amerika.
Baravuga ko uyu muti ugabanya igihe ibimenyetso by'iyi ndwara bimara kuva ku minsi 15 kugera kuri 11 nk'uko ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe mu bitaro bitandukanye ku isi bibyerekana.
Mu cyumweru gishize, amakuru OMS/WHO yashyize kuri internet yavugaga ko uyu muti utari gukora, gusa ayo makuru bahise bayavanaho nyuma y'igihe gitoya.
Amakuru arambuye kuri uyu muti ntabwo aratangazwa, ariko inzobere zivuga ko cyaba ari igisubizo cyiza niba byemejwe ko uvura, nubwo utaba uje kurangiza iki cyorezo.
Bavuga ko uyu muti ushobora gukiza ubuzima bwa benshi kandi ukagabanyiriza ibitaro akazi ko kwakira no kwita ku barwayi.
Remdesivir ubundi yakozwe ari umuti wo kuvura Ebola. Ni umuti urwanya virus, wibasira utunyangingo virus ikenera kugira ngo yiyongere mu turemangingo tw'umubiri wacu.
Ikigo cya Amerika National Institute of Allergy and Infectious Diseases (NIAID),  cyakoze igerageza ryawo ku bantu 1,063. Bamwe muri bo bahawe uwo muti, abandi bahabwa utari wo neza (placebo).
Dr Anthony Fauci utegeka NIAID agira ati: "Ibyavuyemo ni uko Remdesivir igaragaza neza ko igabanya igihe cyo gukira iyi ndwara".
Nta muti cyangwa urukingo biraboneka bivurwa Covid-19 kugeza ubu, mu kuyivura abaganga bavura ibimenyetso byayo ubwirinzi bw'umubiri nabwo bugahangana na virus kugeza umuntu akize cyangwa byanze.
Dr Fauci yavuze ko ibyavuye mu igerageza byerekana ko uyu muti "ushobora kuzibira iyi virus", ibi bikaba "bifungura umuryango ku kuba hashobora kuboneka uburyo bwo kuvura abayirwaye".
Ntiharamenyekana neza abo uyu muti ufasha. Niba ari abagombaga gukira n'ubundi ukiza vuba cyangwa unafasha abantu barembye bakoroherwa.
Ntibiramenyekana kandi niba ukora cyane mu bakiri bato cyangwa abakuze, niba ufasha abasanzwe bafite n'izindi ndwara cyangwa abatazifite, cyangwa niba ufasha gusa abo virus itaraba nyinshi mu mubiri.
Ibi ni ibibazo bizasubizwa mu gihe hazatangazwa amakuru yose kuri uyu muti.
Prof Mahesh Parmar wayoboye igerageza ry'uyu muti mu Burayi avuga ko mbere y'uko uyu muti ukwirakwizwa hakiri ibyo gukora.
Ati: "Imibare n'ibyayivuyemo bigomba gusubirwamo n'abashinzwe ubugenzuzi kugira ngo uyu muti wemerwe kandi wongere ugenzurwe n'inzego zishinzwe iby'imiti mu bindi bihugu".
Avuga ko mu gihe ibi bikiri gukorwa bakomeza kubona amakuru yandi ava mu magerageza, bareba niba uyu muti ushobora no kurengera abagiye kwicwa na Covid-19.
Prof Peter Horby wo muri kaminuza ya Oxford mu Bwongereza, ayoboye itsinda rinini riri gukora igerageza ry'imiti itandukanye yavura Covid-19.
Yagize ati: "Tugomba kureba ibyavuye mu igerageza rya remdesivir byose, gusa ubaye wemejwe yaba ari inkuru nziza mu rugamba ruriho kuri Covid-19.
"Intambwe zakurikiraho ni ukubona amakuru yose no kumenya uko uyu muti wa remdesivir waboneka kuri benshi".
Mbere, amakuru ya leta zunze ubumwe za Amerika kuri uyu muti yari yashyizwe hanze mu gihe kimwe n'ayo mu Bushinwa mu kinyamakuru kivuga iby'ubuzima cy'ikigo Lancet, yavugaga ko utavura.
Gusa, igeregezwa ryari ryakozwe ntiryari rihagije nk'ako abahanga babivuga.
Prof Babak Javid, umuhanga mu ndwara z'ibyorezo wo muri  bitaro bya kaminuza ya Cambridge avuga ko "amakuru ariho kuri uyu muti avuguruzanya".
Ati: "Bivuze ko kuba ubu nta muti uriho uvura Covid bishobora kwihutisha kwemeza remdesivir ko iyivura.
"Gusa, bibonaka ko remdesivir atari igisubizo cyihuse muri ibi; urebye muri rusange ubona warakijije abantu kuri 30%"
Indi miti iri gukorwaho amagerageza ko yavura Covid-19 harimo isanzwe ikoreshwa mu kuvura malaria na SIDA ishobora kurwanya iyi virus cyangwa igaha imbaraga ubwirinzi bw'umubiri.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_51788796' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/51788796' term='COVID'>
Rwanda - Coronavirus: Katolika yafashe ingingo zijanye no gukinga ico kiza
Ekleziya Katolika mu Rwanda ihamagarira abakirisu gukurikiza amategeko atangwa n'inzego zijejwe amagara y'abantu mu ntumbero yo kwirinda wa mugera ruhonyabantu coronavirus, yiswe Covid-19.
Ekleziya Katolika mu Rwanda ihamagarira abakirisu gukurikiza amategeko atangwa n'inzego zijejwe amagara y'abantu mu ntumbero yo kwirinda wa mugera ruhonyabantu coronavirus, yiswe Covid-19.
Ivyo biri mw'itangazo ryaraye risohowe na Antoine Kambanda, Umwepiskopi mukuru wa Diyoseze nkuru ya Kigali akaba n'icegera c'Inama y'Abepiskopi Gatolika mu Rwanda, aho amenyesha ingingo zafashwe mu makoraniro zizofasha abakirisu babo kudakoranako ngo bahave bandukizanya.
Ibihugu bishika umunani ku mugabane wa Afrika bimaze gutangaza ko uwo mugera wamaze kubishikamwo, leta z'u Burundi n'u Rwanda zikaba ziherutse gutangaza ingingo zafashe mu ntumbero yo kwirinda no gukinga uwo mugera.
Mw'iryo tangazo, Inama y'Abepiskopi Gatolika mu Rwanda isaba abakirisu "guhana amahoro ya Kristu ku mutima gusa ata guhana ibiganza canke guhoberana".
Isaba kandi ko "mu gihe co gusangira (guhazwa mu Kinyarwanda) ari ugutega ibiganza, atagutega ururimi".
Iyo nama yafashe kandi ingingo yo gukura "amazi y'umugisha" (amazi ahezagiye mu kirundi) mu twombo yashirwamwo mw'isengero, maze abakirisu bakaja barayakoramwo mu kugira urumenyetso rw'umusaraba.
Basaba abakirisu kudasubira gukora aho yahora ashirwa kuko atakirimwo "kugeza igihe ikibazo kizoba gikemutse".
Muri iryo tangazo, Inama y'Abepisikopi Gatolika mu Rwanda, yemereye abakirisitu ko izobandanya ikurikirana uko bimeze, ikazofata n'izindi ngingo zo kwikingira ni vyaba ngombwa.
Gushika ubu, ibihugu birenga 80 biramaze guterwa n'uwo mugera watanguriye mu gisagara ca Wuhan c'intara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Ku mugabane wa Afrika, ibihugu vya Togo, Nigeria, Senegal, Misiri, Algeria, Tuniziya, Afrika y'Epfo na Cameroon nivyo bimaze guterwa n'uwo mugera.
Mu ntumbero yo kurwanya uwo mugera, ibihugu vy'u Rwanda n'u Burundi biherutse gutangaza ingingo vyafashe mu ntumbero yo gukinga ko ishika muri vyo.
U Burundi  bwatangaje ko ingenzi zivuye mu bihugu vy'u Bushinwa, Koreya y'epfo, Iran, Ubutaliyani, Ubudage, Ubufaransa, Ubuyapani na Espanye zizobanza gushirwa mu kibanza categuwe ukwazo nyene mu kiringo c'iminsi 14.
Nayo mu Rwanda, leta isaba abanyagihugu "kugabanya ingendo zitari ngombwa" mu bihugu birangwamwo coronavirus, yongera kandi itangaza n'ingingo zitandukanye harimwo n'izo isuku, kugira ngo birinde kwandura.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52050182' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52050182' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Kenya yahagaritse ubucuruzi bw’imyenda ya ‘caguwa’ mu kurwanya Covid-19
Kenya yaciye kwinjiza mu gihugu imyenda ya 'sekeni' (second-hand) - izwi nanone nka 'caguwa', nk'uburyo bwo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Kenya yaciye kwinjiza mu gihugu imyenda ya 'sekeni' (second-hand) - izwi nanone nka 'caguwa', nk'uburyo bwo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Ikinyamakuru Daily Nation cyo muri Kenya gisubiramo amagambo ya Minisitiri w'ubucurizi Betty Maina agira ati:
"Kwinjiza mu gihugu imyenda yambawe birahagaritswe guhera ubu [ejo ku wa gatatu] mu kubungabunga ubuzima bw'Abanya-Kenya no guteza imbere inganda z'imyenda zo mu gihugu".
Abantu benshi bagura imyenda yabanje kwambarwa yoherejwe iva i Burayi, muri Amerika y'amajyaruguru no mu Bushinwa.
Bayikundira ko iba inoze, igurika kandi idahuriweho n'abantu benshi, ugereranyije n'imishya ikorerwa imbere mu gihugu.
Umubare munini w'Abanya-Kenya b'amikoro macye babeshejweho n'ubucuruzi bw'imyenda ya 'sekeni'.
Ariko leta ya Kenya ikomeje kugaragaza ko idashaka ubwo bucuruzi, igashyigikira ahubwo inganda z'imbere mu gihugu.
Ejo ku wa gatatu, Minisitiri Maina yakoranye inama n'abacuruza 'sekeni' abashishikariza gukoresha ibikorerwa mu gihugu.
Ariko si buri wese wishimiye iryo hagarikwa rya 'caguwa'.
Depite Yusuf Hassan wo mu karere ka Kamukunji mu murwa mukuru Nairobi mu gace ka Eastleigh aho ubwo bucuruzi busanzwe buhinda, yavuze ko yaguye mu kantu.
Bwana Hassan yanditse ku rubuga rwa Twitter ko Abanya-Kenya babarirwa mu bihumbi bo muri ako gace babeshejweho nabwo, bityo ko imibereho igiye kujya mu kaga.
Muri Kenya ubu hari abantu 28 bamaze kwandura indwara ya Covid-19, harimo batatu bashya batangajwe ejo na Perezida Uhuru Kenyatta.
Bwana Kenyatta yanavuze ko umurwayi wa mbere yamaze kuyikira muri icyo gihugu.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_52154876' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/52154876' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Muri Kenya visi guverineri amaze kuyikira yahise afungwa
Hashize umunsi umwe gusa bimaze kuvugwa ko yakize coronavirus,  Gideon Saburi visi guverineri w'intara ya Kilifi muri Kenya yahise atabwa muri yombi nk'uko polisi ibivuga.
Hashize umunsi umwe gusa bimaze kuvugwa ko yakize coronavirus,  Gideon Saburi visi guverineri w'intara ya Kilifi muri Kenya yahise atabwa muri yombi nk'uko polisi ibivuga.
Bwana Saburi araregwa kwanga kwishyira mu kato nk'uko yari yabisabwe ubwo yari avuye mu mahanga.
Ku gicamunsi cyo kuri uyu wa gatanu nibwo polisi yagiye ku bitaro biri i Nairobi aho yari ari maze atabwa muri yombi.
Ejo kuwa kane umunyamabanga wa leta ushinzwe ubuzima muri Kenya yari yatangaje ko "yishimiye kumenyesha ko Bwana Saburi yakize neza iyi ndwara".
Ariko yongeyeho ko Saburi azabazwa n'amategeko ibyo yakoze.
Uyu munsi kuwa gatanu, Mercy Mwangangi umunyamabanga wa leta wungirije ushinzwe ubuzima muri Kenya yatangaje ko habonetse abandi bantu bashya 12 banduye coronavirus.
Ibi byatumye umubare w'abafite iyi ndwara muri Kenya uba 122.
Madamu Mercy yavuze ko mu bo yishe harimo umwana w'imyaka itandatu wari usanzwe ufite ubundi burwayi.
Abamaze kwicwa na coronavirus muri Kenya kugeza ubu ni bane.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52369746' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52369746' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: CHOGM yasubitswe, Kagame ati: ‘tuzayiha ikaze icyorezo nigitsindwa’
Inama y'abakuru b'ibihugu na za guverinoma bihuriye mu muryango w'ibihugu wa Commonwealth izwi nka CHOGM, yari iteganyijwe kubera i Kigali mu Rwanda mu kwezi kwa gatandatu yasubitswe kubera coronavirus nk'uko uwo muryango ubitangaza.
Inama y'abakuru b'ibihugu na za guverinoma bihuriye mu muryango w'ibihugu wa Commonwealth izwi nka CHOGM, yari iteganyijwe kubera i Kigali mu Rwanda mu kwezi kwa gatandatu yasubitswe kubera coronavirus nk'uko uwo muryango ubitangaza.
Commonwealth igizwe n'ibihugu 54 bikoresha ururimi rw'icyongereza, uvuga ko gusubika iyi nama "ari ngombwa" kubera iki cyorezo, ko izabera i Kigali mu gihe kizatangazwa nyuma.
Byari biteganyijwe ko iyi nama izitabirwa n'abantu bari hagati y'ibihugu birindwi n'ibihumbi 10,000 barimo minisitiri w'intebe w'Ubwongereza Boris Johnson ndetse n'igikomangoma Charles.
Leta y'u Rwanda yatangaje ko yari yarateganyije miliyari 20 z'amafranga y'u Rwanda mu myiteguro yo kwakira iyi nama.
Imirimo yiganjemo ibikorwaremezo mu mujyi wa Kigali imaze amezi ikorwa, iyo irimo kwagura imihanda imwe, kuyirimbisha no kwagura ikibuga cy'indege mpuzamahanga cya Kigali.
Mu kwezi kwa gatatu, ikigo gishinzwe iterambere mu Rwanda cyatangaje ko u Rwanda ruzungukira byinshi muri iyi nama, harimo n'imishinga y'ishoramari ya miliyoni USD 700 izayisinyirwamo.
Abacuruzi mu Rwanda bari barateguriwe - mu nama yabaye mu kwezi gushize kwa gatatu - kubyaza inyungu iyi nama baciye muri Commonwealth Business Forum yari kuzaba mu gihe cya CHOGM.
Commonwealth ivuga ko Perezida w'u Rwanda Paul Kagame yatangaje ko "mu mezi ari imbere ibihugu bigize uyu muryango bizaba bigihanganye na Covid-19 n'ingaruka zayo ku bantu".
Ati: "Twizeye kuzaha ikaze umuryango wa Commonwealth i Kigali mu nama ya CHOGM mu gihe iki cyorezo kizaba cyatsinzwe".
Umunyamabanga mukuru w'uyu muryango Hon. Patricia Scotland avuga ko Covid-19 yahinduye umurongo w'amateka ya none. Ko "abantu bapfuye, ubukungu buri kugwa n'imibereho igaharikwa".
Madamu Patricia avuga ko buri wese abona akaga inama nini ziteje buri wese.
Ati: "Ibihe biriho ubu birasaba gufata ibyemezo bikomeye".
Iyi nama nibera mu Rwanda izaba ari inshuro ya kabiri ibereye muri aka karere nyuma y'iya 2007 yabereye muri Uganda.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_52023142' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/52023142' term='COVID'>
Algeria yemeje ikoreshwa rya chloroquine mu kuvura Covid-19 'ku barwayi bamwe na bamwe'
Minisiteri y'ubuzima muri Algeria yatangaje ko ibitaro byo muri iki gihugu cyo mu majyaruguru y'Afurika bishobora gukoresha chloroquine mu kuvura abarwayi ba Covid-19.
Minisiteri y'ubuzima muri Algeria yatangaje ko ibitaro byo muri iki gihugu cyo mu majyaruguru y'Afurika bishobora gukoresha chloroquine mu kuvura abarwayi ba Covid-19.
Ariko iryo tangazo risobanura neza ko uwo muti ukwiye gukoreshwa mu kuvura "abarwayi bamwe na bamwe" b'iyo ndwara y'ubuhemekero iterwa na virus ya Covid-19.
Rivuga kandi ko bigomba gukurikiza "amabwiriza yabugenewe mu by'ubuvuzi".
Chloroquine ni umwe mu miti yakoreshejwe igihe kirekire mu kuvura malariya - nubwo henshi muri Afurika utagikoreshwa kubera ko malariya yawurushije ubukana.
Mu kuvura abarwayi ba malariya, ibyo binini bikoreshwa mu kugabanya umuriro no kubabuka (inflammation).
Ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS/WHO) rivuga ko kugeza ubu nta gihamya ntakuka iriho ko chloroquine ivura Covid-19.
Ariko OMS yongeraho ko ari umwe mu yindi irimo gukorwaho amagerageza ngo harebwe niba wayivura.
James Gallagher, umunyamakuru wa BBC ukurikiranira hafi inkuru z'ubuzima, agira ati:
"Chloroquine isa nkaho ihagarika coronavirus mu bushakashatsi bwo muri za 'laboratoires'. Hari ibimenyetso by'ibivugwa n'abaganga bavuga ko yagaragaye nk'ifasha".
Mu cyumweru gishize, hari urujijo rwo kumenya niba Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika zemeje uwo muti nk'uvura coronavirus.
Ariko urwego rushinzwe ubuziranenge bw'ibiribwa n'imiti muri icyo gihugu rwavuze ko ucyigwaho.
Abantu 17 bamaze kwicwa na Covid-19 muri Algeria, igihugu kugeza ubu gifite abanduye 230, 54% byabo bakaba bari mu ntara ya Blida iri mu majyepfo y'umurwa mukuru Alger.
Mu cyumweru gishize, leta yafunze imipaka yose, ica ingendo z'indege n'iz'ubwato ndetse n'ingendo zihuza imijyi itandukanye y'icyo gihugu.
Algeria kandi yasabye abakozi bangana na 50% by'abakozi bose kuba bagiye mu kiruhuko cy'ibyumweru bibiri - ariko ikazabibahembera, ibategeka kuguma mu ngo zabo.
Abakora ubucuruzi ku giti cyabo basezeranyijwe ko bazahabwa inkunga y'amafaranga yo kuriha igihombo batewe no kuriha imishahara abakozi babo muri iki gihe batari ku kazi.
Mu bihugu bituranyi bya Maroc na Tunisia, nabyo byahagaritse ubuzima busanzwe, abasirikare bagabwe mu gufasha iyubahirizwa ry'amabwiriza yo kutegerana.
Barimo kandi kugenzura niba koko amaduka n'ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi bufatwa nkaho atari ubwa ngombwa cyane byafunzwe, nkuko byategetswe.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_52290318' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/52290318' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Banki y’isi yemereye u Burundi miliyoni $5 yo kurwanya Covid-19
Banki y'isi yatangaje ko yemeye guha leta y'u Burundi inkunga ya miliyoni eshanu z'amadorari y'Amerika kugira ngo iki gihugu gikomeze inzego z'ubuzima bw'abantu mu kwitegura no guhangana na coronavirus.
Banki y'isi yatangaje ko yemeye guha leta y'u Burundi inkunga ya miliyoni eshanu z'amadorari y'Amerika kugira ngo iki gihugu gikomeze inzego z'ubuzima bw'abantu mu kwitegura no guhangana na coronavirus.
Banki y'isi ivuga ko iyi nkunga ivuye mu kigega cyayo 'International Development Association' (IDA), igamije gufasha u Burundi gukumira ubwandu bushya bwa coronavirus.
Ivuga kandi ko iyo nkunga izafasha kongerera ubushobozi laboratoire zo gupima, gutegura no kubona ibikoresho byo kuvura no guhugura abakozi b'ubuzima ku nzego zitandukanye mu gihugu.
Minisiteri y'ubuzima mu Burundi ivuga ko hamaze kuboneka abantu batanu (5) banduye coronavirus, ko umwe ari we imaze guhitana.
Abantu batandukanye banenga leta y'u Burundi ko nta ngamba yafashe imbere mu gihugu mu kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'iki cyorezo.
Abategetsi mu Burundi bavuga ko ingamba zigenda zifatwa bitewe n'uko iki cyorezo kifashe mu gihugu.
Banki y'isi ivuga ko iri gutegura gutanga inkunga yihutirwa ya miliyari 14 z'amadorari ku bihugu bikennye kugira ngo bibashe guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Iyi banki ivuga kandi ko izatanga inkunga yagutse ya miliyari $160 yo gufasha ibihugu mu bindi birimo kurengera abazahaye, gufasha business no kuzahura ubukungu.
Inzobere mu bukungu n'imari zivuga ko ingaruka z'iki cyorezo zizakomerera ubukungu bw'isi n'imibereho y'abantu uri rusange, cyane cyane abakennye kurusha abandi.
International Development Association (IDA) ni ikigega cya Banki y'isi cyo gufasha ibihugu bikennye kurusha ibindi.
Iki kigega cyashyizweho mu 1960, gitanga inkunga n'inguzanyo zitariho inyungu ku mishinga y'iterambere no kurwanya ubukene.
IDA iri mu bitanga inkunga nini ku bihugu 76 bikennye cyane ku isi, muri byo 39 ni ibyo muri Africa nk'uko iyi banki ibivuga.
</doc>
