Coronavirus: Umuti wa Remdesivir wariko urageragezwa kuyivura warananiwe
Igerageza rya mbere ry'umuti wari wizewe ko ushobora kuvura coronavirus rivugwa ko ataco ryatanze.
Igerageza rya mbere ry'umuti wari wizewe ko ushobora kuvura coronavirus rivugwa ko ataco ryatanze.
Hari icizere c'uko umuti remdesivir wari gushobora kuvura Covid-19.
Ariko igerageza ryabereye mu Bushinwa ryerekana ko uwo muti ataco washitseko, nk'uko vyerekanwa n'icegeranyo caciye mu ryahumye umuryango ujejwe amagara y'abantu kw'isi, OMS/WHO.
Ico cegeranyo kivuga ko uwo muti utashoboye no gutanga ka mitende kubarwayi canke ngo ubure ugabanye n'umugera mu maraso.
Ihinguriro ryo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika ryakoze uwo muti,  Gilead Sciences, rivuga ko iryo geragezwa ryafashwe ukurati ko.
Amakuru y'uko iryo gerageza ataco ryashitseko yagiye kumenyekana inyuma y'aho OMS yerekaniye ku rubuga ngurukanabumenyi rwayo icegeranyo c'ivyavuye muri iryo gerageza, ariko mu nyuma ikaza kugikurako.
OMS ibandanya ivuga ko habaye ukwihenda mu gushira ahabona ico cegeranyo.
Ico cegeranyo cerekana ko iryo geragezwa ryakorewe ku barwayi 237, aho abashika 158 bahawe uwo muti kugira ngo barabe ko hari igihinduka bagereranije n'abandi 79 bobo bahawe iyindi yo gupfupfahaza.
Inyuma y'ukwezi, ibice 13.9% vy'abarwaye bahawe uwo muti barapfuye, mu gihe ibice 12.8% vya bamwe bahabwa imiti yo gupfupfahaza aribo bapfuye.
Ico cegeranyo kivuga kiti: "remdesivir nta kintu yamariye abawufashe, haba mu kubavura canke mu kugabanya ubukari".
Gilead iriyamiriza ico cegeranyo ca OMS.
Umwe mu bavugizi ba Gilead avuga ati: "Twibaza ko inkuru yatanzwe yarimwo ibintu bitari vyo ku vyerekeye iryo gerageza".
Yongera ko y'uko iryo gerageza ryahagaritswe haciye akanya gato kubera atari benshi baryitabiriye, vyumvikana ko ibitigiri bitari bikwiye.
Ati: "Ikiboneka ni uko iryo gerageza ritarangiye, kuko ibiharuro vyerekana ko remdisivir ishobora kugira akarusho, cane cane mu gihe abarwaye bivujije hakiri kare".
Hagati aho, si ukuvuga ko ivy'uwo muti birangiriye aha, kuko ibikorwa vyo kuwugerageza bibandanya mu minsi iri imbere bikazoshobora kwerekana neza isanamu nyayo ku vyerekeye ikoreshwa ryawo.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52081096' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52081096' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Boris Johnson wishyize mu kato yaburiye Abongereza kwitega 'ibihe bibi kurushaho'
Mu ibaruwa yoherereje buri rugo rwo muri iki gihugu, Minisitiri w'intebe w'Ubwongereza yaburiye abaturage ko icyorezo cya coronavirus kizabamerera nabi kurushaho mbere yuko gicisha macye.
Mu ibaruwa yoherereje buri rugo rwo muri iki gihugu, Minisitiri w'intebe w'Ubwongereza yaburiye abaturage ko icyorezo cya coronavirus kizabamerera nabi kurushaho mbere yuko gicisha macye.
Muri iyo baruwa, Boris Johnson, wishyize mu kato guhera ku wa gatanu w'iki cyumweru nyuma yo gusanga yaranduye Covid-19, avuga ko ingamba zikaze kurushaho zishobora gufatwa bibaye ngombwa.
Abongereza kandi barahabwa inyandiko ikubiyemo amabwiriza ya leta ajyanye no kuva mu rugo ndetse irimo n'andi makuru ajyanye n'ubuzima.
Ibyo bibaye nyuma yaho leta y'Ubwongereza inengewe ko nta nama yumvikana neza yagiriye abaturage bayo kuri iyi ndwara y'ubuhumekero ya Covid-19 iterwa n'ubu bwoko bushya bwa coronavirus.
Umubare w'abamaze kwicwa na coronavirus mu Bwongereza waraye ugeze ku 1,019, nyuma yaho abandi bantu bashya 260 yishe batangajwe kuri uwo munsi w'ejo.
Ubu mu Bwongereza hari abarwayi 17,089 bemejwe ko banduye coronavirus.
Muri iyo baruwa iri kohererezwa ingo miliyoni 30 ku giciro bivugwa ko kizagera kuri miliyoni 5.8 z'amapawundi (arenga miliyari 6 mu mafaranga y'u Rwanda), Bwana Johnson agira ati:
"Kuva mu ntangiriro, twashatse gushyiraho ingamba zikwiye mu gihe gikwiye".
"Ntabwo tuzashidikanya kurenzaho [mu ngamba dufata] niba ari yo nama abahanga muri bumenyi bwa siyansi no mu buvuzi batugiriye ko tugomba gufata".
Ingamba zikaze zo guhangana n'ikwirakwira rya coronavirus muri iki gihugu - zirimo guca gutera kw'abantu barenze babiri no gufunga amaduka acuruza ibitari ingenzi cyane - zashyizweho mu cyumweru gishize.
Muri iyo baruwa, Bwana Johnson akomeza agira ati: "Ni ingenzi kubabwiza ukuri - tuzi ko ibintu bizaba bibi kurushaho mbere yuko bimera neza kurushaho".
"Ariko turimo gukora imyiteguro ikwiye, kandi uko twese turushaho gukurikiza amabwiriza, ni ko abantu bapfa bazakomeza kugabanuka kandi ni nako bizihuta ko dusubira mu buzima busanzwe".
Impuguke zavuze ko ziteze ko umubare w'abanduye coronavirus n'uw'abo yica ukomeza kwiyongera mu byumweru biri hagati ya bibiri na bitatu biri imbere, mbere yuko umusaruro w'ingamba zo kutegerana no guhagarika byinshi mu buzima busanzwe utangira kwigaragaza.
Mu ibaruwa ye, Bwana Johnson avuga ko iki cyorezo ari "igihe kidasanzwe ku gihugu", ndetse yongera kwibutsa amabwiriza ya leta yo kuguma mu rugo mu kwirinda kongerera akazi urwego rw'ubuzima mu gihugu ruzwi nka NHS, no kugira ngo ubuzima burokorwe.
Minisitiri w'intebe w'Ubwongereza yemera ko izo ngamba za leta ayoboye zizagira ingaruka ku mibereho y'abaturage.
Ariko, muri iyo baruwa yanditse nyuma yaho abaminisitiri batangaje gahunda y'ingoboka ifite agaciro ka za miliyari z'amapawundi, Bwana Johnson yagize ati:
"Leta izakora ibishoboka byose mu gufasha ngo imibereho ikomeze no mu kubona ifunguro rya buri munsi".
Bwana Johnson kandi yashimagije akazi k'abaganga, abaforomo n'abandi bita ku barwayi ndetse n'abandi babarirwa mu bihumbi amagana bitanze nk'abakorerabushake mu gufasha ab'intege nke cyane.
Inyandiko ya leta iherekeje iyo baruwa, ikubiyemo amabwiriza ku gukaraba intoki, igisobanuro ku bimenyetso bya coronavirus, amategeko ajyanye no kuva mu rugo ndetse n'inama ku gukingira ab'intege nke.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52394153' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52394153' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Impari ku muti kama wa Madagascar
Madagascar ivuga ko yatoye umuti uvura coronavirus ariko OMS yoyo ivuga ko gushika kuri ubu "ata cemezo na kimwe" cerekana ko uwo muti ushobora "gukinga canke kuvura" coronavirus.
Madagascar ivuga ko yatoye umuti uvura coronavirus ariko OMS yoyo ivuga ko gushika kuri ubu "ata cemezo na kimwe" cerekana ko uwo muti ushobora "gukinga canke kuvura" coronavirus.
Ku wa mbere 20/04, umukuru w'ico gihugu Andry Rajoelina yaratangaje umuti avuga ko ushobora gukinga ukanavura umugera coronavirus.
We nyene ubwiwe yaranyoye uwo muti ukozwe mu biti kama anatangaza ko uwo muti mu minsi uzoboneka mu gihugu cose kugira ngo uvure coronavirus.
N'aho yawutangaje ku mugaragaro, umuryango ujejwe amagara y'abantu kw'isi, OMS/WHO uvuga ko ata bushakashatsi bwakozwe n'abahinga kugira ngo bemeze nimba koko uwo muti wa Madagascar uvugwa ko uvura Covid-19 ukora vy'ukuri.
Eka n'ikigo c'igihugu kijejwe ubuvuzi (ANAMEM) kirafise amakenga kuri uwo muti wakozwe n'ikigo c'igihugu kijejwe ubushakashatsi (IMRA).
Ikigo NAMEM kivuga ko uwo muti - Covid-Organics - ushobora kuzogira ingaruka mbi ku magara y'abazowihereza kuko ata "bushakashatsi bwakozwe kugira ngo bwemeze uwo muti".
Uyo muti kama Covid-Organics uhabwa ku buntu abantu ba ntahonikora.
Uyo muti ukozwe mu giterwa citwa artémisia - igiterwa gihingurwamwo umuti uvura malaria - hamwe n'ibindi biterwa vyo muri Madagascar.
Ugurishwa mu macupa nk'icayi (tisane) inyuma y'aho bawugeragereje ku bantu badashika 20 mu kiringo c'indwi zitatu, nk'uko umukuru w'ibiro vya Perezida, Lova Hasinirina Ranoromaro, yabibwiye BBC.
Igihe Covid-Organics  itangazwa ku wa mbere, Perezida Rajoelina yavuze ati; "Uwo muti warageragejwe - hari babiri bari barwaye barawiherezaubu barakize".
"Uwo muti wo kunywa nk'icayi uvura mu kiringo c'iminsi indwi gusa".
Andry Rajoelina yasavye abanyagihugu ko bonywa uwo muti mu ntumbero yo kwikingira.
Ari imbere y'abaserukira ibihugu vyabo muri ico gihugu n'abandi banyecubahiro yavuze ati: "Abanyeshure bategerezwa kuwihereza….buke buke umunsi wose".
Aciye kuri Twitter, Bwana Rajoelina avuga ko yanaronse ubutumwa bwo kumukeza buvuye kwa mugenziwe wa Republika y'Intwaro Rusangi ya Congo, Félix Tshisekedi "kuri uwo muti kama Covid-Organics".
Dr Charles Andrianjara arongoye ikigo IMRA, avugako Covid-Organics yokoreshwa mu buryo bwo kwikingira.
Hagati aho, agumana amakenga kw'ikoreshwa ry'uwo muti mu kuvura iyo ndwara, akavuga ariko ko ubushakashatsi bw'ikiganga bwerekana ko "uwo muti usa n'uwushobora gukiza iyo ndwara", nk'uko bivugwa n'itororokanirizo ry'amakuru AFP risubiramwo amajambo yiwe.
Iryo zinga ryo mw'ibahari Indiano rimaze kumenyesha ko abashika 121 ari bo bamaze kwandura coronavirus, ariko ko ata n'umwe irahitana.
Inyuma y'itanguzwa ry'ikoreshwa rya Covid-Organics, OMS yasohoye itangazo aho ivuga ko gushika kuri ino saha "ata cemezo na kimwe" cerekana ko uwo muti wakorewe muri Madagascar ushobora "gukinga canke gukiza" coronavirus.
Uyo muryango urahagarara cane ku majambo yashikirijwe n'umukuru wawo, Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, aho avuga ko "ata nzira ya hafi" iriho mu ntambara na coronavirus.
Yongera ko y'uko hari ibikorwa vy'igerageza biriko biraka kw'isi mu ntumbero yo kurondera umuti nyawo.
Umupfasoni Ranoromaro umukuru w'ibiro vya perezida wa Madagascar, avuga ko umukuru w'igihugu Rajoelina yari azi neza ko OMS itegerezwa kwubahiriza amategeko ayigenga, ariko y'uko ico gihugu catangaje uwo muti mu bwigenge bwaco.
Ati: "Ni igikorwaciwe co kwitaho abanyagihugu ba Madagascar".
Umwigisha wa kaminuza, Brian Klaas, akaba n'umuhinga ku bibazo vya Madagascar ku kigo ca  kaminuza ca Londres, abona ko ibivugwa na Bwana Rajoelina bishobora guteza ingorane ku banyagihugu hakubazanira urukiza.
Yabwiye ikiganiro Newsday ca BBC ati: "Ni ingorane kubera ibituma bibiri - ica mbere ni uko abantu bazonywa Covid-Organics mu gihe bidakenewe".
"Ubwa kabiri ivyo bizotuma abantu bibaza ko bakomeye, bikazobatuma bijajara bakitwara uko batategerezwa, ivyo navyo bikazobashira mu ngorane nini cane, eka banazitere na bagenzi babo".
Avuga ko mu gihe iyo ndwara yokwiragira cane mu gihugu, abantu bashobora "gutikira" kubera ubuvuzi muri ico gihugu atako bwifashe, nayo igihugu kikaba gifise za mashini zifasha abarwayeguhema zitandatu gusa, ku bantu bangana n'imiliyoni 27.
Mu kwa gatatu, ikigo c'igihugu citaho amagara y'abantu gifise icicaro muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, caragabishije kw'ikoreshwa ry'ivyo abantu bibaza ko ari imiti ivura coronavirus, cane cane ikozwe mu biti kama- aho cavuze ko inzira nyayo yo kwirinda kurwara ari ukwirinda kwandura uwo mugera.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_51819308' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/51819308' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Ibitaramo bya Madonna na Miley Cyrus byahagaritswe
Abahanzi b'ibyamamare Miley Cyrus na Madonna ntibagikoze ibitaramo bari bafite kubera gutinya ikwirakwira rya Covid-19 izwi cyane nka coronavirus, ubu yatangiye kugira ingaruka no kuri muzika.
Abahanzi b'ibyamamare Miley Cyrus na Madonna ntibagikoze ibitaramo bari bafite kubera gutinya ikwirakwira rya Covid-19 izwi cyane nka coronavirus, ubu yatangiye kugira ingaruka no kuri muzika.
Miley Cyrus yatangaje ko atakigiye mu gitaramo yari kuririmbamo kuwa gatanu i Melbourne muri Australia.
Ibitaramo bibiri bya nyuma byari bisigaye kuri 'concerts' Madonna ari gukorera mu Bufaransa nabyo byahagaritswe kubera itangazo rya leta ribuza ikoraniro ry'abantu barenze 1,000.
Miley Cyrus yatangaje ko ababajwe cyane no kutabasha kujya i Merbourne kubera inama yagiriwe n'abategetsi "mu rwego rwo kugabanya ibyago ku buzima".
Cyari igitaramo kigamije gufasha abagizweho ingaruka n'imiriro y'ishyamba imaze igihe gito iyogoje Australia.
Yanditse kuri Twitter ati: "Ndababaye ko ntazahaba, ariko ngomba gukora ibikwiye ku bw'ineza no kurinda ubuzima bwa 'band' yanjye n'abo dukorana".
Madonna, bita 'umwamikazi wa Pop' uyu munsi kuwa kabiri n'ejo kuwa gatatu yari afite ibitaramo i Paris, ibitaromo bisoza ibyo yariho akorera mu Bufaransa byiswe 'Madame X world tour'.
Itangazo ryo ku cyumweru ry'ubutegetsi bw'Ubufaransa ryahagaritse amakoraniro yose arimo abantu barenze 1,000.
Abateguye aho ibi bitaramo byari kubera batangaje ko "babajwe cyane no kumenyesha ko ibi bitaramo byombi bitakibaye".
Amakuru y'uyu munsi ya OMS/WHO ivuga ko mu Bufaransa habarurwa abantu 1,126 banduye coronavirus na 30 imaze kwica, naho muri Australia habarurwa abantu 80 bayanduye na batatu yishe.
Mu Rwanda, ku cyumweru umujyi wa Kigali wategetse isubikwa ry'ibitaramo by'imyidagaduro n'ibindi birori bihuza abantu benshi mu kwirinda ikwirakwira rya coronavirus.
Itangazo ry'umujyi wa Kigali ryatanzwe mbere y'amasaha macye ngo habe igitaramo gikomeye cyari gitegerejwe.
Abateguye iki gitaramo babwiye BBC ko bibaza uko ahari kubera iki gitaramo ari ho hoherejwe abapolisi bakiburizamo na mbere y'uko umujyi wa Kigali utanga iryo tangazo.
Binubira ko cyahagaritswe mu gihe kuri uwo munsi habaye imipira n'ibindi bikorwa bihuza abantu benshi.
Imibare y'uyu munsi ya OMS igaragaza ko coronavirus imaze kugera mu bihugu 101 ku isi, muri Africa imaze kugera mu bihugu 10.
Kugeza ubu coronavirus ntabwo iragera mu karere k'ibiyaga bigari.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_52311398' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/52311398' term='COVID'>
June Almeida, umugore wavumbuye coronavirus ya mbere
Umugore wavumbuye ubwoko bwa mbere bwa coronavirus yibasira abantu yari umukobwa w'umushoferi w'imodoka ya bisi wo muri Scotland mu bwami bw'Ubwongereza, wataye ishuri afite imyaka 16 y'amavuko.
Umugore wavumbuye ubwoko bwa mbere bwa coronavirus yibasira abantu yari umukobwa w'umushoferi w'imodoka ya bisi wo muri Scotland mu bwami bw'Ubwongereza, wataye ishuri afite imyaka 16 y'amavuko.
June Almeida yaje kuba inkomarume (pioneer) mu buhanga bwo gutahura ishusho ya za virusi.
Ibikorwa bye biri kongera gutekerezwaho muri iki gihe isi yugarijwe n'icyorezo cya Covid-19, indwara yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero iterwa n'ubu bwoko bushya bwa coronavirus.
Covid-19 ni indwara nshya ariko iterwa na coronavirus yo mu bwoko bumwe n'ubwavumbuwe bwa mbere na Dr Almeida mu mwaka wa 1964.
Iyo coronavirus yayivumburiye muri 'laboratoire' ye yo mu bitaro bya St Thomas' biri mu murwa mukuru London w'Ubwongereza.
Uyu muhanga mu bumenyi bwa za virusi (cyangwa udukoko) yavutse yitwa June Hart mu mwaka wa 1930.
Akurira mu nzu y'icumbi iri hafi y'icyanya cya Alexandra Park mu majyaruguru ashyira uburasirazuba bw'umujyi wa Glasgow.
Yataye ishuri amaze kugira ubumenyi bucye bwo mu ishuri, ariko aza kubona akazi ko gukora muri 'laboratoire' mu ishami risuzuma imihindagurikire y'utunyangingo tw'umubiri (tissues) kubera indwara, ku bitaro bya Glasgow Royal Infirmary.
Nyuma yaje kwimukira i London gukomeza ibijyanye n'akazi ke, nuko mu mwaka wa 1954 ashakana na Enriques Almeida, umunyabugeni (artist) ukomoka mu gihugu cya Venezuela.
Bombi n'umwana wabo w'umukobwa bimukiye mu mujyi wa Toronto muri Canada.
George Winter, umwanditsi mu bijyanye n'ubuvuzi, avuga ko mu kigo cy'ubushakashatsi ku ndwara ya kanseri cya Ontario Cancer Institute ari ho Dr Almeida yanonosoreye ibya virusi.
By'umwihariko mu bumenyi buhambaye mu gukoresha icyuma cyo kuzipima cya 'electron microscope'.
Yatangije uburyo bwo kuzipima neza kurushaho hakoreshejwe ibizirwanya mu mubiri (antibodies), mu rwego rwo kuzikusanyiriza hamwe.
Bwana Winter yabwiye ikiganiro Drivetime cya BBC Radio Scotland ko impano za Dr Almeida zashimwe mu Bwongereza, akareshywa akahagaruka mu 1964.
Agakora ku ishuri ry'ubuvuzi bw'abantu rishamikiye ku bitaro bya St Thomas' i London.
Ibyo bitaro ni nabyo biherutse kuvura Minisitiri w'intebe w'Ubwongereza Boris Johnson ubwo yari arwaye Covid-19.
Ubwo yari asubiye mu Bwongereza, Dr Almeida yatangiye gukorana na Dr David Tyrrell, wari ukuriye ubushakashatsi ku bicurane (common cold) ahitwa Salisbury mu karere ka Wiltshire.
Bwana Winter avuga ko Dr Tyrrell yari amaze igihe yiga ibijyanye n'isuku yo mu mazuru, ku bari bemeye gukorerwaho ubushakashatsi.
Kandi itsinda rye ryari ryarasanze ko abo bakorerwagaho ubushakashatsi bashoboraga kwadukana virusi nke zifitanye isano n'ibicurane, ariko ko atari ko bose bazigiraga.
Mu gipimo kimwe by'umwihariko cy'abo bakoreweho ubushakashatsi, cyaje kwitwa B814, cyari icy'ibyogejwe mu mazuru y'umunyeshuri wo ku ishuri abanyeshuri biga baba mu kigo.
Ni ikigo cyo mu karere ka Surrey mu majyepfo ashyira uburasirazuba bw'Ubwongereza, hakaba hari mu mwaka wa 1960.
Basanze ko bashoboraga kwanduza ibimenyetso by'ibicurane ku bakorerwaho ubushakashatsi, ariko ko bo batashoboraga kubikuza mu buryo busanzwe bwo muri 'laboratoire'.
Ariko ubushakashatsi bwagaragazaga ko bishobora gukurira ahandi ku ruhande bitandukanyijwe n'umuntu.
Rero Dr Tyrrell yibazaga niba bishobora kubonwa muri 'microscope'.
Nuko boherereza ibipimo June Almeida, waje kubona uduce duto twa virusi muri ibyo bipimo, yavuze ko dusa nka virusi za influenza, ariko ko bitameze neza neza cyo kimwe.
Yatahuye icyaje kumenyekana nka coronavirus ya mbere yibasira abantu.
Bwana Winter na Dr Almeida mu by'ukuri bari baranabonye uduce duto tumeze nkayo ubwo bakoraga iperereza ku ndwara y'umwijima yibasira imbeba ndetse n'ibicurane byandura byo mu nkoko.
Ariko, Bwana Winter avuga ko inyandiko y'ubushakashatsi ya Dr Almeida yoherereje ikinyamakuru cy'ubushakashatsi bugenzurwa n'abo mu rwego rumwe mbere yuko butangazwa (peer-reviewed journal), yanzwe ntitangazwe.
Impamvu ngo ni uko "abayigenzura bavuze ko amashusho yakoresheje yari gusa amafoto mabi agaragaza uduce duto twa virusi ya influenza".
Ubwo buvumbuzi bwe bushya bwo mu gipimo cyiswe B814 bwanditswe mu mwaka wa 1965 mu kinyamakuru cy'ubushakashatsi mu buvuzi bw'abantu cyo mu Bwongereza cya British Medical Journal.
Naho imyaka ibiri nyuma yaho, amafoto ya mbere y'ibyo yari yabonye mu bushakashatsi bwe yatangajwe mu kinyamakuru cy'ubushakashatsi kuri virusi cya Journal of General Virology.
Nkuko Bwana Winter abivuga, ni Dr Tyrrell na Dr Almeida, bafatanyije na Profeseri Tony Waterson wari ukuriye ibitaro bya St Thomas', bise iyo virusi coronavirus.
Impamvu ngo ni uko ishusho yayo muri 'microscope' igaragara nk'uruziga cyangwa urugori, ari byo 'corona'.
Nyuma Dr Almeida yakoze mu ishuri rikuru ry'ubuvuzi ry'i London - Postgraduate Medical School in London - aho yaherewe impamyabumenyi y'ikirenga.
Yarangirije akazi ke mu kigo Wellcome Institute, aho izina rye ryagaragaye mu bushakashatsi bwinshi mu bijyanye no gutahura imiterere ya za virusi.
Nyuma yo kuva muri Wellcome, Dr Almeida yabaye umwarimu w'umukino ngororangingo wa yoga.
Ariko mu mpera y'imyaka ya 1980, yaje gusubira mu rwego rw'ubushakashatsi kuri za virusi, akabikora nk'umujyanama.
Icyo gihe yafashije mu gufata amashusho mashya ya virusi itera SIDA - izwi nka HIV cyangwa VIH.
June Almeida yapfuye mu mwakwa wa 2007, afite imyaka 77 y'amavuko.
None ubu, nyuma y'imyaka 13 apfuye, ari guhabwa icyubahiro akwiye nk'uwabaye inkomarume mu bushakashatsi bwihutishije gusobanukirwa virusi ubu iri gukwirakwira mu bice bitandukanye byo ku isi.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52336723' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52336723' term='COVID'>
DRC: 24 barahitanywe n’isegenya mu gisagara ca Uvira
Ubutegetsi bwa Republika y'Intwaro Rusangi ya Kongo bumenyesha ko abantu 24 bahitanywe n'imvura y'isegenya mu gisagara ca Uvira gihana urubibe n'u Burundi, yaguye mw'ijoro ryo ku wa kane buca ari ku wa gatanu.
Ubutegetsi bwa Republika y'Intwaro Rusangi ya Kongo bumenyesha ko abantu 24 bahitanywe n'imvura y'isegenya mu gisagara ca Uvira gihana urubibe n'u Burundi, yaguye mw'ijoro ryo ku wa kane buca ari ku wa gatanu.
Ivyo biri mw'itangazo ryaraye risohowe n'ibiro vy'umukuru w'ico gihugu biricishije ku rubuga rwa Twitter, aho bimenyesha ko abandi 45 bakomeretse, be n'amazu yabomaguritse.
Ico gihugu gisanzwe kandi gihanganye n'ibiza vya coronavirusi hamwe na Ebola yasubiriye kwibonekeza mu gisagara ca Beni kiri mu buseruko bw'ico gihugu.
Iyo segenya yaguye mu ntara za Kivu y'ubumanuko, Haut-Lomami, Maniema na Tanganyika yatumye haba imyuzurira yahitanye abantu n'ibintu, nk'uko Perezida w'ico gihugu Félix-Antoine Tshisekedi yabibwiye inama nshikiranganji idasanzwe yakoresheje ku mugoroba w'ejo ku wa gatanu aciye ku bihinga bwa videwo.
Yasavye ko hokorwa ibishoboka vyose kugira ngo bagarukire ku banyagihugu bahuye n'ivyago.
Ejo ku wa gatanu, icegera c'umukuru w'igisagara ca Uvira, Kiki Kapenda Kifara, yabwiye radiyo Okapi yo muri ico gihugu ko ibikorwa vyo kurondera abandi boba baguweko n'ibihomoka vyari bikibandanya.
Bwana Kapenda  yavuze kandi ko gushika ku muhingamo w'ejo ku wa gatanu, uruzi rwa Mulongwe rwari rukirengerwa n'amazi yava mu misozi agaca mu mabarabara y'ico gisagara.
Amakaritiye ya Kasenga, Kakombe na Mulongwe niyo yabangamiwe gusumba nk'uko ayop makuru abivuga.
Ivyo biri uko mu gihe ico gihugu gisanzwe gihanganye n'indwara ya Covid-19 kuva ku wa 10 z'ukwa gatatu, aho abashika 287 aribo bamaze kumenyekana ko bayanduye, nayo 23 ikaba imaze kubahitana.
Muri ico gihugu kandi hasubiriye kwibonekeza ikiza ca Ebola, inyuma y'iminsi gisa n'icari catujijwe.
Mu gisagara ca Beni kiri mu ntara ya Kivu y'uburaruko mu buseruko bw'ico gihugu niho hamaze kwibonekeza abandi barwayi, aho abashika batanu ari bo bamaze kwandura.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52081079' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52081079' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Umubare w'abanduye Covid-19 mu Rwanda wageze kuri 60
Minisiteri y'ubuzima mu Rwanda yatangaje ko umubare w'abanduye ubu bwoko bushya bwa coronavirus mu gihugu waraye wiyongereyeho abarwayi batandatu bakagera kuri 60.
Minisiteri y'ubuzima mu Rwanda yatangaje ko umubare w'abanduye ubu bwoko bushya bwa coronavirus mu gihugu waraye wiyongereyeho abarwayi batandatu bakagera kuri 60.
Iyi minisiteri ivuga ko abo batandatu bashya barimo bane baturutse i Dubai muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Abarabu, umwe waturutse muri Amerika ndetse n'undi watahuwe ko yahuye n'urwaye coronavirus mu Rwanda.
Mu ijambo Perezida Paul Kagame w'u Rwanda yavuze ku wa gatanu, yaburiye ko umubare w'abanduye "uzakomeza uzamuke kuko hakomeje gushakishwa abahuye n'abarwayi b'iyo ndwara kugira ngo bapimwe, ndetse abagaragayeho uburwayi bavurwe".
Bwana Kagame yavuze ko ari bwo "buryo bwiza bwo gufasha abashobora kuba baranduye mu rwego rwo kurinda imiryango yabo ndetse natwe twese aho dutuye" no gutsinda iki cyorezo vuba.
Muri aka karere kugeza mu gitondo cyo kuri iki cyumweru, u Rwanda ni urwa kabiri mu kugira umubare w'abanduye benshi.
Rukurikiye Repubulika ya Demokarasi ya Kongo ifite abanduye 65, Kenya ifite 38, Uganda 30 na Tanzania ifite abanduye 14.
U Burundi ni bwo butaratangazwamo uwanduye coronavirus.
Iyi mibare ya Kaminuza ya Johns Hopkins yo muri Amerika igaragaza kandi ko kugeza muri iki gitondo cyo ku cyumweru, muri Afurika hari abanduye 4,229, ikaba imaze kwica 134 naho 254 bamaze kuyikira.
Ku isi abarenga 670,000 ni bo bamaze kwandura iyi ndwara ya Covid-19 yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero iterwa na coronavirus, abarenga 31,000 imaze kubica, naho abarenga 145,000 bamaze kuyikira.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52278289' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52278289' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: IMF yorohereje umwenda ibihugu 25 birimo u Rwanda
Madamu Kristalina Georgieva utegeka ikigega cy'imari ku isi (IMF/FMI) yatangaje ko inama y'ubutegetsi yacyo yorohereje kwishyura umwenda ku bihugu 25 muri gahunda yo kubifasha guhangana n'ingaruka z'icyorezo cya Covid-19.
Madamu Kristalina Georgieva utegeka ikigega cy'imari ku isi (IMF/FMI) yatangaje ko inama y'ubutegetsi yacyo yorohereje kwishyura umwenda ku bihugu 25 muri gahunda yo kubifasha guhangana n'ingaruka z'icyorezo cya Covid-19.
Iki kigega kivuga ko ku ntangiriro, mu gihe cy'amezi atandatu ari imbere ibi bihugu bitazaba byishyura imyenda bifitiye IMF.
Ibyo bihugu ni; Afghanistan, Benin, Burkina Faso, Central African Republic, Chad, Comoros, Congo, D.R., The Gambia, Guinea, Guinea-Bissau, Haiti, Liberia, Madagascar, Malawi, Mali, Mozambique, Nepal, Niger, Rwanda, São Tomé and Príncipe, Sierra Leone, Solomon Islands, Tajikistan, Togo, and Yemen.
Tariki 02 z'uku kwezi iki kigega cyatangaje ko cyahaye u Rwanda inguzanyo yihutirwa yishyurwa nta nyungu ya miliyoni 109 z'amadorari ya Amerika yo guhangana n'ingaruza z'iki cyorezo mu bukungu.
Mu itangazo IMF yaraye isohoye, yavuze ko "ibi ari ugufasha ibihugu bikennye cyane kandi byugarijwe gushyira imari yabyo mu bikorwa by'ubutabazi n'ibindi byo gufasha".
Iki kigega kivuga ko giteganya korohereza ibihugu umwenda wose hamwe ugera kuri miliyoni $500.
Madamu Kristalina asaba ibindi bihugu bigize iki kigega kucyongerera ubushobozi bwo koroshya kwishyura imyenda mu gihe cy'imyaka ibiri ku bihugu binyamuryango by'iki kigega bikennye cyane.
Ntabwo iki kigega cyatangaje ibyo cyagendeyeho mu korohereza umwenda biriya bihugu 25.
</doc>
