<doc docid='bbc_52541441' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/52541441' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Mu Bufaransa habonetse 'umurwayi wa mbere wari warayanduye mu kwezi kwa 12'
Umurwayi basanzemo indwara y'ibihaha hafi y'umurwa mukuru Paris tariki 27/12/2020 umuganga wamuvuye yatangaje ko ubu basanze ahubwo yari afite coronavirus.
Umurwayi basanzemo indwara y'ibihaha hafi y'umurwa mukuru Paris tariki 27/12/2020 umuganga wamuvuye yatangaje ko ubu basanze ahubwo yari afite coronavirus.
Dr Yves Cohen yavuze ko igipimo bamufashe icyo gihe cyasuzumwe muri iyi minsi kikagaragaza ko uyu murwayi yari afite Covid-19.
Uwo ni umugabo w'ikigero cy'imyaka 50, akaba yarakize, we yavuze ko atazi uburyo yaba yaranduye iyo ndwara kuko icyo gihe atari yarigeze agera mu gace ivugwamo.
Aya makuru asobanura ko bishoboka ko iyi virus yaba yarageze mu Bufaransa ukwezi kumwe mbere y'igihe bizwi ko yahagereye.
Kugeza ubu, abantu batatu ba mbere bemejwe ko banduye coronavirus babonetse mu Bufaransa tariki 24 z'ukwezi kwa mbere.
Muri abo, babiri muri bo bari baherutse i Wuhan mu Bushinwa aho iki cyorezo cyabonetse bwa mbere, uwa gatatu yari uwa hafi wo mu muryango wabo.
Dr Cohen umuyobozi w'ishami ryo kuvura indembe mu bitaro bya Avicenne and Jean-Verdier hafi ya Paris yabwiye televiziyo BFMTV ko aherutse gusubira mu bipimo byafashwe abantu baje barwaye ibicurane mu kwezi kwa 12 n'ukwa mbere.
Avuga ko icyo gihe yasuzumye amatembabuzi yo mu mazuru y'abarwayi 14.
Ati: "Duherutse kongera gusuzuma ibyo bipimo tugerageza gukurikirana coronavirus. Ku bipimo by'abarwayi 14, igipimo kimwe nicyo twayisanzemo.
"Twagipimye izindi nshuro ebyiri ngo twizere neza ko nta kwibeshya. N'izo nshuro cyaje kibyemeza".
Dr Cohen avuga ko yahise abimenyesha urwego rwa leta rushinzwe iby'ubuzima, ndetse asaba abandi bahanga mu bya virus gusubiramo ibipimo biri mu bitaro byabo bashakisha Covid-19.
Uyu muganga avuga ko raporo irambuye kubyo yabonye izatangazwa muri International Journal of Antimicrobial Agents mu mpera z'iki cyumweru.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_52409613' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/52409613' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Abayisilamu mu Rwanda batangiye bate Ramadhan mu bihe bidasanzwe?
Abayisilamu ku isi batangiye igisibo gitagatifu cy'idini ryabo kiba buri mwaka, kimwe n'ahandi hamwe na hamwe ku isi, bamwe mu bo mu Rwanda bavuga ko iki gisibo kidasanzwe kuko imigenzo imwe basanzwe bakora mu gisibo ubu itemewe kubera kwirinda coronavirus.
Abayisilamu ku isi batangiye igisibo gitagatifu cy'idini ryabo kiba buri mwaka, kimwe n'ahandi hamwe na hamwe ku isi, bamwe mu bo mu Rwanda bavuga ko iki gisibo kidasanzwe kuko imigenzo imwe basanzwe bakora mu gisibo ubu itemewe kubera kwirinda coronavirus.
Latifa Mwizerwa umuyisilamukazi utuye mu mujyi wa Rubavu yabwiye BBC ko igisibo batangiye uyu munsi kidasanzwe kuri we kuko aribwo bwa mbere atazaba yemerewe kujya ku musigiti gusenga no gusangira n'abakene ifunguro rya nimugoroba.
Mu Rwanda hafashwe ingamba zo guhagarika ubuzima busanzwe (lockdown) zigiye kumara ibyumweru bitandatu kugeza tariki 30/04, mu kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo Covid-19.
Sheikh Mussa Sindayigaya umuvugizi w'umuryango w'abaIslam mu Rwanda avuga ko muri iki gisibo, yaba isengesho rusange rya nimugoroba ku misigiti cyangwa gusangira ifunguro rya nimugoroba n'abakene bikunze kuba ku misigiti byose bibujijwe.
Sheikh  Sindayigaya yabiwye BBC ati: "Ariko gusiba birakomeza, kuba umuntu ari mu rugo ntibimubuza gusiba kuko ni itegeko ry'Imana kandi ni inkingi imwe muri eshanu za Islam".
Mu gisibo gitagatifu, Abayisilamu - ababishoboye - bategekwa kutagira icyo bageza mu nda kuva izuba rirashe kugeza rirenze kandi bagasenga kurushaho.
Bwana Sindayigaya avuga ko umwihariko w'isengesho risanzwe rya Ramadhan ryitwa Taraweeh riba nyuma yo gusiburuka kumugoroba, naryo rizakorerwa mu rugo, buri muryango wose ukwawo kuko imisigiti kimwe n'izindi nsengero nayo ifunze.
Ali Felix Mugabo umuyisilamu wo mu murenge wa Rwezamenyo i Nyamirambo mu mujyi wa Kigali avuga ko yizeye ko tariki 30/04 hashobora kuba impinduka insengero n'imisigiti bigafungurwa.
Yabwiye BBC ati: "Abayisilamu kuba hamwe mu isengesho ni umuco wacu, cyane cyane noneho mu gihe  cy'igisibo. Niba nta gihindutse tariki 30 nk'uko tubyizeye iki gisibo kizaba kidasanzwe".
Bwana Sindayigaya avuga ko idini ya Islam yemera ko imisigiti ifungwa mu gihe hateye indwara abantu bashobora kwanduzanya.
Ati: "...ndetse hari imvugo y'intumwa y'Imana Muhamad,  Imana imuhe amahoro n'imigisha, ngo 'umuntu wanduye ntazegerane n'utarandura'.
"Iyo mvugo igaragaraza ko bitemewe ko umuntu yakwegerana n'abandi mu gihe nk'iki cya coronavirus mu kwirinda kwanduzanya".
Mu gisibo gitagatifu cya Islam, ku misigiti itandukanye mu Rwanda nyuma y'isengesho rya nimugoroba haboneka abakene baza gusangira ifunguro rya nimugoroba (Iftar) riba ryateganyijwe.
Bwana Sindayigaya avuga ko ibi bitazashoboka muri iki gisibo, gusa ko hari uburyo buri gukorwa bwo gufasha abakene.
Avuga ko biciye ku bayobozi b'imisigiti habaruwe abakene na numero za telephone zabo, bihabwa abayisilamu kugira ngo bajye baboherereza amafaranga yo kubafasha muri iki gisibo.
Ati: "Icyo gikorwa kimaze iminsi gikorwa kandi kigenda neza no muri iki gisibo kizakomeza kugira ngo abakene nabo bibafashe mu gisibo".
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52307677' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52307677' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Muri Kenya abikekwa ko Covid-19 bashatse gutoroka ikigo bashizwemwo
Abanyakenya baharurwa muri mirongo basanzwe bashizwe mu kigo categuriwe abikeketswe ko banduye coronavirus i Nairobi ejo baragerageje gusohoka ku nguvu, bakavuga ko babayeho nabi cane.
Abanyakenya baharurwa muri mirongo basanzwe bashizwe mu kigo categuriwe abikeketswe ko banduye coronavirus i Nairobi ejo baragerageje gusohoka ku nguvu, bakavuga ko babayeho nabi cane.
Umushikiranganji w'amagara y'abantu avuga ko abantu 225 mu gihugu cose bamaze kwandura uwo mugera, kandi ko abantu bose binjiye mu gihugu imbibe zitarugarwa bashizwe ukwabo mu ntumbero yo guhagarika ikwirakwira ryawo.
Hagati aho, abenshi muri bo babwiye BBC ko babayeho mu gahinda katagira izina kubera ingingo leta iherutse gufata yo kwongereza ikiringo co kuguma muri ico kigo.
Bagiriza leta ko ari nk'uko yabashize mu gasho, aho n'ibibabeshaho bitanakwiye.
Simon Mugambi asanzwe ari mu kigo kiri ku bitaro vy'ishure kaminuza ry'ubuganga Kenyatta University yabwiye abanyamakuru ati:
"Kuva ubu ntidukeneye gusubira muri ico kigo. Ubwa mbere kubera tutagishoboye kuriha, ubwa kabiri kubera ko bitumvikana igituma tubandanya tuba muri kino kigo".
"Ingorane ni uko babandanya batwugaranye kandi ku ncuro zibiri zose ibipimo vyerekana ko ata mugera twanduye. Leta ibandanya ivuga ko ari twebwe dutegerezwa kwirihira mu gihe ata buryo dusigaranye".
Uwuvugira abo bantu yamenyekanye kw'izina rya Tanui, yongerako ati:
"Twarakurikije neza ingingo ya leta yo kuguma  kwugaranywe mu kiringo c'iminsi 14, uno munsi tugeze ku munsi wa 23 tuba muri kino kigo.
"Tumaze gupimwa incuro zibiri bikaboneka ko tutanduye, twategerezwa kurekurwa ubwo nyene tukaja mu miryango yacu. Ntidutahura ikindi leta idushakako n'igituma dutegekwa kuguma twugaraniwe hano".
Umushikiranganji w'amagara y'abantu, Dr. Evanson Kimuri, arahakana ibiregwa leta ko ibafata nabi muri ico kigo.
Ati: "Bariko barifata nabi cane mbere n'imbere y'abakozi; mbere na bamwe mu bakozi banje hariho abambwiye ko bakubaguwe…
"Ico nomenyesha ni uko aba bakozi bakorera harya bemeye gutanga ubuzima bwabo, ico mwokora nk'Abakenya ni uko mwobashigikira gusa, mukabubahiriza mu kazi kabo".
Abapolisi bo mu gisata kijejwe kurwanya imigumuko barungitswe kuri ico kigo nibo bashoboye kwinjiza abo bantu.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52500394' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52500394' term='COVID'>
Tanzania - Umunsi w'umurimo:"Batanzania, dukomeze akazi Imana izaturinda” – Magufuli
Mu butumwa bw'umunsi w'umurimo Perezida John Pombe Magufli yahaye abaturage ba Tanzania, yabasabye gukomeza gukora imirimo yabo nubwo hari icyorezo, yongeraho ko "Imana izabarinda".
Mu butumwa bw'umunsi w'umurimo Perezida John Pombe Magufli yahaye abaturage ba Tanzania, yabasabye gukomeza gukora imirimo yabo nubwo hari icyorezo, yongeraho ko "Imana izabarinda".
Bwana Magufuli yabwiye abaturage ko coronavirus idakwiye kubuza abakozi gukorera igihugu cyabo.
Mu itangazo ryasohowe n'ibiro bye, yavuze ko bagomba gusa gukurikiza amabwiriza y'abashinzwe ubuzima mu kwirinda iki cyorezo.
Yavuze ko kubera iyi virus nta birori biri bubeho byo kwizihiza umunsi w'umurimo nk'uko bisanzwe.
Yagize ati: "Ndabasaba ko muri iki gihe isi iri guca mu  bihe bikomeye byo guhangana na corona, twebwe dukomeza gukora akazi, iyi ndwara ntitubere impamvu yo gusubira inyuma. Njyewe nizera ko Imana izayiturenza".
Muri Tanzania hamaze kuboneka abantu 480 banduye coronavirus, nicyo gihugu ubu gifite umubare munini w'abamaze kumenyekana bayanduye muri aka karere.
Nubwo OMS/WHO itanga inama zibuza abantu guhura ari benshi, Perezida Magufuli yashishikarije abantu gukomeza gusengera hamwe mu nsengero kuko 'coronavirus idashobora gutura mu mubiri urimo Kristu'.
Abo ku ruhande rutavuga rumwe na leta muri Tanzania bavuga ko leta itashyize imbaraga zihagije mu kurinda abaturage Covid-19.
Ishyaka ritavuga rumwe n'ubutegetsi CHADEMA uyu munsi ryasabye abadepite barihagarariye mu nteko guhagarika kwitabira imirimo yayo no kutagera ku nyubako z'inteko muri Dodoma na Dar es Salaam, mu byumweru bibiri.
Leta ya Tanzania yakomeje kunengwa na bamwe mu baturage, abanyapolitiki n'uhagarariye OMS muri Tanzania ko itafashe ingamba zikwiye mu kwirinda ikwirakwira ryayo.
</doc>
