<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-51993140' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-51993140' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Ibikorwa byose bisa n'ibihagaritswe mu Rwanda kubera indwara ya Covid-19
Leta y'u Rwanda yatangaje ingamba nshya zikomeye ivuga ko zigamije gukumira ikwirakwira rya Covid-19 mu gihugu.
Leta y'u Rwanda yatangaje ingamba nshya zikomeye ivuga ko zigamije gukumira ikwirakwira rya Covid-19 mu gihugu.
Itangazo rya Édouard Ngirente, Minisitiri w'intebe w'u Rwanda, rivuga ko harebwe uko iyi ndwara ihagaze ku isi n'uko mu bindi bihugu byagenze, ari ngombwa ko hafatwa ingamba ziruseho mu kwirindwa ko iyi ndwara ikomeza gukwirakwira.
Ibyo byamezo bishya byafashwe bigomba gukurikizwa mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri kuva muri ijoro ry'ejo ku wa gatandatu, ibyo birimo ko:
Ibi byemezo byatangiye gukurikizwa saa tanu n'iminota 59 zo mu ijoro ry'ejo ku wa gatandatu, nkuko iri tangazo ribivuga.
U Rwanda nicyo gihugu cya mbere cyo muri Afurika yo munsi y'ubutayu bwa Sahara gifashe ibyemezo nk'ibi.
Urwego rw'ubuhinzi rurimo abantu bagera kuri 37%, abagera kuri 17% bari mu by'inganda, 45% bari mu rwego rwa serivisi naho 3% ni abakozi ba leta nk'uko bivuvugwa na raporo ya leta ya 2019 ku mirimo mu Rwanda.
Byitezwe ko ibi byumweru bibiri bishobora kugora cyane imibereho y'abaturage babarirwa muri za miliyoni bari mu nzego z'imirimo zibabeshaho ari uko bavuye mu rugo buri munsi.
Gusa abahanga bavuga ko ibyemezo nk'ibi ari ingenzi mu gukumira ikwirakwira ry'iyi ndwara, ndetse byafashwe mu bihugu bimwe mu Burayi, leta zimwe muri Amerika n'ibihugu bimwe muri Afurika ya ruguru.
Ku rubuga rwa Facebook rwa BBC Gahuzamiryango, hatanzwe ibitekerezo bitandukanye kuri izo ngamba nshya, hari abazishima n'abazinenga.
Minisiteri y'ubuzima mu Rwanda ivuga ko kugeza ubu abantu 17 ari bo bamaze gusangamo iyi ndwara mu Rwanda, benshi muri bo bahageze bavuye mu mahanga.
Iyi minisiteri kandi yatangaje ko mu bipimo byafashwe ejo ku wa gatandatu nta murwayi ufite indwara ya Covid-19 wagaragaye, abayirwaye bakomeje kuba 17.
Mu bice bimwe byo mu mujyi wa Kigali aho BBC Gahuzamiryango yageze kuri iki cyumweru, bigaragara ko izo ngamba nshya za leta y'u Rwanda zatangiye gushyirwa mu bikorwa.
