<doc docid='bbc_52089030' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/52089030' term='COVID'>
Rwanda: Abaturage babujijwe gukoresha chloroquine aho itagenewe
Ikigo gishinzwe kugenzura ibiribwa n'imiti mu Rwanda (FDA) kibwira abaturage ko imiti yo mu bwoko bwa chroloquine atari imiti ivura coronavirus, ko kuyikoresha mu buryo itagenewe bibujijwe.
Ikigo gishinzwe kugenzura ibiribwa n'imiti mu Rwanda (FDA) kibwira abaturage ko imiti yo mu bwoko bwa chroloquine atari imiti ivura coronavirus, ko kuyikoresha mu buryo itagenewe bibujijwe.
Imiti ivugwa n'iki kigo FDA ni; chloroquine, hydroxychloroquine na azithromycin.
Mu bihugu bitandukanye, hari aho bagiye bemeza ko uyu muti waba uvura iyi virus.
Ku mbuga nkoranyambaga hari amakuru yakwiriye y'abavuga ko umuti wa chloroquine iyo uvanzwe na azithromycin bishobora kwica iyi virus ya covid-19.
Gusa kugeza ubu, ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye rishinzwe ubuzima ku isi, OMS, ntiriremeza ko iyi miti ivura cyangwa irinda iyi ndwara.
Ikigo FDA cyo mu Rwanda mu itangazo cyasohoye kivuga ko "iyi miti itaremezwa n'inzego zibishinzwe ko ivura cyangwa irinda coronavirus (Covid-19).
Iki kigo kivuga ko imwe muri iyo miti isanzwe ikoreshwa mu kuvura indwara mu Rwanda, ariko ko kuyikoresha mu buryo butagenwe bibujijwe.
Kivuga kandi ko iyi miti itangwa gusa iyo herekanywe urupapuro rwa muganga wayandikiye umurwayi.
Mu gihe gito gishize, Perezida Donald Trump wa Amerika yumvikanye avuga ko chloroquine 'ikiza iyi virus', gusa aya makuru ntabwo yemejwe n'ikigo gishinzwe imiti muri Amerika.
Umuhanga mu by'imiti wikorera mu Rwanda, yabwiye BBC ko umuti wa Chloroquine wakoreshwaga mu myaka ishize mu kuvura malaria ubu utakiboneka ku isoko mu Rwanda kubera imiti igezweho iyivura.
Avuga ko umuti wa hydroxychloroquine ugurishwa mu Rwanda, ufatwa n'abantu bagiye ahantu bakeka ko hari malaria nk'uburyo bwo kwikingira.
Naho umuti wa Azithromycin - nawo usanzwe ku isoko ry'u Rwanda - ni umuti wo mu bwoko bwa 'antibiotics' nk'uko uyu muhanga mu by'imiti abivuga.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52270617' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52270617' term='COVID'>
Covid-19: Andi makuru; B.Johnson yayikize, Nicaragua, Ububiligi, Burundi, kwambara ‘mask’...
Minisitiri w'intebe w'Ubwongereza bamupimye basanga nta Covid-19 ikiri mu mubiri we, ejo yahise avanwa mu bitaro nk'uko umuvugizi wa guverinoma abivuga.
Minisitiri w'intebe w'Ubwongereza bamupimye basanga nta Covid-19 ikiri mu mubiri we, ejo yahise avanwa mu bitaro nk'uko umuvugizi wa guverinoma abivuga.
Uyu mugabo ubu yagiye 'gutora mitende' ari iwe mu rugo,  akaba atarasubira mu mirimo ye y'ubutegetsi.
Hashize iminsi imibare y'abandura n'impfu izamuka cyane, ariko ubu iyo mibare iri kumanuka bigatanga ikizere ko ingamba zo kubuza abantu kuva mu ngo zabo ziri gutanga umusaruro.
Uretse Amerika, Ubutaliyani nibwo bufite imibare minini, hafi 20,000 barapfuye gusa imibare iheruka yerekana ko ubwandu buri kugabanuka.
Muri Espagne abo yishe ubu bagera ku 17,500 - ni iya gatatu mu bihugu. Abamaze kwandura barasatira 170,000 ariko naho imibare y'abandura iri kugabanuka.
Uyu munsi kuwa mbere, imibare y'abashinzwe ubuzima ivuga ko hamaze gupfa abantu 303, bose hamwe ubu bamaze kugera ku 3,903, mu gihe umuntu wa mbere yishwe n'iyi virus tariki 11 z'ukwezi gushize.
Iyo mibare irimo n'abaguye mu nzu zifasha abageze muzabukuru bikekwa ko bafite coronavirus, ariko bitabaye ngombwa ko bapimwa.
Nubwo imibare ya hano iboneka nkaho ari micye ugereranyije n'ibindi bihugu mu Burayi, Ububiligi bufite abaturage miliyoni 11,5 mu gihe Ubudage bufite abaturage miliyoni 83 ariko hamaze gupfa abantu bagera ku 3,000.
Bivuze ko ugereranyije n'umubare w'abatuye ibihugu, Ububiligi buri hafi y'Ubutaliyani na Espagne mu kwibasirwa n'iki cyorezo. Abantu 30,000 bamaze kubonwaho iyi virus mu Bubiligi.
Ejo ku cyumweru habonetse amafoto y'abantu benshi bari muri 'festival', ndetse n'abari kuri stade kureba imikino ya shampiyona.
Muri iki gihugu hamaze kuboneka abantu icyenda(9) banduye Covid-19 ndetse umwe yaramuhitanye.
Igitandukanyije iki gihugu n'ibindi mu karere kirimo ni uburyo ubutegetsi buri gufata iki cyorezo.
Mu gihe mu bihugu bituranye hafashwe ingamba zo kubuza abantu guhura no gufunga imipaka, visi perezida w'iki gihugu Rosario Murillo yabwiye abaturage "gutuza bagakomeza ibyabo uko bisanzwe".
Rosario Murillo niwe uyoboye ishyaka riri ku butegetsi akaba na visi perezida.
Yungirije umugabo we Daniel Ortega w'imyaka 74, uheruka kuboneka tariki 12 z'ukwezi gushize, ntabwo bizwi neza niba ubuzima bwe bumeze neza.
Ikigo Pan-American Health Organization cyatangaje ko gitewe impungenge n'uburyo Nicaragua yifashe imbere y'iki cyorezo.
Impungenge nk'izi kandi zatanzwe n'imiryango itandukanye ku Burundi aho imbere mu gihugu naho ubuzima busanzwe bukomeje.
Ejo ku cyumweru habonetse amafoto y'abantu bakoraniye mu nsengero ari benshi bizihiza umunsi wa Pasika, muri iki gihugu hamaze kuboneka abantu batanu banduye iki cyorezo.
David Nabarro umuvugizi w'itsinda rya OMS/WHO ryashinzwe kurwanya Covid-19 avuga ko kwambara udukoresho turinda amazuru n'umunwa bishobora kuzaba ibya buri gihe.
Yabwiye BBC ko abantu bagomba gutangira kumenyera ubuzima bushya bwo kubana n'iyi virus bayirinda.
Ati: "Iyi virus ntaho izajya. Ntabwo tuzi niba abanduye iyi virus umubiri wabo utongera kuyandura, kandi ntituzi igihe urukingo rwayo ruzabonekera.
"Uburyo bwose bwo kurinda mu maso nzi neza ko bugiye kuba ihame. Ntekereza ko bizaba kubera ibyo nita guhora twiteguye Covid-19."
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-51766498' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-51766498' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Ibiro bya perezida byemeye ko Amerika idafite ibikoresho bihagije byo kuyipima
Ibiro bya perezida wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, White House, byemeye ko iki gihugu kidafite ibikoresho bihagije byo gupima coronavirus, mu gihe umubare w'abayanduye wiyongereye muri iki gihugu.
Ibiro bya perezida wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, White House, byemeye ko iki gihugu kidafite ibikoresho bihagije byo gupima coronavirus, mu gihe umubare w'abayanduye wiyongereye muri iki gihugu.
Visi Perezida Mike Pence yavuze ko ubutegetsi bw'Amerika butazashobora kugera ku ntego yabwo yo gutanga ibikoresho miliyoni imwe muri iki cyumweru byo gupima coronavirus.
Hagati aho, inteko ishingamategeko y'Amerika yatoye mu buryo bwihuse bidasanzwe yemera inkunga itubutse y'ingoboka yo kurwanya coronavirus.
Ku isi hose, abategetsi bemeje ko abantu barenga 92,000 bamaze kwandura iyo virusi.
Umubare munini w'abo bayanduye ku isi - ni ukuvuga abantu 80,552 - ni abo mu Bushinwa, aho iyo virusi yatangiriye. Kugeza ubu, abantu 3,042 imaze kubica muri icyo gihugu.
Ku munsi w'ejo ku wa kane, umubare w'abamaze kwicwa na coronavirus muri Amerika warazamutse ugera ku bantu 12, bose ukuyemo umwe bakaba ari abo muri leta ya Washington.
Ubu muri Amerika hari abantu barenga 200 banduye Covid-19 - indwara y'ubuhumekero iterwa n'iyo virusi - muri leta 20 mu zigize icyo gihugu.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52549187' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52549187' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: WHO irabuza abantu gukoresha imiti itarapimwe
Ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS/WHO) ryaburiye abantu kudakoresha imiti itarigeze igeragezwa ivugwa ko ivura coronavirus.
Ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS/WHO) ryaburiye abantu kudakoresha imiti itarigeze igeragezwa ivugwa ko ivura coronavirus.
OMS ivuga ko Abanyafurika bakwiye kubona imiti yabanje guca mu mageragezwa nyayo kabone niyo yaba ari imiti gakondo.
Iri tangazo rya OMS rije nyuma yaho perezida wa Madagascar atangaje umuti gakondo avuga ko uvura Covid-19, indwara yo mu buhumekero iterwa n'ubu bwoko bushya bwa coronavirus.
Uvuga kuri uwo muti wa Madagascar, umuryango w'ubumwe bw'Afurika (UA/AU) wavuze ko ushaka kubona amakuru ashingiye kuri siyansi ajyanye "nuko ntacyo wakwangiza ku buzima ndetse no ku bushobozi bwawo".
Uwo muti wahawe izina rya Covid-Organics, wageragerejwe ku bantu batageze kuri 20 mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bitatu, nkuko umwe mu bajyanama ba perezida wa Madagascar yabibwiye BBC.
Uko wageragejwe binyuranye n'amabwiriza ya OMS ajyanye n'igeragezwa ry'imiti.
Ayo mabwiriza ya OMS ashobora kumara igihe kirekire aho igishobora kuvamo umuti gipimwa mu byiciro bine, kigeragerezwa ku barwayi bacye nyuma kikageragerezwa ku bantu benshi ku rwego rw'igihugu.
Nubwo hari ibyo bisabwa, ibihugu bimwe byo muri Afurika, birimo nka Guinea-Bissau, Equatorial Guinea, Liberia na Tanzania, byamaze gutumiza uwo muti wa Covid-Organics wo muri Madagascar.
Uva mu kimera kitwa 'artemisia' - cyo mu bwoko by'inyabarasanya, mu Kinyarwanda - kivamo ibikoreshwa mu muti uvura malaria. Icyo kimera gikomatanywa n'ibindi bimera byo muri Madagascar.
Mu cyumweru gishize, Perezida Andry Rajoelina wa Madagascar yavugiye mu nama yakozwe mu buryo bw'iyakure bwo kuri internet abwira abategetsi bo muri Afurika ibijyanye n'uwo muti.
Nyuma y'iyo nama, AU yasabye ko yakwerekwa andi makuru ajyanye na Covid-Organics, akagenzurwa n'ikigo nyafurika cyo kurwanya no kwirinda indwara (CDC).
Mu itangazo ryayo, OMS yashimye uko guhanga udushya dushingiye ku miti gakondo n'ibimera, ariko ivuga ko utwo dushya "dukwiye kugeragezwa ngo harebwe umumaro watwo ndetse niba nta ngaruka twakira ku buzima".
Iryo tangazo ryongeyeho riti:
"Abanyafurika bakwiriye gukoresha imiti yageragejwe ku bipimo bimwe nkuko bigenda ahandi hose ku isi".
Ejo ku wa mbere, hemewe inkunga irenga miliyari 8 z'amadolari y'Amerika agenewe gufasha mu gukora urukingo rwa coronavirus.
Anagenewe kandi gukora ubushakashatsi mu buvuzi n'umuti by'iyi ndwara ya Covid-19.
Imishinga y'ubushakashatsi ibarirwa muri za mirongo, mu bice bitandukanye by'isi, kuri ubu iri kugerageza kubona urukingo rwayo.
Nyinshi mu mpuguke zivuga ko bishobora gufata kugeza hagati mu mwaka utaha wa 2021 - ni ukuvuga igihe kiri hagati y'amezi 12 na 18 uhereye igihe iyi virusi yagaragaye bwa mbere - ngo urukingo ruboneke rutangire gukoreshwa.
Ibihugu byinshi byo muri Afurika byakoranye ibakwe mu kugerageza kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'ubwandu bwa coronavirus.
Izo ngamba byafashe zirimo nka gahunda ya 'guma mu rugo' ndetse n'imikwabu yo kutarenza igihe runaka abantu bakiri hanze.
Ariko izo ngamba ubu zatangiye kudohorwa mu bice bimwe na bimwe, mu gihe za leta zigerageza gushyira ku munzani inyungu zo mu rwego rw'ubuzima no ku rwego rw'ubukungu.
Kudohora ingamba za gahunda ya 'guma mu rugo' byongereye gushaka ko mu buryo bwihutirwa haboneka imiti ya Covid-19.
Kugeza ubu muri Madagascar hamaze kwemezwa abarwayi 151 ba Covid-19 ndetse nta muntu irica muri icyo gihugu, nkuko ikigo CDC cyo kurwanya no gukumira indwara muri Afurika kibivuga.
Perezida wa Madagascar yari yategetse ko abatuye imijyi itatu mikuru yaho baguma mu rugo, ariko ubu izo ngamba zaradohowe, nkuko ibiro ntaramakuru AFP bibitangaza.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52549811' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52549811' term='COVID'>
Abanyarwanda barahitishwamo kubahiriza ingamba cyangwa gusubira muri 'lockdown'
Muri ibi bihe bidasanzwe byo kwirinda ikwirakwira rya coronavirus, umunyamabanga wa leta muri minisiteri y'ubuzima ushinzwe ubuvuzi bw'ibanze avuga ko Abanyarwanda bafite guhitamo kubahiriza amabwiriza ariho cyangwa gusubira muri "lockdown".
Jean Claude Mwambutsa/BBC Gahuzamiryango i Kigali
Muri ibi bihe bidasanzwe byo kwirinda ikwirakwira rya coronavirus, umunyamabanga wa leta muri minisiteri y'ubuzima ushinzwe ubuvuzi bw'ibanze avuga ko Abanyarwanda bafite guhitamo kubahiriza amabwiriza ariho cyangwa gusubira muri "lockdown".
Ejo kuwa mbere ku munsi wa mbere wo gufungura ibikorwa bimwe na bimwe nyuma y'iminsi 45 ibikorwa hafi ya byose mu gihugu buhagaritswe, hamwe na hamwe hagaragaye kutubahiriza amabwiriza amwe yatanzwe.
Kwambara udupfukamunwa, guhana intera hagati y'umuntu n'undi, kutinjira no kudasohoka mu mbago nshya zabaye zishyizweho z'umujyi wa Kigali no kuba abantu bose bari mu ngo zabo saa mbiri z'ijoro ni zimwe mu ngamba nshya zafashwe.
Hagaragaye abantu bafunzwe ndetse bamaranwa igihe kinini na polisi kuko barengeje saa mbiri z'ijoro bataagera mu ngo zabo.
Habonetse kandi abantu bacye batambaye udupfukamunwa n'abatwambara nabi.
Amashusho yakwirakwiye ku mbuga nkoranyambaga yerekanye imirongo miremire y'abagenzi bategereje imodoka zitaza kandi amasaha y'umukwabu yari  yageze .
Abaturage bavuga ko imodoka zitwara abagenzi zabaye nke bigatuma benshi batinda ku mirongo bategereje imodoka zibatahana bityo bakarenza amasaha yavuzwe yo kugera mu ngo zabo.
Mu kiganiro kuri televiziyo y'u Rwanda kuri izi ngamba nshya, Pudence Rubingisa uyobora Umujyi wa Kigali yavuze ko basaba abatwara abantu kongera imodoka kugira ngo ibyo ntibyongere kubaho.
Hari abatekereza ko udupfukamunwa twaba ari ducye kuko hari bacye bataratangira kutwambara,  Minisiteri y'ubuzima ivuga ko hari abatubahiriza no kutwambara neza.
Dr Tharcisse Mpunga umunyamabanga wa leta muri minisiteri y'ubuzima ushinzwe ubuvuzi bw'ibanze avuga ko kugeza ejo hari hamaze gukorwa udupfukamunwa turenga miliyoni eshatu bityo tutaba dushize.
Muri icyo kiganiro kuri televiziyo yagize ati: "Ahubwo ikibazo wenda ni imico y'abantu, burya guhinduka ako kanya biragorana hari abakitwambara munsi y'akananwa n'ugafite ntiyumve impamvu yo kukambara.
"Abanyarwanda bafite amahitamo abiri; gukurikiza izi ngamba tukambara agapfukamunwa, gukaraba no guhana intera hagati yawe n'undi cyangwa se guhitamo gusubira muri lockdown".
Yongeraho ati: "Kandi ndibaza ko nta muntu ushimishwa no kuguma aryamye mu rugo kuko ntawe byari bimereye neza".
Nyuma yo gutakamba, abatuye inkengero z'umujyi wa Kigali ariko bafite impamvu ituma binjira muri Kigali bemerewe kuhinjira.
Gusa ibi byatangiye gutera impungenge nk'uko bivugwa n'umuyobozi w'Umujyi  wa Kigali, yemeza ko hari abari kuva mu zindi ntara bakinjira muri Kigali baciye muri utwo duce tuyegereye.
Biracyagoye kumenya ukwiriye kwemererwa kwinjira muri Kigali n'utabyemerewe, gusa Bwana Rubingisa avuga ko uturere twegereye Kigali twasabwe kwerekana abantu bagomba kwemererwa  kwinjira i Kigali
Mu Rwanda, ministeri y'ubuzima ivuga ko mu bipimo 35,096 bimaze gufatwa kuva ku ntangiriro hamaze kuboneka abantu 261 banduye Covid-19 , naho 128 muri bo bayikize.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_51887092' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/51887092' term='COVID'>
U Rwanda rwemeje umuntu wa mbere wanduye coronavirus
Itangazo rya minisiteri y'ubuzima rivuga ko uwo murwayi wanduye icyorezo cya coronavirus ari umuturage w'Ubuhinde wageze mu Rwanda ku itariki ya 8 y'uku kwezi kwa gatatu.
Itangazo rya minisiteri y'ubuzima rivuga ko uwo murwayi wanduye icyorezo cya coronavirus ari umuturage w'Ubuhinde wageze mu Rwanda ku itariki ya 8 y'uku kwezi kwa gatatu.
Iryo tangazo rivuga ko uwo mugabo yari avuye mu mujyi wa Mumbai, yamara gusuzumwa bakayimusangamo nubwo ngo yari yageze mu Rwanda nta bimenyetso agaragaza.
Yijyanye ku kigo nderabuzima ku itariki ya 13 y'uku kwezi, nkuko bivugwa n'iryo tangazo, ari nabwo yasuzumwe bakamusangamo indwara ya Covid-19 yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero iterwa n'ubu bwoko bushya bwa corovarirus.
Minisiteri y'ubuzima ivuga ko ubu "avurwa, ameze neza, kandi yatandukanyijwe n'abandi barwayi".
Yongeyeho ko hamaze gushakishwa "abo yaba yarahuye nabo kugira ngo niba hari uwanduye avurwe, kandi indwara ntikwirakwizwe".
Iryo tangazo risoza rivuga ko "Abanyarwanda bose bagomba gukomeza gukurikiza amabwiriza y'isuku atangwa n'ubuyobozi bw'urwego rw'ubuzima, cyane cyane gukaraba intoki igihe cyose".
Rinabasaba kandi kwirinda kujya ahantu hahurira abantu benshi no kumenyesha inzego zibishinzwe mu gihe hari ugaragaje ibimenyetso, hakoreshejwe umurongo wa telefone utishyurwa wa 114.
Mu kiganiro na Radio Rwanda, Dr Ngamije Daniel, Minisitiri w'ubuzima w'u Rwanda, yavuze ko igihugu cyiteguye mu nzego zitandukanye.
Ati: "Igihugu kiriteguye...mu bushobozi buhari bujyanye n'abakozi bahuguwe..."
Dr Ngamije yavuze kandi ko mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri biri imbere guhera kuri uyu wa gatandatu, hahagaritswe guterana "bitari ngombwa" kw'abantu benshi cyangwa ahandi hahuriwe n'abantu benshi mu buryo bw'ubucucike.
Mu ruhererekane rw'ubutumwa bwo kuri Twitter, Perezida Paul Kagame yavuze ko "Nkuko bisanzwe, tuzatsinda muri ibi bihe bikomeye binyuze mu bufatanye no gukorera hamwe".
Yasabye kuzirikana ku bo "imaze kuvutsa ubuzima [ku isi], imiryango yabo n'inshuti zabo".
Bwana Kagame yanifurije "abayirwaye bose gukira vuba", anashimira Dr Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, umukuru w'ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS/WHO) n'iryo shami ubwaryo "bakomeje kutugenda imbere muri ibi bihe".
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52369740' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52369740' term='COVID'>
Perezida wa Madagascar yerekanye ikinyobwa avuga ko ari “umuti” wa coronavirus
Perezida Andry Rajoelina wa Madagascar yamuritse umuti ukozwe mu byatsi byo kuri icyo kirwa we yemeza ko urinda kandi ukavura ubu bwoko bushya bwa coronavirus nk'uko bivugwa na AFP.
Perezida Andry Rajoelina wa Madagascar yamuritse umuti ukozwe mu byatsi byo kuri icyo kirwa we yemeza ko urinda kandi ukavura ubu bwoko bushya bwa coronavirus nk'uko bivugwa na AFP.
Inzego zishinzwe ubuzima ku isi no muri Afurika ntacyo ziratanga kuri uyu muti watangajwe na Bwana Rajoelina.
Ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima, OMS,  kugeza ubu nta muti riratangaza wakorewe ubushakashatsi uvura Covid-19.
Ku kigo Malagasy Institute of Applied Research (IMRA) cyakoze uwo muti unyobwa, imbere y'abaminisitiri, abadipolomate n'abanayamakuru Rajoelina yagize ati: "Twakoze isuzuma - abantu babiri ubu bakijijwe n'uyu muti.
"Iki ni icyayi cy'ibyatsi kivura mu minsi irindwi".
Mu kuwushimangira yagize ati: "Ninjye wa mbere uri buwunywe uyu munsi imbere yanyu, mubone ko ukiza kandi utica".
Uyu muti wiswe  Covid-Organics, ukozwe mu byatsi byitwa Artemisia - umuti byemejwe ko bikoreshwa mu kuvura Malaria - hamwe n'ibintu byatsi gakondo nk'uko ikigo IMRA kibivuga.
Ubuziranenge bwawo no kuba uvura Covid-19 koko ntabwo biragenzurwa ku rwego mpuzamahanga, nta mibare kandi itangwa n'ubushakashatsi bw'uko wageragejwe.
Abahanga muri siyansi bakomeje kuburira abantu ingaruka mbi bashobora guterwa no gukoresha imiti inyobwa itarapimwe ikozwe mu byatsi .
Bwana Rajoelina ibyo abishyira ku ruhande, avuga ko uwo muti uzahabwa abana b'abanyeshuri mu gihugu kuko ari "inshingano ye kurengera abaturage ba Madagascar".
Kugeza ubu kuri iki kirwa hamaze kuboneka abantu 121 banduye coronavirus, ntawe irahitana muri iki gihugu.
Ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima, OMS, ryakomeje kuburira abantu kwirinda abantu bemeza ko babonye umuti wa Covid-19, ntabwo ryari mu gikorwa cyo kwerekana uwo muti nk'uko AFP ibivuga.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52269542' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52269542' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Iyo kuguma mu rugo bihindutse kuguma mu kaga 'ku bagore' Iburayi
Amabendera yururukijwe agezwa hagati, hanatangazwa iminsi itatu y'icyunamo mu gace ka Almassora muri Espagne kubera urupfu rwa Carina.
Amabendera yururukijwe agezwa hagati, hanatangazwa iminsi itatu y'icyunamo mu gace ka Almassora muri Espagne kubera urupfu rwa Carina.
Iyo biba mu bihe bisanzwe, abahatuye bari guhurira mu kiriyo cy'uyu muturanyi wabo w'imyaka 35. Ariko ubu bagomba kuguma mu ngo zabo kubera coronavirus iri 'kuvuza ubuhuha'.
Bavugije inzogera nini ndetse humvikana indirimbo z'agahinda za Mozart, icyo abantu bakoze ni ukujya mu madirishya y'inzu zabo no ku mabaraza kureba hanze.
Ni nyuma yo kumenya inkuru y'urupfu rwa Carina wiciwe mu rugo imbere y'abana be. Umugabo we José yijyanye ku bashinzwe umutekano muri uyu mujyi avuga ibyo yakoze.
Guhagarika ubuzima busanzwe byongereye ibyago ku bagore ubu bagomba kugumana mu rugo n'abantu bari basanzwe babahohotera.
No guhamagara ubufasha ntibihabwa agaciro nka mbere, ubu hari ikindi kihutirwa.
Muri uyu mwaka, Carina ni umugore wa 17 wishwe n'umugabo babana cyangwa uwahoze ari umugabo we. Niwe wa mbere wari wishwe muri ibi bihe bidasanzwe muri Espagne.
Guhohoterwa mu nzu, hanze virus
Hagiye gushira ukwezi ubuzima busanzwe mu bihugu byinshi mu Burayi buhagaritswe, haracyari kare kubarura ingaruka zabyo ku ihohoterwa rishingiye ku gitsina riri gukorerwa mu ngo.
Gusa inzobere muri ibi zibona ko hari akaga gakomeye abagore bamwe barimo ko gutinya abagabo babahohotera ubu bagomba guhorana mu nzu, no gutinya virusi iri hanze y'inzu.
Kika Fumero umugore wo muri Espagne wo mu kigo Institute for Equality, ukurikirana iby'iri hohoterwa avuga ko guhera tariki 14 z'ukwezi kwa gatatu impungenge zari zitangiye.
Ati: "Kuva icyo gihe nari mbizi ko ibyiza biri gukorwa ngo bahagarike Covid-19 ari akaga ku bagore bamwe n'abana babo bahora bahohoterwa mu ngo zabo".
Yabwiye BBC ko yabonye kwiyongera cyane kw'ihohoterwa  kubagore mu bihe abantu basabwa kuguma mu ngo zabo mu gihe cyashize, mu gihe cy'imyuzure cyangwa ibiruhuko.
Kimwe na Espagne, Ubutaliyani nabwo iki cyago ku bagore kiri kuboneka.
Lorena Quaranta w'imyaka 27, yari hafi kubona impamyabumenyi nka muganga, apfa tariki 30 z'ukwezi gushize. Ariko ntiyishwe na Covid-19. Umukunzi we Antonio yabwiye polisi ko yamwishe.
Ubwo isanduku irimo umurambo we yari igaruwe aho akomoka mu mujyi wa Favara muri Sicily, abantu bagiye mu madirishya no ku mabaraza bamanika udutambaro tw'umweru mu gahinda.
Utegeka uyu mujyi yavuze ko bisobanuye "Ubusugi bw'umutima we, n'ibara ry'impuzankano yari inzozi ze kuzahora yambaye".
Ubufaransa bwari bwatangaje kugabanuka kw'ihohoterwa nk'iri kubera umurongo wa telephone polisi yashyizeho.
Ariko mu cyumweru kimwe polisi yatangaje ko ihohotera mu ngo ryongeye kuzamukaho kimwe cya gatatu mu gihugu.
Muri Espagne, serivisi z'abagore bahuye n'ihohoterwa rishingiye ku gitsina ubu ziri mu zikora cyane muri ibi bihe kandi guverinoma yazihaye ibya ngombwa bishoboka.
Institute for Equality yatangije ubukangurambaga yise "Mascarilla-19" (Mask-19), ivuga ko guhunga ihohoterwa ari impamvu yatuma umuntu yemererwa kuva mu rugo muri ibi bihe.
Inzu zigurisha imiti (farumasi) ni hamwe mu hantu abantu bemerewe gusohoka bakajya.
Kika Fumero wagize iki gitekerezo ati: "Igihe umugore akorewe ihohoterwa mu rugo, ashobora kujya kuri farumasi imwegereye agasaba Mask-19, mask izamukiriza ubuzima".
Farumasi ifata izina, aho uwo mugore aba na telephone ye ikabwira inzego z'ubutabazi bw'ibanze. Icyo gihe ashobora kujya mu rugo cyangwa gutegereza polisi cyangwa abandi bakozi babishinzwe.
Umugore w'imyaka 78 uherutse kwicwa n'umugabo we ahitwa Gran Canaria, ni uwa kabiri wari wiciwe mu rugo rwe muri iki gihe cya 'lockdown' muri Espagne.
Mask-19 ubu irakoreshwa hose muri Espagne, mu Bufaransa, Ubudage, Ubutaliyani, Norvège na Argentine.
Ibihe bidasanzwe akaga ku bagore
Virginia Gil, ufite ikigo Aspacia foundation i Madrid, avuga ko afite impungenge ko abagore bavuga ihohoterwa bakorewe muri ibi bihe ari 'nk'igitonyanga mu nyanja'.
Atekereza ko bahura n'imbogamizi nyinshi: gufatwa n'abo babahohotera, guterwa ubwoba no kwandura coronavirus iri hanze, kutamenya neza serivisi iri bubafashe muri ibi bihe...
Madamu Virginia avuga ko n'abakora ihohoterwa polisi idapfa kubafata kuko muri iki gihe gufungwa atari ikintu polisi yihutira gukora.
Mu Burusiya, Mariya yaheze mu cyeragati yibaza niba ava iwe cyangwa ahaguma, muri ibi bihe. Atuye muri 113Km uvuye i Moscow.
Mariya, siryo zina rye nyaryo, ntabwo umugabo we yari yarigeze amukubita mbere. Ariko tariki 26/03 umugabo we yagize umujinya ukomeye wamaze amaha 18.
Ati: "Yabanje kudutuka mu magambo. Nyuma atangira kumenagura ibintu byose abidutera njyewe n'abana. Yashwanyaguje ibintu byose kuva ku isahani kugera kuri frigo. Abana bagize ubwoba bwinshi".
Mariya yabwiye BBC ishami ry'Ikirusiya ko icyasembuye uwo mujinya w'umuranduranzuzi ari itangazo rya Perezida Vladimir Putin ry'uko akazi gahagaritswe icyumweru, bikamutera igihombo.
Ubwo uyu mugabo yasohotse agiye kugura inzora, Mariya yahise ahamagara polisi.
Bamubwira ko umugabo badashobora kumuvana muri iyo nzu kuko ari iye. Ko ari we ugomba gushaka aho ahungira n'abana.
Ubufasha busaba ahantu ho gucumbikirwa byihutirwa bwikubye kabiri kuva leta ya Denmark yasaba abantu bose kuguma mu ngo zabo.
Ibi byatumye leta isaba amashuri amwe gufungurira ibyumba byayo abagore baje gusaba ubuhungiro.
Mu Bubiligi, Jean-Louis Simoens ukora muri serivisi zo kwitaba abashaka ubufasha, avuga ko abahamagara kubera ihohoterwa rikorerwa mu ngo bikubye gatatu.
Ati: "Hari umugore wahamagaye ambwira ko afite iminota 15 gusa yo kumbwira, mu gihe umugabo we agiye hanze kugura isegereti"
Yari afite ubwoba bwinshi, twagomba kuvugana vuba vuba.Yari yamukubise bikomeye cyane, yari yangije isura ye ku buryo atashoboraga gufungura amaso neza".
Uyu mugore yamubwiye ko kuguma mu rugo byatumye umugabo we arushaho kugira ubukana.
Bwana Jean Louis yamufashije kumenya aho ari bwerekeze umugabo niyongera gusohoka gato. Gusa ntabwo azi niba yarabashije kubigeraho.
Impamvu kuguma mu rugo 'atari byiza'
Coronavirus mu buryo bumwe ni imbogamizi ituma benshi ubu nta bufasha babona nk'uko bivugwa na Marceline Naudi, ukuriye itsinda ry'impuguke mu kurwanya ihohoterwa mu Burayi.
Hamwe na hamwe, abagore bakorewe ihohoterwa birinda no kujya kwa muganga kwivuza kubera gutinya kuhandurira, ariko n'aho kujya kwivuriza ubu ni hacyeya.
Marceline ati: "Ibigo byakiraga abahohotewe mu ngo hamwe byarafunze kuko bitizeye uko byarwanya ikwirakwira rya coronavirus".
Anavuga ko kuba benshi ubu baratakaje akazi, abagore bamwe ubu bagomba kwisunga abagabo babahohotera kuko byabagora kubaho bonyine.
Mu gihe iki cyorezo kimaze kwica abantu ibihumbi n'ibihumbi mu Burayi, ubutumwa bwo gusaba abantu kuguma mu rugo ni ububabwira ko ari ugukiza ubuzima bwabo.
Gusa ntabwo ubu butumwa buha gutuza abagore bameze nk'abafungiwe mu rugo n'ababakorera ihohotera, gusa bagasanga nta kundi guhitamo bafite imbere y'iki cyorezo.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-51894822' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-51894822' term='COVID'>
Perezida Trump nta coronavirus bamusanzemo
Perezida Donald Trump wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika basanze nta coronavirus arwaye, nkuko byatangajwe n'umuganga wo mu biro bye bya White House.
Perezida Donald Trump wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika basanze nta coronavirus arwaye, nkuko byatangajwe n'umuganga wo mu biro bye bya White House.
Mu itangazo yasohoye ku munsi w'ejo ku wa gatandatu, Sean Conley yagize ati: "Kuri uyu mugoroba nabonye gihamya yuko ibizamini byo kwa muganga bigaragaza ko ntayo arwaye".
Bwana Trump yipimishije hashize iminsi akoresheje inama mu nzu y'uburuhukiro ye iri muri leta ya Florida ari kumwe n'intumwa zivuye muri Brazil, bamwe muri izo ntumwa bakaba barasanzwemo coronavirus.
Fabio Wajngarten, umwe mu bajyanama ba perezida wa Brazil, ni umwe mu bemejwe nyuma yaho ko barwaye indwara yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero ya Covid-19 iterwa n'ubu bwoko bushya bwa coronavirus.
Bwana Conley yagize ati: "Nyuma y'icyumweru asangiye ifunguro rya nimugoroba n'intumwa zo muri Brazil mu nyubako ya Mar-a-Lago, perezida nta kimenyetso kiramugaragaraho".
Bwana Trump w'imyaka 73 y'amavuko, ntabwo yigeze yishyira mu kato nyuma y'iyo nama, avuga ko nta bimenyetso bya coronavirus afite.
Ariko nyuma yo guhatwa ibibazo nyuma mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru mu biro bye bya White House, yemeye ko azipimisha.
Yapimwe ku wa gatanu, nkuko uwo muganga wo mu biro bye abivuga.
Iryo tangazo rya Bwana Conley ryongeyeho riti:
"Nakomeje kuvugana umunsi ku munsi na CDC [ikigo cy'Amerika cyo gukumira no guhashya indwara, Centers for Disease Control and Prevention] ndetse n'itsinda ryo mu biro bya White House ryo kurwanya coronavirus".
"Kandi dukomeje gusaba ko bakoresha uburyo bushoboka bwose mu kugabanya aho abantu bahurira nayo no kugabanya ubwandu".
Inama itangwa na leta y'Amerika ni uko abantu bagize aho bahurira n'umuntu wanduye coronavirus bakwiye kuguma mu rugo mu gihe cy'iminsi 14.
Muri Amerika habarurwa abantu 2,700 bamaze kuyandura naho abandi 54 imaze kubica.
Ku wa gatanu w'iki cyumweru, Perezida Trump yatangaje ko igihugu kiri mu bihe bidasanzwe kubera coronavirus ndetse ategeka ko leta isohora miliyari 50 z'amadolari yo guhangana n'ikwirakwira ryayo.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_52046125' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/52046125' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Ubucuruzi muri ‘betting’ bwahombye 99% muri aka karere kubera Covid-19
Urwego rw'imikino y'amahirwe (betting) mu karere k'Afurika y'uburasirazuba ubu ruri "mu kaga neza neza" kubera ihagarikwa ry'imikino ku isi bitewe na coronavirus.
Urwego rw'imikino y'amahirwe (betting) mu karere k'Afurika y'uburasirazuba ubu ruri "mu kaga neza neza" kubera ihagarikwa ry'imikino ku isi bitewe na coronavirus.
Ibyo ni ibitangazwa na kompanyi ya 'betting' yo muri Uganda.
Amasoko ya 'betting' yarahungabanye bikomeye bitewe n'ihagarikwa rya shampiyona zikomeye z'umupira w'amaguru mu bice bitandukanye ku isi.
Byatumye rero abantu babura ibyo bageragerezaho amahirwe.
Ariko muri Afurika y'uburasirazuba, iri soko ry'imikino y'amahirwe ryarashegeshwe kurushaho kuko abantu bacye ari bo bakorera 'betting' ku rubuga rwa Internet.
Ivan Kalanzi, ushinzwe ibyo kwamamaza urubuga rwa internet rwa 'betting' ruzwi nka GAL Sport Betting, yabwiye BBC ati:
"Mu bijyanye n'ubucuruzi, twahombye hafi 99% kubera ko benshi mu bakiliya bacu ntabwo bakorera 'betting' kuri Internet".
Yongeyeho ati: "Ntabwo dufite abakora 'betting' benshi cyane (kuri Internet) muri Kenya na Tanzania, aho turi cyane mu nzu za 'betting'".
Inzu nyinshi zikorerwamo 'betting' zo muri aka karere zafunze imiryango mu ntangiriro y'uku kwezi kwa gatatu kubera coronavirus ikomeje kwiyongera.
Kubera ibyo, uru rwego rwa 'betting' ubundi rwinjiza agera kuri miliyoni 20 z'amadolari ku mwaka muri Kenya, miliyoni 12 muri Uganda na miliyoni 10 muri Tanzania, rwarahonnye.
Bwana Kalanzi ati:
"Wenda nka 30% ni bo bakora 'betting' kuri Internet, benshi muri bo ni ab'amikoro aciriritse, akenshi bashishikazwa na shampiyona zikomeye nko mu Bufaransa n'Ubudage, ubu zahagaritswe".
"Rero ubu ni akaga neza neza".
Nyinshi muri za shampiyona mu mikino itandukanye zarahagaritswe mu kwezi gushize kubera icyorezo cya coronavirus gikomeje gukwirakwira ku isi.
Hagati aho, bamwe mu bakina imikino ya 'betting' babona iri hagarikwa rya za shampiyona nkaho atari igihombo kuri bo ahubwo ari umwanya wo kugira amafaranga bizigamira.
Meshack, ufite inzu icuruza serivisi za internet - cyber café - mu burengerazuba bwa Kenya, agira ati:
"Byaramfashije gacye kurushaho kuko amafaranga nari kuba naratakaje ndayagumana".
"Nkora 'betting' kuri Premier League, shampiyona ya Turukiya, Bundesliga, La Liga, shampiyona zose zikomeye harimo no muri Brazil na Chili, basketball na ice hockey".
Ariko nanone avuga ko amafaranga y'inyongera yabonaga buri munsi ari hagati y'amadolari y'Amerika 10 na 30 (hagati ya 9,000 na 28,000 y'u Rwanda), atakiyabona.
Ati: "Kuri twe urubyiruko - na benshi mu baturage ba Kenya - nta kazi gahari, rero ushyira icyizere cyawe [muri 'betting'] ko ushobora gutsindira akayabo ukiteza imbere mu buzima".
"Icyo cyizere ubu cyarayoyotse. Mu by'ukuri kuba nta mikino iri kuba, birabishye kuba nta 'betting' iri gukorwa".
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52200669' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52200669' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Iki kiza kiriko gikora ibara mu turere tw’abirabure b’Abanyamerika
Ibiharuro biteye agahinda bitangwa n'abajejwe amagara y'abantu mu gisagara ca Chicago vyerekana ibitigiri vy'umurengera vya coronavirus mu banyamerika b'abirabure.
Ibiharuro biteye agahinda bitangwa n'abajejwe amagara y'abantu mu gisagara ca Chicago vyerekana ibitigiri vy'umurengera vya coronavirus mu banyamerika b'abirabure.
Abirabure bo muri Chicago bangana hafi igice c'abamaze kwandura coronavirus muri ico gisagara, hamwe n'ibice birenga 70% vy'abamaze guhitanwa n'uwo mugera, n'aho bangana n'ibice 30% vy'abanyagihugu baba muri ico gisagara.
Eka n'ibindi bisagara bifise abirabure benshi, harimwo Detroit, Milwaukee, Nouvelles Orléans na New York, navyo nyene vyabaye ikiririmbiro rya coronavirus.
Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika ziharurwamwo hafi abantu 370.000 bamaze kwandura uwo mugera, hamwe n'abashika 11.OOO bamaze gupfa.
Gushika ku wa 05 z'uku kwa kane, abantu 1824 kuri 4680 bari bamaze kwandura Covid-19 muri Chicago, bari abirabure, nk'uko vyashikirijwe n'abarongoye ico gisagara ejo ku wa mbere.
Aho ni mu gihe abazungu bari bamaze kwandura ari 847, aba Hispanic (abanyamerika bava muri Amerika y'Epfo bavuga iki Espagnole) 478, hamwe na 126 bakomoka muri Aziya.
Gushika ku wa Mungu, Chicago yari imaze guharurwamwo abantu 98 bamaze gupfa, muri bo ibice 72% bakaba ari abirabure.
Ubwo busumbane buribonekeza mu ntara yose ya Illinois, aho abamaze guhitanwa na Covid-19 ibice 41% ari abirabure, mu gihe bagize ibice 14% vy'abanyagihugu bose baba muri iyo ntara.
Umukuru w'igisata kijejwe amagara y'abantu mu gisagara ca Chicago, Dr Allison Arwady, avuga ko abirabure bari basanzwe babayeho mu buzima bubayabaye ugereranije na bagenzi babo b'abazungu.
Umukuru w'ico gisagara, Lori Lightfoot, avuga ko coronavirus "ibandanya  yiha inkumbi mu birabure ba Chicago".
Avuga ko abagenzuzi b'igisagara bashobora kuzunguruka mu maduka kugira ngo barabe ko bose bakurikiza ingingo zo kutegerana.
Umupfasoni Lightfoot, avuga y'uko bibaye ngombwa bashobora gutera umukwabu bagahagarika uruja n'uruza mu turere abantu bakoraniramwo bihereza inzoga zikaze cane, nk'uko vyandikwa n'ikinyamakuru gikorera aho muri Chicago, Sun-Times.
N'aho coronavirus ivugwa ko "itarenganya", ibiharuro birerekana ko uburere bwose butabangamiwe ku rugero rumwe.
Muri Michigan, Abanyamerika b'abirabure bangana ibice 14% vy'abanyagihugu bose, ariko mu bantu bose bamaze kwandura abirabure bangana n'ibice 33%, nayo mu bamaze kuhasiga ubuzima abirabure bangana n'ibice 41%, nk'uko vyerekanwa n'igisata kijejwe amagara y'abantu muri iyo ntara ejo ku wa mbere.
Muri abo bamaze kwandura muri iyo ntara nyene, abazungu ni ibice 23% , hamwe na 28% vy'abamaze gupfa, nk'uko ivyo biharuro bivyerekana.
Mu gisagara ca Detroit muri iyo ntara ya Michigan, abirabure bangana n'ibice 80%, abashizwe ukwabo muri ico gisagara no mu micungararo yaco bakaba ari ibice 80%.
Ubwo busumbane kandi buribonekeza mu gisagara ca Milwaukee c'intara ya Wisconsin, kiri mu bisagara vyashizwe inyuma cane muri Amerika.
Mu bantu hafi 1000 banduye ku wa gatanu w'indwi iheze muri Amerika, hafi inusu y'abanduye mu gisagara ca Milwaukee bari abirabure, bakaba kandi bangana n'ibice 81% muri 27 bapfuye muri ico gisagara, n'aho abirabure baba muri co bangana n'ibice 26%, nk'uko vyerekanwa n'icigwa cakozwe n'ikigo ProPublica.
Mu ntara ya Louisiana, ibice hafi 40% vy'abamaze guhitanwa na coronavirus biri mu karere ka Nouvelle-Orléans gasanzwe gatuwemwo n'abirabure benshi gusumba abandi.
Muri Amerika, ico kiza kiriko kirunyura ubusumbasumbane bufatiye ku butunzi n'amoko, nk'uko Dr Cameron Webb, umunyamerika w'umwirabure ariko yiyamamariza ubukenguzamateka mu ntara ya Virginia yabibwiye BBC.
Ati: "Ni ukuri kiriko kiragaragaza ubusumbasumbane buri mu gihugu cacu".
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-52365033' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-52365033' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus - Uganda: habonetse Umurundi w’impunzi baa Nakivale wayanduye
Minisiteri y'ubuzima muri Uganda yatangaje ko habonetse abantu babiri bashya banduye coronavirus, umwe muri bo ni Umurundi w'imyaka 46 w'impunzi wageze muri Uganda avuye muri Tanzania.
Minisiteri y'ubuzima muri Uganda yatangaje ko habonetse abantu babiri bashya banduye coronavirus, umwe muri bo ni Umurundi w'imyaka 46 w'impunzi wageze muri Uganda avuye muri Tanzania.
Iyi minisiteri yatangaje ko tariki 12/04/2020 uyu yari yashyizwe mu kato avuye muri Tanzania ageze mu karere ka Rakai, akarere kari mu majyepfo ya Uganda gahana imbibi n'intara ya Kagera ya Tanzania.
Minisiteri y'ubuzima ya Uganda ivuga ko uyu asanzwe ari impamzu iba mu nkambi ya Nakivale iri mu karere ka Isingiro mu majyepfo ashyira uburengerazuba bwa Uganda.
Iyi minisiteri ivuga ko uyu yageze muri Uganda nta bimenyetso bya Covid-19 agaragaza agashyirwa mu kato. Ivuga ko ubu agiye kujyanwa mu bitaro bya Masaka.
Ntibizwi neza niba uyu muntu w'impunzi yarageze muri Uganda avuye mu nkambi y'impunzi muri Tanzania, ahari impunzi z'Abarundi zirenga ibihumbi 160.
Muri Uganda ho habarurwa  impunzi z'Abarundi 48,232 nk'uko imibare ya UNHCR yo mu kwezi gushize ibivuga.
Imiryango mpuzamahanga itandukanye yagiye itangaza impungenge ifite mu gihe iki cyorezo cyagera mu nkambi z'impunzi ziri mu bihugu bitandukanye muri Afurika.
Leta ya Uganda yafashe ingamba zo gusubiza iwabo abantu batari abaturage ba Uganda basanzemo iki cyorezo, hari abashoferi b'amakamyo babiri basubijwe iwabo muri Kenya na Tanzania.
Kugeza ubu, abantu 58 nibo bamaze kumenyekana ko banduye coronavirus muri Uganda, minisiteri y'ubuzima ivuga ko 38 muri bo bakize.
</doc>
