<doc docid='bbc_51324702' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/51324702' term='SARS'>
Umunyamabanga w'ubudandaji wa Amerika Wilbur Ross avuga ko coronavirus izotuma ubuzi bwiyongera
Umunyamabanga ajejwe ubudandaji wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, Wilbur Ross, avuga ko ikiza ca coronavirus mu Bushinwa gishobora gutuma ubutunzi bwa Amerika bwiyongera.
Umunyamabanga ajejwe ubudandaji wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, Wilbur Ross, avuga ko ikiza ca coronavirus mu Bushinwa gishobora gutuma ubutunzi bwa Amerika bwiyongera.
Mu kiganiro yagiranye na televiziyo imwe, Bwana Ross yavuze ati: "Ndibaza ko kizofasha mu kugarukana ubuzi bwinshi muri Amerika ya Ruguru".
Ayo majambo yiyamirijwe bikomeye n'abanegura ubutegetsi bwa Perezida Donald Trump.
Ikwirakwira ry'ico kiza ryatumye haba ubwoba ko ubutunzi bw'Ubushinwa bushobora kugira ibibazo.
Yishura ku kibazo yari abajijwe na televiziyo Fox Business nimba ico kiza gishobora kugira ingaruka mbi ku butunzi bwa Amerika, Bwana Ross yavuze ati: "Si nipfuza kuvuga ko ari intsinzi ntoya mfatiye ku ndwara nk'iyo ije guteza ibibazo, indwara mbi cane".
"Ariko ikiriho ni uko ivyo bituma amakompanyi aronka ikindi kintu afatirako mu bikorwa vyayo n'aho akorera... Rero ndibaza ko ivyo bizotuma ubuzi bugaruka muri Amerika ya uguru".
Mu nyuma niho ubunyamabanga bw'ubudandaji bwasubiramwo amajambo yiwe buti : "Nk'uko umunyamabanga Ross yabisiguye, igikorwa ca mbere ni ukurwanya uwo mugera no gufasha abawanduye".
Umuvugizi wabwo ati: "Ariko kandi ni ngombwa kwihweza neza ibijanye no gukorana n'igihugu kimenyereye kunyegeza ibibazo bihanze abanyagihugu baco n'isi yose".
Ayo majambo yiyamirijwe bikomeye n'umushingamateka w'umu Démocrate Don Beyer abona ko ari ugukina ku muvyimba abantu mu gushaka kwungukira ku kiza ruhonyanganda nk'ico.
Eka n'abahinga muvyo ubutunzi baneguye ayo majambo ya Bwana Ross.
Simon Baptist umuhinga muvyo ubutunzi wo mu gihugu ca Singapour yabwiye BBC ko yakubiswe n'inkuba yumvise amajambo ya Ross.
Avuga ko uwo mugera ushobora kugira ingaruka mbi kuri Amerika aho kuzana akarusho.
Ati: "Ikiriho ni uko Amerika izohahombera cane kuko n'aho bimeze uko bimaze, Amerika irashorera cane mu Bushinwa. Rero iyo ubutunzi bw'Ubushinwa bugize ibibazo bikomeye, bigira ingaruka mbi kuri Amerika".
Ishami ry'ishirahamwe ONU ryitaho amagara kw'isi OMS ryatangaje ko isi iri mu bihe bidasanzwe kubera uwo mugera  ubandanya ukwiragira hanze y'Ubushinwa.
Umaze guhitana abantu bashika 213 mu Bushinwa, mu gihe umaze gushika mu bindi bihugu 18.
Abahinga muvyo ubutunzi bavuga ko Coronavirus ishobora kugira ingaruka mbi cane ku butunzi bw'isi gusumba ikiza ca SARS co mu mwaka 2002-2003.
Ico kiza candukiye abantu barenga 8000, abarenga 700 nabo bahasiga ubuzima, bikaba vyasavye imiliyaridi zirenga 30 z'amadolari kugira kirwanywe.
Muri kino gihe, uwu mugera coronavirus watumye amakompanyi mpuzamakungu akomeye harimwo ay'ubuhinga bwa none, ayakora n'ayagurisha imiduga ahagarika vy'agateganyo ibikorwa vyayo mu Bushinwa.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-51238896' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-51238896' term='SARS'>
Ikiza c'ibicurane bita Coronavirus mu Bushinwa : Kiva hehe? Bacikingira gute?
Ubwoko bw'umugera watumye ikiza gihitana abantu mu Bushinwa burazwi neza - kandi buteye ubwoba abaganga.
Ubwoko bw'umugera watumye ikiza gihitana abantu mu Bushinwa burazwi neza - kandi buteye ubwoba abaganga.
Uri mu bwoko bw'ubwandu   bita coronaviruses butera  ubushuhe buvanze n'inkorora bugahava buvamwo umusonga kandi bugatuma umugwayi ahema nabi.
Ubwo bwandu bw'uyo mugera  wa coronavirus bwitwa SARS. Mu majambo yose babwita (severe acute respiratory syndrome)- bumaze kwica abantu  41 mu gihe abashika 1287 babaze kumenyekana ko bawanduye.
Ubundi bwandu bwa coronaviruses  burangwa nivyo bimenyesto nyene ariko bukaze ugusumba. Bwitwa  Mers (Middle East respiratory syndrome) bwabonetse ubwambere muri Arabiya Saoudite bukaba bumaze guhitana hafi ibice 35% vy'abantu babwanduye.
Kuber'iki ubu bwoko bw'uyu mugera  bukwiragira hose mu kanya gato ,  ni kuber'iki bishoshora gutera ubwoba?
Ni hehe uyo mugera wa coronaviruses utereye ubwoba ?
Ibintu vyakabuye ubwo bwandu bita Sars na Mers hamwe n'ikiza ca kino gihe vyibazwa ko bitavuye mu bantu ariko mu bikoko.
Mugihe ibikoko vyinshi bigendana  imigera myinshi iteye ubwoba, amahirwe n'uko  idakunze kuboneka ko isimbira ku bantu.
Akenshi hariho umurongo ntarengwa ku  bwoko  bw'ibinyabuzima,  bigatuma  uyo mugera utabifata, nk'uko bivugwa n'umwigisha w'ibinyabuzima Andrew Easton wo muri Kaminuza ya  Warwick.
Ariko iyo umubiri w'umuntu udafise ububasha bw'ukwikingira, canke hakaba ikindi gituma umugera uronka aho winjirira , umuntu arashobora kurwara yanduye kandi bidakunze kuboneka.
Igitera ubwoba kenshi,  ni igihe bihera ku mpinduka itari yitezwe
Usanga ifise uburyo bwo gukurira muri ico kibanza gishasha.
Ako gake cane  uyo mugera wa coronavirus winjira mu magara y'abantu , bishobora kugorana cane.
Ariko birakenewe kwibutsa ko ubwoko  bw'imigera bwose bwa coronovirus budateye ubwoba rwose- abantu benshi  bitega kubabara buke buke igihe cose - ariko  uyo mugera wanse imiti  bashobora kubabara cane.
Kubera iki umugera uvuye mu bindi binyabuzima uteye ubwoba?
''Igihe umugera wimukiye mu  kinyabuzima kindi  ntushobora kumenya ico ukora kugira uwurwanye, mu ntango bishobora kugorana'', nk'uko umwigisha Easton abivuga.
Ni kubera y'uko iyo umugera wa coronavirus uvuye ku bikoko ukaja mu bantu , umubiri wacu ushobora gutakaza inguvu,  kubera utaba wari umenyereye ikintu nk'ico gishasha cawujemwo.
Ingorane imeze uko iyo ibicurane bikwiragiye mu bwoko bw'ibinyabuzima bibiri bidasa.
''Mugihe hari ikwiragira ry'ibicurane, abantu bakura ku nyoni ziba mu mazi , amakenga n'uko igihe bishitse ku bantu , iyo ndwara igira ubukari bukomeye''umwigisha Easton niko avuga.
Ikiza c'ibicurane cabayemu 1918-1919 kizwi ko cavuye ku nyoni , kandi cahitanye abantu barenga imliyoni 50.
Ntavyemezo vyerekana ko iki kiza ca coronavirus kizokwica ukwo , ariko muri kahise k 'ibiza bikomeye vyavuye ku bikoko bigashika mu bantu,  vyarateye amakenga mu bijanye n'amagara y'abantu.
none iyi migera ya coronavirus irashobora gukwiragiracane mu kanya gato ?
Inkuru nziza ni uko hari icizere ko iyo umugera wavuye ku bikoko ukaja ku bantu udashobora kuva ku muntu uja ku wundi muntu.
Easton ati: ''Iyo ni iyindi ntambamyi  kuri uwo mugera".
Hagati aho, avuga ko bishobora guhinduka mu kanya gato, kandi ko mu gihe birinze  bihinduka,  bishobora kuba ikibazo gikomeye cane .
Ati: "Imigera ya  coronaviruses yihimbaguramwo uduce twinshi".
Iyo rero umugera umaze kwihindura ugafata iyindi sura, ushobora gukwiragira uva kumuntu ukaja ku wundi, bivuga ko ukwiragira  ku rugero runini cane kandi mu kanya gato.
Ibi vyarabaye ku vyerekeye iki kiza mu Bushinwa arico gituma hafashwe ingingo zikomeye zo kurwanya ikwiragira ry'uwo mugera.
Ariko biguma biboneka ko abantu babandanya bandura.
Mu gihe umuntu afise amagara meza umubiri wiwe urashobora kugira ubushobozi bwo kuwurwanya.
Imigera imwe imwe yinjira ubw onyene, hanyuma iyindi ikinjira buhoro buhoro.  Kimwe mu bibazo umuntu yokwibaza ni aho  uyo mugera wa coronavirus  uba.
Hokorwa iki mugihe ikiza c'umugera wa coronavirus catanguye ?
Inkuru mbi n'uko umuti atari wo nyishu nyayo kenshi.
''Hariho imiti ikiza cane ico kiza", niko Easton yavuze.
Ariko hariho izindi ngingo zisanzwe zikwiye gufatwa, cane nko gukaraba mu minwe no gukoresha udutambara.
Avuga ko isuku risanzwe ari ikintu ciza cane. Bikingira ibintu vyose kandi ni naco kirwanisho nyamukuru kiriho kubera ata miti iriho muri aka kanya ka vuba.
Kiretse ukuwukinga , uburyo abayobozi bafasha uwamaze kwandura uwo mugera navyo nyene bifise uruhara rudasanzwe.
''Ikindi ni ukurondera abantu banduye mu kiringo ca vuba kugira bafashwe vyihuta , bongere bashirwe mu kibanza kugira uwo mugera ntukwiragire ''.
Amahirwe ni uko amakungu yihutira kurwanya ibiza nk'ivyo vya Sars na Mers iyo birinze vyaduka.
Easton ati: "Twarabibonye incuro zitari nke, aho wasanga iyo bikenewe ko hafatwa ingingo zihuta zaca zifatwa mu buryo bubangutse.
Umugwi w'abaganga  ku rwego mpuzamakungu bizeye ko bigiye ku bindi biza vy'imigera ya coronaviruses yabaye imbere y'aho, kandi ko bizobafasha kugwanya iyi yadutse ubu, mber no muri kazoza, kugira ngo ntikore ibara.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-51292077' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-51292077' term='SARS'>
Indwara nka coronavirus ziri kwiyongera. Biterwa n'iki?
Mu myaka 30 ishize, umubare w'indwara z'ibyorezo ziterwa na virusi kandi zikwirakwira byihuse - nka coronavirus mu Bushinwa ubu - wariyongereye kurusha mbere. Ariko se biterwa n'iki?
Mu myaka 30 ishize, umubare w'indwara z'ibyorezo ziterwa na virusi kandi zikwirakwira byihuse - nka coronavirus mu Bushinwa ubu - wariyongereye kurusha mbere. Ariko se biterwa n'iki?
Ni ibintu bigaragara ku buryo bworoshye ko kuri ubu dutuye isi turi benshi cyane kurusha mu kindi gihe kigeze kubaho - ubu abatuye isi ni miliyari 7.7 kandi bakomeje kwiyongera.
Dukomeje kandi gutura mu buryo bwegeranye kurushaho.
Abantu benshi batuye mu buryo bw'ubucucike, ibyo bivuze ko hari ibyago biri hejuru cyane byo guhura n'ibitera indwara.
Indwara ya coronavirus isa nk'iyandura ivuye ku muntu umwe akayanduza undi gutyo gutyo iyo habayeho gukorora cyangwa kwitsamura hakagira umwanda na mucye usohoka.
Iyo virusi imara igihe gito ifite ubuzima iyo iri hanze y'umubiri w'umuntu, rero bisaba ko abantu baba begeranye kugira ngo yandure.
Mu mwaka wa 2014, icyorezo cya Ebola cyasakaye binyuze mu maraso cyangwa andi matembabuzi ava mu mubiri, gusa abahuye mu buryo bwegeranye ni bo bayanduye.
Ariko si virusi zose zandura mu buryo bw'umuntu umwe uyanduza undi. Ndetse na Zika, abantu bandura ivuye mu mibu, nayo irushaho kwandura iyo abantu begeranye.
Imibu itera Zika yororokera mu bice by'imijyi aho itungwa n'amaraso y'abantu. Yororoka neza mu bice bituwe mu buryo bw'ubucucike, ahantu hahehereye ndetse n'ahashushye by'akazuyazi.
Kuva mu 2007 abantu barushijeho gutura mu mijyi kurusha mu byaro. Abantu barenga miliyari enye ubu batuye ku gice kingana na 1% by'ubuso bw'ubutaka bw'iyi si dutuyeho.
Kandi imijyi myinshi turi kwimukiramo ntabwo itwiteguye. Rero abantu benshi birangira batuye ahantu h'akajagari aho babura amazi meza ndetse n'uburyo bwiza bwo kuyobora imyanda (sewage system).
Rero indwara ikwirakwira byihuse.
Indege, gariyamoshi n'imodoka, ibyo bivuze ko virusi ishobora kugera mu ntera igera mu cyakabiri cy'isi mu gihe kitageze ku munsi.
Mu byumweru bicye bishize coronavirus igaragaraye, habonetse abayicyekwaho mu bihugu birenga 16.
Mu mwaka ushize wa 2019, kompanyi z'indege zatwaye abagenzi miliyari 4.5 - mu myaka icumi yabanje zari zatwaye gusa abagenzi miliyari 2.4.
Wuhan ni hamwe mu hantu h'ingenzi ho mu Bushinwa hanyura za gariyamoshi zigenda ku muvuduko wo hejuru.
Kandi iyo virusi yahagaragaye ubwo Ubushinwa bwiteguraga ubutembere bwa mbere bukozwe n'abantu benshi mu mateka y'isi.
Ingendo zirenga miliyari eshatu zikorwa mu Bushinwa mu ntangiriro y'umwaka wo muri iki gihugu.
Kimwe mu byorezo bibi cyane byabayeho ni icyitwa influenza - kizwi ku izina rya 'Spanish flu' - cyabayeho kuva mu mwaka wa 1918 kugera mu 1920.
Cyadutse i Burayi ubwo nabwo habaga urundi rujya n'uruza runini rw'abantu, intambara ya mbere y'isi iri kurangira.
Mu gihe ibyo bicurane byakwiragiraga, abasirikare bari barimo gusubira iwabo mu bihugu baturutsemo, bava ku rugamba, batahana ibyo bicurane.
Bajyanye iyo virusi aho baba, mu bantu batari barateguye uburyo bwo kuyirwanya, bituma ubwirinzi bw'umubiri w'umuntu bugubwa gitumo neza neza.
Ubushakashatsi bumwe bw'impuguke mu bya virusi, John Oxford, buvuga ko intandaro y'iyo virusi ishobora kuba yari inkambi abasirikare barenga 100,000 bacagamo buri munsi.
Ndetse no mu gihe cya mbere y'ingendo zo mu ndege, icyo cyorezo cyakwiragiye hafi muri buri gice cy'isi. Cyahitanye abantu babarirwa hagati ya miliyoni 50 na miliyoni 100.
Ariko icyo cyorezo cya 'Spanish flu' cyafashe igihe kiri hagati y'amezi atandatu n'amezi icyenda ngo kibashe gukwirakwira ku isi.
Muri iyi si y'ubu aho dushobora kuyitembera yose mu munsi umwe, ubundi bwoko bushya bwa virusi bwo bushobora gukwirakwira byihuse kurushaho.
Ebola, SARS, noneho ubu na Wuhan coronavirus, ni ndwara zandura ziterwa na virusi - zandujwe abantu zivuye ku nyamaswa.
Ubu bwoko bushya bwa coronavirus busa nk'ubwaturutse mu isoko ry'inyama ry'i Wuhan - amakuru y'ibanze avuga ko ishobora kuba yaravuye ku nzoka zikiri nzima.
Muri iyi minsi hafi indwara eshatu muri buri ndwara enye nshya ziterwa n'inyamaswa.
Uko abantu bakunda inyama ku isi biri kwiyongera, ubworozi bw'amatungo atanga umusaruro w'ibiribwa ndetse n'ayororerwa kwishimisha buri kwaguka.
Niko ibice bimwe by'isi byiyongeramo abakire ndetse bakayoboka n'amafunguro arimo inyama.
Ibicurane biterwa na virusi, abantu bakunze kubyandura binyuze mu matungo boroye, rero ubushobozi bwo kuba amatungo yanduye ashobora kugira aho ahurira n'abantu nabwo bwariyongereye.
Virusi zo mu bwoko bwa coronavirus zisimbuka ziva mu nyamaswa zo mu gasozi zikajya mu bantu.
Mu Bushinwa, amasoko acuruzwamo inyamaswa zikiri nzima ndetse n'acuruzwamo inyama aramenyerewe mu bice bituwe mu bucucike.
Ibyo bishobora kuba byasobanura impamvu ibyorezo bibiri biherutse byavuye muri ibyo bice bituwe mu buryo bw'ubucucike.
Ikindi, uko imijyi dutuyemo yaguka, turushaho gusatira ibice by'icyaro aho abantu bagira aho bahurira n'inyamaswa zo mu gasozi.
Virusi ya 'Lassa fever' nayo ni indi virusi ikwira muri ubu buryo - uko abantu batema amashyamba ngo bahinge kuri ubwo butaka, imbeba zo mu gasozi zahungiye mu ngo zihajyana iyo virusi.
Nubwo isi isigaye imeze nk'iyabaye umudugudu umwe cyane kurusha mu kindi gihe cyigeze kubaho mbere, ntabwo turagira uburyo buhuriweho nk'isi bwo guhangana n'ibishobora gutera ibyorezo tubisanze aho bituruka.
Mu guhagarika indwara yandura, ducungira gusa kuri leta yo muri icyo gihugu iyo ndwara yatangiriyemo. Iyo iyo leta inaniwe, abatuye isi bose bibashyira mu kaga.
Nta handi ibyo byagaragaye kurushaho kurusha muri Afurika y'uburengerazuba mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya Ebola, ubwo inzego z'ubuvuzi zo muri Guinea, Liberia na Sierra Leone zananirwaga guhagarika ikwirakwira ryayo.
Ebola yishe abantu 11,310 muri Afurika y'uburengerazuba.
By'amahire ku batuye isi, iyo ni virusi urebye ikwirakwira gahoro, ariko virusi zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero nka 'influenza' cyangwa coronavirus zikwirakwira byihuse cyane.
Biba bibi kandi kurushaho kuko haba hari ibyago byinshi byuko indwara nk'izo ziba zishobora kwandurira mu bice bituwe n'abakene aho inzego z'ubuvuzi zifite intege nke.
Kuba nta mategeko n'ubukangurambaga ku isuku n'isukura, ndetse n'abaturage batuye mu bucucike, byose byongera ibyago by'indwara nk'izo.
Kandi nanone byinshi muri ibyo bihugu byugarijwe n'ikibazo cyuko abikomokamo bo mu rwego rw'ubuzima bakomeje kubivamo bajya mu mahanga aho bizeye akazi keza kurushaho (bizwi nka 'brain drain').
Inzego nke cyane z'ubuzima ku isi ni zo ziba zifite ubushake bwo gushora ubushobozi - muri bucye zifite - mu kwitegura indwara zikaze cyane biba bishobora kurangira zitanageze muri ibyo bihugu.
Ubwo ibicurane by'ingurube - bizwi nka 'swine flu' - byadukaga, habayeho uburyo bwo gukwirakwiza imiti ku isi, ariko iyo gahunda yaranenzwe bivugwa ko uburyo bwo kubirwanya bwabayemo gukabya kuko byaje kugaragara ko byari ibicurane byoroheje cyane.
Nubwo rwose dufite ikoranabuhanga ryo gukora imiti ishobora kurinda zimwe muri izi virusi, ntabwo ibyo biba bihagije kugira ngo kompanyi zikora imiti zumve zashoramo amafaranga gutyo gusa.
Niba virusi runaka izica gusa abantu babarirwa mu bihumbi bicye, nta mafaranga izo kompanyi zikora imiti ziba zumva zizabibonamo.
Nubwo tuba tuzi ko izo ndwara ziri hafi kutugeraho, kuri nyinshi muri zo ntituba dushobora kumenya ngo zizatugeraho ryari cyangwa hehe, kandi kwaduka kw'indwara zandura hafi buri gihe zitugwa gitumo.
Nubwo ubu turi kubona indwara nyinshi yanduza abantu benshi kurusha mu bindi bihe byabayeho mbere, abantu bacye ugereranyije na mbere ni bo barwara zikanabahitana.
Ibi bikubiye mu bushakashatsi bw'ikigo cya siyansi cya Royal Society cyo mu Bwongereza.
Iyo ubukungu bwiyongera byihuse, nkuko twabibonye mu Bushinwa, isuku y'ibanze no kugera ku bikorwa by'ubuvuzi bitera imbere. Ni nako bigenda ku bukangurambaga bwo kwirinda kwandura izo ndwara.
Ubuvuzi buba bwiza kurushaho, abantu benshi kurushaho bagera kuri ubwo buvuzi kandi dukomeje no gutera imbere mu buryo bwo kwirinda indwara. Inkingo ziri gukorwa mu buryo bwihuse kurushaho.
Nubwo uburyo bwo ku rwego rw'isi bwo guhangana n'ibiza atari shyashya, dukomeje gutera imbere mu buryo bwo gutahura no kugira igikorwa iyo bigaragaye.
Igihugu nk'Ubushinwa gishobora kubaka ibitaro birimo ibitanda 1,000 by'abarwayi mu gihe cy'icyumweru kimwe, ikintu cyari kuba ari nk'inzozi gusa mu mwaka wa 1918.
