<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-49251318' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-49251318' term='ebola'>
Malaria imaze guhitana abantu 1800 uno mwaka mu Burundi
Malariya imaze guhitana abantu barenga 1800 mu Burundi uno mwaka, igitigiri kingana hafi nico abamaze guhitanwa n'ikiza ca Ebola muri Repubulkika y'Intwaro Rusangi ya Kongo, nk'uko bivugwa n'igisata ca ONU kijejwe ubutabazi, OCHA.
Malariya imaze guhitana abantu barenga 1800 mu Burundi uno mwaka, igitigiri kingana hafi nico abamaze guhitanwa n'ikiza ca Ebola muri Repubulkika y'Intwaro Rusangi ya Kongo, nk'uko bivugwa n'igisata ca ONU kijejwe ubutabazi, OCHA.
Mu cegeranyo giherutse, OCHA ivuga ko abantu imiliyoni zitanu n'ibice indwi banduye malariya muri uno mwaka mu Burundi, igitigiri kingana hafi igice c'abanyagihugu bose muri ico gihugu.
Muri abo bantu bose, abangana 1801 barahitanywe n'iyo ndwara iterwa n'umubu kuva mu kwezi kwa mbere gushika ku wa 21 z'ukw'indwi.
Leta y'Uburundi ntiratangaza niba iyo ndwara ari ikiza, n'aho OCHA yoyo yemeza ko mu kwezi kwa gatanu ibitigiri vyarengeye ibisanzwe bifatirwako kugira indwara ifatwe nk'ikiza.
Ikinyamakuru ca OCHA gisohoka ku ndwi ku ndwi ku vyerekeye ubutabazi, kivuga kiti: "Integuro y'igihugu y'uguhangana n'ikiza ca malaria, isanzwe iriko irigwa, irerekana ko hari ikena ry'abakozi, uburyo n'amafaranga".
"Abegwa n'iki kibazo bose, harimwo abategetsi b'igihugu n'amashirahamwe, basabwa kwegeranya ibisabwa vyose kugira ngo hatorwe inyishu ikomeye kuri iki kibazo amazi atararenga inkombe".
OCHA ivuga ko kubona ata ngingo z'ugukinga zifatwa nk'ugukoresha imisegetera, ihindagurika ry'ibirere hamwe n'uruja n'uruza rw'abantu badakingiwe rwiyongereye, biri mu bituma iyo ndwara yiyongera.
Umwe mu bategetsi ba OCHA yabwiye itororokanirizo ry'amakuru AFP ko "ingingo y'ugutangaza ikiza ari ingingo yega leta y'Uburundi nk'igihugu cigenga".
Mu kwezi kwa gatandatu uno mwaka, OCHA yamenyesheje ko igitigiri c'uburere bw'ubuvuzi aho malariya igenda iba nk'ikiza ciyongereye mu kwezi kwa gatanu, aho cashitse ku burere 33 kuri 46.
OCHA ivuga ko malaria yiyongereye ku bice 164 kw'ijana (164%) ku ndwi igira 29 y'umwaka wa 2019 ugereranije n'indwi ya 29 y'umwaka uheze wa 2018.
Mu kwezi kwa gatatu kw'umwaka wa 2017, leta yaratangaje malariya nk'ikiza igihe abantu umuliyoni n'ibihumbi 800 bari bamaze kwandura iyo ndwara, abandi nabo 700 irabahitana, ariko ubu ntirafata ingingo nk'iyo.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_140702_ebola' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='http://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru/2014/07/140702_ebola' term='ebola'>
Inama mpuzamahanga kuri Ebola
Abaminisitiri b'ubuzima bo mu bihugu byo muri Afurika y'uburengerazuba bari mu nama i Accra muri Ghana igamije gushaka ukuntu icyorezo cy'indwara ya Ebola muri ako karere cyahagarara.
Abaminisitiri b'ubuzima bo mu bihugu byo muri Afurika y'uburengerazuba bari mu nama i Accra muri Ghana igamije gushaka ukuntu icyorezo cy'indwara ya Ebola muri ako karere cyahagarara.
Iyi nama yatumijwe n'ishami rya ONU ryita ku buzima, OMS, ibaye mu gihe mu cyumweru gishize habonetse abandi bantu 22 banduye iyo ndwara.
Benshi muri abo babonetse muri Sierra Leonne kurusha muri Guinee aho iyo ndwara yabonetse bwa mbere muri ako karere.
Abaganga bahanganye n'iyo ndwara baravuga ko imaze guhitana abantu hafi 470.
Baravuga ko ubwoba abantu bafite bwo kuyandura ndetse no kudashaka kuyivuza ku bayanduye ari inzitizi zikomeye mu rugamba rwo kugerageza kuyikumira.
Usibye abaministri b'ubuzima bo mu bihugu 11 bo muri Afurika y'uburengerazuba, iyi nama yitabiriwe kandi n'abakize iyo ndwara ndetse n'abahagarariye amasosiyete y'indege n'amasosiyite acukura amabuye y'agaciro.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-48407945' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-48407945' term='ebola'>
Ibitero ku bigo bivurirwamo Ebola muri Kongo biri kwiyongera
Abakuriye ibikorwa by'ubuzima muri Repubulika ya Demokarasi ya Kongo bavuga ko hamaze kugabwa ibitero birenga 130 ku bigo bivurirwamo Ebola kuva yatangazwa ko yongeye kwaduka muri iki gihugu mu kwezi kwa munani mu mwaka ushize wa 2018.
Abakuriye ibikorwa by'ubuzima muri Repubulika ya Demokarasi ya Kongo bavuga ko hamaze kugabwa ibitero birenga 130 ku bigo bivurirwamo Ebola kuva yatangazwa ko yongeye kwaduka muri iki gihugu mu kwezi kwa munani mu mwaka ushize wa 2018.
Abantu bane bamaze kwicwa naho abandi bagera hafi kuri 40 barakomereka.
Ni ku nshuro ya 10 Ebola yadutse muri Kongo. Yahadutse bwa mbere mu mwaka wa 1976.
Igitero giheruka kuba ku wa kane w'iki cyumweru mu mujyi wa Butembo mu ntara ya Kivu y'amajyaruguru, mu burasirazuba bw'iki gihugu, cyatumye ibigo bitandatu bivurirwamo Ebola bifunga imiryango n'abaganga bajya kwihisha.
Abakora mu bikorwa by'ubuzima muri uyu mujyi bakoze imyigaragambyo y'igice, basaba ko hagira igikorwa kurushaho mu kubarinda mu kazi kabo.
Kutagirirwa icyizere n'abaturage - bamwe bavuga ko Ebola itabaho naho abandi bamwe bakavuga ko yazanywe n'abo baganga - ndetse n'umutekano mucye umaze imyaka urangwa muri aka karere, byagize uruhare mu ngorane abakora mu bikorwa by'ubuvuzi bwa Ebola bari guhura nabyo.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_141018_sierra_leone_ebola' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='http://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru/2014/10/141018_sierra_leone_ebola' term='ebola'>
Umugwi mushasha wo kurwanya ebola muri Sierra Leone
