<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-45081480' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-45081480' term='ebola'>
Repubulika ya demokarasi ya Kongo yatangaje ko indwara nshya ya Ebola imaze guhitana abantu 33
Minisiteri y'ubuzima muri Repubulika ya demokarasi ya Kongo, yatangaje ko byibazwa ko abantu 33 ari bo bamaze guhitanwa n'indwara ya Ebola kuva yakongera kwaduka muri iki gihugu mu ntangiriro y'uku kwezi kwa munani mu ntara ya Kivu y'amajyaruguru.
Minisiteri y'ubuzima muri Repubulika ya demokarasi ya Kongo, yatangaje ko byibazwa ko abantu 33 ari bo bamaze guhitanwa n'indwara ya Ebola kuva yakongera kwaduka muri iki gihugu mu ntangiriro y'uku kwezi kwa munani mu ntara ya Kivu y'amajyaruguru.
Ku wa gatandatu, Minisitiri w'ubuzima Oly Ilunga Kalenga yabwiye ibiro ntaramakuru AFP ko n'abantu 13 bamaze kwandura Ebola kuva yakongera kwaduka muri iki gihugu.
Dogiteri Ilunga Kalenga yongeyeho ko batatu muri 33 byibazwa ko bamaze guhitanwa na Ebola, ari abo mu iri itsinda ry'abantu 13 bari bazwi ko bamaze kuyandura.
Ku wa gatanu, Dogiteri Peter Salama ushinzwe ibikorwa by'ubutabazi bwihuse mu ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumye ryita ku buzima OMS, yabwiye abanyamakuru ko guhangana na Ebola mu "karere kibasiwe n'intambara" ka Kongo ari imwe  mu ngorane zikomeye cyane OMS ihuye nazo.
Ebola yongeye kwaduka muri Kivu y'amajyaruguru hashize icyumweru kimwe OMS n'ubutegetsi bwa Kongo bishimiye ko bashoboye guhagarika indwara ya Ebola yari yadutse mu ntara ya Équateur iri mu majyaruguru ashyira uburengerazuba bw'igihugu, aho yishe abantu 33.
Minisiteri y'ubuzima muri Kongo yatangaje ko cyo kimwe na mbere, "gutanga inkingo ari uburyo bw'ibanze" igiye gukoresha mu guhangana na Ebola.
Iyi ni inshuro ya 10 Ebola igaragaye muri Kongo kuva mu mwaka wa 1976 ubwo yagaragaraga bwa mbere mu majyaruguru y'iki gihugu kikitwa Zaïre.
Ebola ni imwe mu ndwara zitinywa cyane ku isi. Bimwe mu bimenyetso byayo ni ukuva amaraso mu kanwa, mu maso no mu matwi.
Kuva mu mwaka wa 2013 kugera mu mwaka wa 2015, Ebola yibasiye ibihugu bya Guinea, Liberia na Siera Leone byo mu burengerazuba bw'Afurika, ihitana abarenga ibihumbi 11. Mu mateka y'iyi ndwara, ni bwo yari ihitanye abantu benshi cyane ku isi.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-47690756' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-47690756' term='ebola'>
Ku nshuro ya mbere, abarwayi ba Ebola muri Kongo bamaze kurenga 1000
Imiryango ifasha ivuga ko umubare w'abantu bazwi ko banduye indwara ya Ebola mu burasirazuba bwa Repubulika ya Demokarasi ya Kongo, ku nshuro ya mbere umaze kurenga 1000.
Imiryango ifasha ivuga ko umubare w'abantu bazwi ko banduye indwara ya Ebola mu burasirazuba bwa Repubulika ya Demokarasi ya Kongo, ku nshuro ya mbere umaze kurenga 1000.
Abantu 629 ni bo bamaze gupfa bazize Ebola kuva yatangazwa ko yongeye kwaduka muri iki gihugu mu kwezi kwa munani mu mwaka ushize wa 2018.
Umubare w'abarwayi ba Ebola wariyongereye cyane mu cyumweru gishize - abarwayi 58 bashya mu cyumweru kimwe, umubare munini wa mbere ubayeho mu gihe nk'icyo muri uyu mwaka.
Umwe mu miryangoi ifasha wa  International Rescue Committee, uvuga ko Kongo yateye "intambwe ibabaje".
Itangazo wasohoye rigira riti: "Hashize hafi amezi arindwi iyi ndwara yadutse, ubundi kuri ubu twakagombye kuba tubona umubare w'abayandura ugabanuka, aho kwiyongera".
"Tugerageje kugira umutima wo kwizera, bisa nkaho iyi ndwara izamara n'andi mezi atandatu ari imbere - ariko mu by'ukuri, birashoboka ko hashobora gushira undi mwaka tugihanganye n'iyi ndwara".
Abakora mu bikorwa by'ubuvuzi bwa Ebola bugarijwe n'ikibazo cy'umutekano mucye muri ako karere ndetse na bamwe mu baturage barwanya ibikorwa by'ubuvuzi.
Ibigo byinshi bivurirwamo Ebola byagabweho ibitero n'abantu batamenyekanye ndetse n'ababwari ba Ebola - bashobora kwanduza - bava aho bavurirwaga.
Hari impungenge ko hari abantu bamwe baba bakure yaho ibigo by'ubuvuzi bwa Ebola biherereye - ibintu bituma bigorana gukumira ko iyi ndwara ikomeza gukwirakwira.
Ni ku nshuro ya 10 Ebola yadutse muri Kongo mu mateka y'iki gihugu, ariko kugeza ubu iyi yo kuri iyi nshuro igaragara nkaho guhangana na yo biri kuba urusobe.
Ni na yo yibasiye abantu benshi cyane kurusha izindi zabanje muri iki gihugu, ikaba n'iya kabiri ikaze cyane ibayeho ku isi.
</doc>
