Umubare w'abamaze guhitanwa na Ebola muri Repubulika ya Demokarasi ya Kongo ukomeje kwiyongera
Abategetsi bakora mu rwego rw'ubuzima muri Repubulika ya Demokarasi ya Kongo, baravuga ko abantu 55 ari bo byibazwa ko bamaze guhitanwa n'indwara ya Ebola yadutse mu burasirazuba bw'iki gihugu.
Abategetsi bakora mu rwego rw'ubuzima muri Repubulika ya Demokarasi ya Kongo, baravuga ko abantu 55 ari bo byibazwa ko bamaze guhitanwa n'indwara ya Ebola yadutse mu burasirazuba bw'iki gihugu.
Leta yemeje ko nta shiti 28 muri bo bazize virusi ya Ebola.
Inkingo n'imiti ya Ebola ikiri mu igeragezwa, ni byo biri kwifashishwa mu gukumira ko Ebola isakara no mu bice itarageramo. Ariko abategetsi bateganya ko umubare w'abarwayi ba Ebola uziyongera.
Ibigo bibiri biri kuvurirwamo Ebola muri Kivu y'amajyaruguru birenda kurengerwa ubushobozi mu gihe ikigo gishya cyo kuvuriramo Ebola kiri hafi kubakwa mu ntara bituranye ya Ituri.
Abakora mu bikorwa by'ubuzima bari gukurikirana abantu 1500 bagize aho bahurira n'abarwayi ba Ebola.
Ariko ni akazi kagoye kubera ibikorwa by'umutekano mucye byongeye kubura mu burasirazuba bwa Kongo, ahakorera imitwe myinshi y'inyeshyamba.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_150329_guineeebola' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='http://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru/2015/03/150329_guineeebola' term='ebola'>
Amategeko adasanzwe yo gukumira Ebola muri Guinee
Umukuru w'igihugu wa Guinee yatangaje ko yashyizeho amategeko adasanzwe arebana n'ubuvuzi mu ntara 5 muri gahunda yo kurandura burundu indwara ya Ebola muri icyo gihugu.
Umukuru w'igihugu wa Guinee yatangaje ko yashyizeho amategeko adasanzwe arebana n'ubuvuzi mu ntara 5 muri gahunda yo kurandura burundu indwara ya Ebola muri icyo gihugu.
Alpha Conde yavuze ko iyo ndwara ikomeje kuba ibamba.
Mu ngamba yashyizeho harimo gushyira mu kato ibitaro byose n'amavuriro bifite abakozi banduye Ebola.
Yashyizeho kandi amategeko mashya agenga gushyingura no guha uburenganzira abategetsi bwo kubuza abantu kuva mu mago yabo bibaye ngombwa.
Ayo mategeko mashya azakurikizwa mu turere dukikije umurwa mukuru Conakry azamara iminsi 45.
Muri Sierra Leone bitunyuranye ho kuri iki cyumweru niwo munsi wa nyuma abaturage badasohoka mu mago yabo muri gahunda yo gukumira burundu Ebola.
Naho muri Liberia habonetse abantu babiri bakekwaho kuba baranduye iyo ndwara mu gihe hari hashize ibyumweru bibiri nta muntu n'umwe igaragayeho muri icyo gihugu.
