Uhagarariye Leta Zunze Ubumwe muri Amerika  Samantha Power yatanguye urugendo mu bihugu bitatu bisisnzikajwe na Ebola agaye cane ivyo amakungu amaze gufasha gushika ubu.
Samantha Power yashikiye muri Guinee ariko akazogendera Sierra Leone na Liberia. Yabwiye NBC ko bimwe mu bihugu vyemeye guafasha bitarabishira mu bikorwa mu gutanga imfashanyo n'abaganga.
