Yavuze ati'' hari ibihugu muri ONU aho nkora vyririgwa biremeza ingingo bishimagiza igikorwa coza ca Amerika, Ubwongereza n'abandi bariko barakora ariko vyonyene ata na kimwe birakora mu kurungika abaganga, ibitanda canke amafaranga afadika''.
