CAF yahaye ibihano Maroc
Ishyirahamwe ry’umupira w’amaguru muri Afurika – CAF – ryahanishije igihugu cya Maroc kutazakina mu marushanwa abiri ataha y’igikombe cya Afurika cy’ibihugu.
Ishyirahamwe ry’umupira w’amaguru muri Afurika – CAF – ryahanishije igihugu cya Maroc kutazakina mu marushanwa abiri ataha y’igikombe cya Afurika cy’ibihugu.
Maroc ihawe iki gihano kubera ko yanze kwakira imikino y’icyo gikombe cy’uyu mwaka nkuko byari biteganijwe kubera gutinya ko abafana binjiza ku butaka bwayo indwara ya Ebola.
Maroc yasabaga ko itariki iyo mikino yagombaga kuberaho yimurwa ikigizwa inyuma ariko ishyirahamwe CAF rirabyanga.
Ishyirahamwe ry’umupira w’amaguru muri Maroc ryo ryahanishijwe kwishyura CAF amafaranga y’ihazabu agera kuri miliyoni imwe y’amadolari y’abanyamerika n’impozamarira igera kuri miliyoni 8 z’ama Euro.
CAF yagombye kwitabaza igihugu cya Guinee Equatoriale kugira ngo kiyakire.
Umukino wa nyuma mu irushanwa ry'uyu mwaka uteganijwe kubera muri Guinee Equatoriale ku cyumweru itariki ya 8 z’ukwa kabiri hagati ya Ghana na Cote d’ivoire.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_140812_ebola_rda' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='http://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru/2014/08/140812_ebola_rda' term='ebola'>
Umugabo yakekwako Ebola mu Rwanda ntayo afite
Umuyobozi w'ishyami rishinzwe kurwanya indwara z'ibyorezo mu kigo cy'igihugu cy'ubuzima Thierry Nyatanyi avuga ko ibipimo by'amaraso y'uwo mugabo, byagaragaje ko nta Ebola imurangwaho.
Umuyobozi w'ishyami rishinzwe kurwanya indwara z'ibyorezo mu kigo cy'igihugu cy'ubuzima Thierry Nyatanyi avuga ko ibipimo by'amaraso y'uwo mugabo, byagaragaje ko nta Ebola imurangwaho.
Ivyo bipimo byari byoherejwe mu gihugu c'Ubugande, byatangiwe ibisubizo  uyu munsi mu gitondo.
Kubera ko yari yashizwe mu kato, yahise arekurwa arataha, kimwe n'abandi bose bari bahuye nawe barimo abaganga b'aho yari yagiye kwivuriza.
Uyu mugabo yari yakesweho iyi ndwara ubwo yajyaga kwa muganga ibyuma bikagaragaza ko ibipimo by'umubiri we bifite ubushyuhe budasanzwe.
Umuriro ni kimwe mu bimenyetso by'indwara ya Ebola.
Iyi nkuru y'uko uyu muntu wakekwagaho indwara ya Ebola basanze atariyo ishobora gutuma benshi biruhutsa, kubera ubwoba yari yateye mu bantu.
Cyakora nk'uko bitangazwa n'inzego z'ubuzima mu Rwanda, ngo ibi ntibyatuma barera amaboko.
Gahunda yo gupima abantu bose binjira mu Rwanda irakomeje, ndetse no gukangurira abantu uburyo iyi ndwara imaze guhitana abatari batari bake mu bihugu bya Africa y'uburengerazuba yakwirindwa.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-35841828' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='http://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-35841828' term='ebola'>
Ebola yasubiye kwaduka muri Guinee




Abandi bantu babiri bafise umugera wa Ebola babonetse muri Guinee, inyuma y'amezi yababa atatu, ico gihugu kigize umusi mukuru wo gutsinda ico kiza.

Abandi bantu batatu b'uwo muryango bikekwa ko boba baheruka gupfa bazize uwo mugera.

Abo bantu bavugwa mu karere ko mu bumanuko ka Nzerekore, aho ico kiza catanguriye mu 2013.

Ikiza c'umugera wa Ebola cahitanye ubuzima bw'abantu 11,300, benshi muri bo bari abo muri Guinee hamwe n'ibihugu bibanyi vya Sierra Leone na Liberia.

Abo bantu babiri bavuzwe n'ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu rijejwe amagara y'abantu kw'isi (OMS), amasaha make inyuma rimenyeshereje ko ingwara yarangiye muri Sierra Leone.

OMS yaragabishije ko hashobora kuza haraboneka abafise uwo mugera kuko ushobora kwinyegeza mu mubiri wa bamwe mu bacitse kw'icumu.

Abo bantu bashasha bafise uwo mugera ni incamugongo ku twigoro two kubandanya kurwanya uwo mugera wa Ebola, nk'uko bivuga n'umumenyeshamakuru wa BBC global health, Tulip Mazumdar.
</doc>
