<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-45294264' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-45294264' term='ebola'>
Ebola imaze guhitana abantu 61 muri Repubulika ya Demokarasi ya Kongo
Ibiro ntaramakuru AFP byatangaje ko abategetsi ba Repubulika ya Demokarasi ya Kongo babibwiye ko abantu 61 ari bo bamaze guhitanwa n'indwara ya Ebola yadutse mu burasirazuba bw'iki gihugu.
Ibiro ntaramakuru AFP byatangaje ko abategetsi ba Repubulika ya Demokarasi ya Kongo babibwiye ko abantu 61 ari bo bamaze guhitanwa n'indwara ya Ebola yadutse mu burasirazuba bw'iki gihugu.
Bongeyeho ko imiti ine mishya yongewe ku yindi iri kwifashishwa mu guhangana n'iyi ndwara.
Minisiteri y'ubuzima muri Kongo yatangaje ko kugeza ku itariki ya 22 y'uku kwezi kwa munani, abantu 103 ari bo bari bamaze gusanganwa iyi ndwara ya Ebola, muri bo 76 bikaba byaremejwe n'ibizamini byo kwa muganga.
Muri abo 103, abantu 61 bamaze kwitaba Imana -  ibizamini byo kwa muganga byemeje ko 34 muri aba bazize Ebola mu gihe 27 bandi bo bafatwa nk'abo "bishoboka" ko bazize Ebola.
Ku itariki ya mbere y'uku kwezi kwa munani nibwo iyi ndwara ya Ebola yagaragaye mu ntara ya Kivu y'amajyaruguru mu gace ka Mangina, ubu ikaba inavugwa mu ntara bituranye ya Ituri.
Yahagaragaye hashize icyumweru ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima na leta ya Kongo batangaje ko bahagaritse Ebola yari yadutse mu ntara ya Équateur  mu majyaruguru ashyira uburengerazuba bwa Kongo ikica abantu 33.
Leta ya Kongo iteganya gukoresha miliyoni 43 z'amadolari y'Amerika mu guhangana n'iyi ndwara ya Ebola yadutse mu burasirazuba bw'igihugu.
Hagati aho, ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima ryatangaje ko hari umuganga wanduye Ebola akaba arwariye ku bitaro biri mu mujyi wa Oicha biri mu burasirazuba bw'igihugu ku mupaka na Uganda. Ni agace kazengurutswe n'inyeshyamba za Allied Democratic Forces (ADF).
Byibazwa ko uwo muganga w'umugabo yagize aho ahurira n'abantu 97 muri ako gace, bikaba bigoye kubageraho kubera umutekano mucye.
Ni ku nshuro ya 10 Ebola igaragaye muri Kongo guhera mu mwaka wa 1976 ubwo yahagaragaraga bwa mbere.
Hagati y'umwaka wa 2013 na 2015 ubwo Ebola yabaye mbi cyane mu mateka yibasiraga uburengerazuba bw'Afurika mu bihugu bya Guinea, Liberia na Sierra Leone, yahitanye abarenga ibihumbi 11.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-43084433' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='http://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-43084433' term='ebola'>
Oxfam igiye gutohoza ku mabi ashingiye ku gitsina aregwa abakozi bayo
Umuyobozi nshingwabikorwa wa Oxfam, Winnie Byanyima yavuze ko ubutungane buzokora, abagigwa n'amabi ashingiye ku gitsina bagahanwa, umugwi w'itohoza agiye gushinga ni warangiza igikorwa cawo.
Umuyobozi nshingwabikorwa wa Oxfam, Winnie Byanyima yavuze ko ubutungane buzokora, abagigwa n'amabi ashingiye ku gitsina bagahanwa, umugwi w'itohoza agiye gushinga ni warangiza igikorwa cawo.
Uwo mukenyezi yasavye abakorewe amabi guseruka kugira ngo batunganirizwe, avuga ko ikibanza arimwo kimuhamagarira gufasha abagore bose bakorewe amabi.
Iryo shirahamwe ryo mu Bwongereza ryihaye intego yo gufasha, ryaridogewe ku kuntu ryitwaye ku bivugwa ko abakozi baryo bahaye akazi imaraya mu 2011 mu gihugu ca Haiti.
Avuga ko vyababaje iryo shirahamwe ariko yongera avuga ati: "Nta kuntu rino shirahamwe ryacu ryosenyuka...amakungu ararikeneye."
Madamu Byanyima, niwe mutegetsi mukuru cane wo hejuru muri Oxfam agize ico avuga kuri ico kibazo, akavuga ko yatanguye kwumva ayo majambo ubwa mbere mu makuru mu ndwi iheze.
Mu kiganiro n'umumenyeshamakuru wa BBC ajejwe abanyamahanga James Landale, yavuze mu rurimi rw'i Buganda ko asavye ikigongwe: "Bivuye ku mutima tugirire ikigongwe, girira ikigongwe Oxfam."
Yemeye ko adashobora kwemeza ko ata bakozi boba bakoze amabi ashingiye ku gitsina bari mw'ishirahamwe arongoye, ariko avuga ko Oxfam yiyemeje gushinga inyifato itihanganira iyo ngeso.
Amabi nka mwenayo ngo yarakozwe n'abakozi ba Oxfam no mu gihugu ca Tchad.
Oxfam ifise abakozi bashika 10000 bakorera mu bihugu 90 kw'isi.
Oxfam ishaka ko ibihugu vyahuye na Ebola bifashwa
Mu ntango ya kuno kwezi hari amakuru yavuga ko igihe Oxfam igiriye gutabara muri Haiti mu 2011, umuyobozi wayo mu gihugu, Roland van Hauwermeiren yahaye akazi imaraya, azikoteshereza n'inzu yishugwa na Oxfam.
Bwana Van Hauwermeiren, yasezereye Oxfam mu 2011 kubera ivyo yaregwa vy'ubusambanyi, yarahakanye ko yahaye akazi imaraya ariko avuga ko yagiranye imigenderanire n'umugore ariko ko atari imaraya.
Inyuma y'aho ayo makuru asohorewe, iryo shirahamwe ryidogewe na Leta y'Ubwongereza hamwe n'umukuru w'igihugu ca Haiti.
Umunyamabanga ajejwe iterambere ku rwego mpuzamakungu, Secretary Penny Mordaunt avuga ko ashobora guhagarika amahera yaha iryo shirahamwe, yashitse ku miliyoni z'amapawundi £32 mu mwaka uheze.
Inyuma y'ivyo riregwa, iryo shirahamwe ryatumye abanyecubahiro bariserukira nk'umukinyi wa sinema Minnie Driver na Desmond Tutu yigeze gustindira agashimwe kitiriwe Nobel, barivako.
Madamu Byanyima yavuze ko ababajwe no kubona aba ambasaderi "yubaha cabe" bagiye.
Umugwi ugiye kugenwa mw'iryo shirahamwe ugiye gutanguza itohoza ariko ukaba ufise amakenga ko "udashobora kuronka amakuru yose kandi y'ukuri" kuri ayo mabi ashingiye ku gitsina yakorewe muri Haiti.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_140828_ebola_drugs' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='http://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru/2014/08/140828_ebola_drugs' term='ebola'>
GlaxoSmithKline iri ku rukingo rwa ebola
Ikigo co mu Bwongereza gihingura imiti, GlaxoSmithKline, kivuga ko kiriko kiranyarutsa igerageza ku bantu ry'urukingo rwa ebola.
Ikigo co mu Bwongereza gihingura imiti, GlaxoSmithKline, kivuga ko kiriko kiranyarutsa igerageza ku bantu ry'urukingo rwa ebola.
Ico kigo kivuga ko gitegekanya kubika inkingo zishika ibihumbi cumi zo kurungika vyihutirwa.
GlazoSmithKline kandi ivuga ko iriko irafashanya muri ico gikorwa n'ibigo bikorera muri leta zunze umwe za Amerika.
Ngo mu gihe igerageza ku bantu ryotanga inyushu nziza, urukingo rushobora gutangura gukoreshwa mu 2015.
Ikigo co muri Amerika, Johnson and Johnson, kiriko naco nyene kirakora igerageza ku rundi rukingo.
Imiti ibiri ihabwa abarwayi bamaze kwandura ebola nayo iriko irakorwa, ikaba ari Zmapp ukorerwa muri Amerika na KTM-Ebola ukorerwa muri Canada.
Ariko gushika ubu ntirageragezwa ku buryo bushimishije, kandi hamaze gukorwa mike cane.
Hagati aho ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu rijejwe amagara kw'isi, OMS, rivuga ko ikiza ca ebola mu burengero bwa Afrika, gishobora kwandukira abantu ibihumbi 20 imbere y'uko gihagarikwa.
Gushika ubu abarenga gatoyi ibihumbi bitatu nibo bizwi ko banduye, ariko OMS ivuga ko igitigiri nyaco gishobora kuba kiruta ngaho.
Abantu barenga igihumbi n'amajana atanu baramaze kuhasiga ubuzima, hafi ya bose kababa baguye muri Liberia, Sierra Leone na Guinea.
Abantu batanu nibo bamaze guhitanwa na ebola mu muji mukuru muri Nigeria, Lagos, uwundi muntu umwe akaba yapfuye uno munsi i Port Harcourt, akarere gafise ubutunzi bwinshi bw'ibitoro muri Nigeria.
Abashikiranganji bajejwe amagara mu bihugu vyo mu burengero bwa Afrika, bari mu nama muri Ghana igamije kuraba ukuntu bobuza ico kiza kubandanya gikwiragira muri ako karere.
