Coronavirus: Isi yashyizwe mu bihe bidasanzwe, Rwandair yahagaritse ingendo zayo mu Bushinwa
Ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima, OMS/WHO,ryatangaje ko ubu isi iri mu bihe bidasanzwe kubera virus ya Coronavirus ikomeje gukwirakwira no hanze y'Ubushinwa.
Ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima, OMS/WHO,ryatangaje ko ubu isi iri mu bihe bidasanzwe kubera virus ya Coronavirus ikomeje gukwirakwira no hanze y'Ubushinwa.
Tedros Ghebreyesus, utegeka OMS  yagize ati: "Impamvu nyamukuru yo gutangaza ibi si ibiri kubera mu Bushinwa ahubwo n'ibiri kuba no mu bindi bihugu".
Impungenge ziriho ni uko iyi ndwara ishobora kugera mu bihugu bifite ubuvuzi budateye imbere.
Umuryango w'ibihugu bigize Africa y'iburasirazuba, EAC, wasabye ibihugu biwugize kuba maso bikitegura guhangana n'iyi virus.
Kompanyi y'indege ya leta y'u Rwanda, Rwandair, imaze gutangaza ko kuva uyu munsi kugeza igihe kizatangazwa, ihagaritse ingendo yakoreraga i Guangzhou mu Bushinwa.
Mu itangazo yasohoye, Rwandair ivuga ko ibi bitewe n'indwara ya coronavirus yamaze gutangazwa nk'icyorezo cyatumye isi ijya mu bihe bidasanzwe by'ubuzima.
Usibye Rwandair na Kenya Airways, izindi kompanyi eshatu Air Madagascar, Air Mauritus na Royal Air Maroc nazo zahagaritse ingendo zakoreraga mu Bushinwa kubera iyi virus.
Ibikorwa nk'ibi byo kwitegura no kwirinda birakorwa n'ibindi bihugu byo mu karere.
Mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru i Geneve, Bwana Tedros yavuze ko iyi virus "ari icyorezo kidasanzwe" ariko "kiri kurwanywa mu buryo budasanzwe".
Yashimye umuhate n'ingamba za leta y'Ubushinwa mu kurwanya iyi virus, avuga ko abona nta mpamvu yo kugabanya cyangwa kubuza abantu kujya mu Bushinwa.
Gusa ibihugu nka Leta zunze ubumwe za Amerika zabujije abaturage bazo kujya mu Bushinwa.
Muri Amerika kandi ejo kuwa kane abashinzwe ubuzima bemeje ko babonye umuntu wa mbere wanduye iyi ndwara atarageze mu Bushinwa ayivaye ku wahavuye.
Naho Uburusiya bwamaze gufunga umupaka wabwo wose n'Ubushinwa.
Mu Bushinwa iyi ndwara imaze guhitana abantu 213, abantu hafi 10,000 bamaze kuyandura.
OMS ivuga ko hari abantu 98 mu bihugu 18 ku isi bamaze kuyandura, gusa ntawe irahitana hanze y'Ubushinwa.
Ibihugu na kompanyi zinyuranye biri guhagarika no kugabanya ingendo n'ibikorwa mu Bushinwa.
Kompanyi nka Google, Ikea, Starbucks na Tesla zafunze ibikorwa byazo mu Bushinwa.
Gutangaza ko isi yinjiye mu bihe bidasanzwe biba bigamije kongera umuhate mu gukumira no kurwanya icyorezo kidasanzwe;
</doc>
