OMS rimaze kumenya abantu barenga 500 bashobora kuba baregeranye n'abantu bafashwe n'iyo ngwara ya Ebola muri Congo.
Bashobora kuba mu bantu ba mbere uyu musi baza guhabwa urwo rucanco ruriko rurageragezwa.
Igice ca mbere c'urwo rucanco cashikanywe mu gihugu ca Congo ku musi wa gatatu.
Iyo ngwara imaze kwaduka incuro zitatu zose muri Congo kuva mu 2014-2016 muri Afrika y'uburengero.
Ico urucanco rwa Ebola rufasha
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe kuri urwo rucanco rwa Ebola mu mwaka uheze, bwerekanye ko rushobora gukingira umuntu umugera w'iyo ngwara mu kiringo c'umwaka.
Ubwo bushakashatsi bwashizwe mu kinyamakuru ca New England Journal of Medicine, bwakorewe mu gihugu ca Liberia ku bagwayi bashika 1.500
Abahawe urwo rucanco barashoboye gukingirwa iyo ngwara mu kiringo cababa umwaka umwe.
Ingwara ya Ebola muri RD Congo 'ntirakwiragira hose'
Ubwo bushakashatsi bwerekana ko iryo geragezwa rishobora gufasha mu kurokora ubuzima bw'abantu mu gihe Ebola izoba iteye mu misi iri imbere.
Ingwara ya Ebola yahitanye abantu barenga 11.000 mu bihugu vya Liberia, Sierra Leone na Guinee, igihe yaterayo hagati y'imyaka ya 2014-2015.
