<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-48793845' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-48793845' term='ebola'>
U Rwanda rurifuza miliyoni 12 z'amadolari y'Amerika yo gukumira Ebola mu mezi 6
Kuri uyu mugoroba wo ku wa kane, minisiteri y'ubuzima mu Rwanda yabwiye abaterankunga ko ikeneye miliyoni 12 z'amadolari y'Amerika mu mezi atandatu ngo ikomeze gukumirira  Ebola ivugwa muri Kongo.
Kuri uyu mugoroba wo ku wa kane, minisiteri y'ubuzima mu Rwanda yabwiye abaterankunga ko ikeneye miliyoni 12 z'amadolari y'Amerika mu mezi atandatu ngo ikomeze gukumirira  Ebola ivugwa muri Kongo.
Ebola imaze igihe ivugwa muri Kongo Kinshasa aho imaze guhitana abantu barenga 1,500 kuva mu kwezi kwa munani umwaka ushize. Muri uku kwezi yageze no muri Uganda aho yahitanye abantu babiri.
Minisiteri y'ubuzima mu Rwanda yamurikiye iyi ngengo y'imari ibigo mpuzamahanga n'imiryango nterankunga ndetse n'ishami  ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima, OMS.
Iri shami rivuga ko u Rwanda rugomba gukomeza kwirinda no kwitegura igihe cyose Ebola yaba igeze mu gihugu kuko iri mu gihugu gituranyi, nkuko umunyamakuru wa BBC Jean Claude Mwambutsa uri i Kigali abivuga.
Umunyamabanga wa Leta muri minisiteri y'ubuzima yavuze ko ayo mafaranga yose ari ayo gukoresha mu gihe cy'amezi atandatu asigaye ngo uyu mwaka urangire.
Aya ngo naboneka azajya mu bikorwa by'ubukangurambaga mu turere 15 tw'igihugu twugarijwe no kugerwamo na Ebola, gupima iyi ndwara ahahurira abantu benshi, no kurinda abavura Ebola.
Dr Patrick Ndimubanzi, umunyamabanga wa Leta ushinzwe ubuzima rusange n'ubuvuzi bw'ibanze muri minisiteri y'ubuzima, avuga ko iyi ndwara itaragera mu Rwanda ariko kwirinda bisaba ubushobozi.
Abajijwe niba ingano y'amafaranga u Rwanda rwifuza itagaragaza ko hari ubwoba budasanzwe ko Ebola yagera no mu Rwanda, Dr Ndimubanzi yavuze ko bidateye ubwoba.
Ati: "Kwitegura byose bisaba amafaranga. Tugomba kwitegura, tukagenda tubishyira mu bikorwa uko ubushobozi bubonetse".
Abaterankunga batumijwe ntibavuze inkunga bemeye muri iyi nama.
Ikigo cy'Ubwongereza gishinzwe iterambere mpuzamahanga, DFID, ni cyo gusa  cyatangaje ko cyemeye kurekura miliyoni imwe y'amadolari.
Aya ariyongera kuri miliyoni 2,6 z'amadolari Ubwongereza bwari bwaremeye gutanga, yose hamwe abe miliyoni 3,6 z'amadolari agenewe gukumira no kwitegura Ebola.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-48605833' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-48605833' term='ebola'>
Umwana w'umuhungu wo muri Uganda yatangajwe ko yanduye Ebola
Ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS) ryemeje ko umwana w'umuhungu w'imyaka itanu y'amavuko w'i Kasese mu burengerazuba bwa Uganda yanduye indwara ya Ebola.
Ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS) ryemeje ko umwana w'umuhungu w'imyaka itanu y'amavuko w'i Kasese mu burengerazuba bwa Uganda yanduye indwara ya Ebola.
Uyu ni we muntu wa mbere wemejwe ko yanduye Ebola muri iki gihugu, mu gihe mu gihugu gituranyi cya Repubulika ya Demokarasi ya Kongo imaze guhitana abantu hafi 1400 kuva mu kwezi kwa munani umwaka ushize.
Abantu barenga 2000 bamaze gutangazwa ko banduye Ebola muri Kongo mu mezi 10 ashize ihadutse.
Bivugwa ko uwo mwana w'umuhungu wo muri Uganda yari yambutse umupaka ku cyumweru ava muri Kongo ari kumwe n'abo mu muryango we.
Abategetsi bavuga ko yahise ajyanwa mu bitaro muri Uganda nyuma yaho yari yagaragaje ibimenyetso birimo kuruka amaraso.
Nyuma ku munsi w'ejo ku wa kabiri, ikigo cya Uganda gipima za virusi cyemeza ko koko uwo mwana w'umuhungu yanduye Ebola, mbere yuko biza gutangazwa n'abategetsi.
Itangazo rihuriweho ryasohowe na minisiteri y'ubuzima muri Uganda ndetse OMS, rivuga ko impande zombi zohereje itsinda ry'ubutabazi bwihuse ngo ritahure abandi bafite ibyago byo kwandura Ebola.
Mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru ejo ku wa kabiri, Minisitiri w'ubuzima wa Uganda, Dr. Jane Ruth Aceng, yavuze ko abo mu muryango w'uwo mwana bari gukurikiranwa, barimo na babiri bagaragaza ibimenyetso bijya gusa n'ibya Ebola.
Nyuma yaho, yatangaje ubutumwa ku rubuga nkoranyambaga rwa Twitter avuga ko ubu iki gihugu cyagiye "mu bihe bidasanzwe" kubera iyi ndwara.
Iryo tangazo rya minisiteri y'ubuzima ya Uganda na OMS ryongeraho ko Uganda isanzwe yarakingiye Ebola abakora mu bikorwa by'ubuvuzi bagera hafi ku 4700.
</doc>
