<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-48525622' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-48525622' term='ebola'>
Abantu barenga 2000 bamaze kumenyekana ko banduye Ebola muri Kongo
Abategetsi muri Repubulika ya Demokarasi ya Kongo bavuga ko abantu barenga 2000 bamaze kwandura indwara ya Ebola mu mezi 10 ashize.
Abategetsi muri Repubulika ya Demokarasi ya Kongo bavuga ko abantu barenga 2000 bamaze kwandura indwara ya Ebola mu mezi 10 ashize.
Minisiteri y'ubuzima muri Kongo yongeyeho ko bibiri bya gatatu byabo - ni ukuvuga abarenga 1300 - yabahitanye.
Iyi ndwara ya Ebola mu burasirazuba bwa Kongo ni iya kabiri mu mateka yibasiye abantu benshi, mu byumweru bishize bya vuba ikaba ari bwo yiyongereye.
Ariko ibikorwa by'abaganga byo kugerageza kuyihagarika, byakomwe mu nkokora nuko aba baganga ahanini batizerwa n'abaturage ndetse n'umutekano mucye muri aka karere.
Nubwo abarenga 1300 bamaze kwicwa na Ebola kuva yakongera kwaduka muri iki gihugu, umuryango mpuzamahanga ufasha wa Oxfam uvuga ko buri munsi abakozi bawo bahura n'abaturage na n'ubu batemera ko Ebola ibaho, nkuko umunyamakuru wa BBC Will Ross abivuga.
Abandi bo ntibizera abaganga, bigatuma abantu bafite ibimenyetso bya Ebola batabona ubuvuzi, bityo bikarushaho gukomera guhagarika gukwirakwira kwayo.
Kugeza ubu, imaze guhagarikwa mu ntara ebyiri, ariko kugenzura uko ikomeza gukwirakwira bikomeje kurushaho kugorana kubera umutekano mucye uri mu karere k'uburasirazuba bw'iki gihugu.
Hagati y'ukwezi kwa mbere n'ukwa gatanu uyu mwaka, habaye ibitero birenga 40 ku bigo nderabuzima. Ariko mu byumweru bicye bishize, ibikorwa by'urugomo byaragabanutse.
Ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima, OMS, ryatangaje ko ibyago byuko iyi Ebola yakwira ahandi ku isi biri hasi, ariko ko bishoboka cyane ko yakwadukira n'ibihugu bituranye na Kongo.
Kenshi Ebola iyo yadutse ihita irangira vuba kandi ikibasira abantu bacye. Mbere y'iyi yadutse muri Kongo, inshuro imwe gusa ni bwo Ebola yamaze amezi arenga umunani. Icyo gihe hari mu burengerazuba bw'Afurika, hagati y'umwaka wa 2013 na 2016, aho yahitanye abantu 11310.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_49102151' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/49102151' term='ebola'>
Musa Bility yahagaritswe na FIFA imyaka 10 acibwa n'amande

FIFA yahagaritse umuyobozi nshingwabikorwa wa CAF, imurega amakosa arimwo gukoresha nabi amafranga n'igihagararo ciwe mw'ishirahamwe.
Umuyobozi nshingwabikorwa w'urunani rw'amashirahamwe y'umupira w'amaguru muri Afrika -CAF yahagaritswe imyaka icumi acibwa amande y'ama dorari ibihumbi amajana atanu ($500,000) n'ishirahamwe ry'umupira w'amaguru kw'isi FIFA.
Musa Bility yahanywe kubera kurenga ku mategeko no kugira inyifato idahuye n'akarangamutima urwego abereye umuyobozi rugenderako.
FIFA yasanze uwo yahoze ari umukuru w'ishirahamwe ry'umupira w'amaguru muri Liberia, ", mu maakosa yakoze harimwo kwigarurira amafranga avuye mu kigega ca FIFA, kwikwegerako inyungu no gukoresha abo bafitanye ubucuti bwa hafi, ku buryo bushobora kubangamira akazi".
Kuva mu mwaka wa 2018, FIFA imenyesha ko yakoze amatohoza kuri uwo mugabo w'imyaka 52, igihe yari amaze gukorerwa isuzuma  n'ishirahamwe ry'umupira w'amaguru ry'igihugu ciwe -LFA, kw'ikoreshwa ry'amafranga.
Amafranga aregwa kwigarurira yavuye ku yari yagenewe isekeza ryo kurwanya Ebola " 11 against Ebola" hamwe n'igice c'amafranga y'umugambi wo kurishigikira.
Liberia ni kimwe mu bihugu bitatu vyo muri Afrika vyahuye n'ikiza ca Ebola hagati y'imyaka ya 2013 na 2016, aho abantu barenga ibihumbi icumi bahasize ubuzima.
Mw'itangazo ryayo, FIFA yavuze ko hari n'ayandi mafranga yarishwe mu mice kwinshi n'ishirahamwe LFA, yagiye mu bigo vyegukira bwana Bility canke bifise aho bihuriye nawe canke umuryango wiwe.
Igihano ciwe gitangurana n'uyu wa gatatu nk'uko iryo tangazo ribivuga.
Iki gihano ca bwana Bility, kije mu gihe yaheruka kurega FIFA na CAF muri sentare ijejwe gutatura amatita afatiye ku nkino.
Avuga ko atanezerejwe n'ico yise "amasezerano yo gukorana" hagati ya CAF na FIFA, agashaka ko "aseswa ata kindi kirinze gusabwa".
Muri aya masezerano mashasha, umunyamabanga mukuru wa FIFA Fatma Samoura, azokorana na CAF nk'intumwa nkuru ya Afrika.
Uwo munya Senegalekazi  akazotangura mu mabanga yiwe kw'itariki ya mbere y'ukwezi kuza.
Mu nama y'abayobozi nshingwabikorwa ba CAF iheruka i Cairo mu ndwi iheze, Bility niwe wenyene atemeye uwo mugambi.
Yemeza ko uteye kubiri n'amategeko ya CAF hamwe n'aya FIFA.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-44936472' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='http://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-44936472' term='ebola'>
Ebola: Ingene ingwara ruhonyanganda yagaritswe
Umwe mu migera yica cane kw'isi, Ebola warahitanye igice c'abawanduye. Ariko n'aho yaboneka nk'ingara y'icaduka, iyiherutse yaje mu bundi buryo bwihariye.
Umwe mu migera yica cane kw'isi, Ebola warahitanye igice c'abawanduye. Ariko n'aho yaboneka nk'ingara y'icaduka, iyiherutse yaje mu bundi buryo bwihariye.
Bwari bubaye ubugira icenda Ebola yaduka mu gihugu ca RD Congo mu myaka cumi., ihitana abantu 29 isiga abana b'impfvyi 60.
Mu gihe hapfuye umuntu umwe gusa,  baba ari abantu benshi ku rundi ruhande, iyo ngwara yahitanye abantu 11.000 mu burengero bwa Afrika, bikaba vyitezwe ko mu mpera z'iyi ndwi ishami rya Onu rijejwe amagara y'abantu OMS rizomenyesha ku mugaragaro ko iyo ngwara yaranduranywe n'imizi.
Ico gitigiri gisa n'igisanzwe c'abahitanywe n'iyo ngwara cakurikiwe n'ikoreshwa ry'urucanco rwariko rurageragezwa, rushobora kuba rwararokowe abantu amajana n'amajana eka mbere nkeka ibihumbi n'ibihumbi.
Igisata c'amagara y'abantu kigoyagoya
N'aho uwo mugera wadutse mu karere ka kure cane, hari ubwoba ko igitigiri kinini c'abantu gishobora kwandukirwa.
Uwo mugera wadutse hagufi y'igihugu ca Centrafrique na RD Congo - akarere kanini cane kagwiriyemwo abantu ariko igisata c'amagara y'abantu kitifashe neza. N'akarere kandi kegereye imihora yo mu mazi n'amabarabara agana i Kinshasa ku mugwa mukuru - haba abantu imiliyoni cumi.
Urwo rucanco rwakoreshejwe ruzwi kw'izina rya rVSV-ZEBOV rwari rugikorwa igihe uwo mugera waduka mu 2014-2016. Ariko ubu vyaragaragaye ko rushobora gukora.
Igihe uwo mugera wasubira kwaduka mu 2018, wari gushobora gukwiragira n'ingoga, ariko reta ya Congo yaciye yemera ko rugeragerezwa ku bantu. Urwo rucanco rwagenewe gukoreshwa kuri Ebola yo muri Zaire.
Abahinga n'abakozi muvyo amagara y'abantu barakwiragijwe kugira bakurikirana abandukiwe bose kuva hakiboneka umuntu wa mbere yanduye.
Abakozi bo mu magara y'abantu bari muri ako karere, abegereye abamaze kwandura hamwe n'abo bamaze kubonana bose bakeneye guhabwa urwo rucanco.
Ariko kubika neza urwo rucanco n'ukugira uko ushoboye ngo rushikire abo rugenewe n'akandi kazi katoroshe.
Urwo rucanco rutegerezwa kubikwa mu kibanza gikanye cane, muri -70C.
Ibi rero birazimvye kandi biragoye mu karere kari kure cane y'igisagara hadashika umuyagankuba. Uretse urwo rucanco, hakenewe ibintu bikanyisha n'imashini itanga umuyagankuba bizanwa na kajugujugu.
Ikibanza cihariye hamwe n'aho kubavurira bikenewe kubakwa, ikibanza co gupimiramwo hamwe n'abahinga bo gupima bategerzwa kwigishwa kugira baze baremeza abamaze kwandura Ebola.
Kugira urwo rucanco rukore neza, rutegerezwa guhabwa abarukwiye vy'ukuri.
Abakozi muvyo amagara y'abantu baravuganye n'abagwayi, imiryango yabo hamwe  n'abantu bose kugira ntihabe ibihuha, habe uwkizerana no kwigizayo ubwoba.
Ibi babisigurira abarongoye abandi, ntiryari isekeza rigenewe bose.
Urucanco rwahabwa abagwaye Ebola, abagenzi, incuti hamwe n;abo babonanye - co kimwe n'abashinzwe amagara y'abantu hamwe n'abafasha mu gikorwa co guhamba abapfuye. Bose bategerezwa kuvyiyemerera.
Kumenya no gutoa abantu bose bashobora kuba barabonanye n'umugwayi wa Ebola cari igikorwa kitoroshe kubera aho baba.
Abashinzwe amagara y'abantu bategerezwa kugenda n'udupikipiki mu turere turangwamwo amabarabara mabi.
N'aho hari izo ngorane, abantu benshi barabonetse, abashika ibice 98% mu bashoboye kumenyekana bararonse urucanco.
</doc>
