Minisitiri w'ubuzima yatangaje ko Ebola yarangiye muri DRC
Repubulika Iharanira Demokarsi ya Congo yatangaje ko icyorezo cya Ebola cyarangiye.
Repubulika Iharanira Demokarsi ya Congo yatangaje ko icyorezo cya Ebola cyarangiye.
Minisitiri w'ubuzima, Oly Ilunga Kalenga, yatangaje ko iminsi 42 ikenewe yarangiye nta bundi bwandu bugaragaye.
Dr Kalenga yavuze ko icyorezo cy'ingwara ya Ebola cyamaze amezi abiri mu gihugu cyishe abantubane ku munani bayanduye.
