<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-48206956' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-48206956' term='ebola'>
Abantu 12 baguye mu mirwanyo ya FARDC na Mayi Mayi i Butembo muri Kongo
Mu mugi wa Butembo uri mu burasirazuba bwa Repubulika ya Demokarasi ya Kongo habaye imirwanyo yashyamiranyije inyashyamba za Mayi Mayi n'ingabo za Leta (FARDC) 12 barapfa.
Mu mugi wa Butembo uri mu burasirazuba bwa Repubulika ya Demokarasi ya Kongo habaye imirwanyo yashyamiranyije inyashyamba za Mayi Mayi n'ingabo za Leta (FARDC) 12 barapfa.
Uyu mugi wa Butembo utuwe n'abantu bagera kuri miliyoni imwe, uri mu Ntara ya Kivu y'amajyaruguru, umaze iminsi ishegeshwe n'icyorezo cya Ebola cyahitanye abarenga 1000.
Kubera imirwano yabaye mu gitondo cyo kuri uyu wa gatatu imirimo y'amatsinda y'abavuzi barwanya iki cyorezo yahagaritswe.
Abaturage ba hano bavuga ko imirwano muri aka gace yatangiye saa kumi n'imwe z'igitondo ikamara igihe kigera ku isaha imwe.
Sylvain Kanyamanda umuyobozi w'umugi wa Butembo yatangaje ko umuntu umwe ku ruhande rw'ingabo za Leta ari we wapfuye.
Uruhande rw'ingabo za Leta rwemeza ko aba Mayi-Mayi 11 ari bo bishwe mu bari bateye umugi wa Butembo bagasubizwa inyuma.
Nyuma y'iyi mirwano, abantu benshi mu mugi wa Butembo bahisemo kuguma mu ngo zabo uyu munsi nk'uko umunyamakuru wigenga uriyo yabibwiye BBC.
Muri uyu mugi wibasiwe na Ebola, abarwanyi bitwaje intwaro nabo bibasiye ibigo bifasha abarwaye iyi ndwara, mu byumweru bibiri bishize umuganga ukomoka muri Kameruni waje mu butumwa bwa OMS/WHO kurwanya Ebola yarishwe.
Nta kiragaraza ko igitero cya none cy'aba Mayi-Mayi cyari kigambiriye ikigo gifasha abarwaye Ebola nk'uko umuyobozi w'umugi wa Butembo abivuga.
Kugeza ubu Minisiteri y'ubuzima muri Kongo yabujije abaganga b'inzobere kujya kurwanya Ebola muri Butembo.
Kuva iki cyorezo cyakwaduka kimaze guhitana abantu barenga 1000 mu ntara ya Kivu ya ruguru na Ituri.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-49350805' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-49350805' term='ebola'>
Icyorezo Ebola: Mu Burundi batangiye gukingira ‘abahangana nayo’
Ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima,OMS, ryatangaje ko mu Burundi abakozi mu by'ubuzima n'ababafasha ku mipaka batangiye guhabwa urukingo rwa Ebola.
Ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima,OMS, ryatangaje ko mu Burundi abakozi mu by'ubuzima n'ababafasha ku mipaka batangiye guhabwa urukingo rwa Ebola.
Mu ntangiriro z'iki cyumweru inkingo za Ebola zagejejwe mu Burundi.
Abakozi bo ku mupaka wa Gatumba - hafi ya Repubulika ya Demokarasi ya Congo aho Ebola imaze guhitana abantu barenga 1,800 mu gihe cy'umwaka - nibo bahereweho bahabwa urukingo.
Aba bakozi mu by'ubuzima n'abandi bo ku mupaka bari guterwa urukingo rwa rVSV-ZEBOV rukiri mu igeragezwa. Biteganyijwe ko abagera ku 4,300 ari bo bazakingirwa.
Mu itangazo ryayo, OMS ivuga ko "nubwo uru rukingo rukiri mu igeragezwa kandi rutemerewe no kugurishwa, rwagaragaje ko rukora neza kandi rwarinze abantu kwandura Ebola muri Afurika y'iburengerazuba".
Uru rukingo rwakozwe n'ikigo gikora imiti cyo muri Amerika kitwa Merck, rwageragejwe bwa mbere muri Guinea mu 2015 nk'uko bivugwa n'uhagarariye OMS mu Burundi Dr Kazadi Mulombo.
Agira ati: "Gukingira abakozi mu buzima n'abandi bari guhangana na Ebola ni intambwe ikomeye mu kwitegura gukumira iki cyorezo".
Kugeza ubu indwara ya Ebola ntabwo iragera mu Burundi, gusa kuba iki gihugu gihana imbibi na Congo - ahavugwa iyi ndwara - bishyira aka gace mu kaga ko kuba yahagera.
Mu cyumweru gishize Uganda nayo yatangiye igerageza ry'urukingo rwa kabiri rwa Ebola rwakozwe n'indi kompanyi ikora imiti yo muri Amerika.
Muri iki cyumweru kandi abahanga batangaje ko imiti ibiri ya Ebola imaze iminsi mu igerageza muri Congo ivura abarwayi bayo ku kigero cya 90%.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_amakuru-46423992' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-46423992' term='ebola'>
OMS itangaza ko indwara ya Ebola muri Kongo ari 'iya kabiri ikaze cyane ibayeho mu mateka'
Ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima, OMS, ritangaza ko indwara ya Ebola mu burasirazuba bwa Repubulika ya Demokarasi ya Kongo ubu ari yo Ebola ya kabiri ikaze cyane ibayeho mu mateka y'isi.
Ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima, OMS, ritangaza ko indwara ya Ebola mu burasirazuba bwa Repubulika ya Demokarasi ya Kongo ubu ari yo Ebola ya kabiri ikaze cyane ibayeho mu mateka y'isi.
Mu mujyi wa Beni no mu nkengero zawo, abantu 379 byamaze kwemezwa ko bayirwaye mu gihe 47 bacyekwa kuyirwara - bituma iyi ndwara irenga mu bukana kuri Ebola yadutse muri Uganda mu mwaka wa 2000.
Umujyi wa Beni uri rwagati mu gace k'imirwano, ndetse ibikorwa by'ubutabazi byagiye bikomwa mu nkokora n'ibitero by'inyeshyamba.
Imibare itangwa na OMS na leta ya Kongo ivuga ko iyi ndwara ya Ebola imaze guhitana abarenga 200 naho 126 bakaba bamaze kuyikira.
Ariko iracyari ku kigero cyo hasi uyigereranyije n'icyorezo cya Ebola cyibasiye ibihugu bimwe byo mu burengerazuba bw'Afurika guhera mu mwaka wa 2013 kugera mu wa 2016, kigahitana abantu ibihumbi 11 na 310.
Ni ubwa kabiri Ebola igaragaye muri Kongo muri uyu mwaka wa 2018. Ubwa mbere, ubwo yadukaga mu burengerazuba bw'igihugu, yahitanye abantu 33, nkuko bitangazwa na leta ya Kongo.
Peter Salama, umuyobozi mukuru wungirije wa OMS ushinzwe ibikorwa by'ubutabazi bwihuse, ku wa kane yatangaje ubutumwa ku rubuga nkoranyambaga rwa Twitter agira ati:
"Ebola yo muri Kongo ubu ni yo ya kabiri ikaze cyane ibayeho mu mateka... OMS n'abafatanyabikorwa tuzakomeza gukorana bya hafi na minisiteri y'ubuzima muri Kongo dukora ibishoboka byose ngo iyi ndwara icike".
Iyi ndwara ya Ebola muri Kongo yatangiye mu kwezi kwa karindwi, ikaba ari ku nshuro ya 10 igaragaye muri Kongo kuva yahagaragara bwa mbere mu mwaka wa 1976.
Abakora mu bikorwa by'ubuzima bizeye ko uburyo bw'igerageza bwa mbere bukomatanya imiti ivura Ebola bwatangijwe na minisiteri y'ubuzima ya Kongo ku wa mbere w'icyumweru gishize, buzafasha mu guhashya iyi Ebola ndetse n'izindi zishobora kwaduka mu gihe kiri imbere.
Umutekano mucye urangwa mu burasirasuba bwa Kongo wagize ingaruka ku bikorwa by'ubutabazi ku ndwara ya Ebola.
Igitero cy'inyeshyamba cyabaye mu kwezi kwa cyenda, cyatumye icyo gihe abakora mu bikorwa by'ubuzima baba bahagaritse gukingira no gushakisha abantu bashobora kuba baragize aho bahurira n'abacyekwa kuba abarwayi ba Ebola.
</doc>
<doc docid='bbc_140810_ebola5' lang='kin' type='mono' source_url='http://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru/2014/08/140810_ebola5' term='ebola'>
Inzego z'ubuvuzi za Liberia zarengewe na Ebola
MSF iravuga ko minisiteri y'ubuvuzi muri Liberia yarengewe kubera indwara ya Ebola ivugwa muri icyo gihugu.
MSF iravuga ko minisiteri y'ubuvuzi muri Liberia yarengewe kubera indwara ya Ebola ivugwa muri icyo gihugu.
Umuryango utanga imfashanyo ku bari mu kaga, MSF (Medecins Sans Frontieres), uravuga ko minisiteri y'ubuvuzi muri Liberia yarengewe kubera indwara ya Ebola.
Umushingwabikorwa wawo, Lindis Hurum, yavuze ko iyo minisiteri yirengagije ubukana bw'iyi ndwara.
Ku wa gatandatu, igipolisi gihosha imvururu cyatatanyije imyigaragambyo yamaganaga ukuntu leta yitwaye muri iki kibazo.
Igihugu cya Espagne cyatangaje ko umupadiri wanduriye Ebola muri Liberia agiye kuvurirwa mu bitaro by'i Madrid hakoreshejwe umuti urimo kugeragezwa witwa Zmapp.
Uwo muti wakoreshejwe muri Leta zunze ubumwe z'amerika ku bakozi b'abanyamerika babiri batanga imfashanyo bayanduye maze batangira kworoherwa.
Abantu bagera hafi ku 1000 nibo bamaze guhitanwa na Ebola muri Afurika y'uburengerazuba.
