Abategetsi bo muri Nigeria batangiye gushyira mu bikorwa ingamba nshya zo gukumira Ebola ngo idasakara mu gihugu.
Ibi birakorwa nyuma y'umunsi umwe Perezida Goodluck Jonathan w'icyo gihugu atangaje ko igihugu kiri mu bihe bidasanzwe.
Muri izo ngamba nshya harimo gushyiraho ibigo byo gushyiramo abarwayi bahawe akato n'igikorwa cyo kugeza ku baturage amakuru arebana n'iyo ndwara.
Muri Nigeria habonetse abantu bake cyane banduye indwara ya Ebola.
Abategetsi ariko barashaka gukora uko bashoboye ngo ibintu bitabarenga nkuko bimeze muri Liberia na Sierra Leone aho abakozi bashinzwe ubuzima bibagoye cyane guhangana nayo.
